41 
42 CEulerSolver::CEulerSolver(CGeometry *geometry, CConfig *config,
43  unsigned short iMesh, const bool navier_stokes) :
44  CFVMFlowSolverBase<CEulerVariable, ENUM_REGIME::COMPRESSIBLE>(*geometry, *config) {
45 
46  /*--- Based on the navier_stokes boolean, determine if this constructor is
47  * being called by itself, or by its derived class CNSSolver. ---*/
48  string description;
49  unsigned short nSecVar;
50  if (navier_stokes) {
51  description = "Navier-Stokes";
52  nSecVar = 8;
53  }
54  else {
55  description = "Euler";
56  nSecVar = 2;
57  }
58 
59  const auto nZone = geometry->GetnZone();
60  const bool restart = (config->GetRestart() || config->GetRestart_Flow());
61  const bool rans = (config->GetKind_Turb_Model() != TURB_MODEL::NONE);
62  const auto direct_diff = config->GetDirectDiff();
63  const bool dual_time = (config->GetTime_Marching() == TIME_MARCHING::DT_STEPPING_1ST) ||
64  (config->GetTime_Marching() == TIME_MARCHING::DT_STEPPING_2ND);
65  const bool time_stepping = (config->GetTime_Marching() == TIME_MARCHING::TIME_STEPPING);
66  const bool adjoint = config->GetContinuous_Adjoint() || config->GetDiscrete_Adjoint();
67 
68  int Unst_RestartIter = 0;
69  unsigned long iPoint, iMarker, counter_local = 0, counter_global = 0;
70  unsigned short iDim;
71  su2double StaticEnergy, Density, Velocity2, Pressure, Temperature;
72 
73  /*--- A grid is defined as dynamic if there's rigid grid movement or grid deformation AND the problem is time domain ---*/
74  dynamic_grid = config->GetDynamic_Grid();
75 
76  /*--- Store the multigrid level. ---*/
77  MGLevel = iMesh;
78 
79  /*--- Check for a restart file to evaluate if there is a change in the angle of attack
80  before computing all the non-dimesional quantities. ---*/
81 
82  if (restart && (iMesh == MESH_0) && nZone <= 1 && config->GetFixed_CL_Mode()) {
83 
84  /*--- Modify file name for a dual-time unsteady restart ---*/
85 
86  if (dual_time) {
87  if (adjoint) Unst_RestartIter = SU2_TYPE::Int(config->GetUnst_AdjointIter())-1;
88  else if (config->GetTime_Marching() == TIME_MARCHING::DT_STEPPING_1ST)
89  Unst_RestartIter = SU2_TYPE::Int(config->GetRestart_Iter())-1;
90  else Unst_RestartIter = SU2_TYPE::Int(config->GetRestart_Iter())-2;
91  }
92 
93  /*--- Modify file name for a time stepping unsteady restart ---*/
94 
95  if (time_stepping) {
96  if (adjoint) Unst_RestartIter = SU2_TYPE::Int(config->GetUnst_AdjointIter())-1;
97  else Unst_RestartIter = SU2_TYPE::Int(config->GetRestart_Iter())-1;
98  }
99 
100  /*--- Read and store the restart metadata. ---*/
101 
102  string filename_ = "flow";
103  filename_ = config->GetFilename(filename_, ".meta", Unst_RestartIter);
104  Read_SU2_Restart_Metadata(geometry, config, adjoint, filename_);
105 
106  }
107 
108  /*--- Set the gamma value ---*/
109 
110  Gamma = config->GetGamma();
111  Gamma_Minus_One = Gamma - 1.0;
112 
113  /*--- Define geometry constants in the solver structure
114  Compressible flow, primitive variables (T, vx, vy, vz, P, rho, h, c, lamMu, EddyMu, ThCond, Cp).
115  ---*/
116 
117  nDim = geometry->GetnDim();
118 
119  nVar = nDim+2;
120  nPrimVar = nDim+9; nPrimVarGrad = nDim+4;
121  nSecondaryVar = nSecVar; nSecondaryVarGrad = 2;
122 
123  /*--- Initialize nVarGrad for deallocation ---*/
124 
125  nVarGrad = nPrimVarGrad;
126 
127  nMarker = config->GetnMarker_All();
128  nPoint = geometry->GetnPoint();
129  nPointDomain = geometry->GetnPointDomain();
130 
131  /*--- Store the number of vertices on each marker for deallocation later ---*/
132 
133  nVertex.resize(nMarker);
134  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < nMarker; iMarker++)
135  nVertex[iMarker] = geometry->nVertex[iMarker];
136 
137  /*--- Perform the non-dimensionalization for the flow equations using the
138  specified reference values. ---*/
139 
140  SetNondimensionalization(config, iMesh);
141 
142  /*--- Check if we are executing a verification case. If so, the
143  VerificationSolution object will be instantiated for a particular
144  option from the available library of verification solutions. Note
145  that this is done after SetNondim(), as problem-specific initial
146  parameters are needed by the solution constructors. ---*/
147 
148  SetVerificationSolution(nDim, nVar, config);
149 
150  /*--- Allocate base class members. ---*/
151 
152  Allocate(*config);
153 
154  /*--- MPI + OpenMP initialization. ---*/
155 
156  HybridParallelInitialization(*config, *geometry);
157 
158  /*--- Jacobians and vector structures for implicit computations ---*/
159 
160  if (config->GetKind_TimeIntScheme_Flow() == EULER_IMPLICIT) {
161 
162  if (rank == MASTER_NODE)
163  cout << "Initialize Jacobian structure (" << description << "). MG level: " << iMesh <<"." << endl;
164 
165  Jacobian.Initialize(nPoint, nPointDomain, nVar, nVar, true, geometry, config, ReducerStrategy);
166  }
167  else {
168  if (rank == MASTER_NODE)
169  cout << "Explicit scheme. No Jacobian structure (" << description << "). MG level: " << iMesh <<"." << endl;
170  }
171 
172  /*--- Store the value of the primitive variables + 2 turb variables at the boundaries,
173  used for IO with a donor cell ---*/
174 
175  AllocVectorOfMatrices(nVertex, (rans? nPrimVar+2 : nPrimVar), DonorPrimVar);
176 
177  /*--- Store the value of the characteristic primitive variables index at the boundaries ---*/
178 
179  DonorGlobalIndex.resize(nMarker);
180  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < nMarker; iMarker++)
181  DonorGlobalIndex[iMarker].resize(nVertex[iMarker],0);
182 
183  /*--- Actuator Disk Radius allocation ---*/
184  ActDisk_R.resize(nMarker);
185 
186  /*--- Actuator Disk Center allocation ---*/
187  ActDisk_C.resize(nMarker, MAXNDIM);
188 
189  /*--- Actuator Disk Axis allocation ---*/
190  ActDisk_Axis.resize(nMarker, MAXNDIM);
191 
192  /*--- Actuator Disk Fa, Fx, Fy and Fz allocations ---*/
193  AllocVectorOfVectors(nVertex, ActDisk_Fa);
194  AllocVectorOfVectors(nVertex, ActDisk_Fx);
195  AllocVectorOfVectors(nVertex, ActDisk_Fy);
196  AllocVectorOfVectors(nVertex, ActDisk_Fz);
197 
198  /*--- Actuator Disk BEM Fa, Fx, Fy and Fz allocations ---*/
199 
200  AllocVectorOfVectors(nVertex, ActDisk_Fa_BEM);
201  AllocVectorOfVectors(nVertex, ActDisk_Fx_BEM);
202  AllocVectorOfVectors(nVertex, ActDisk_Fy_BEM);
203  AllocVectorOfVectors(nVertex, ActDisk_Fz_BEM);
204 
205  /*--- Store the value of the Delta P at the Actuator Disk ---*/
206 
207  AllocVectorOfVectors(nVertex, ActDisk_DeltaP);
208 
209  /*--- Store the value of DeltaP_r, Thrust_r and Torque_r at the Actuator Disk for BEM ---*/
210 
211  AllocVectorOfVectors(nVertex, ActDisk_DeltaP_r);
212  AllocVectorOfVectors(nVertex, ActDisk_Thrust_r);
213  AllocVectorOfVectors(nVertex, ActDisk_Torque_r);
214 
215  /*--- Store the value of the Delta T at the Actuator Disk ---*/
216 
217  AllocVectorOfVectors(nVertex, ActDisk_DeltaT);
218 
219  /*--- Supersonic coefficients ---*/
220 
221  CEquivArea_Inv.resize(nMarker);
222 
223  /*--- Engine simulation ---*/
224 
225  Inflow_MassFlow.resize(nMarker);
226  Inflow_Pressure.resize(nMarker);
227  Inflow_Mach.resize(nMarker);
228  Inflow_Area.resize(nMarker);
229 
230  Exhaust_Temperature.resize(nMarker);
231  Exhaust_MassFlow.resize(nMarker);
232  Exhaust_Pressure.resize(nMarker);
233  Exhaust_Area.resize(nMarker);
234 
235  /*--- Turbomachinery simulation ---*/
236  AverageMassFlowRate.resize(nMarker);
237 
238  /*--- Read farfield conditions from config ---*/
239 
240  Temperature_Inf = config->GetTemperature_FreeStreamND();
241  Velocity_Inf = config->GetVelocity_FreeStreamND();
242  Pressure_Inf = config->GetPressure_FreeStreamND();
243  Density_Inf = config->GetDensity_FreeStreamND();
244  Energy_Inf = config->GetEnergy_FreeStreamND();
245  Mach_Inf = config->GetMach();
246 
247  /*--- Initialize the secondary values for direct derivative approxiations ---*/
248 
249  switch(direct_diff) {
250  case NO_DERIVATIVE:
251  /*--- Default ---*/
252  break;
253  case D_DENSITY:
254  SU2_TYPE::SetDerivative(Density_Inf, 1.0);
255  break;
256  case D_PRESSURE:
257  SU2_TYPE::SetDerivative(Pressure_Inf, 1.0);
258  break;
259  case D_TEMPERATURE:
260  SU2_TYPE::SetDerivative(Temperature_Inf, 1.0);
261  break;
262  case D_MACH: case D_AOA:
263  case D_SIDESLIP: case D_REYNOLDS:
264  case D_TURB2LAM: case D_DESIGN:
265  /*--- Already done in postprocessing of config ---*/
266  break;
267  default:
268  break;
269  }
270 
271  SetReferenceValues(*config);
272 
273  /*--- Initialize fan face pressure, fan face mach number, and mass flow rate ---*/
274 
275  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < nMarker; iMarker++) {
276  Inflow_MassFlow[iMarker] = 0.0;
277  Inflow_Mach[iMarker] = Mach_Inf;
278  Inflow_Pressure[iMarker] = Pressure_Inf;
279  Inflow_Area[iMarker] = 0.0;
280 
281  Exhaust_MassFlow[iMarker] = 0.0;
282  Exhaust_Temperature[iMarker] = Temperature_Inf;
283  Exhaust_Pressure[iMarker] = Pressure_Inf;
284  Exhaust_Area[iMarker] = 0.0;
285 
286  AverageMassFlowRate[iMarker] = 0.0;
287  }
288 
289  /*--- Initialize the solution to the far-field state everywhere. ---*/
290 
291  if (navier_stokes) {
292  nodes = new CNSVariable(Density_Inf, Velocity_Inf, Energy_Inf, nPoint, nDim, nVar, config);
293  } else {
294  nodes = new CEulerVariable(Density_Inf, Velocity_Inf, Energy_Inf, nPoint, nDim, nVar, config);
295  }
296  SetBaseClassPointerToNodes();
297 
298  if (iMesh == MESH_0) {
299  nodes->NonPhysicalEdgeCounter.resize(geometry->GetnEdge()) = 0;
300  }
301 
302  /*--- Check that the initial solution is physical, report any non-physical nodes ---*/
303 
304  counter_local = 0;
305 
306  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nPoint; iPoint++) {
307 
308  Density = nodes->GetDensity(iPoint);
309 
310  Velocity2 = 0.0;
311  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
312  Velocity2 += pow(nodes->GetSolution(iPoint,iDim+1)/Density,2);
313 
314  StaticEnergy= nodes->GetEnergy(iPoint) - 0.5*Velocity2;
315 
316  GetFluidModel()->SetTDState_rhoe(Density, StaticEnergy);
317  Pressure= GetFluidModel()->GetPressure();
318  Temperature= GetFluidModel()->GetTemperature();
319 
320  /*--- Use the values at the infinity ---*/
321 
322  su2double Solution[MAXNVAR] = {0.0};
323  if ((Pressure < 0.0) || (Density < 0.0) || (Temperature < 0.0)) {
324  Solution[0] = Density_Inf;
325  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
326  Solution[iDim+1] = Velocity_Inf[iDim]*Density_Inf;
327  Solution[nDim+1] = Energy_Inf*Density_Inf;
328  nodes->SetSolution(iPoint,Solution);
329  nodes->SetSolution_Old(iPoint,Solution);
330  counter_local++;
331  }
332 
333  }
334 
335  /*--- Warning message about non-physical points ---*/
336 
337  if (config->GetComm_Level() == COMM_FULL) {
338 
339  SU2_MPI::Reduce(&counter_local, &counter_global, 1, MPI_UNSIGNED_LONG, MPI_SUM, MASTER_NODE, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
340 
341  if ((rank == MASTER_NODE) && (counter_global != 0))
342  cout << "Warning. The original solution contains " << counter_global << " points that are not physical." << endl;
343  }
344 
345  /*--- Initial comms. ---*/
346 
347  CommunicateInitialState(geometry, config);
348 
349  /*--- Add the solver name.. ---*/
350  SolverName = "C.FLOW";
351 
352  /*--- Finally, check that the static arrays will be large enough (keep this
353  * check at the bottom to make sure we consider the "final" values). ---*/
354  if((nDim > MAXNDIM) || (nPrimVar > MAXNVAR) || (nSecondaryVar > MAXNVAR))
355  SU2_MPI::Error("Oops! The CEulerSolver static array sizes are not large enough.",CURRENT_FUNCTION);
356 }
357 
358 CEulerSolver::~CEulerSolver() {
359 
360  for(auto& model : FluidModel) delete model;
361 }
362 
363 void CEulerSolver::InstantiateEdgeNumerics(const CSolver* const* solver_container, const CConfig* config) {
364 
365  BEGIN_SU2_OMP_SAFE_GLOBAL_ACCESS
366  {
367 
368  if (config->Low_Mach_Correction())
369  SU2_MPI::Error("Low-Mach correction is not supported with vectorization.", CURRENT_FUNCTION);
370 
371  if (solver_container[TURB_SOL])
372  edgeNumerics = CNumericsSIMD::CreateNumerics(*config, nDim, MGLevel, solver_container[TURB_SOL]->GetNodes());
373  else
374  edgeNumerics = CNumericsSIMD::CreateNumerics(*config, nDim, MGLevel);
375 
376  if (!edgeNumerics)
377  SU2_MPI::Error("The numerical scheme + gas model in use do not "
378  "support vectorization.", CURRENT_FUNCTION);
379 
380  }
381  END_SU2_OMP_SAFE_GLOBAL_ACCESS
382 }
383 
384 void CEulerSolver::InitTurboContainers(CGeometry *geometry, CConfig *config){
385 
386  /*--- Initialize quantities for the average process for internal flow ---*/
387 
388  const auto nSpanWiseSections = config->GetnSpanWiseSections();
389 
390  AverageVelocity.resize(nMarker);
391  AverageTurboVelocity.resize(nMarker);
392  OldAverageTurboVelocity.resize(nMarker);
393  ExtAverageTurboVelocity.resize(nMarker);
394  AverageFlux.resize(nMarker);
395  SpanTotalFlux.resize(nMarker);
396  AveragePressure.resize(nMarker,nSpanWiseSections+1) = su2double(0.0);
397  OldAveragePressure = AveragePressure;
398  RadialEquilibriumPressure = AveragePressure;
399  ExtAveragePressure = AveragePressure;
400  AverageDensity = AveragePressure;
401  OldAverageDensity = AveragePressure;
402  ExtAverageDensity = AveragePressure;
403  AverageNu = AveragePressure;
404  AverageKine = AveragePressure;
405  AverageOmega = AveragePressure;
406  ExtAverageNu = AveragePressure;
407  ExtAverageKine = AveragePressure;
408  ExtAverageOmega = AveragePressure;
409 
410  for (unsigned long iMarker = 0; iMarker < nMarker; iMarker++) {
411  AverageVelocity[iMarker].resize(nSpanWiseSections+1,nDim) = su2double(0.0);
412  AverageTurboVelocity[iMarker].resize(nSpanWiseSections+1,nDim) = su2double(0.0);
413  OldAverageTurboVelocity[iMarker].resize(nSpanWiseSections+1,nDim) = su2double(0.0);
414  ExtAverageTurboVelocity[iMarker].resize(nSpanWiseSections+1,nDim) = su2double(0.0);
415  AverageFlux[iMarker].resize(nSpanWiseSections+1,nVar) = su2double(0.0);
416  SpanTotalFlux[iMarker].resize(nSpanWiseSections+1,nVar) = su2double(0.0);
417  }
418 
419  /*--- Initialize primitive quantities for turboperformace ---*/
420 
421  const auto nMarkerTurboPerf = config->GetnMarker_TurboPerformance();
422  const auto nSpanMax = config->GetnSpanMaxAllZones();
423 
424  DensityIn.resize(nMarkerTurboPerf,nSpanMax+1) = su2double(0.0);
425  PressureIn = DensityIn;
426  TurboVelocityIn.resize(nMarkerTurboPerf);
427  DensityOut = DensityIn;
428  PressureOut = DensityIn;
429  TurboVelocityOut.resize(nMarkerTurboPerf);
430  KineIn = DensityIn;
431  OmegaIn = DensityIn;
432  NuIn = DensityIn;
433  KineOut = DensityIn;
434  OmegaOut = DensityIn;
435  NuOut = DensityIn;
436 
437  for (unsigned long iMarker = 0; iMarker < nMarkerTurboPerf; iMarker++) {
438  TurboVelocityIn[iMarker].resize(nSpanMax+1,nDim) = su2double(0.0);
439  TurboVelocityOut[iMarker].resize(nSpanMax+1,nDim) = su2double(0.0);
440  }
441 
442  /*--- Initialize quantities for NR BC ---*/
443 
444  if(config->GetBoolGiles()){
445 
446  CkInflow.resize(nMarker);
447  CkOutflow1.resize(nMarker);
448  CkOutflow2.resize(nMarker);
449 
450  for (unsigned long iMarker = 0; iMarker < nMarker; iMarker++) {
451  CkInflow[iMarker].resize(nSpanWiseSections,2*geometry->GetnFreqSpanMax(INFLOW)+1) = complex<su2double>(0.0,0.0);
452  CkOutflow1[iMarker].resize(nSpanWiseSections,2*geometry->GetnFreqSpanMax(OUTFLOW)+1) = complex<su2double>(0.0,0.0);
453  CkOutflow2[iMarker] = CkOutflow1[iMarker];
454  }
455  }
456 }
457 
458 void CEulerSolver::Set_MPI_ActDisk(CSolver **solver_container, CGeometry *geometry, CConfig *config) {
459 
460  unsigned long iter, iPoint, iVertex, jVertex, iPointTotal,
461  Buffer_Send_nPointTotal = 0;
462  long iGlobalIndex, iGlobal;
463  unsigned short iVar, iMarker, jMarker;
464  long nDomain = 0, iDomain, jDomain;
465  //bool ActDisk_Perimeter;
466  bool rans = (config->GetKind_Turb_Model() != TURB_MODEL::NONE) && (solver_container[TURB_SOL] != nullptr);
467 
468  unsigned short nPrimVar_ = nPrimVar;
469  if (rans) nPrimVar_ += 2; // Add two extra variables for the turbulence.
470 
471  /*--- MPI status and request arrays for non-blocking communications ---*/
472 
473  SU2_MPI::Status status;
474  SU2_MPI::Request req;
475 
476  /*--- Define buffer vector interior domain ---*/
477 
478  su2double *Buffer_Send_PrimVar = nullptr;
479  long *Buffer_Send_Data = nullptr;
480 
481  auto *nPointTotal_s = new unsigned long[size];
482  auto *nPointTotal_r = new unsigned long[size];
483  auto *iPrimVar = new su2double [nPrimVar_];
484 
485  unsigned long Buffer_Size_PrimVar = 0;
486  unsigned long Buffer_Size_Data = 0;
487 
488  unsigned long PointTotal_Counter = 0;
489 
490  /*--- Allocate the memory that we only need if we have MPI support ---*/
491 
492  su2double *Buffer_Receive_PrimVar = nullptr;
493  long *Buffer_Receive_Data = nullptr;
494 
495  /*--- Basic dimensionalization ---*/
496 
497  nDomain = size;
498 
499  /*--- This loop gets the array sizes of points for each
500  rank to send to each other rank. ---*/
501 
502  for (iDomain = 0; iDomain < nDomain; iDomain++) {
503 
504  /*--- Loop over the markers to perform the dimensionalizaton
505  of the domain variables ---*/
506 
507  Buffer_Send_nPointTotal = 0;
508 
509  /*--- Loop over all of the markers and count the number of each
510  type of point and element that needs to be sent. ---*/
511 
512  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < config->GetnMarker_All(); iMarker++) {
513  if ((config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ACTDISK_INLET) ||
514  (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ACTDISK_OUTLET)) {
515  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[iMarker]; iVertex++) {
516  //ActDisk_Perimeter = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetActDisk_Perimeter();
517  iPoint = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNode();
518  jDomain = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetDonorProcessor();
519 // if ((iDomain == jDomain) && (geometry->nodes->GetDomain(iPoint)) && (!ActDisk_Perimeter)) {
520  if ((iDomain == jDomain) && (geometry->nodes->GetDomain(iPoint))) {
521  Buffer_Send_nPointTotal++;
522  }
523  }
524  }
525  }
526 
527  /*--- Store the counts on a partition by partition basis. ---*/
528 
529  nPointTotal_s[iDomain] = Buffer_Send_nPointTotal;
530 
531  /*--- Total counts for allocating send buffers below ---*/
532 
533  Buffer_Size_PrimVar += nPointTotal_s[iDomain]*(nPrimVar_);
534  Buffer_Size_Data += nPointTotal_s[iDomain]*(3);
535 
536  }
537 
538  /*--- Allocate the buffer vectors in the appropiate domain (master, iDomain) ---*/
539 
540  Buffer_Send_PrimVar = new su2double[Buffer_Size_PrimVar];
541  Buffer_Send_Data = new long[Buffer_Size_Data];
542 
543  /*--- Now that we know the sizes of the point, we can
544  allocate and send the information in large chunks to all processors. ---*/
545 
546  for (iDomain = 0; iDomain < nDomain; iDomain++) {
547 
548  /*--- A rank does not communicate with itself through MPI ---*/
549 
550  if (rank != iDomain) {
551 
552  /*--- Communicate the counts to iDomain with non-blocking sends ---*/
553 
554  SU2_MPI::Isend(&nPointTotal_s[iDomain], 1, MPI_UNSIGNED_LONG, iDomain, iDomain, SU2_MPI::GetComm(), &req);
555  SU2_MPI::Request_free(&req);
556 
557  } else {
558 
559  /*--- If iDomain = rank, we simply copy values into place in memory ---*/
560 
561  nPointTotal_r[iDomain] = nPointTotal_s[iDomain];
562 
563  }
564 
565  /*--- Receive the counts. All processors are sending their counters to
566  iDomain up above, so only iDomain needs to perform the recv here from
567  all other ranks. ---*/
568 
569  if (rank == iDomain) {
570 
571  for (jDomain = 0; jDomain < size; jDomain++) {
572 
573  /*--- A rank does not communicate with itself through MPI ---*/
574 
575  if (rank != jDomain) {
576 
577  /*--- Recv the data by probing for the current sender, jDomain,
578  first and then receiving the values from it. ---*/
579 
580  SU2_MPI::Recv(&nPointTotal_r[jDomain], 1, MPI_UNSIGNED_LONG, jDomain, rank, SU2_MPI::GetComm(), &status);
581 
582  }
583  }
584 
585  }
586  }
587 
588  /*--- Wait for the non-blocking sends to complete. ---*/
589 
590  SU2_MPI::Barrier(SU2_MPI::GetComm());
591 
592  /*--- Initialize the counters for the larger send buffers (by domain) ---*/
593 
594  PointTotal_Counter = 0;
595 
596  for (iDomain = 0; iDomain < nDomain; iDomain++) {
597 
598  /*--- Set the value of the interior geometry. Initialize counters. ---*/
599 
600  iPointTotal = 0;
601 
602  /*--- Load up the actual values into the buffers for sending. ---*/
603 
604  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < config->GetnMarker_All(); iMarker++) {
605 
606  if ((config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ACTDISK_INLET) ||
607  (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ACTDISK_OUTLET)) {
608  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[iMarker]; iVertex++) {
609  iPoint = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNode();
610 
611  jDomain = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetDonorProcessor();
612  //ActDisk_Perimeter = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetActDisk_Perimeter();
613 
614 // if ((iDomain == jDomain) && (geometry->nodes->GetDomain(iPoint)) && (!ActDisk_Perimeter)) {
615  if ((iDomain == jDomain) && (geometry->nodes->GetDomain(iPoint))) {
616 
617  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nPrimVar; iVar++) {
618  Buffer_Send_PrimVar[(nPrimVar_)*(PointTotal_Counter+iPointTotal)+iVar] = nodes->GetPrimitive(iPoint,iVar);
619  }
620  if (rans) {
621  Buffer_Send_PrimVar[(nPrimVar_)*(PointTotal_Counter+iPointTotal)+nPrimVar] = solver_container[TURB_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetSolution(iPoint,0);
622  Buffer_Send_PrimVar[(nPrimVar_)*(PointTotal_Counter+iPointTotal)+(nPrimVar+1)] = 0.0;
623  }
624 
625  iGlobalIndex = geometry->nodes->GetGlobalIndex(iPoint);
626  jVertex = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetDonorVertex();
627  jMarker = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetDonorMarker();
628 
629  Buffer_Send_Data[(3)*(PointTotal_Counter+iPointTotal)+(0)] = iGlobalIndex;
630  Buffer_Send_Data[(3)*(PointTotal_Counter+iPointTotal)+(1)] = jVertex;
631  Buffer_Send_Data[(3)*(PointTotal_Counter+iPointTotal)+(2)] = jMarker;
632 
633  iPointTotal++;
634 
635  }
636 
637  }
638 
639  }
640 
641  }
642 
643  /*--- Send the buffers with the geometrical information ---*/
644 
645  if (iDomain != rank) {
646 
647  /*--- Communicate the coordinates, global index, colors, and element
648  date to iDomain with non-blocking sends. ---*/
649 
650  SU2_MPI::Isend(&Buffer_Send_PrimVar[PointTotal_Counter*(nPrimVar_)],
651  nPointTotal_s[iDomain]*(nPrimVar_), MPI_DOUBLE, iDomain,
652  iDomain, SU2_MPI::GetComm(), &req);
653  SU2_MPI::Request_free(&req);
654 
655  SU2_MPI::Isend(&Buffer_Send_Data[PointTotal_Counter*(3)],
656  nPointTotal_s[iDomain]*(3), MPI_LONG, iDomain,
657  iDomain+nDomain, SU2_MPI::GetComm(), &req);
658  SU2_MPI::Request_free(&req);
659  }
660 
661  else {
662 
663  /*--- Allocate local memory for the local recv of the elements ---*/
664 
665  Buffer_Receive_PrimVar = new su2double[nPointTotal_s[iDomain]*(nPrimVar_)];
666  Buffer_Receive_Data = new long[nPointTotal_s[iDomain]*(3)];
667 
668  for (iter = 0; iter < nPointTotal_s[iDomain]*(nPrimVar_); iter++)
669  Buffer_Receive_PrimVar[iter] = Buffer_Send_PrimVar[PointTotal_Counter*(nPrimVar_)+iter];
670 
671  for (iter = 0; iter < nPointTotal_s[iDomain]*(3); iter++)
672  Buffer_Receive_Data[iter] = Buffer_Send_Data[PointTotal_Counter*(3)+iter];
673 
674 
675  /*--- Recv the point data from ourselves (same procedure as above) ---*/
676 
677  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nPointTotal_r[iDomain]; iPoint++) {
678 
679  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nPrimVar_; iVar++)
680  iPrimVar[iVar] = Buffer_Receive_PrimVar[iPoint*(nPrimVar_)+iVar];
681 
682  iGlobal = Buffer_Receive_Data[iPoint*(3)+(0)];
683  iVertex = Buffer_Receive_Data[iPoint*(3)+(1)];
684  iMarker = Buffer_Receive_Data[iPoint*(3)+(2)];
685 
686  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nPrimVar_; iVar++)
687  DonorPrimVar[iMarker][iVertex][iVar] = iPrimVar[iVar];
688 
689  SetDonorGlobalIndex(iMarker, iVertex, iGlobal);
690 
691  }
692 
693  /*--- Delete memory for recv the point stuff ---*/
694 
695  delete [] Buffer_Receive_PrimVar;
696  delete [] Buffer_Receive_Data;
697 
698  }
699 
700  /*--- Increment the counters for the send buffers (iDomain loop) ---*/
701 
702  PointTotal_Counter += iPointTotal;
703 
704  }
705 
706  /*--- Wait for the non-blocking sends to complete. ---*/
707 
708  SU2_MPI::Barrier(SU2_MPI::GetComm());
709 
710  /*--- The next section begins the recv of all data for the interior
711  points/elements in the mesh. First, create the domain structures for
712  the points on this rank. First, we recv all of the point data ---*/
713 
714  for (iDomain = 0; iDomain < size; iDomain++) {
715 
716  if (rank != iDomain) {
717 
718 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
719 
720  /*--- Allocate the receive buffer vector. Send the colors so that we
721  know whether what we recv is an owned or halo node. ---*/
722 
723  Buffer_Receive_PrimVar = new su2double [nPointTotal_r[iDomain]*(nPrimVar_)];
724  Buffer_Receive_Data = new long [nPointTotal_r[iDomain]*(3)];
725 
726  /*--- Receive the buffers with the coords, global index, and colors ---*/
727 
728  SU2_MPI::Recv(Buffer_Receive_PrimVar, nPointTotal_r[iDomain]*(nPrimVar_) , MPI_DOUBLE,
729  iDomain, rank, SU2_MPI::GetComm(), &status);
730 
731  SU2_MPI::Recv(Buffer_Receive_Data, nPointTotal_r[iDomain]*(3) , MPI_LONG,
732  iDomain, rank+nDomain, SU2_MPI::GetComm(), &status);
733 
734  /*--- Loop over all of the points that we have recv'd and store the
735  coords, global index vertex and markers ---*/
736 
737  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nPointTotal_r[iDomain]; iPoint++) {
738 
739  iGlobal = Buffer_Receive_Data[iPoint*(3)+(0)];
740  iVertex = Buffer_Receive_Data[iPoint*(3)+(1)];
741  iMarker = Buffer_Receive_Data[iPoint*(3)+(2)];
742 
743  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nPrimVar_; iVar++)
744  iPrimVar[iVar] = Buffer_Receive_PrimVar[iPoint*(nPrimVar_)+iVar];
745 
746  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nPrimVar_; iVar++) {
747  DonorPrimVar[iMarker][iVertex][iVar] = iPrimVar[iVar];
748  }
749 
750  SetDonorGlobalIndex(iMarker, iVertex, iGlobal);
751 
752  }
753 
754  /*--- Delete memory for recv the point stuff ---*/
755 
756  delete [] Buffer_Receive_PrimVar;
757  delete [] Buffer_Receive_Data;
758 
759 #endif
760 
761  }
762 
763  }
764 
765  /*--- Wait for the non-blocking sends to complete. ---*/
766 
767  SU2_MPI::Barrier(SU2_MPI::GetComm());
768 
769  /*--- Free all of the memory used for communicating points and elements ---*/
770 
771  delete[] Buffer_Send_PrimVar;
772  delete[] Buffer_Send_Data;
773 
774  /*--- Release all of the temporary memory ---*/
775 
776  delete [] nPointTotal_s;
777  delete [] nPointTotal_r;
778  delete [] iPrimVar;
779 
780 }
781 
782 void CEulerSolver::SetNondimensionalization(CConfig *config, unsigned short iMesh) {
783 
784  su2double Temperature_FreeStream = 0.0, Mach2Vel_FreeStream = 0.0, ModVel_FreeStream = 0.0,
785  Energy_FreeStream = 0.0, ModVel_FreeStreamND = 0.0, Velocity_Reynolds = 0.0,
786  Omega_FreeStream = 0.0, Omega_FreeStreamND = 0.0, Viscosity_FreeStream = 0.0,
787  Density_FreeStream = 0.0, Pressure_FreeStream = 0.0, Tke_FreeStream = 0.0, Re_ThetaT_FreeStream = 0.0,
788  Length_Ref = 0.0, Density_Ref = 0.0, Pressure_Ref = 0.0, Velocity_Ref = 0.0,
789  Temperature_Ref = 0.0, Time_Ref = 0.0, Omega_Ref = 0.0, Force_Ref = 0.0,
790  Gas_Constant_Ref = 0.0, Viscosity_Ref = 0.0, Conductivity_Ref = 0.0, Energy_Ref= 0.0,
791  Froude = 0.0, Pressure_FreeStreamND = 0.0, Density_FreeStreamND = 0.0,
792  Temperature_FreeStreamND = 0.0, Gas_ConstantND = 0.0,
793  Velocity_FreeStreamND[3] = {0.0, 0.0, 0.0}, Viscosity_FreeStreamND = 0.0,
794  Tke_FreeStreamND = 0.0, Energy_FreeStreamND = 0.0,
795  Total_UnstTimeND = 0.0, Delta_UnstTimeND = 0.0, TgammaR = 0.0, Heat_Flux_Ref = 0.0;
796 
797  unsigned short iDim;
798 
799  /*--- Local variables ---*/
800 
801  su2double Alpha = config->GetAoA()*PI_NUMBER/180.0;
802  su2double Beta = config->GetAoS()*PI_NUMBER/180.0;
803  su2double Mach = config->GetMach();
804  su2double Reynolds = config->GetReynolds();
805  bool unsteady = (config->GetTime_Marching() != TIME_MARCHING::STEADY);
806  bool viscous = config->GetViscous();
807  bool gravity = config->GetGravityForce();
808  bool turbulent = (config->GetKind_Turb_Model() != TURB_MODEL::NONE);
809  bool tkeNeeded = (turbulent && config->GetKind_Turb_Model() == TURB_MODEL::SST);
810  bool free_stream_temp = (config->GetKind_FreeStreamOption() == FREESTREAM_OPTION::TEMPERATURE_FS);
811  bool reynolds_init = (config->GetKind_InitOption() == REYNOLDS);
812  bool aeroelastic = config->GetAeroelastic_Simulation();
813 
814  /*--- Set temperature via the flutter speed index ---*/
815  if (aeroelastic) {
816  su2double vf = config->GetAeroelastic_Flutter_Speed_Index();
817  su2double w_alpha = config->GetAeroelastic_Frequency_Pitch();
818  su2double b = config->GetLength_Reynolds()/2.0; // airfoil semichord, Reynolds length is by defaul 1.0
819  su2double mu = config->GetAeroelastic_Airfoil_Mass_Ratio();
820  // The temperature times gamma times the gas constant. Depending on the FluidModel temp is calculated below.
821  TgammaR = ((vf*vf)*(b*b)*(w_alpha*w_alpha)*mu) / (Mach*Mach);
822  }
823 
824  /*--- Compressible non dimensionalization ---*/
825 
826  /*--- Compute the Free Stream velocity, using the Mach number ---*/
827 
828  Pressure_FreeStream = config->GetPressure_FreeStream();
829  Density_FreeStream = config->GetDensity_FreeStream();
830  Temperature_FreeStream = config->GetTemperature_FreeStream();
831 
832  /*--- The dimensional viscosity is needed to determine the free-stream conditions.
833  To accomplish this, simply set the non-dimensional coefficients to the
834  dimensional ones. This will be overruled later.---*/
835 
836  config->SetTemperature_Ref(1.0);
837  config->SetViscosity_Ref(1.0);
838  config->SetConductivity_Ref(1.0);
839 
840  CFluidModel* auxFluidModel = nullptr;
841 
842  switch (config->GetKind_FluidModel()) {
843 
844  case STANDARD_AIR:
845 
846  switch (config->GetSystemMeasurements()) {
847  case SI: config->SetGas_Constant(287.058); break;
848  case US: config->SetGas_Constant(1716.49); break;
849  }
850 
851  auxFluidModel = new CIdealGas(1.4, config->GetGas_Constant());
852 
853  if (free_stream_temp && aeroelastic) {
854  Temperature_FreeStream = TgammaR / (config->GetGas_Constant()*1.4);
855  config->SetTemperature_FreeStream(Temperature_FreeStream);
856  }
857  break;
858 
859  case IDEAL_GAS:
860 
861  auxFluidModel = new CIdealGas(Gamma, config->GetGas_Constant());
862  break;
863 
864  case VW_GAS:
865 
866  auxFluidModel = new CVanDerWaalsGas(Gamma, config->GetGas_Constant(),
867  config->GetPressure_Critical(), config->GetTemperature_Critical());
868  break;
869 
870  case PR_GAS:
871 
872  auxFluidModel = new CPengRobinson(Gamma, config->GetGas_Constant(), config->GetPressure_Critical(),
873  config->GetTemperature_Critical(), config->GetAcentric_Factor());
874  break;
875 
876  case DATADRIVEN_FLUID:
877 
878  auxFluidModel = new CDataDrivenFluid(config);
879 
880  break;
881  case COOLPROP:
882 
883  auxFluidModel = new CCoolProp(config->GetFluid_Name());
884  break;
885 
886  default:
887  SU2_MPI::Error("Unknown fluid model.", CURRENT_FUNCTION);
888  break;
889  }
890 
891  if (free_stream_temp) {
892  auxFluidModel->SetTDState_PT(Pressure_FreeStream, Temperature_FreeStream);
893  Density_FreeStream = auxFluidModel->GetDensity();
894  config->SetDensity_FreeStream(Density_FreeStream);
895  }
896  else {
897  auxFluidModel->SetTDState_Prho(Pressure_FreeStream, Density_FreeStream );
898  Temperature_FreeStream = auxFluidModel->GetTemperature();
899  config->SetTemperature_FreeStream(Temperature_FreeStream);
900  }
901 
902  Mach2Vel_FreeStream = auxFluidModel->GetSoundSpeed();
903 
904  /*--- Compute the Free Stream velocity, using the Mach number ---*/
905 
906  if (nDim == 2) {
907  config->GetVelocity_FreeStream()[0] = cos(Alpha)*Mach*Mach2Vel_FreeStream;
908  config->GetVelocity_FreeStream()[1] = sin(Alpha)*Mach*Mach2Vel_FreeStream;
909  }
910  if (nDim == 3) {
911  config->GetVelocity_FreeStream()[0] = cos(Alpha)*cos(Beta)*Mach*Mach2Vel_FreeStream;
912  config->GetVelocity_FreeStream()[1] = sin(Beta)*Mach*Mach2Vel_FreeStream;
913  config->GetVelocity_FreeStream()[2] = sin(Alpha)*cos(Beta)*Mach*Mach2Vel_FreeStream;
914  }
915 
916  /*--- Compute the modulus of the free stream velocity ---*/
917 
918  ModVel_FreeStream = 0.0;
919  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
920  ModVel_FreeStream += config->GetVelocity_FreeStream()[iDim]*config->GetVelocity_FreeStream()[iDim];
921  ModVel_FreeStream = sqrt(ModVel_FreeStream); config->SetModVel_FreeStream(ModVel_FreeStream);
922 
923  /*--- Viscous initialization ---*/
924 
925  if (viscous) {
926 
927  /*--- Check if there is mesh motion. If yes, use the Mach
928  number relative to the body to initialize the flow. ---*/
929 
930  if (dynamic_grid) Velocity_Reynolds = config->GetMach_Motion()*Mach2Vel_FreeStream;
931  else Velocity_Reynolds = ModVel_FreeStream;
932 
933  /*--- Reynolds based initialization ---*/
934 
935  if (reynolds_init) {
936 
937  /*--- For viscous flows, pressure will be computed from a density
938  that is found from the Reynolds number. The viscosity is computed
939  from the dimensional version of Sutherland's law or the constant
940  viscosity, depending on the input option.---*/
941 
942  auxFluidModel->SetLaminarViscosityModel(config);
943 
944  Viscosity_FreeStream = auxFluidModel->GetLaminarViscosity();
945  config->SetViscosity_FreeStream(Viscosity_FreeStream);
946 
947  Density_FreeStream = Reynolds*Viscosity_FreeStream/(Velocity_Reynolds*config->GetLength_Reynolds());
948  config->SetDensity_FreeStream(Density_FreeStream);
949  auxFluidModel->SetTDState_rhoT(Density_FreeStream, Temperature_FreeStream);
950  Pressure_FreeStream = auxFluidModel->GetPressure();
951  config->SetPressure_FreeStream(Pressure_FreeStream);
952  Energy_FreeStream = auxFluidModel->GetStaticEnergy() + 0.5*ModVel_FreeStream*ModVel_FreeStream;
953 
954  }
955 
956  /*--- Thermodynamics quantities based initialization ---*/
957 
958  else {
959 
960  auxFluidModel->SetLaminarViscosityModel(config);
961  Viscosity_FreeStream = auxFluidModel->GetLaminarViscosity();
962  config->SetViscosity_FreeStream(Viscosity_FreeStream);
963  Energy_FreeStream = auxFluidModel->GetStaticEnergy() + 0.5*ModVel_FreeStream*ModVel_FreeStream;
964 
965  /*--- Compute Reynolds number ---*/
966  Reynolds = (Density_FreeStream*Velocity_Reynolds*config->GetLength_Reynolds())/Viscosity_FreeStream;
967  config->SetReynolds(Reynolds);
968  }
969 
970  /*--- Turbulence kinetic energy ---*/
971 
972  Tke_FreeStream = 3.0/2.0*(ModVel_FreeStream*ModVel_FreeStream*config->GetTurbulenceIntensity_FreeStream()*config->GetTurbulenceIntensity_FreeStream());
973 
974  }
975  else {
976 
977  /*--- For inviscid flow, energy is calculated from the specified
978  FreeStream quantities using the proper gas law. ---*/
979 
980  Energy_FreeStream = auxFluidModel->GetStaticEnergy() + 0.5*ModVel_FreeStream*ModVel_FreeStream;
981 
982  }
983 
984  /*-- Compute the freestream energy. ---*/
985 
986  if (tkeNeeded) { Energy_FreeStream += Tke_FreeStream; }; config->SetEnergy_FreeStream(Energy_FreeStream);
987 
988  /*--- Compute non dimensional quantities. By definition,
989  Lref is one because we have converted the grid to meters. ---*/
990 
991  if (config->GetRef_NonDim() == DIMENSIONAL) {
992  Pressure_Ref = 1.0;
993  Density_Ref = 1.0;
994  Temperature_Ref = 1.0;
995  }
996  else if (config->GetRef_NonDim() == FREESTREAM_PRESS_EQ_ONE) {
997  Pressure_Ref = Pressure_FreeStream; // Pressure_FreeStream = 1.0
998  Density_Ref = Density_FreeStream; // Density_FreeStream = 1.0
999  Temperature_Ref = Temperature_FreeStream; // Temperature_FreeStream = 1.0
1000  }
1001  else if (config->GetRef_NonDim() == FREESTREAM_VEL_EQ_MACH) {
1002  Pressure_Ref = Gamma*Pressure_FreeStream; // Pressure_FreeStream = 1.0/Gamma
1003  Density_Ref = Density_FreeStream; // Density_FreeStream = 1.0
1004  Temperature_Ref = Temperature_FreeStream; // Temp_FreeStream = 1.0
1005  }
1006  else if (config->GetRef_NonDim() == FREESTREAM_VEL_EQ_ONE) {
1007  Pressure_Ref = Mach*Mach*Gamma*Pressure_FreeStream; // Pressure_FreeStream = 1.0/(Gamma*(M_inf)^2)
1008  Density_Ref = Density_FreeStream; // Density_FreeStream = 1.0
1009  Temperature_Ref = Temperature_FreeStream; // Temp_FreeStream = 1.0
1010  }
1011  config->SetPressure_Ref(Pressure_Ref);
1012  config->SetDensity_Ref(Density_Ref);
1013  config->SetTemperature_Ref(Temperature_Ref);
1014 
1015  Length_Ref = 1.0; config->SetLength_Ref(Length_Ref);
1016  Velocity_Ref = sqrt(config->GetPressure_Ref()/config->GetDensity_Ref()); config->SetVelocity_Ref(Velocity_Ref);
1017  Time_Ref = Length_Ref/Velocity_Ref; config->SetTime_Ref(Time_Ref);
1018  Omega_Ref = Velocity_Ref/Length_Ref; config->SetOmega_Ref(Omega_Ref);
1019  Force_Ref = config->GetDensity_Ref()*Velocity_Ref*Velocity_Ref*Length_Ref*Length_Ref; config->SetForce_Ref(Force_Ref);
1020  Heat_Flux_Ref = Density_Ref*Velocity_Ref*Velocity_Ref*Velocity_Ref; config->SetHeat_Flux_Ref(Heat_Flux_Ref);
1021  Gas_Constant_Ref = Velocity_Ref*Velocity_Ref/config->GetTemperature_Ref(); config->SetGas_Constant_Ref(Gas_Constant_Ref);
1022  Viscosity_Ref = config->GetDensity_Ref()*Velocity_Ref*Length_Ref; config->SetViscosity_Ref(Viscosity_Ref);
1023  Conductivity_Ref = Viscosity_Ref*Gas_Constant_Ref; config->SetConductivity_Ref(Conductivity_Ref);
1024  Froude = ModVel_FreeStream/sqrt(STANDARD_GRAVITY*Length_Ref); config->SetFroude(Froude);
1025 
1026  /*--- Divide by reference values, to compute the non-dimensional free-stream values ---*/
1027 
1028  Pressure_FreeStreamND = Pressure_FreeStream/config->GetPressure_Ref(); config->SetPressure_FreeStreamND(Pressure_FreeStreamND);
1029  Density_FreeStreamND = Density_FreeStream/config->GetDensity_Ref(); config->SetDensity_FreeStreamND(Density_FreeStreamND);
1030 
1031  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
1032  Velocity_FreeStreamND[iDim] = config->GetVelocity_FreeStream()[iDim]/Velocity_Ref; config->SetVelocity_FreeStreamND(Velocity_FreeStreamND[iDim], iDim);
1033  }
1034 
1035  Temperature_FreeStreamND = Temperature_FreeStream/config->GetTemperature_Ref(); config->SetTemperature_FreeStreamND(Temperature_FreeStreamND);
1036 
1037  Gas_ConstantND = config->GetGas_Constant()/Gas_Constant_Ref; config->SetGas_ConstantND(Gas_ConstantND);
1038 
1039 
1040  ModVel_FreeStreamND = 0.0;
1041  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) ModVel_FreeStreamND += Velocity_FreeStreamND[iDim]*Velocity_FreeStreamND[iDim];
1042  ModVel_FreeStreamND = sqrt(ModVel_FreeStreamND); config->SetModVel_FreeStreamND(ModVel_FreeStreamND);
1043 
1044  Viscosity_FreeStreamND = Viscosity_FreeStream / Viscosity_Ref; config->SetViscosity_FreeStreamND(Viscosity_FreeStreamND);
1045 
1046  Tke_FreeStream = 3.0/2.0*(ModVel_FreeStream*ModVel_FreeStream*config->GetTurbulenceIntensity_FreeStream()*config->GetTurbulenceIntensity_FreeStream());
1047  config->SetTke_FreeStream(Tke_FreeStream);
1048 
1049  Tke_FreeStreamND = 3.0/2.0*(ModVel_FreeStreamND*ModVel_FreeStreamND*config->GetTurbulenceIntensity_FreeStream()*config->GetTurbulenceIntensity_FreeStream());
1050  config->SetTke_FreeStreamND(Tke_FreeStreamND);
1051 
1052  Omega_FreeStream = Density_FreeStream*Tke_FreeStream/(Viscosity_FreeStream*config->GetTurb2LamViscRatio_FreeStream());
1053  config->SetOmega_FreeStream(Omega_FreeStream);
1054 
1055  Omega_FreeStreamND = Density_FreeStreamND*Tke_FreeStreamND/(Viscosity_FreeStreamND*config->GetTurb2LamViscRatio_FreeStream());
1056  config->SetOmega_FreeStreamND(Omega_FreeStreamND);
1057 
1058  if (config->GetTurbulenceIntensity_FreeStream() *100 <= 1.3) {
1059  if (config->GetTurbulenceIntensity_FreeStream() *100 >=0.027) {
1060  Re_ThetaT_FreeStream = (1173.51-589.428*config->GetTurbulenceIntensity_FreeStream() *100+0.2196/
1061  (config->GetTurbulenceIntensity_FreeStream() *100*config->GetTurbulenceIntensity_FreeStream() *100));
1062  }
1063  else {
1064  Re_ThetaT_FreeStream = (1173.51-589.428*config->GetTurbulenceIntensity_FreeStream() *100+0.2196/(0.27*0.27));
1065  }
1066  }
1067  else {
1068  Re_ThetaT_FreeStream = 331.5*pow(config->GetTurbulenceIntensity_FreeStream() *100-0.5658,-0.671);
1069  }
1070  config->SetReThetaT_FreeStream(Re_ThetaT_FreeStream);
1071 
1072  const su2double MassDiffusivityND = config->GetDiffusivity_Constant() / (Velocity_Ref * Length_Ref);
1073  config->SetDiffusivity_ConstantND(MassDiffusivityND);
1074 
1075  /*--- Initialize the dimensionless Fluid Model that will be used to solve the dimensionless problem ---*/
1076 
1077  /*--- Auxilary (dimensional) FluidModel no longer needed. ---*/
1078  delete auxFluidModel;
1079 
1080  /*--- Create one final fluid model object per OpenMP thread to be able to use them in parallel.
1081  * GetFluidModel() should be used to automatically access the "right" object of each thread. ---*/
1082 
1083  assert(FluidModel.empty() && "Potential memory leak!");
1084  FluidModel.resize(omp_get_max_threads());
1085 
1086  SU2_OMP_PARALLEL
1087  {
1088  const int thread = omp_get_thread_num();
1089 
1090  switch (config->GetKind_FluidModel()) {
1091 
1092  case STANDARD_AIR:
1093  FluidModel[thread] = new CIdealGas(1.4, Gas_ConstantND);
1094  break;
1095 
1096  case IDEAL_GAS:
1097  FluidModel[thread] = new CIdealGas(Gamma, Gas_ConstantND);
1098  break;
1099 
1100  case VW_GAS:
1101  FluidModel[thread] = new CVanDerWaalsGas(Gamma, Gas_ConstantND,
1102  config->GetPressure_Critical() / config->GetPressure_Ref(),
1103  config->GetTemperature_Critical() / config->GetTemperature_Ref());
1104  break;
1105 
1106  case PR_GAS:
1107  FluidModel[thread] = new CPengRobinson(Gamma, Gas_ConstantND,
1108  config->GetPressure_Critical() / config->GetPressure_Ref(),
1109  config->GetTemperature_Critical() / config->GetTemperature_Ref(),
1110  config->GetAcentric_Factor());
1111  break;
1112 
1113  case DATADRIVEN_FLUID:
1114  FluidModel[thread] = new CDataDrivenFluid(config, false);
1115  break;
1116 
1117  case COOLPROP:
1118  FluidModel[thread] = new CCoolProp(config->GetFluid_Name());
1119  break;
1120  }
1121 
1122  GetFluidModel()->SetEnergy_Prho(Pressure_FreeStreamND, Density_FreeStreamND);
1123  if (viscous) {
1124  GetFluidModel()->SetLaminarViscosityModel(config);
1125  GetFluidModel()->SetThermalConductivityModel(config);
1126  GetFluidModel()->SetMassDiffusivityModel(config);
1127  }
1128 
1129  }
1130  END_SU2_OMP_PARALLEL
1131 
1132  Energy_FreeStreamND = GetFluidModel()->GetStaticEnergy() + 0.5*ModVel_FreeStreamND*ModVel_FreeStreamND;
1133 
1134  if (tkeNeeded) Energy_FreeStreamND += Tke_FreeStreamND;
1135 
1136  config->SetEnergy_FreeStreamND(Energy_FreeStreamND);
1137 
1138  Energy_Ref = Energy_FreeStream/Energy_FreeStreamND; config->SetEnergy_Ref(Energy_Ref);
1139 
1140  Total_UnstTimeND = config->GetTotal_UnstTime() / Time_Ref; config->SetTotal_UnstTimeND(Total_UnstTimeND);
1141  Delta_UnstTimeND = config->GetDelta_UnstTime() / Time_Ref; config->SetDelta_UnstTimeND(Delta_UnstTimeND);
1142 
1143  /*--- Write output to the console if this is the master node and first domain ---*/
1144 
1145  if ((rank == MASTER_NODE) && (MGLevel == MESH_0)) {
1146 
1147  cout.precision(6);
1148 
1149  if (viscous) {
1150  cout << "Viscous flow: Computing pressure using the ideal gas law" << endl;
1151  cout << "based on the free-stream temperature and a density computed" << endl;
1152  cout << "from the Reynolds number." << endl;
1153  } else {
1154  cout << "Inviscid flow: Computing density based on free-stream" << endl;
1155  cout << "temperature and pressure using the ideal gas law." << endl;
1156  }
1157 
1158  if (dynamic_grid) cout << "Force coefficients computed using MACH_MOTION." << endl;
1159  else cout << "Force coefficients computed using free-stream values." << endl;
1160 
1161  stringstream NonDimTableOut, ModelTableOut;
1162  stringstream Unit;
1163 
1164  cout << endl;
1165  PrintingToolbox::CTablePrinter ModelTable(&ModelTableOut);
1166  ModelTableOut <<"-- Models:"<< endl;
1167 
1168  ModelTable.AddColumn("Viscosity Model", 25);
1169  ModelTable.AddColumn("Conductivity Model", 26);
1170  ModelTable.AddColumn("Fluid Model", 25);
1171  ModelTable.SetAlign(PrintingToolbox::CTablePrinter::RIGHT);
1172  ModelTable.PrintHeader();
1173 
1174  PrintingToolbox::CTablePrinter NonDimTable(&NonDimTableOut);
1175  NonDimTable.AddColumn("Name", 22);
1176  NonDimTable.AddColumn("Dim. value", 14);
1177  NonDimTable.AddColumn("Ref. value", 14);
1178  NonDimTable.AddColumn("Unit", 10);
1179  NonDimTable.AddColumn("Non-dim. value", 14);
1180  NonDimTable.SetAlign(PrintingToolbox::CTablePrinter::RIGHT);
1181 
1182  NonDimTableOut <<"-- Fluid properties:"<< endl;
1183 
1184  NonDimTable.PrintHeader();
1185 
1186  if (viscous) {
1187 
1188  switch(config->GetKind_ViscosityModel()){
1189  case VISCOSITYMODEL::CONSTANT:
1190  ModelTable << "CONSTANT_VISCOSITY";
1191  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) Unit << "N.s/m^2";
1192  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) Unit << "lbf.s/ft^2";
1193  NonDimTable << "Viscosity" << config->GetMu_Constant() << config->GetMu_Constant()/config->GetMu_ConstantND() << Unit.str() << config->GetMu_ConstantND();
1194  Unit.str("");
1195  NonDimTable.PrintFooter();
1196  break;
1197 
1198  case VISCOSITYMODEL::COOLPROP:
1199  ModelTable << "COOLPROP";
1200  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) Unit << "N.s/m^2";
1201  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) Unit << "lbf.s/ft^2";
1202  NonDimTable << "Viscosity" << "--" << "--" << Unit.str() << config->GetMu_ConstantND();
1203  Unit.str("");
1204  NonDimTable.PrintFooter();
1205  break;
1206 
1207  case VISCOSITYMODEL::SUTHERLAND:
1208  ModelTable << "SUTHERLAND";
1209  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) Unit << "N.s/m^2";
1210  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) Unit << "lbf.s/ft^2";
1211  NonDimTable << "Ref. Viscosity" << config->GetMu_Ref() << config->GetViscosity_Ref() << Unit.str() << config->GetMu_RefND();
1212  Unit.str("");
1213  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) Unit << "K";
1214  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) Unit << "R";
1215  NonDimTable << "Sutherland Temp." << config->GetMu_Temperature_Ref() << config->GetTemperature_Ref() << Unit.str() << config->GetMu_Temperature_RefND();
1216  Unit.str("");
1217  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) Unit << "K";
1218  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) Unit << "R";
1219  NonDimTable << "Sutherland Const." << config->GetMu_S() << config->GetTemperature_Ref() << Unit.str() << config->GetMu_SND();
1220  Unit.str("");
1221  NonDimTable.PrintFooter();
1222  break;
1223 
1224  default:
1225  break;
1226 
1227  }
1228  switch(config->GetKind_ConductivityModel()){
1229  case CONDUCTIVITYMODEL::CONSTANT_PRANDTL:
1230  ModelTable << "CONSTANT_PRANDTL";
1231  NonDimTable << "Prandtl (Lam.)" << "-" << "-" << "-" << config->GetPrandtl_Lam();
1232  Unit.str("");
1233  NonDimTable << "Prandtl (Turb.)" << "-" << "-" << "-" << config->GetPrandtl_Turb();
1234  Unit.str("");
1235  NonDimTable.PrintFooter();
1236  break;
1237 
1238  case CONDUCTIVITYMODEL::CONSTANT:
1239  ModelTable << "CONSTANT";
1240  Unit << "W/m^2.K";
1241  NonDimTable << "Molecular Cond." << config->GetThermal_Conductivity_Constant() << config->GetThermal_Conductivity_Constant()/config->GetThermal_Conductivity_ConstantND() << Unit.str() << config->GetThermal_Conductivity_ConstantND();
1242  Unit.str("");
1243  NonDimTable.PrintFooter();
1244  break;
1245 
1246  case CONDUCTIVITYMODEL::COOLPROP:
1247  ModelTable << "COOLPROP";
1248  Unit << "W/m^2.K";
1249  NonDimTable << "Molecular Cond." << "--" << "--" << Unit.str() << config->GetThermal_Conductivity_ConstantND();
1250  Unit.str("");
1251  NonDimTable.PrintFooter();
1252  break;
1253 
1254  default:
1255  break;
1256 
1257  }
1258  } else {
1259  ModelTable << "-" << "-";
1260  }
1261 
1262  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) Unit << "N.m/kg.K";
1263  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) Unit << "lbf.ft/slug.R";
1264  if (config->GetKind_FluidModel() == COOLPROP) {
1265  CCoolProp auxFluidModel(config->GetFluid_Name());
1266  NonDimTable << "Gas Constant" << auxFluidModel.GetGas_Constant() << config->GetGas_Constant_Ref() << Unit.str() << auxFluidModel.GetGas_Constant()/config->GetGas_Constant_Ref();
1267  }
1268  else {
1269  NonDimTable << "Gas Constant" << config->GetGas_Constant() << config->GetGas_Constant_Ref() << Unit.str() << config->GetGas_ConstantND();
1270  }
1271  Unit.str("");
1272  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) Unit << "N.m/kg.K";
1273  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) Unit << "lbf.ft/slug.R";
1274  if (config->GetKind_FluidModel() == COOLPROP) {
1275  NonDimTable << "Spec. Heat Ratio" << "-" << "-" << "-" << "-";
1276  }
1277  else {
1278  NonDimTable << "Spec. Heat Ratio" << "-" << "-" << "-" << Gamma;
1279  }
1280  Unit.str("");
1281 
1282  switch(config->GetKind_FluidModel()){
1283  case STANDARD_AIR:
1284  ModelTable << "STANDARD_AIR";
1285  break;
1286  case IDEAL_GAS:
1287  ModelTable << "IDEAL_GAS";
1288  break;
1289  case VW_GAS:
1290  ModelTable << "VW_GAS";
1291  break;
1292  case PR_GAS:
1293  ModelTable << "PR_GAS";
1294  break;
1295  case COOLPROP:
1296  ModelTable << "CoolProp library";
1297  break;
1298  }
1299 
1300  if (config->GetKind_FluidModel() == VW_GAS || config->GetKind_FluidModel() == PR_GAS){
1301  NonDimTable << "Critical Pressure" << config->GetPressure_Critical() << config->GetPressure_Ref() << Unit.str() << config->GetPressure_Critical() /config->GetPressure_Ref();
1302  Unit.str("");
1303  Unit << "K";
1304  NonDimTable << "Critical Temperature" << config->GetTemperature_Critical() << config->GetTemperature_Ref() << Unit.str() << config->GetTemperature_Critical() /config->GetTemperature_Ref();
1305  Unit.str("");
1306  }
1307  if (config->GetKind_FluidModel() == COOLPROP) {
1308  CCoolProp auxFluidModel(config->GetFluid_Name());
1309  NonDimTable << "Critical Pressure" << auxFluidModel.GetPressure_Critical() << config->GetPressure_Ref() << Unit.str() << auxFluidModel.GetPressure_Critical() /config->GetPressure_Ref();
1310  Unit.str("");

1312  NonDimTable << "Critical Temperature" << auxFluidModel.GetTemperature_Critical() << config->GetTemperature_Ref() << Unit.str() << auxFluidModel.GetTemperature_Critical() /config->GetTemperature_Ref();
1313  Unit.str("");
1314  }
1315  NonDimTable.PrintFooter();
1316 
1317  NonDimTableOut <<"-- Initial and free-stream conditions:"<< endl;
1318 
1319  NonDimTable.PrintHeader();
1320 
1321  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) Unit << "Pa";
1322  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) Unit << "psf";
1323  NonDimTable << "Static Pressure" << config->GetPressure_FreeStream() << config->GetPressure_Ref() << Unit.str() << config->GetPressure_FreeStreamND();
1324  Unit.str("");
1325  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) Unit << "kg/m^3";
1326  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) Unit << "slug/ft^3";
1327  NonDimTable << "Density" << config->GetDensity_FreeStream() << config->GetDensity_Ref() << Unit.str() << config->GetDensity_FreeStreamND();
1328  Unit.str("");

1330  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) Unit << "R";
1331  NonDimTable << "Temperature" << config->GetTemperature_FreeStream() << config->GetTemperature_Ref() << Unit.str() << config->GetTemperature_FreeStreamND();
1332  Unit.str("");
1333  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) Unit << "m^2/s^2";
1334  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) Unit << "ft^2/s^2";
1335  NonDimTable << "Total Energy" << config->GetEnergy_FreeStream() << config->GetEnergy_Ref() << Unit.str() << config->GetEnergy_FreeStreamND();
1336  Unit.str("");
1337  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) Unit << "m/s";
1338  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) Unit << "ft/s";
1339  NonDimTable << "Velocity-X" << config->GetVelocity_FreeStream()[0] << config->GetVelocity_Ref() << Unit.str() << config->GetVelocity_FreeStreamND()[0];
1340  NonDimTable << "Velocity-Y" << config->GetVelocity_FreeStream()[1] << config->GetVelocity_Ref() << Unit.str() << config->GetVelocity_FreeStreamND()[1];
1341  if (nDim == 3){
1342  NonDimTable << "Velocity-Z" << config->GetVelocity_FreeStream()[2] << config->GetVelocity_Ref() << Unit.str() << config->GetVelocity_FreeStreamND()[2];
1343  }
1344  NonDimTable << "Velocity Magnitude" << config->GetModVel_FreeStream() << config->GetVelocity_Ref() << Unit.str() << config->GetModVel_FreeStreamND();
1345  Unit.str("");
1346 
1347  if (viscous){
1348  NonDimTable.PrintFooter();
1349  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) Unit << "N.s/m^2";
1350  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) Unit << "lbf.s/ft^2";
1351  NonDimTable << "Viscosity" << config->GetViscosity_FreeStream() << config->GetViscosity_Ref() << Unit.str() << config->GetViscosity_FreeStreamND();
1352  Unit.str("");
1353  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) Unit << "W/m^2.K";
1354  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) Unit << "lbf/ft.s.R";
1355  NonDimTable << "Conductivity" << "-" << config->GetThermal_Conductivity_Ref() << Unit.str() << "-";
1356  Unit.str("");
1357  if (turbulent){
1358  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) Unit << "m^2/s^2";
1359  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) Unit << "ft^2/s^2";
1360  NonDimTable << "Turb. Kin. Energy" << config->GetTke_FreeStream() << config->GetTke_FreeStream()/config->GetTke_FreeStreamND() << Unit.str() << config->GetTke_FreeStreamND();
1361  Unit.str("");
1362  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) Unit << "1/s";
1363  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) Unit << "1/s";
1364  NonDimTable << "Spec. Dissipation" << config->GetOmega_FreeStream() << config->GetOmega_FreeStream()/config->GetOmega_FreeStreamND() << Unit.str() << config->GetOmega_FreeStreamND();
1365  Unit.str("");
1366  if (config-> GetKind_Trans_Model() == TURB_TRANS_MODEL::LM) {
1367  NonDimTable << "Intermittency" << "-" << "-" << "-" << config->GetIntermittency_FreeStream();
1368  Unit.str("");
1369  NonDimTable << "Moment. Thick. Re" << "-" << "-" << "-" << config->GetReThetaT_FreeStream();
1370  Unit.str("");
1371  }
1372  }
1373  if (config->GetKind_Species_Model() != SPECIES_MODEL::NONE) {
1374  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) Unit << "m^2/s";
1375  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) Unit << "ft^2/s";
1376  NonDimTable << "Mass Diffusivity" << config->GetDiffusivity_Constant() << config->GetDiffusivity_Constant()/config->GetDiffusivity_ConstantND() << Unit.str() << config->GetDiffusivity_ConstantND();
1377  Unit.str("");
1378  }
1379  }
1380 
1381  NonDimTable.PrintFooter();
1382  NonDimTable << "Mach Number" << "-" << "-" << "-" << config->GetMach();
1383  if (viscous){
1384  NonDimTable << "Reynolds Number" << "-" << "-" << "-" << config->GetReynolds();
1385  }
1386  if (gravity) {
1387  NonDimTable << "Froude Number" << "-" << "-" << "-" << Froude;
1388  NonDimTable << "Wave Length" << "-" << "-" << "-" << 2.0*PI_NUMBER*Froude*Froude;
1389  }
1390  NonDimTable.PrintFooter();
1391  ModelTable.PrintFooter();
1392 
1393  if (unsteady){
1394  NonDimTableOut << "-- Unsteady conditions" << endl;
1395  NonDimTable.PrintHeader();
1396  NonDimTable << "Total Time" << config->GetMax_Time() << config->GetTime_Ref() << "s" << config->GetMax_Time()/config->GetTime_Ref();
1397  Unit.str("");
1398  NonDimTable << "Time Step" << config->GetTime_Step() << config->GetTime_Ref() << "s" << config->GetDelta_UnstTimeND();
1399  Unit.str("");
1400  NonDimTable.PrintFooter();
1401  }
1402 
1403  cout << ModelTableOut.str();
1404  cout << NonDimTableOut.str();
1405 
1406  }
1407
