1409 
1410 void CEulerSolver::SetReferenceValues(const CConfig& config) {
1411 
1412  /*--- Evaluate reference values for non-dimensionalization. For dynamic meshes,
1413  use the motion Mach number as a reference value for computing the force coefficients.
1414  Otherwise, use the freestream values, which is the standard convention. ---*/
1415 
1416  su2double RefVel2;
1417 
1418  if (dynamic_grid && !config.GetFSI_Simulation()) {
1419  su2double Gas_Constant = config.GetGas_ConstantND();
1420  su2double Mach2Vel = sqrt(Gamma * Gas_Constant * Temperature_Inf);
1421  su2double Mach_Motion = config.GetMach_Motion();
1422  RefVel2 = pow(Mach_Motion * Mach2Vel, 2);
1423  }
1424  else {
1425  RefVel2 = GeometryToolbox::SquaredNorm(nDim, Velocity_Inf);
1426  }
1427 
1428  DynamicPressureRef = 0.5 * Density_Inf * RefVel2;
1429  AeroCoeffForceRef = DynamicPressureRef * config.GetRefArea();
1430 
1431 }
1432 
1433 void CEulerSolver::SetInitialCondition(CGeometry **geometry, CSolver ***solver_container, CConfig *config, unsigned long TimeIter) {
1434 
1435  const bool restart = (config->GetRestart() || config->GetRestart_Flow());
1436  const bool SubsonicEngine = config->GetSubsonicEngine();
1437 
1438  /*--- Use default implementation, then add solver-specifics. ---*/
1439 
1440  BaseClass::SetInitialCondition(geometry, solver_container, config, TimeIter);
1441 
1442  /*--- Set subsonic initial condition for engine intakes at iteration 0 ---*/
1443 
1444  if (!SubsonicEngine || (TimeIter != 0) || restart) return;
1445 
1446  /*--- Start OpenMP parallel region. ---*/
1447 
1448  SU2_OMP_PARALLEL {
1449 
1450  unsigned long iPoint;
1451  unsigned short iMesh, iDim;
1452  su2double X0[MAXNDIM] = {0.0}, X1[MAXNDIM] = {0.0}, X2[MAXNDIM] = {0.0},
1453  X1_X0[MAXNDIM] = {0.0}, X2_X0[MAXNDIM] = {0.0}, X2_X1[MAXNDIM] = {0.0},
1454  CP[MAXNDIM] = {0.0}, Distance, DotCheck, Radius;
1455 
1456  su2double Velocity_Cyl[MAXNDIM] = {0.0}, Velocity_CylND[MAXNDIM] = {0.0}, Viscosity_Cyl,
1457  Density_Cyl, Density_CylND, Pressure_CylND, ModVel_Cyl, ModVel_CylND, Energy_CylND,
1458  T_ref = 0.0, S = 0.0, Mu_ref = 0.0;
1459  const su2double *Coord, *SubsonicEngine_Cyl, *SubsonicEngine_Values;
1460 
1461  SubsonicEngine_Values = config->GetSubsonicEngine_Values();
1462  su2double Mach_Cyl = SubsonicEngine_Values[0];
1463  su2double Alpha_Cyl = SubsonicEngine_Values[1];
1464  su2double Beta_Cyl = SubsonicEngine_Values[2];
1465  su2double Pressure_Cyl = SubsonicEngine_Values[3];
1466  su2double Temperature_Cyl = SubsonicEngine_Values[4];
1467 
1468  su2double Alpha = Alpha_Cyl*PI_NUMBER/180.0;
1469  su2double Beta = Beta_Cyl*PI_NUMBER/180.0;
1470 
1471  su2double Gamma_Minus_One = Gamma - 1.0;
1472  su2double Gas_Constant = config->GetGas_Constant();
1473 
1474  su2double Mach2Vel_Cyl = sqrt(Gamma*Gas_Constant*Temperature_Cyl);
1475 
1476  for (iMesh = 0; iMesh <= config->GetnMGLevels(); iMesh++) {
1477 
1478  auto FlowNodes = solver_container[iMesh][FLOW_SOL]->GetNodes();
1479 
1480  SU2_OMP_FOR_STAT(omp_chunk_size)
1481  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < geometry[iMesh]->GetnPoint(); iPoint++) {
1482 
1483  Velocity_Cyl[0] = cos(Alpha)*cos(Beta)*Mach_Cyl*Mach2Vel_Cyl;
1484  Velocity_Cyl[1] = sin(Beta)*Mach_Cyl*Mach2Vel_Cyl;
1485  Velocity_Cyl[2] = sin(Alpha)*cos(Beta)*Mach_Cyl*Mach2Vel_Cyl;
1486 
1487  ModVel_Cyl = GeometryToolbox::Norm(nDim, Velocity_Cyl);
1488 
1489  if (config->GetViscous()) {
1490  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) { T_ref = 273.15; S = 110.4; Mu_ref = 1.716E-5; }
1491  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) {
1492  T_ref = (273.15 - 273.15) * 1.8 + 491.67;
1493  S = (110.4 - 273.15) * 1.8 + 491.67;
1494  Mu_ref = 1.716E-5/47.88025898;
1495  }
1496  Viscosity_Cyl = Mu_ref*(pow(Temperature_Cyl/T_ref, 1.5) * (T_ref+S)/(Temperature_Cyl+S));
1497  Density_Cyl = config->GetReynolds()*Viscosity_Cyl/(ModVel_Cyl*config->GetLength_Reynolds());
1498  Pressure_Cyl = Density_Cyl*Gas_Constant*Temperature_Cyl;
1499  }
1500  else {
1501  Density_Cyl = Pressure_Cyl/(Gas_Constant*Temperature_Cyl);
1502  }
1503 
1504  Density_CylND = Density_Cyl/config->GetDensity_Ref();
1505  Pressure_CylND = Pressure_Cyl/config->GetPressure_Ref();
1506 
1507  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
1508  Velocity_CylND[iDim] = Velocity_Cyl[iDim]/config->GetVelocity_Ref();
1509  }
1510 
1511  ModVel_CylND = GeometryToolbox::Norm(nDim, Velocity_CylND);
1512 
1513  Energy_CylND = Pressure_CylND/(Density_CylND*Gamma_Minus_One)+0.5*ModVel_CylND*ModVel_CylND;
1514 
1515  Coord = geometry[iMesh]->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint);
1516 
1517  SubsonicEngine_Cyl = config->GetSubsonicEngine_Cyl();
1518 
1519  X0[0] = Coord[0]; X0[1] = Coord[1]; if (nDim==3) X0[2] = Coord[2];
1520  X1[0] = SubsonicEngine_Cyl[0]; X1[1] = SubsonicEngine_Cyl[1]; X1[2] = SubsonicEngine_Cyl[2];
1521  X2[0] = SubsonicEngine_Cyl[3]; X2[1] = SubsonicEngine_Cyl[4]; X2[2] = SubsonicEngine_Cyl[5];
1522  Radius = SubsonicEngine_Cyl[6];
1523 
1524  GeometryToolbox::Distance(3, X1, X2, X2_X1);
1525  GeometryToolbox::Distance(3, X0, X1, X1_X0);
1526  GeometryToolbox::Distance(3, X0, X2, X2_X0);
1527 
1528  GeometryToolbox::CrossProduct(X2_X1, X1_X0, CP);
1529 
1530  Distance = sqrt(GeometryToolbox::SquaredNorm(3,CP) / GeometryToolbox::SquaredNorm(3,X2_X1));
1531 
1532  DotCheck = -GeometryToolbox::DotProduct(3, X1_X0, X2_X1);
1533  if (DotCheck < 0.0) Distance = GeometryToolbox::Norm(3, X1_X0);
1534 
1535  DotCheck = GeometryToolbox::DotProduct(3, X2_X0, X2_X1);
1536  if (DotCheck < 0.0) Distance = GeometryToolbox::Norm(3, X2_X0);
1537 
1538  if (Distance < Radius) {
1539  FlowNodes->SetSolution(iPoint, 0, Density_CylND);
1540  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
1541  FlowNodes->SetSolution(iPoint, iDim+1, Density_CylND*Velocity_CylND[iDim]);
1542  FlowNodes->SetSolution(iPoint, nVar-1, Density_CylND*Energy_CylND);
1543  }
1544 
1545  }
1546  END_SU2_OMP_FOR
1547 
1548  FlowNodes->Set_OldSolution();
1549 
1550  }
1551 
1552  }
1553  END_SU2_OMP_PARALLEL
1554 
1555 }
1556 
1557 void CEulerSolver::CommonPreprocessing(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver_container, CConfig *config, unsigned short iMesh,
1558  unsigned short iRKStep, unsigned short RunTime_EqSystem, bool Output) {
1559 
1560  bool cont_adjoint = config->GetContinuous_Adjoint();
1561  bool disc_adjoint = config->GetDiscrete_Adjoint();
1562  bool implicit = (config->GetKind_TimeIntScheme() == EULER_IMPLICIT);
1563  bool center = (config->GetKind_ConvNumScheme_Flow() == SPACE_CENTERED);
1564  bool center_jst = (config->GetKind_Centered_Flow() == CENTERED::JST) && (iMesh == MESH_0);
1565  bool center_jst_ke = (config->GetKind_Centered_Flow() == CENTERED::JST_KE) && (iMesh == MESH_0);
1566  bool center_jst_mat = (config->GetKind_Centered_Flow() == CENTERED::JST_MAT) && (iMesh == MESH_0);
1567  bool engine = ((config->GetnMarker_EngineInflow() != 0) || (config->GetnMarker_EngineExhaust() != 0));
1568  bool actuator_disk = ((config->GetnMarker_ActDiskInlet() != 0) || (config->GetnMarker_ActDiskOutlet() != 0));
1569  bool fixed_cl = config->GetFixed_CL_Mode();
1570  unsigned short kind_row_dissipation = config->GetKind_RoeLowDiss();
1571  bool roe_low_dissipation = (kind_row_dissipation != NO_ROELOWDISS) &&
1572  (config->GetKind_Upwind_Flow() == UPWIND::ROE ||
1573  config->GetKind_Upwind_Flow() == UPWIND::SLAU ||
1574  config->GetKind_Upwind_Flow() == UPWIND::SLAU2);
1575 
1576  /*--- Set the primitive variables ---*/
1577 
1578  ompMasterAssignBarrier(ErrorCounter, 0);
1579 
1580  SU2_OMP_ATOMIC
1581  ErrorCounter += SetPrimitive_Variables(solver_container, config);
1582 
1583  BEGIN_SU2_OMP_SAFE_GLOBAL_ACCESS
1584  { /*--- Ops that are not OpenMP parallel go in this block. ---*/
1585 
1586  if ((iMesh == MESH_0) && (config->GetComm_Level() == COMM_FULL)) {
1587  unsigned long tmp = ErrorCounter;
1588  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(&tmp, &ErrorCounter, 1, MPI_UNSIGNED_LONG, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
1589  config->SetNonphysical_Points(ErrorCounter);
1590  }
1591 
1592  /*--- Update the angle of attack at the far-field for fixed CL calculations (only direct problem). ---*/
1593 
1594  if (fixed_cl && !disc_adjoint && !cont_adjoint) {
1595  SetFarfield_AoA(geometry, solver_container, config, iMesh, Output);
1596  }
1597 
1598  /*--- Compute the engine properties ---*/
1599 
1600  if (engine) GetPower_Properties(geometry, config, iMesh, Output);
1601 
1602  /*--- Compute the actuator disk properties and distortion levels ---*/
1603 
1604  if (actuator_disk) {
1605  Set_MPI_ActDisk(solver_container, geometry, config);
1606  GetPower_Properties(geometry, config, iMesh, Output);
1607  SetActDisk_BCThrust(geometry, solver_container, config, iMesh, Output);
1608  }
1609 
1610  }
1611  END_SU2_OMP_SAFE_GLOBAL_ACCESS
1612 
1613  /*--- Artificial dissipation ---*/
1614 
1615  if (center && !Output) {
1616  if (!center_jst_mat) SetMax_Eigenvalue(geometry, config);
1617  if (center_jst || center_jst_ke || center_jst_mat) {
1618  SetCentered_Dissipation_Sensor(geometry, config);
1619  if (!center_jst_ke) SetUndivided_Laplacian(geometry, config);
1620  }
1621  }
1622 
1623  /*--- Roe Low Dissipation Sensor ---*/
1624 
1625  if (roe_low_dissipation) {
1626  SetRoe_Dissipation(geometry, config);
1627  if (kind_row_dissipation == FD_DUCROS || kind_row_dissipation == NTS_DUCROS){
1628  SetUpwind_Ducros_Sensor(geometry, config);
1629  }
1630  }
1631 
1632  /*--- Initialize the Jacobian matrix and residual, not needed for the reducer strategy
1633  * as we set blocks (including diagonal ones) and completely overwrite. ---*/
1634 
1635  if(!ReducerStrategy && !Output) {
1636  LinSysRes.SetValZero();
1637  if (implicit) Jacobian.SetValZero();
1638  else {SU2_OMP_BARRIER} // because of "nowait" in LinSysRes
1639  }
1640 
1641 }
1642 
1643 void CEulerSolver::Preprocessing(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver_container, CConfig *config, unsigned short iMesh,
1644  unsigned short iRKStep, unsigned short RunTime_EqSystem, bool Output) {
1645  const auto InnerIter = config->GetInnerIter();
1646  const bool muscl = config->GetMUSCL_Flow() && (iMesh == MESH_0);
1647  const bool center = (config->GetKind_ConvNumScheme_Flow() == SPACE_CENTERED);
1648  const bool limiter = (config->GetKind_SlopeLimit_Flow() != LIMITER::NONE) && (InnerIter <= config->GetLimiterIter());
1649  const bool van_albada = (config->GetKind_SlopeLimit_Flow() == LIMITER::VAN_ALBADA_EDGE);
1650 
1651  /*--- Common preprocessing steps. ---*/
1652 
1653  CommonPreprocessing(geometry, solver_container, config, iMesh, iRKStep, RunTime_EqSystem, Output);
1654 
1655  /*--- Upwind second order reconstruction ---*/
1656 
1657  if (!Output && muscl && !center) {
1658 
1659  /*--- Gradient computation for MUSCL reconstruction. ---*/
1660 
1661  switch (config->GetKind_Gradient_Method_Recon()) {
1662  case GREEN_GAUSS:
1663  SetPrimitive_Gradient_GG(geometry, config, true); break;
1664  case LEAST_SQUARES:
1665  case WEIGHTED_LEAST_SQUARES:
1666  SetPrimitive_Gradient_LS(geometry, config, true); break;
1667  default: break;
1668  }
1669 
1670  /*--- Limiter computation ---*/
1671 
1672  if (limiter && !van_albada) SetPrimitive_Limiter(geometry, config);
1673  }
1674 }
1675 
1676 unsigned long CEulerSolver::SetPrimitive_Variables(CSolver **solver_container, const CConfig *config) {
1677 
1678  /*--- Number of non-physical points, local to the thread, needs
1679  * further reduction if function is called in parallel ---*/
1680  unsigned long nonPhysicalPoints = 0;
1681 
1682  AD::StartNoSharedReading();
1683 
1684  SU2_OMP_FOR_STAT(omp_chunk_size)
1685  for (unsigned long iPoint = 0; iPoint < nPoint; iPoint ++) {
1686 
1687  /*--- Compressible flow, primitive variables nDim+9, (T, vx, vy, vz, P, rho, h, c, lamMu, eddyMu, ThCond, Cp) ---*/
1688 
1689  bool physical = nodes->SetPrimVar(iPoint, GetFluidModel());
1690  nodes->SetSecondaryVar(iPoint, GetFluidModel());
1691 
1692  /* Check for non-realizable states for reporting. */
1693 
1694  if (!physical) nonPhysicalPoints++;
1695  }
1696  END_SU2_OMP_FOR
1697 
1698  AD::EndNoSharedReading();
1699 
1700  return nonPhysicalPoints;
1701 }
1702 
1703 void CEulerSolver::SetTime_Step(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver_container, CConfig *config,
1704  unsigned short iMesh, unsigned long Iteration) {
1705 
1706  /*--- Define an object to compute the speed of sound. ---*/
1707  struct SoundSpeed {
1708  FORCEINLINE su2double operator() (const CEulerVariable& nodes, unsigned long iPoint, unsigned long jPoint) const {
1709  return 0.5 * (nodes.GetSoundSpeed(iPoint) + nodes.GetSoundSpeed(jPoint));
1710  }
1711 
1712  FORCEINLINE su2double operator() (const CEulerVariable& nodes, unsigned long iPoint) const {
1713  return nodes.GetSoundSpeed(iPoint);
1714  }
1715 
1716  } soundSpeed;
1717 
1718  /*--- Define an object to compute the viscous eigenvalue. ---*/
1719  struct LambdaVisc {
1720  const su2double gamma, prandtlLam, prandtlTurb;
1721 
1722  LambdaVisc(su2double g, su2double pl, su2double pt) : gamma(g), prandtlLam(pl), prandtlTurb(pt) {}
1723 
1724  FORCEINLINE su2double lambda(su2double laminarVisc, su2double eddyVisc, su2double density) const {
1725  su2double Lambda_1 = (4.0/3.0)*(laminarVisc + eddyVisc);
1726  /// TODO: (REAL_GAS) removing gamma as it cannot work with FLUIDPROP
1727  su2double Lambda_2 = (1.0 + (prandtlLam/prandtlTurb)*(eddyVisc/laminarVisc))*(gamma*laminarVisc/prandtlLam);
1728  return (Lambda_1 + Lambda_2) / density;
1729  }
1730 
1731  FORCEINLINE su2double operator() (const CEulerVariable& nodes, unsigned long iPoint, unsigned long jPoint) const {
1732  su2double laminarVisc = 0.5*(nodes.GetLaminarViscosity(iPoint) + nodes.GetLaminarViscosity(jPoint));
1733  su2double eddyVisc = 0.5*(nodes.GetEddyViscosity(iPoint) + nodes.GetEddyViscosity(jPoint));
1734  su2double density = 0.5*(nodes.GetDensity(iPoint) + nodes.GetDensity(jPoint));
1735  return lambda(laminarVisc, eddyVisc, density);
1736  }
1737 
1738  FORCEINLINE su2double operator() (const CEulerVariable& nodes, unsigned long iPoint) const {
1739  su2double laminarVisc = nodes.GetLaminarViscosity(iPoint);
1740  su2double eddyVisc = nodes.GetEddyViscosity(iPoint);
1741  su2double density = nodes.GetDensity(iPoint);
1742  return lambda(laminarVisc, eddyVisc, density);
1743  }
1744 
1745  } lambdaVisc(Gamma, Prandtl_Lam, Prandtl_Turb);
1746 
1747  /*--- Now instantiate the generic implementation with the two functors above. ---*/
1748 
1749  SetTime_Step_impl(soundSpeed, lambdaVisc, geometry, solver_container, config, iMesh, Iteration);
1750 
1751 }
1752 
1753 void CEulerSolver::Centered_Residual(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver_container, CNumerics **numerics_container,
1754  CConfig *config, unsigned short iMesh, unsigned short iRKStep) {
1755 
1756  EdgeFluxResidual(geometry, solver_container, config);
1757 }
1758 
1759 void CEulerSolver::Upwind_Residual(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver_container,
1760  CNumerics **numerics_container, CConfig *config, unsigned short iMesh) {
1761 
1762  const bool ideal_gas = (config->GetKind_FluidModel() == STANDARD_AIR) ||
1763  (config->GetKind_FluidModel() == IDEAL_GAS);
1764  const bool low_mach_corr = config->Low_Mach_Correction();
1765 
1766  /*--- Use vectorization if the scheme supports it. ---*/
1767  if (config->GetKind_Upwind_Flow() == UPWIND::ROE && ideal_gas && !low_mach_corr) {
1768  EdgeFluxResidual(geometry, solver_container, config);
1769  return;
1770  }
1771 
1772  const bool implicit = (config->GetKind_TimeIntScheme() == EULER_IMPLICIT);
1773 
1774  const bool roe_turkel = (config->GetKind_Upwind_Flow() == UPWIND::TURKEL);
1775  const auto kind_dissipation = config->GetKind_RoeLowDiss();
1776 
1777  const bool muscl = (config->GetMUSCL_Flow() && (iMesh == MESH_0));
1778  const bool limiter = (config->GetKind_SlopeLimit_Flow() != LIMITER::NONE);
1779  const bool van_albada = (config->GetKind_SlopeLimit_Flow() == LIMITER::VAN_ALBADA_EDGE);
1780 
1781  /*--- Non-physical counter. ---*/
1782  unsigned long counter_local = 0;
1783  SU2_OMP_MASTER
1784  ErrorCounter = 0;
1785  END_SU2_OMP_MASTER
1786 
1787  /*--- Pick one numerics object per thread. ---*/
1788  CNumerics* numerics = numerics_container[CONV_TERM + omp_get_thread_num()*MAX_TERMS];
1789 
1790  /*--- Static arrays of MUSCL-reconstructed primitives and secondaries (thread safety). ---*/
1791  su2double Primitive_i[MAXNVAR] = {0.0}, Primitive_j[MAXNVAR] = {0.0};
1792  su2double Secondary_i[MAXNVAR] = {0.0}, Secondary_j[MAXNVAR] = {0.0};
1793 
1794  /*--- For hybrid parallel AD, pause preaccumulation if there is shared reading of
1795  * variables, otherwise switch to the faster adjoint evaluation mode. ---*/
1796  bool pausePreacc = false;
1797  if (ReducerStrategy) pausePreacc = AD::PausePreaccumulation();
1798  else AD::StartNoSharedReading();
1799 
1800  /*--- Loop over edge colors. ---*/
1801  for (auto color : EdgeColoring)
1802  {
1803  /*--- Chunk size is at least OMP_MIN_SIZE and a multiple of the color group size. ---*/
1804  SU2_OMP_FOR_DYN(nextMultiple(OMP_MIN_SIZE, color.groupSize))
1805  for(auto k = 0ul; k < color.size; ++k) {
1806 
1807  auto iEdge = color.indices[k];
1808 
1809  unsigned short iDim, iVar;
1810 
1811  /*--- Points in edge and normal vectors ---*/
1812 
1813  auto iPoint = geometry->edges->GetNode(iEdge,0);
1814  auto jPoint = geometry->edges->GetNode(iEdge,1);
1815 
1816  numerics->SetNormal(geometry->edges->GetNormal(iEdge));
1817 
1818  auto Coord_i = geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint);
1819  auto Coord_j = geometry->nodes->GetCoord(jPoint);
1820 
1821  /*--- Roe Turkel preconditioning ---*/
1822 
1823  if (roe_turkel) {
1824  numerics->SetVelocity2_Inf(GeometryToolbox::SquaredNorm(nDim, config->GetVelocity_FreeStream()));
1825  }
1826 
1827  /*--- Grid movement ---*/
1828 
1829  if (dynamic_grid) {
1830  numerics->SetGridVel(geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint),
1831  geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(jPoint));
1832  }
1833 
1834  /*--- Get primitive and secondary variables ---*/
1835 
1836  auto V_i = nodes->GetPrimitive(iPoint); auto V_j = nodes->GetPrimitive(jPoint);
1837  auto S_i = nodes->GetSecondary(iPoint); auto S_j = nodes->GetSecondary(jPoint);
1838 
1839  /*--- Set them with or without high order reconstruction using MUSCL strategy. ---*/
1840 
1841  if (!muscl) {
1842 
1843  numerics->SetPrimitive(V_i, V_j);
1844  numerics->SetSecondary(S_i, S_j);
1845 
1846  }
1847  else {
1848  /*--- Reconstruction ---*/
1849 
1850  su2double Vector_ij[MAXNDIM] = {0.0};
1851  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
1852  Vector_ij[iDim] = 0.5*(Coord_j[iDim] - Coord_i[iDim]);
1853  }
1854 
1855  auto Gradient_i = nodes->GetGradient_Reconstruction(iPoint);
1856  auto Gradient_j = nodes->GetGradient_Reconstruction(jPoint);
1857 
1858  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nPrimVarGrad; iVar++) {
1859 
1860  su2double Project_Grad_i = 0.0;
1861  su2double Project_Grad_j = 0.0;
1862 
1863  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
1864  Project_Grad_i += Vector_ij[iDim]*Gradient_i[iVar][iDim];
1865  Project_Grad_j -= Vector_ij[iDim]*Gradient_j[iVar][iDim];
1866  }
1867 
1868  su2double lim_i = 1.0;
1869  su2double lim_j = 1.0;
1870 
1871  if (van_albada) {
1872  su2double V_ij = V_j[iVar] - V_i[iVar];
1873  lim_i = LimiterHelpers<>::vanAlbadaFunction(Project_Grad_i, V_ij, EPS);
1874  lim_j = LimiterHelpers<>::vanAlbadaFunction(-Project_Grad_j, V_ij, EPS);
1875  }
1876  else if (limiter) {
1877  lim_i = nodes->GetLimiter_Primitive(iPoint, iVar);
1878  lim_j = nodes->GetLimiter_Primitive(jPoint, iVar);
1879  }
1880 
1881  Primitive_i[iVar] = V_i[iVar] + lim_i * Project_Grad_i;
1882  Primitive_j[iVar] = V_j[iVar] + lim_j * Project_Grad_j;
1883 
1884  }
1885 
1886  /*--- Recompute the reconstructed quantities in a thermodynamically consistent way. ---*/
1887 
1888  if (!ideal_gas || low_mach_corr) {
1889  ComputeConsistentExtrapolation(GetFluidModel(), nDim, Primitive_i, Secondary_i);
1890  ComputeConsistentExtrapolation(GetFluidModel(), nDim, Primitive_j, Secondary_j);
1891  }
1892 
1893  /*--- Low-Mach number correction. ---*/
1894 
1895  if (low_mach_corr) {
1896  LowMachPrimitiveCorrection(GetFluidModel(), nDim, Primitive_i, Primitive_j);
1897  }
1898 
1899  /*--- Check for non-physical solutions after reconstruction. If found, use the
1900  cell-average value of the solution. This is a locally 1st order approximation,
1901  which is typically only active during the start-up of a calculation. ---*/
1902 
1903  bool neg_pres_or_rho_i = (Primitive_i[prim_idx.Pressure()] < 0.0) || (Primitive_i[prim_idx.Density()] < 0.0);
1904  bool neg_pres_or_rho_j = (Primitive_j[prim_idx.Pressure()] < 0.0) || (Primitive_j[prim_idx.Density()] < 0.0);
1905 
1906  su2double R = sqrt(fabs(Primitive_j[prim_idx.Density()]/Primitive_i[prim_idx.Density()]));
1907  su2double sq_vel = 0.0;
1908  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
1909  su2double RoeVelocity = (R * Primitive_j[iDim + prim_idx.Velocity()] +
1910  Primitive_i[iDim + prim_idx.Velocity()]) / (R+1);
1911  sq_vel += pow(RoeVelocity, 2);
1912  }
1913  su2double RoeEnthalpy = (R * Primitive_j[prim_idx.Enthalpy()] + Primitive_i[prim_idx.Enthalpy()]) / (R+1);
1914 
1915  const bool neg_sound_speed = ((Gamma-1)*(RoeEnthalpy-0.5*sq_vel) < 0.0);
1916  bool bad_recon = neg_sound_speed || neg_pres_or_rho_i || neg_pres_or_rho_j;
1917  bad_recon = nodes->UpdateNonPhysicalEdgeCounter(iEdge, bad_recon);
1918  counter_local += bad_recon;
1919 
1920  numerics->SetPrimitive(bad_recon? V_i : Primitive_i, bad_recon? V_j : Primitive_j);
1921  numerics->SetSecondary(bad_recon? S_i : Secondary_i, bad_recon? S_j : Secondary_j);
1922 
1923  }
1924 
1925  /*--- Roe Low Dissipation Scheme ---*/
1926 
1927  if (kind_dissipation != NO_ROELOWDISS) {
1928 
1929  numerics->SetDissipation(nodes->GetRoe_Dissipation(iPoint),
1930  nodes->GetRoe_Dissipation(jPoint));
1931 
1932  if (kind_dissipation == FD_DUCROS || kind_dissipation == NTS_DUCROS){
1933  numerics->SetSensor(nodes->GetSensor(iPoint),
1934  nodes->GetSensor(jPoint));
1935  }
1936  if (kind_dissipation == NTS || kind_dissipation == NTS_DUCROS){
1937  numerics->SetCoord(Coord_i, Coord_j);
1938  }
1939  }
1940 
1941  /*--- Compute the residual ---*/
1942 
1943  auto residual = numerics->ComputeResidual(config);
1944 
1945  /*--- Set the final value of the Roe dissipation coefficient ---*/
1946 
1947  if ((kind_dissipation != NO_ROELOWDISS) && (MGLevel != MESH_0)) {
1948  nodes->SetRoe_Dissipation(iPoint,numerics->GetDissipation());
1949  nodes->SetRoe_Dissipation(jPoint,numerics->GetDissipation());
1950  }
1951 
1952  /*--- Update residual value ---*/
1953 
1954  if (ReducerStrategy) {
1955  EdgeFluxes.SetBlock(iEdge, residual);
1956  if (implicit)
1957  Jacobian.SetBlocks(iEdge, residual.jacobian_i, residual.jacobian_j);
1958  }
1959  else {
1960  LinSysRes.AddBlock(iPoint, residual);
1961  LinSysRes.SubtractBlock(jPoint, residual);
1962 
1963  /*--- Set implicit computation ---*/
1964  if (implicit)
1965  Jacobian.UpdateBlocks(iEdge, iPoint, jPoint, residual.jacobian_i, residual.jacobian_j);
1966  }
1967 
1968  /*--- Viscous contribution. ---*/
1969 
1970  Viscous_Residual(iEdge, geometry, solver_container,
1971  numerics_container[VISC_TERM + omp_get_thread_num()*MAX_TERMS], config);
1972  }
1973  END_SU2_OMP_FOR
1974  } // end color loop
1975 
1976  FinalizeResidualComputation(geometry, pausePreacc, counter_local, config);
1977 }
1978 
1979 void CEulerSolver::ComputeConsistentExtrapolation(CFluidModel *fluidModel, unsigned short nDim,
1980  su2double *primitive, su2double *secondary) {
1981  const CEulerVariable::CIndices<unsigned short> prim_idx(nDim, 0);
1982  const su2double density = primitive[prim_idx.Density()];
1983  const su2double pressure = primitive[prim_idx.Pressure()];
1984  const su2double velocity2 = GeometryToolbox::SquaredNorm(nDim, &primitive[prim_idx.Velocity()]);
1985 
1986  fluidModel->SetTDState_Prho(pressure, density);
1987 
1988  primitive[prim_idx.Temperature()] = fluidModel->GetTemperature();
1989  primitive[prim_idx.Enthalpy()] = fluidModel->GetStaticEnergy() + pressure / density + 0.5*velocity2;
1990  primitive[prim_idx.SoundSpeed()] = fluidModel->GetSoundSpeed();
1991  secondary[0] = fluidModel->GetdPdrho_e();
1992  secondary[1] = fluidModel->GetdPde_rho();
1993 
1994 }
1995 
1996 void CEulerSolver::LowMachPrimitiveCorrection(CFluidModel *fluidModel, unsigned short nDim,
1997  su2double *primitive_i, su2double *primitive_j) {
1998  unsigned short iDim;
1999 
2000  su2double velocity2_i = 0.0;
2001  su2double velocity2_j = 0.0;
2002 
2003  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
2004  velocity2_i += pow(primitive_i[iDim+1], 2);
2005  velocity2_j += pow(primitive_j[iDim+1], 2);
2006  }
2007  su2double mach_i = sqrt(velocity2_i)/primitive_i[nDim+4];
2008  su2double mach_j = sqrt(velocity2_j)/primitive_j[nDim+4];
2009 
2010  su2double z = min(max(mach_i,mach_j),1.0);
2011  velocity2_i = 0.0;
2012  velocity2_j = 0.0;
2013  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
2014  su2double vel_i_corr = ( primitive_i[iDim+1] + primitive_j[iDim+1] )/2.0
2015  + z * ( primitive_i[iDim+1] - primitive_j[iDim+1] )/2.0;
2016  su2double vel_j_corr = ( primitive_i[iDim+1] + primitive_j[iDim+1] )/2.0
2017  + z * ( primitive_j[iDim+1] - primitive_i[iDim+1] )/2.0;
2018 
2019  velocity2_i += pow(vel_i_corr, 2);
2020  velocity2_j += pow(vel_j_corr, 2);
2021 
2022  primitive_i[iDim+1] = vel_i_corr;
2023  primitive_j[iDim+1] = vel_j_corr;
2024  }
2025 
2026  fluidModel->SetEnergy_Prho(primitive_i[nDim+1], primitive_i[nDim+2]);
2027  primitive_i[nDim+3]= fluidModel->GetStaticEnergy() + primitive_i[nDim+1]/primitive_i[nDim+2] + 0.5*velocity2_i;
2028 
2029  fluidModel->SetEnergy_Prho(primitive_j[nDim+1], primitive_j[nDim+2]);
2030  primitive_j[nDim+3]= fluidModel->GetStaticEnergy() + primitive_j[nDim+1]/primitive_j[nDim+2] + 0.5*velocity2_j;
2031 
2032 }
2033 
2034 void CEulerSolver::Source_Residual(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver_container,
2035  CNumerics **numerics_container, CConfig *config, unsigned short iMesh) {
2036 
2037  const bool implicit = config->GetKind_TimeIntScheme() == EULER_IMPLICIT;
2038  const bool viscous = config->GetViscous();
2039  const bool rotating_frame = config->GetRotating_Frame();
2040  const bool axisymmetric = config->GetAxisymmetric();
2041  const bool gravity = (config->GetGravityForce() == YES);
2042  const bool harmonic_balance = (config->GetTime_Marching() == TIME_MARCHING::HARMONIC_BALANCE);
2043  const bool body_force = config->GetBody_Force();
2044  const bool vorticity_confinement = config->GetVorticityConfinement();
2045  const bool ideal_gas = (config->GetKind_FluidModel() == STANDARD_AIR) ||
2046  (config->GetKind_FluidModel() == IDEAL_GAS);
2047  const bool rans = (config->GetKind_Turb_Model() != TURB_MODEL::NONE);
2048 
2049  /*--- Pick one numerics object per thread. ---*/
2050  CNumerics* numerics = numerics_container[SOURCE_FIRST_TERM + omp_get_thread_num()*MAX_TERMS];
2051 
2052  unsigned short iVar;
2053  unsigned long iPoint;
2054 
2055  if (body_force) {
2056 
2057  /*--- Loop over all points ---*/
2058  AD::StartNoSharedReading();
2059  SU2_OMP_FOR_STAT(omp_chunk_size)
2060  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nPointDomain; iPoint++) {
2061 
2062  /*--- Load the conservative variables ---*/
2063  numerics->SetConservative(nodes->GetSolution(iPoint),
2064  nodes->GetSolution(iPoint));
2065 
2066  /*--- Load the volume of the dual mesh cell ---*/
2067  numerics->SetVolume(geometry->nodes->GetVolume(iPoint));
2068 
2069  /*--- Compute the rotating frame source residual ---*/
2070  auto residual = numerics->ComputeResidual(config);
2071 
2072  /*--- Add the source residual to the total ---*/
2073  LinSysRes.AddBlock(iPoint, residual);
2074 
2075  }
2076  END_SU2_OMP_FOR
2077  AD::EndNoSharedReading();
2078  }
2079 
2080  if (rotating_frame) {
2081 
2082  /*--- Include the residual contribution from GCL due to the static
2083  mesh movement that is set for rotating frame. ---*/
2084 
2085  SetRotatingFrame_GCL(geometry, config);
2086 
2087  /*--- Loop over all points ---*/
2088  AD::StartNoSharedReading();
2089  SU2_OMP_FOR_DYN(omp_chunk_size)
2090  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nPointDomain; iPoint++) {
2091 
2092  /*--- Load the conservative variables ---*/
2093  numerics->SetConservative(nodes->GetSolution(iPoint),
2094  nodes->GetSolution(iPoint));
2095 
2096  /*--- Load the volume of the dual mesh cell ---*/
2097  numerics->SetVolume(geometry->nodes->GetVolume(iPoint));
2098 
2099  /*--- Compute the rotating frame source residual ---*/
2100  auto residual = numerics->ComputeResidual(config);
2101 
2102  /*--- Add the source residual to the total ---*/
2103  LinSysRes.AddBlock(iPoint, residual);
2104 
2105  /*--- Add the implicit Jacobian contribution ---*/
2106  if (implicit) Jacobian.AddBlock2Diag(iPoint, residual.jacobian_i);
2107 
2108  }
2109  END_SU2_OMP_FOR
2110  AD::EndNoSharedReading();
2111  }
2112 
2113  if (axisymmetric) {
2114 
2115  /*--- For viscous problems, we need an additional gradient. ---*/
2116  if (viscous) {
2117  ComputeAxisymmetricAuxGradients(geometry, config);
2118  }
2119 
2120  /*--- loop over points ---*/
2121  AD::StartNoSharedReading();
2122  SU2_OMP_FOR_DYN(omp_chunk_size)
2123  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nPointDomain; iPoint++) {
2124 
2125  /*--- Set solution ---*/
2126  numerics->SetConservative(nodes->GetSolution(iPoint), nodes->GetSolution(iPoint));
2127 
2128  /*--- Set control volume ---*/
2129  numerics->SetVolume(geometry->nodes->GetVolume(iPoint));
2130 
2131  /*--- Set y coordinate ---*/
2132  numerics->SetCoord(geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint), geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint));
2133 
2134  /*--- Set primitive variables for viscous terms and/or generalised source ---*/
2135  if (!ideal_gas || viscous) numerics->SetPrimitive(nodes->GetPrimitive(iPoint), nodes->GetPrimitive(iPoint));
2136 
2137  /*--- Set secondary variables for generalised source ---*/
2138  if (!ideal_gas) numerics->SetSecondary(nodes->GetSecondary(iPoint), nodes->GetSecondary(iPoint));
2139 
2140  if (viscous) {
2141 
2142  /*--- Set gradient of primitive variables ---*/
2143  numerics->SetPrimVarGradient(nodes->GetGradient_Primitive(iPoint), nodes->GetGradient_Primitive(iPoint));
2144 
2145  /*--- Set gradient of auxillary variables ---*/
2146  numerics->SetAuxVarGrad(nodes->GetAuxVarGradient(iPoint), nullptr);
2147 
2148  /*--- Set turbulence kinetic energy ---*/
2149  if (rans){
2150  CVariable* turbNodes = solver_container[TURB_SOL]->GetNodes();
2151  numerics->SetTurbKineticEnergy(turbNodes->GetSolution(iPoint,0), turbNodes->GetSolution(iPoint,0));
2152  }
2153  }
2154 
2155  /*--- Compute Source term Residual ---*/
2156  auto residual = numerics->ComputeResidual(config);
2157 
2158  /*--- Add Residual ---*/
2159  LinSysRes.AddBlock(iPoint, residual);
2160 
2161  /*--- Implicit part ---*/
2162  if (implicit)
2163  Jacobian.AddBlock2Diag(iPoint, residual.jacobian_i);
2164  }
2165  END_SU2_OMP_FOR
2166 
2167  AD::EndNoSharedReading();
2168  }
2169 
2170  AD::StartNoSharedReading();
2171 
2172  if (gravity) {
2173 
2174  /*--- loop over points ---*/
2175  SU2_OMP_FOR_DYN(omp_chunk_size)
2176  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nPointDomain; iPoint++) {
2177 
2178  /*--- Set solution ---*/
2179  numerics->SetConservative(nodes->GetSolution(iPoint), nodes->GetSolution(iPoint));
2180 
2181  /*--- Set control volume ---*/
2182  numerics->SetVolume(geometry->nodes->GetVolume(iPoint));
2183 
2184  /*--- Compute Source term Residual ---*/
2185  auto residual = numerics->ComputeResidual(config);
2186 
2187  /*--- Add Residual ---*/
2188  LinSysRes.AddBlock(iPoint, residual);
2189 
2190  }
2191  END_SU2_OMP_FOR
2192 
2193  }
2194 
2195  if (harmonic_balance) {
2196 
2197  /*--- loop over points ---*/
2198  SU2_OMP_FOR_STAT(omp_chunk_size)
2199  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nPointDomain; iPoint++) {
2200 
2201  /*--- Get control volume ---*/
2202  su2double Volume = geometry->nodes->GetVolume(iPoint);
2203 
2204  /*--- Get stored time spectral source term and add to residual ---*/
2205  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++) {
2206  LinSysRes(iPoint,iVar) += Volume * nodes->GetHarmonicBalance_Source(iPoint,iVar);
2207  }
2208  }
2209  END_SU2_OMP_FOR
2210  }
2211 
2212  if (vorticity_confinement) {
2213 
2214  CNumerics* second_numerics = numerics_container[SOURCE_SECOND_TERM + omp_get_thread_num()*MAX_TERMS];
2215 
2216  /*--- calculate and set the average volume ---*/
2217  const su2double AvgVolume = config->GetDomainVolume() / geometry->GetGlobal_nPointDomain();
2218  second_numerics->SetAvgVolume(AvgVolume);
2219 
2220  /*--- set vorticity magnitude as auxilliary variable ---*/
2221  SU2_OMP_FOR_STAT(omp_chunk_size)
2222  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nPoint; iPoint++) {
2223  const su2double VorticityMag = max(GeometryToolbox::Norm(3, nodes->GetVorticity(iPoint)), 1e-12);
2224  nodes->SetAuxVar(iPoint, 0, VorticityMag);
2225  }
2226  END_SU2_OMP_FOR
2227 
2228  /*--- calculate the gradient of the vorticity magnitude (AuxVarGradient) ---*/
2229  SetAuxVar_Gradient_GG(geometry, config);
2230 
2231  SU2_OMP_FOR_DYN(omp_chunk_size)
2232  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nPointDomain; iPoint++) {
2233  second_numerics->SetPrimitive(nodes->GetPrimitive(iPoint), nullptr);
2234  second_numerics->SetVorticity(nodes->GetVorticity(iPoint), nullptr);
2235  second_numerics->SetAuxVarGrad(nodes->GetAuxVarGradient(iPoint), nullptr);
2236  second_numerics->SetDistance(geometry->nodes->GetWall_Distance(iPoint), 0);
2237  second_numerics->SetVolume(geometry->nodes->GetVolume(iPoint));
2238  auto residual = second_numerics->ComputeResidual(config);
2239 
2240  LinSysRes.AddBlock(iPoint, residual);
2241 
2242  if (implicit) Jacobian.AddBlock2Diag(iPoint, residual.jacobian_i);
2243  }
2244  END_SU2_OMP_FOR
2245 
2246  }
2247 
2248  /*--- Check if a verification solution is to be computed. ---*/
2249 
2250  if ( VerificationSolution ) {
2251  if ( VerificationSolution->IsManufacturedSolution() ) {
2252 
2253  /*--- Get the physical time. ---*/
2254  su2double time = 0.0;
2255  if (config->GetTime_Marching() != TIME_MARCHING::STEADY) time = config->GetPhysicalTime();
2256 
2257  /*--- Loop over points ---*/
2258  SU2_OMP_FOR_DYN(omp_chunk_size)
2259  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nPointDomain; iPoint++) {
2260 
2261  /*--- Get control volume size. ---*/
2262  su2double Volume = geometry->nodes->GetVolume(iPoint);
2263 
2264  /*--- Get the current point coordinates. ---*/
2265  const su2double *coor = geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint);
2266 
2267  /*--- Get the MMS source term. ---*/
2268  vector<su2double> sourceMan(nVar,0.0);
2269  VerificationSolution->GetMMSSourceTerm(coor, time, sourceMan.data());
2270 
2271  /*--- Compute the residual for this control volume and subtract. ---*/
2272  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++) {
2273  LinSysRes(iPoint,iVar) -= sourceMan[iVar]*Volume;
2274  }
2275  }
2276  END_SU2_OMP_FOR
2277  }
2278  }
2279 
2280  AD::EndNoSharedReading();
2281 }

2317 void CEulerSolver::SetUndivided_Laplacian(CGeometry *geometry, const CConfig *config) {
2318 
2319  /*--- Loop domain points. ---*/
2320 
2321  SU2_OMP_FOR_DYN(omp_chunk_size)
2322  for (unsigned long iPoint = 0; iPoint < nPointDomain; ++iPoint) {
2323 
2324  const bool boundary_i = geometry->nodes->GetPhysicalBoundary(iPoint);
2325  const su2double Pressure_i = nodes->GetPressure(iPoint);
2326 
2327  /*--- Initialize. ---*/
2328  for (unsigned short iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
2329  nodes->SetUnd_Lapl(iPoint, iVar, 0.0);
2330 
2331  /*--- Loop over the neighbors of point i. ---*/
2332  for (auto jPoint : geometry->nodes->GetPoints(iPoint)) {
2333 
2334  bool boundary_j = geometry->nodes->GetPhysicalBoundary(jPoint);
2335 
2336  /*--- If iPoint is boundary it only takes contributions from other boundary points. ---*/
2337  if (boundary_i && !boundary_j) continue;
2338 
2339  /*--- Add solution differences, with correction for compressible flows which use the enthalpy. ---*/
2340 
2341  for (unsigned short iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
2342  nodes->AddUnd_Lapl(iPoint, iVar, nodes->GetSolution(jPoint,iVar)-nodes->GetSolution(iPoint,iVar));
2343 
2344  su2double Pressure_j = nodes->GetPressure(jPoint);
2345  nodes->AddUnd_Lapl(iPoint, nVar-1, Pressure_j-Pressure_i);
2346  }
2347  }
2348  END_SU2_OMP_FOR
2349 
2350  /*--- Correct the Laplacian across any periodic boundaries. ---*/
2351 
2352  for (unsigned short iPeriodic = 1; iPeriodic <= config->GetnMarker_Periodic()/2; iPeriodic++) {
2353  InitiatePeriodicComms(geometry, config, iPeriodic, PERIODIC_LAPLACIAN);
2354  CompletePeriodicComms(geometry, config, iPeriodic, PERIODIC_LAPLACIAN);
2355  }
2356 
2357  /*--- MPI parallelization ---*/
2358 
2359  InitiateComms(geometry, config, MPI_QUANTITIES::UNDIVIDED_LAPLACIAN);
2360  CompleteComms(geometry, config, MPI_QUANTITIES::UNDIVIDED_LAPLACIAN);
2361 
2362 }

2377 void CEulerSolver::SetUpwind_Ducros_Sensor(CGeometry *geometry, CConfig *config){
2378 
2379  SU2_OMP_FOR_STAT(omp_chunk_size)
2380  for (unsigned long iPoint = 0; iPoint < geometry->GetnPoint(); iPoint++) {
2381 
2382  /*---- Ducros sensor for iPoint and its neighbor points to avoid lower dissipation near shocks. ---*/
2383 
2384  su2double Ducros_i = 0.0;
2385  const auto nNeigh = geometry->nodes->GetnPoint(iPoint);
2386 
2387  for (unsigned short iNeigh = 0; iNeigh <= nNeigh; iNeigh++) {
2388 
2389  auto jPoint = iPoint; // when iNeigh == nNeigh
2390  if (iNeigh < nNeigh) jPoint = geometry->nodes->GetPoint(iPoint, iNeigh);
2391 
2392  /*---- Dilatation for jPoint ---*/
2393 
2394  su2double uixi=0.0;
2395  for(unsigned short iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++){
2396  uixi += nodes->GetGradient_Primitive(jPoint,iDim+1, iDim);
2397  }
2398 
2399  /*--- Compute norm of vorticity ---*/
2400 
2401  const su2double* Vorticity = nodes->GetVorticity(jPoint);
2402  su2double Omega = 0.0;
2403  for (unsigned short iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
2404  Omega += pow(Vorticity[iDim], 2);
2405  }
2406  Omega = sqrt(Omega);
2407 
2408  su2double Ducros_j = 0.0;
2409 
2410  if (config->GetKind_RoeLowDiss() == FD_DUCROS) {
2411  Ducros_j = -uixi / (fabs(uixi) + Omega + 1e-20);
2412  }
2413  else if (config->GetKind_RoeLowDiss() == NTS_DUCROS) {
2414  Ducros_j = pow(uixi,2.0) /(pow(uixi,2.0)+ pow(Omega,2.0) + 1e-20);
2415  }
2416  Ducros_i = max(Ducros_i, Ducros_j);
2417  }
2418 
2419  nodes->SetSensor(iPoint, Ducros_i);
2420  }
2421  END_SU2_OMP_FOR
2422 
2423  InitiateComms(geometry, config, MPI_QUANTITIES::SENSOR);
2424  CompleteComms(geometry, config, MPI_QUANTITIES::SENSOR);
2425 
2426 }

2445 void CEulerSolver::PrepareImplicitIteration(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver**, CConfig *config) {

2447  struct LowMachPrec {
2448  const CEulerSolver* solver;
2449  const bool active;
2450  su2activematrix matrix;
2451 
2452  LowMachPrec(const CEulerSolver* s, bool a, unsigned short nVar) : solver(s), active(a) {

2454  }

2457  solver->SetPreconditioner(config, iPoint, delta, matrix);
2458  return matrix;
2459  }
2460 
2461  } precond(this, config->Low_Mach_Preconditioning() || (config->GetKind_Upwind_Flow() == UPWIND::TURKEL), nVar);

2470 
2471 void CEulerSolver::SetPreconditioner(const CConfig *config, unsigned long iPoint,
2472  su2double delta, su2activematrix& preconditioner) const {
2473 
2474  unsigned short iDim, jDim, iVar, jVar;
2475  su2double local_Mach, rho, enthalpy, soundspeed, sq_vel;
2476  su2double *U_i = nullptr;
2477  su2double Beta_max = config->GetmaxTurkelBeta();
2478  su2double Mach_infty2, Mach_lim2, aux, parameter;
2479 
2480  /*--- Variables to calculate the preconditioner parameter Beta ---*/
2481  local_Mach = sqrt(nodes->GetVelocity2(iPoint))/nodes->GetSoundSpeed(iPoint);
2482 
2483  /*--- Weiss and Smith Preconditioning---*/
2484  Mach_infty2 = pow(config->GetMach(),2.0);
2485  Mach_lim2 = pow(0.00001,2.0);
2486  aux = max(pow(local_Mach,2.0),Mach_lim2);
2487  parameter = min(1.0, max(aux,Beta_max*Mach_infty2));
2488 
2489  U_i = nodes->GetSolution(iPoint);
2490 
2491  rho = U_i[0];
2492  enthalpy = nodes->GetEnthalpy(iPoint);
2493  soundspeed = nodes->GetSoundSpeed(iPoint);
2494  sq_vel = nodes->GetVelocity2(iPoint);
2495 
2496  /*---Calculating the inverse of the preconditioning matrix that multiplies the time derivative */
2497  preconditioner[0][0] = 0.5*sq_vel;
2498  preconditioner[0][nVar-1] = 1.0;
2499  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim ++)
2500  preconditioner[0][1+iDim] = -1.0*U_i[iDim+1]/rho;
2501 
2502  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim ++) {
2503  preconditioner[iDim+1][0] = 0.5*sq_vel*U_i[iDim+1]/rho;
2504  preconditioner[iDim+1][nVar-1] = U_i[iDim+1]/rho;
2505  for (jDim = 0; jDim < nDim; jDim ++) {
2506  preconditioner[iDim+1][1+jDim] = -1.0*U_i[jDim+1]/rho*U_i[iDim+1]/rho;
2507  }
2508  }
2509 
2510  preconditioner[nVar-1][0] = 0.5*sq_vel*enthalpy;
2511  preconditioner[nVar-1][nVar-1] = enthalpy;
2512  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim ++)
2513  preconditioner[nVar-1][1+iDim] = -1.0*U_i[iDim+1]/rho*enthalpy;
2514 
2515 
2516  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar ++ ) {
2517  for (jVar = 0; jVar < nVar; jVar ++ ) {
2518  preconditioner[iVar][jVar] = (parameter - 1.0) * ((Gamma-1.0)/(soundspeed*soundspeed))*preconditioner[iVar][jVar];
2519  if (iVar == jVar)
2520  preconditioner[iVar][iVar] += 1.0;
2521 
2522  preconditioner[iVar][jVar] *= delta;
2523  }
2524  }
2525 
2526 }
2527 
2528 void CEulerSolver::GetPower_Properties(CGeometry *geometry, CConfig *config, unsigned short iMesh, bool Output) {
2529 
2530  unsigned short iDim, iMarker, jMarker;
2531  unsigned long iVertex, iPoint;
2532  su2double *V_inlet = nullptr, *V_outlet = nullptr, Pressure, Temperature, Velocity[3], Vn,
2533  Velocity2, Density, Area, SoundSpeed, TotalPressure, Vel_Infty2, RamDrag,
2534  TotalTemperature, VelocityJet,
2535  Vel_Infty, MaxPressure, MinPressure, MFR, InfVel2;
2536  su2double DeltaPressure = 0.0, DeltaThrust = 0.0, DeltaTorque = 0.0;
2537  unsigned short iMarker_Inlet, iMarker_Outlet, nMarker_Inlet, nMarker_Outlet;
2538  string Inlet_TagBound, Outlet_TagBound;
2539  su2double DeltaPress = 0.0, DeltaTemp = 0.0, TotalPressRatio = 0.0, TotalTempRatio = 0.0, StaticPressRatio = 0.0, StaticTempRatio = 0.0,
2540  NetThrust = 0.0, GrossThrust = 0.0, Power = 0.0, MassFlow = 0.0, Mach = 0.0, Force = 0.0;
2541  bool ReverseFlow, Engine = false, Pair = true;
2542  su2double Vector[MAXNDIM] = {0.0};
2543 
2544  su2double Gas_Constant = config->GetGas_ConstantND();
2545  su2double Cp = Gas_Constant*Gamma / (Gamma-1.0);
2546  su2double Alpha = config->GetAoA()*PI_NUMBER/180.0;
2547  su2double Beta = config->GetAoS()*PI_NUMBER/180.0;
2548  bool write_heads = ((((config->GetInnerIter() % (config->GetScreen_Wrt_Freq(2)*40)) == 0) && (config->GetInnerIter()!= 0)) || (config->GetInnerIter() == 1));
2549  bool Evaluate_BC = ((((config->GetInnerIter() % (config->GetBc_Eval_Freq())) == 0)) || (config->GetInnerIter() == 1) || (config->GetDiscrete_Adjoint()));
2550 
2551  if ((config->GetnMarker_EngineInflow() != 0) || (config->GetnMarker_EngineExhaust() != 0)) Engine = true;
2552  if ((config->GetnMarker_ActDiskInlet() != 0) || (config->GetnMarker_ActDiskOutlet() != 0)) Engine = false;

2554 
2555  if (Engine) { nMarker_Inlet = config->GetnMarker_EngineInflow(); nMarker_Outlet = config->GetnMarker_EngineExhaust(); }
2556  else { nMarker_Inlet = config->GetnMarker_ActDiskInlet(); nMarker_Outlet = config->GetnMarker_ActDiskOutlet(); }
2557 
2558  /*--- Evaluate the MPI for the actuator disk IO ---*/
2559 
2560  if (Evaluate_BC) {
2561 
2562  auto *Inlet_MassFlow = new su2double [config->GetnMarker_All()]();
2563  auto *Inlet_ReverseMassFlow = new su2double [config->GetnMarker_All()]();
2564  auto *Inlet_Pressure = new su2double [config->GetnMarker_All()]();
2565  auto *Inlet_Mach = new su2double [config->GetnMarker_All()]();
2566  auto *Inlet_MaxPressure = new su2double [config->GetnMarker_All()]();
2567  auto *Inlet_MinPressure = new su2double [config->GetnMarker_All()]();
2568  auto *Inlet_TotalPressure = new su2double [config->GetnMarker_All()]();
2569  auto *Inlet_Temperature = new su2double [config->GetnMarker_All()]();
2570  auto *Inlet_TotalTemperature = new su2double [config->GetnMarker_All()]();
2571  auto *Inlet_Area = new su2double [config->GetnMarker_All()]();
2572  auto *Inlet_RamDrag = new su2double [config->GetnMarker_All()]();
2573  auto *Inlet_Force = new su2double [config->GetnMarker_All()]();
2574  auto *Inlet_Power = new su2double [config->GetnMarker_All()]();
2575  auto *Inlet_XCG = new su2double [config->GetnMarker_All()]();
2576  auto *Inlet_YCG = new su2double [config->GetnMarker_All()]();
2577  auto *Inlet_ZCG = new su2double [config->GetnMarker_All()]();
2578 
2579  auto *Outlet_MassFlow = new su2double [config->GetnMarker_All()]();
2580  auto *Outlet_Pressure = new su2double [config->GetnMarker_All()]();
2581  auto *Outlet_TotalPressure = new su2double [config->GetnMarker_All()]();
2582  auto *Outlet_Temperature = new su2double [config->GetnMarker_All()]();
2583  auto *Outlet_TotalTemperature = new su2double [config->GetnMarker_All()]();
2584  auto *Outlet_Area = new su2double [config->GetnMarker_All()]();
2585  auto *Outlet_GrossThrust = new su2double [config->GetnMarker_All()]();
2586  auto *Outlet_Force = new su2double [config->GetnMarker_All()]();
2587  auto *Outlet_Power = new su2double [config->GetnMarker_All()]();
2588 
2589  auto *Outlet_DeltaP = new su2double [config->GetnMarker_All()]();
2590  auto *Outlet_Thrust = new su2double [config->GetnMarker_All()]();
2591  auto *Outlet_Torque = new su2double [config->GetnMarker_All()]();
2592 
2593  /*--- Comute MassFlow, average temp, press, etc. ---*/
2594 
2595  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < config->GetnMarker_All(); iMarker++) {
2596 
2597  MinPressure = +1E10; MaxPressure = -1E10;
2598 
2599  if ((config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ACTDISK_INLET) ||
2600  (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ENGINE_INFLOW)) {
2601 
2602  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[iMarker]; iVertex++) {
2603 
2604  iPoint = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNode();
2605 
2606  if (geometry->nodes->GetDomain(iPoint)) {
2607 
2608  V_inlet = nodes->GetPrimitive(iPoint);
2609 
2610  geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNormal(Vector);
2611 
2612  Temperature = V_inlet[0];
2613  Pressure = V_inlet[nDim+1];
2614 
2615  Density = V_inlet[nDim+2];
2616  SoundSpeed = sqrt(Gamma*Pressure/Density);
2617 
2618  Velocity2 = 0.0; MassFlow = 0.0; Vel_Infty2 =0.0;
2619  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
2620  Velocity[iDim] = V_inlet[iDim+1];
2621  Velocity2 += Velocity[iDim]*Velocity[iDim];
2622  Vel_Infty2 += GetVelocity_Inf(iDim)*GetVelocity_Inf(iDim);
2623  MassFlow -= Vector[iDim]*Velocity[iDim]*Density;
2624  }
2625 
2626  Area = GeometryToolbox::Norm(nDim, Vector);
2627  Vn = 0.0; ReverseFlow = false;
2628  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) { Vn -= Velocity[iDim]*Vector[iDim]/Area; }
2629  if (Vn < 0.0) { ReverseFlow = true; }
2630 
2631  Vel_Infty = sqrt (Vel_Infty2);
2632  Mach = sqrt(Velocity2)/SoundSpeed;
2633  TotalPressure = Pressure * pow( 1.0 + Mach * Mach * 0.5 * (Gamma - 1.0), Gamma / (Gamma - 1.0));
2634  TotalTemperature = Temperature * (1.0 + Mach * Mach * 0.5 * (Gamma - 1.0));
2635  MinPressure = min(MinPressure, TotalPressure);
2636  MaxPressure = max(MaxPressure, TotalPressure);
2637 
2638  RamDrag = MassFlow * Vel_Infty;
2639 
2640  Inlet_MassFlow[iMarker] += MassFlow;
2641  Inlet_Pressure[iMarker] += Pressure*MassFlow;
2642  Inlet_Mach[iMarker] += Mach*MassFlow;
2643  Inlet_MinPressure[iMarker] = min (MinPressure, Inlet_MinPressure[iMarker]);
2644  Inlet_MaxPressure[iMarker] = max(MaxPressure, Inlet_MaxPressure[iMarker]);
2645  Inlet_TotalPressure[iMarker] += TotalPressure*MassFlow;
2646  Inlet_Temperature[iMarker] += Temperature*MassFlow;
2647  Inlet_TotalTemperature[iMarker] += TotalTemperature*MassFlow;
2648  Inlet_Area[iMarker] += Area;
2649  Inlet_RamDrag[iMarker] += RamDrag;
2650  Inlet_Power[iMarker] += MassFlow*Cp*TotalTemperature;
2651  if (ReverseFlow) Inlet_ReverseMassFlow[iMarker] += MassFlow;
2652 
2653  su2double Inlet_ForceX = -(Pressure - Pressure_Inf)*Vector[0] + MassFlow*Velocity[0];
2654  su2double Inlet_ForceY = -(Pressure - Pressure_Inf)*Vector[1] + MassFlow*Velocity[1];
2655  su2double Inlet_ForceZ = 0.0;
2656  if (nDim == 3) Inlet_ForceZ = -(Pressure - Pressure_Inf)*Vector[2] + MassFlow*Velocity[2];
2657  Inlet_Force[iMarker] += Inlet_ForceX*cos(Alpha)*cos(Beta) + Inlet_ForceY*sin(Beta) +Inlet_ForceZ*sin(Alpha)*cos(Beta);
2658 
2659  Inlet_XCG[iMarker] += geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint, 0)*Area;
2660  Inlet_YCG[iMarker] += geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint, 1)*Area;
2661  if (nDim == 3) Inlet_ZCG[iMarker] += geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint, 2)*Area;
2662 
2663  }
2664  }
2665 
2666  }
2667 
2668  if ((config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ACTDISK_OUTLET) ||
2669  (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ENGINE_EXHAUST)) {
2670 
2671  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[iMarker]; iVertex++) {
2672 
2673  iPoint = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNode();
2674 
2675  if (geometry->nodes->GetDomain(iPoint)) {
2676 
2677  V_outlet = nodes->GetPrimitive(iPoint);
2678 
2679  geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNormal(Vector);
2680 
2681  Temperature = V_outlet[0];
2682  Pressure = V_outlet[nDim+1];
2683 
2684  Density = V_outlet[nDim+2];
2685  SoundSpeed = sqrt(Gamma*Pressure/Density);
2686 
2687  Velocity2 = 0.0; MassFlow = 0.0; Vel_Infty2 = 0.0;
2688  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
2689  Velocity[iDim] = V_outlet[iDim+1];
2690  Velocity2 += Velocity[iDim]*Velocity[iDim];
2691  Vel_Infty2 += GetVelocity_Inf(iDim)*GetVelocity_Inf(iDim);
2692  MassFlow += Vector[iDim]*Velocity[iDim]*Density;
2693  }
2694 
2695  Vel_Infty = sqrt (Vel_Infty2);
2696  Area = GeometryToolbox::Norm(nDim, Vector);
2697  Mach = sqrt(Velocity2)/SoundSpeed;
2698  TotalPressure = Pressure * pow( 1.0 + Mach * Mach * 0.5 * (Gamma - 1.0), Gamma / (Gamma - 1.0));
2699  TotalTemperature = Temperature * (1.0 + Mach * Mach * 0.5 * (Gamma - 1.0));
2700  VelocityJet = sqrt(Velocity2) ;
2701  DeltaPressure = ActDisk_DeltaP_r[iMarker][iVertex];
2702  DeltaThrust = ActDisk_Thrust_r[iMarker][iVertex];
2703  DeltaTorque = ActDisk_Torque_r[iMarker][iVertex];
2704 
2705  GrossThrust = MassFlow * VelocityJet;
2706 
2707  Outlet_MassFlow[iMarker] += MassFlow;
2708  Outlet_Pressure[iMarker] += Pressure*MassFlow;
2709  Outlet_TotalPressure[iMarker] += TotalPressure*MassFlow;
2710  Outlet_Temperature[iMarker] += Temperature*MassFlow;
2711  Outlet_TotalTemperature[iMarker] += TotalTemperature*MassFlow;
2712  Outlet_Area[iMarker] += Area;
2713  Outlet_GrossThrust[iMarker] += GrossThrust;
2714  Outlet_Power[iMarker] += MassFlow*Cp*TotalTemperature;
2715  Outlet_DeltaP[iMarker] += DeltaPressure * Area;
2716  Outlet_Thrust[iMarker] += DeltaThrust * Area;
2717  Outlet_Torque[iMarker] += DeltaTorque * Area;
2718 
2719  su2double Outlet_ForceX = -(Pressure - Pressure_Inf)*Vector[0] -MassFlow*Velocity[0];
2720  su2double Outlet_ForceY = -(Pressure - Pressure_Inf)*Vector[1] -MassFlow*Velocity[1];
2721  su2double Outlet_ForceZ = 0.0;
2722  if (nDim == 3) Outlet_ForceZ = -(Pressure - Pressure_Inf)*Vector[2] -MassFlow*Velocity[2];
2723 
2724  if (nDim == 2) Outlet_Force[iMarker] += Outlet_ForceX*cos(Alpha) + Outlet_ForceY*sin(Alpha);
2725  if (nDim == 3) Outlet_Force[iMarker] += Outlet_ForceX*cos(Alpha)*cos(Beta) + Outlet_ForceY*sin(Beta) + Outlet_ForceZ*sin(Alpha)*cos(Beta);
2726 
2727  }
2728  }
2729 
2730  }
2731 
2732  }
2733 
2734  /*--- Copy to the appropriate structure ---*/
2735 
2736  auto *Inlet_MassFlow_Local = new su2double [nMarker_Inlet]();
2737  auto *Inlet_ReverseMassFlow_Local = new su2double [nMarker_Inlet]();
2738  auto *Inlet_Temperature_Local = new su2double [nMarker_Inlet]();
2739  auto *Inlet_TotalTemperature_Local = new su2double [nMarker_Inlet]();
2740  auto *Inlet_Pressure_Local = new su2double [nMarker_Inlet]();
2741  auto *Inlet_Mach_Local = new su2double [nMarker_Inlet]();
2742  auto *Inlet_MinPressure_Local = new su2double [nMarker_Inlet]();
2743  auto *Inlet_MaxPressure_Local = new su2double [nMarker_Inlet]();
2744  auto *Inlet_Power_Local = new su2double [nMarker_Inlet]();
2745  auto *Inlet_TotalPressure_Local = new su2double [nMarker_Inlet]();
2746  auto *Inlet_RamDrag_Local = new su2double [nMarker_Inlet]();
2747  auto *Inlet_Force_Local = new su2double [nMarker_Inlet]();
2748  auto *Inlet_Area_Local = new su2double [nMarker_Inlet]();
2749  auto *Inlet_XCG_Local = new su2double [nMarker_Inlet]();
2750  auto *Inlet_YCG_Local = new su2double [nMarker_Inlet]();
2751  auto *Inlet_ZCG_Local = new su2double [nMarker_Inlet]();
2752 
2753  auto *Inlet_MassFlow_Total = new su2double [nMarker_Inlet]();
2754  auto *Inlet_ReverseMassFlow_Total = new su2double [nMarker_Inlet]();
2755  auto *Inlet_Pressure_Total = new su2double [nMarker_Inlet]();
2756  auto *Inlet_Mach_Total = new su2double [nMarker_Inlet]();
2757  auto *Inlet_MinPressure_Total = new su2double [nMarker_Inlet]();
2758  auto *Inlet_MaxPressure_Total = new su2double [nMarker_Inlet]();
2759  auto *Inlet_Power_Total = new su2double [nMarker_Inlet]();
2760  auto *Inlet_TotalPressure_Total = new su2double [nMarker_Inlet]();
2761  auto *Inlet_Temperature_Total = new su2double [nMarker_Inlet]();
2762  auto *Inlet_TotalTemperature_Total = new su2double [nMarker_Inlet]();
2763  auto *Inlet_RamDrag_Total = new su2double [nMarker_Inlet]();
2764  auto *Inlet_Force_Total = new su2double [nMarker_Inlet]();
2765  auto *Inlet_Area_Total = new su2double [nMarker_Inlet]();
2766  auto *Inlet_XCG_Total = new su2double [nMarker_Inlet]();
2767  auto *Inlet_YCG_Total = new su2double [nMarker_Inlet]();
2768  auto *Inlet_ZCG_Total = new su2double [nMarker_Inlet]();
2769 
2770  auto *Outlet_MassFlow_Local = new su2double [nMarker_Outlet]();
2771  auto *Outlet_Pressure_Local = new su2double [nMarker_Outlet]();
2772  auto *Outlet_TotalPressure_Local = new su2double [nMarker_Outlet]();
2773  auto *Outlet_Temperature_Local = new su2double [nMarker_Outlet]();
2774  auto *Outlet_TotalTemperature_Local = new su2double [nMarker_Outlet]();
2775  auto *Outlet_GrossThrust_Local = new su2double [nMarker_Outlet]();
2776  auto *Outlet_Force_Local = new su2double [nMarker_Outlet]();
2777  auto *Outlet_Power_Local = new su2double [nMarker_Outlet]();
2778  auto *Outlet_Area_Local = new su2double [nMarker_Outlet]();
2779  auto *Outlet_DeltaP_Local = new su2double [nMarker_Outlet]();
2780  auto *Outlet_Thrust_Local = new su2double [nMarker_Outlet]();
2781  auto *Outlet_Torque_Local = new su2double [nMarker_Outlet]();
2782 
2783  auto *Outlet_MassFlow_Total = new su2double [nMarker_Outlet]();
2784  auto *Outlet_Pressure_Total = new su2double [nMarker_Outlet]();
2785  auto *Outlet_TotalPressure_Total = new su2double [nMarker_Outlet]();
2786  auto *Outlet_Temperature_Total = new su2double [nMarker_Outlet]();
2787  auto *Outlet_TotalTemperature_Total = new su2double [nMarker_Outlet]();
2788  auto *Outlet_GrossThrust_Total = new su2double [nMarker_Outlet]();
2789  auto *Outlet_Force_Total = new su2double [nMarker_Outlet]();
2790  auto *Outlet_Power_Total = new su2double [nMarker_Outlet]();
2791  auto *Outlet_Area_Total = new su2double [nMarker_Outlet]();
2792  auto *Outlet_DeltaP_Total = new su2double [nMarker_Outlet]();
2793  auto *Outlet_Thrust_Total = new su2double [nMarker_Outlet]();
2794  auto *Outlet_Torque_Total = new su2double [nMarker_Outlet]();
2795 
2796  /*--- Copy the values to the local array for MPI ---*/
2797 
2798  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < config->GetnMarker_All(); iMarker++) {
2799 
2800  if ((config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ACTDISK_INLET) || (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ENGINE_INFLOW)) {
2801  for (iMarker_Inlet = 0; iMarker_Inlet < nMarker_Inlet; iMarker_Inlet++) {
2802 
2803  if (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ACTDISK_INLET) Inlet_TagBound = config->GetMarker_ActDiskInlet_TagBound(iMarker_Inlet);
2804  if (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ENGINE_INFLOW) Inlet_TagBound = config->GetMarker_EngineInflow_TagBound(iMarker_Inlet);
2805 
2806  if (config->GetMarker_All_TagBound(iMarker) == Inlet_TagBound) {
2807  Inlet_MassFlow_Local[iMarker_Inlet] += Inlet_MassFlow[iMarker];
2808  Inlet_ReverseMassFlow_Local[iMarker_Inlet] += Inlet_ReverseMassFlow[iMarker];
2809  Inlet_Pressure_Local[iMarker_Inlet] += Inlet_Pressure[iMarker];
2810  Inlet_Mach_Local[iMarker_Inlet] += Inlet_Mach[iMarker];
2811  Inlet_MinPressure_Local[iMarker_Inlet] += Inlet_MinPressure[iMarker];
2812  Inlet_MaxPressure_Local[iMarker_Inlet] += Inlet_MaxPressure[iMarker];
2813  Inlet_TotalPressure_Local[iMarker_Inlet] += Inlet_TotalPressure[iMarker];
2814  Inlet_Temperature_Local[iMarker_Inlet] += Inlet_Temperature[iMarker];
2815  Inlet_TotalTemperature_Local[iMarker_Inlet] += Inlet_TotalTemperature[iMarker];
2816  Inlet_RamDrag_Local[iMarker_Inlet] += Inlet_RamDrag[iMarker];
2817  Inlet_Force_Local[iMarker_Inlet] += Inlet_Force[iMarker];
2818  Inlet_Power_Local[iMarker_Inlet] += Inlet_Power[iMarker];
2819  Inlet_Area_Local[iMarker_Inlet] += Inlet_Area[iMarker];
2820  Inlet_XCG_Local[iMarker_Inlet] += Inlet_XCG[iMarker];
2821  Inlet_YCG_Local[iMarker_Inlet] += Inlet_YCG[iMarker];
2822  if (nDim == 3) Inlet_ZCG_Local[iMarker_Inlet] += Inlet_ZCG[iMarker];
2823  }
2824 
2825  }
2826  }
2827 
2828  if ((config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ACTDISK_OUTLET) || (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ENGINE_EXHAUST)) {
2829  for (iMarker_Outlet= 0; iMarker_Outlet < nMarker_Outlet; iMarker_Outlet++) {
2830 
2831  if (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ACTDISK_OUTLET) Outlet_TagBound = config->GetMarker_ActDiskOutlet_TagBound(iMarker_Outlet);
2832  if (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ENGINE_EXHAUST) Outlet_TagBound = config->GetMarker_EngineExhaust_TagBound(iMarker_Outlet);
2833 
2834  if (config->GetMarker_All_TagBound(iMarker) == Outlet_TagBound) {
2835  Outlet_MassFlow_Local[iMarker_Outlet] += Outlet_MassFlow[iMarker];
2836  Outlet_Pressure_Local[iMarker_Outlet] += Outlet_Pressure[iMarker];
2837  Outlet_TotalPressure_Local[iMarker_Outlet] += Outlet_TotalPressure[iMarker];
2838  Outlet_Temperature_Local[iMarker_Outlet] += Outlet_Temperature[iMarker];
2839  Outlet_TotalTemperature_Local[iMarker_Outlet] += Outlet_TotalTemperature[iMarker];
2840  Outlet_GrossThrust_Local[iMarker_Outlet] += Outlet_GrossThrust[iMarker];
2841  Outlet_Force_Local[iMarker_Outlet] += Outlet_Force[iMarker];
2842  Outlet_Power_Local[iMarker_Outlet] += Outlet_Power[iMarker];
2843  Outlet_Area_Local[iMarker_Outlet] += Outlet_Area[iMarker];
2844  Outlet_DeltaP_Local[iMarker_Outlet] += Outlet_DeltaP[iMarker];
2845  Outlet_Thrust_Local[iMarker_Outlet] += Outlet_Thrust[iMarker];
2846  Outlet_Torque_Local[iMarker_Outlet] += Outlet_Torque[iMarker];
2847  }
2848 
2849  }
2850  }
2851 
2852  }
2853 
2854  /*--- Correct the min max values for the MPI ---*/
2855 
2856  bool ActDisk = false;
2857  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < config->GetnMarker_All(); iMarker++) {
2858  if ((config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ACTDISK_INLET) ||
2859  (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ENGINE_INFLOW)) { ActDisk = true; break; }
2860  }
2861 
2862  if (!ActDisk) {
2863  for (iMarker_Inlet = 0; iMarker_Inlet < nMarker_Inlet; iMarker_Inlet++) {
2864  Inlet_MinPressure_Local[iMarker_Inlet] = 1E10;
2865  Inlet_MaxPressure_Local[iMarker_Inlet] = -1E10;
2866  }
2867  }
2868 
2869  /*--- All the ranks to compute the total value ---*/
2870 
2871  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Inlet_MassFlow_Local, Inlet_MassFlow_Total, nMarker_Inlet, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
2872  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Inlet_ReverseMassFlow_Local, Inlet_ReverseMassFlow_Total, nMarker_Inlet, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
2873  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Inlet_Pressure_Local, Inlet_Pressure_Total, nMarker_Inlet, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
2874  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Inlet_Mach_Local, Inlet_Mach_Total, nMarker_Inlet, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
2875  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Inlet_MinPressure_Local, Inlet_MinPressure_Total, nMarker_Inlet, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_MIN, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
2876  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Inlet_MaxPressure_Local, Inlet_MaxPressure_Total, nMarker_Inlet, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_MAX, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
2877  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Inlet_TotalPressure_Local, Inlet_TotalPressure_Total, nMarker_Inlet, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
2878  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Inlet_Temperature_Local, Inlet_Temperature_Total, nMarker_Inlet, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
2879  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Inlet_TotalTemperature_Local, Inlet_TotalTemperature_Total, nMarker_Inlet, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
2880  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Inlet_RamDrag_Local, Inlet_RamDrag_Total, nMarker_Inlet, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
2881  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Inlet_Force_Local, Inlet_Force_Total, nMarker_Inlet, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
2882  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Inlet_Power_Local, Inlet_Power_Total, nMarker_Inlet, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
2883  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Inlet_Area_Local, Inlet_Area_Total, nMarker_Inlet, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
2884  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Inlet_XCG_Local, Inlet_XCG_Total, nMarker_Inlet, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
2885  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Inlet_YCG_Local, Inlet_YCG_Total, nMarker_Inlet, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
2886  if (nDim == 3) SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Inlet_ZCG_Local, Inlet_ZCG_Total, nMarker_Inlet, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
2887 
2888  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Outlet_MassFlow_Local, Outlet_MassFlow_Total, nMarker_Outlet, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
2889  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Outlet_Pressure_Local, Outlet_Pressure_Total, nMarker_Outlet, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
2890  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Outlet_TotalPressure_Local, Outlet_TotalPressure_Total, nMarker_Outlet, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
2891  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Outlet_Temperature_Local, Outlet_Temperature_Total, nMarker_Outlet, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
2892  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Outlet_TotalTemperature_Local, Outlet_TotalTemperature_Total, nMarker_Outlet, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
2893  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Outlet_GrossThrust_Local, Outlet_GrossThrust_Total, nMarker_Outlet, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
2894  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Outlet_Force_Local, Outlet_Force_Total, nMarker_Outlet, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
2895  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Outlet_Power_Local, Outlet_Power_Total, nMarker_Outlet, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
2896  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Outlet_Area_Local, Outlet_Area_Total, nMarker_Outlet, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
2897  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Outlet_DeltaP_Local, Outlet_DeltaP_Total, nMarker_Outlet, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
2898  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Outlet_Thrust_Local, Outlet_Thrust_Total, nMarker_Outlet, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
2899  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Outlet_Torque_Local, Outlet_Torque_Total, nMarker_Outlet, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
2900 
2901  /*--- Compute the value of the average surface temperature and pressure and
2902  set the value in the config structure for future use ---*/
2903 
2904  for (iMarker_Inlet = 0; iMarker_Inlet < nMarker_Inlet; iMarker_Inlet++) {
2905  if (Inlet_Area_Total[iMarker_Inlet] != 0.0) {
2906  Inlet_Pressure_Total[iMarker_Inlet] /= Inlet_MassFlow_Total[iMarker_Inlet];
2907  Inlet_Mach_Total[iMarker_Inlet] /= Inlet_MassFlow_Total[iMarker_Inlet];
2908  Inlet_TotalPressure_Total[iMarker_Inlet] /= Inlet_MassFlow_Total[iMarker_Inlet];
2909  Inlet_Temperature_Total[iMarker_Inlet] /= Inlet_MassFlow_Total[iMarker_Inlet];
2910  Inlet_TotalTemperature_Total[iMarker_Inlet] /= Inlet_MassFlow_Total[iMarker_Inlet];
2911  Inlet_XCG_Total[iMarker_Inlet] /= Inlet_Area_Total[iMarker_Inlet];
2912  Inlet_YCG_Total[iMarker_Inlet] /= Inlet_Area_Total[iMarker_Inlet];
2913  if (nDim == 3) Inlet_ZCG_Total[iMarker_Inlet] /= Inlet_Area_Total[iMarker_Inlet];
2914  }
2915  else {
2916  Inlet_Pressure_Total[iMarker_Inlet] = 0.0;
2917  Inlet_Mach_Total[iMarker_Inlet] = 0.0;
2918  Inlet_TotalPressure_Total[iMarker_Inlet] = 0.0;
2919  Inlet_Temperature_Total[iMarker_Inlet] = 0.0;
2920  Inlet_TotalTemperature_Total[iMarker_Inlet] = 0.0;
2921  Inlet_XCG_Total[iMarker_Inlet] = 0.0;
2922  Inlet_YCG_Total[iMarker_Inlet] = 0.0;
2923  if (nDim == 3) Inlet_ZCG_Total[iMarker_Inlet] = 0.0;
2924  }
2925 
2926  if (iMesh == MESH_0) {
2927

3133  su2double RefVel2 = 0.0; for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) RefVel2 += Velocity_Inf[iDim]*Velocity_Inf[iDim];
3134 
3135  su2double Factor = (0.5*RefDensity*RefArea*RefVel2);
3136  su2double Ref = config->GetDensity_Ref() * config->GetVelocity_Ref() * config->GetVelocity_Ref() * 1.0 * 1.0;
3137  su2double DmT = GetTotal_CD() * Factor;

3200  T2 = config->GetExhaust_TotalTemperature(Outlet_TagBound);

3298  cout << setprecision(3) << DeltaPress * config->GetPressure_Ref();
3299  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) cout << setprecision(3) << ". T in/out jump (K): ";
3300  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) cout << setprecision(3) << ". T in/out jump (R): ";
3301  cout << setprecision(3) << DeltaTemp * config->GetTemperature_Ref() <<"."<< endl;
3302  }
3303  else if (config->GetActDisk_Jump() == RATIO) {
3304  cout << setprecision(3) << "P in/out ratio: ";
3305  cout << setprecision(3) << StaticPressRatio;
3306  cout << setprecision(3) <<". T in/out ratio: ";
3307  cout << setprecision(3) << StaticTempRatio <<"."<< endl;
3308  }
3309  }
3310 
3311  cout << setprecision(1) << "\nProp. eff. (D-T.V/Shaft P): " << 100*mu_prop << "%. By-pass prop. eff. (NetT.V/Shaft P): " << 100*mu_bypass_prop << "%." << endl;
3312  cout << setprecision(1) << "Fan adiabatic eff.: " << 100*mu_isentropic << "%. Fan poly. eff.: " << 100*mu_polytropic << "%. Poly coeff. (n): " << setprecision(4) << poly_coeff << "." << endl;
3313 
3314  cout << endl;
3315 
3316 
3317  /*--- Forces descritption ---*/
3318 
3319  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) cout << setprecision(1) << "Ram Drag (N): ";
3320  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) cout << setprecision(1) << "Ram Drag (lbf): ";
3321  cout << (GrossThrust-NetThrust) * Ref;
3322 
3323  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) cout << setprecision(1) << ". Gross Thrust (N): ";
3324  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) cout << setprecision(1) << ". Gross Thrust (lbf): ";
3325  cout << -GrossThrust * Ref << "." << endl;
3326 
3327  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) cout << setprecision(1) << "Open surfaces Thurst (N): ";
3328  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) cout << setprecision(1) << "Open surfaces Thrust (lbf): ";
3329  cout<< setprecision(1) << Force * Ref << ". Open surfaces CT: " << setprecision(5) << -Force / Factor << "." << endl;
3330 
3331  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) cout << "Solid surfaces Drag (N): ";
3332  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) cout << "Solid surfaces Drag (lbf): ";
3333  cout << setprecision(1) << Solid_Drag * Ref << ". Solid surfaces CD: " << setprecision(5) << Solid_CD << "." << endl;
3334 
3335  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) cout << setprecision(1) <<"Net Thrust (N): ";
3336  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) cout << setprecision(1) << "Net Thrust (lbf): ";
3337  cout << setprecision(5) << -NetThrust * Ref << ". Net CT: " << CT;
3338 
3339  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) {
3340  cout << ". Power (W): ";
3341  cout << setprecision(1) << Power * Ref * config->GetVelocity_Ref() << "." << endl;
3342  }
3343  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) {
3344  cout << ". Power (HP): ";
3345  cout << setprecision(1) << Power * Ref * config->GetVelocity_Ref() / 550.0 << "." << endl;
3346  }
3347 
3348  if (config->GetKind_ActDisk() == BLADE_ELEMENT) {
3349  cout << setprecision(5);
3350  cout << "Thrust_BEM (N): " << config->GetActDiskOutlet_Thrust_BEM(Outlet_TagBound) << ". ";
3351  cout << "Torque_BEM (N-m): " << config->GetActDiskOutlet_Torque_BEM(Outlet_TagBound) << "." << endl;
3352  }
3353  }
3354 
3355  }
3356 
3357  if (write_heads && Output && !config->GetDiscrete_Adjoint()) cout << "-------------------------------------------------------------------------" << endl << endl;
3358 
3359  }
3360 
3361  }
3362 
3363  delete [] Outlet_MassFlow_Local;
3364  delete [] Outlet_Temperature_Local;
3365  delete [] Outlet_TotalTemperature_Local;
3366  delete [] Outlet_Pressure_Local;
3367  delete [] Outlet_TotalPressure_Local;
3368  delete [] Outlet_Area_Local;
3369  delete [] Outlet_GrossThrust_Local;
3370  delete [] Outlet_Force_Local;
3371  delete [] Outlet_Power_Local;
3372  delete [] Outlet_DeltaP_Local;
3373  delete [] Outlet_Thrust_Local;
3374  delete [] Outlet_Torque_Local;
3375

3377  delete [] Outlet_Temperature_Total;
3378  delete [] Outlet_TotalTemperature_Total;
3379  delete [] Outlet_Pressure_Total;
3380  delete [] Outlet_TotalPressure_Total;
3381  delete [] Outlet_Area_Total;
3382  delete [] Outlet_GrossThrust_Total;
3383  delete [] Outlet_Force_Total;
3384  delete [] Outlet_Power_Total;
3385  delete [] Outlet_DeltaP_Total;
3386  delete [] Outlet_Thrust_Total;
3387  delete [] Outlet_Torque_Total;

3390  delete [] Inlet_ReverseMassFlow_Local;
3391  delete [] Inlet_Temperature_Local;

3400  delete [] Inlet_Force_Local;
3401  delete [] Inlet_Power_Local;
3402  delete [] Inlet_XCG_Local;
3403  delete [] Inlet_YCG_Local;
3404  delete [] Inlet_ZCG_Local;
3405

3408  delete [] Inlet_Temperature_Total;
3409  delete [] Inlet_TotalTemperature_Total;

3456 
3457 void CEulerSolver::SetActDisk_BCThrust(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver_container,
3458  CConfig *config, unsigned short iMesh, bool Output) {
3459 
3460  su2double Massflow = 0.0 , Target_Massflow = 0.0, DragMinusThrust = 0.0 ,
3461  Target_DragMinusThrust = 0.0, Target_NetThrust = 0.0, BCThrust = 0.0, BCThrust_inc = 0.0;
3462  unsigned short iDim, iMarker;
3463  unsigned long iVertex, iPoint;
3464  su2double *V_inlet = nullptr, Pressure,
3465  Density, T0_Ti, ATerm, BTerm, LHS, RHS, RHS_PDelta, RHS_MDelta, F, DF_DLa, CTerm_, DTerm_,
3466  ETerm, La, La_old, TotalArea, To_Ti, DeltaT, Po_Pi, DeltaP, Area, Velocity_Normal,
3467  SoundSpeed2, Force_Normal,
3468  RefDensity, RefArea, RefVel2, Factor, Ref;
3469  unsigned short iter;
3470  string Marker_Tag;
3471  su2double Target_Force, Force, Target_Power, Power, NetThrust, BCThrust_old, Initial_BCThrust;
3472  bool ActDisk_Info;
3473  su2double MyBCThrust, BCThrust_Init;
3474  su2double Vector[MAXNDIM] = {0.0};
3475 
3476  su2double dNetThrust_dBCThrust = config->GetdNetThrust_dBCThrust();
3477  unsigned short Kind_ActDisk = config->GetKind_ActDisk();
3478  bool ratio = (config->GetActDisk_Jump() == RATIO);
3479  unsigned long Update_BCThrust = config->GetUpdate_BCThrust();
3480  unsigned long Iter_Fixed_NetThrust = config->GetIter_Fixed_NetThrust();
3481  unsigned long InnerIter = config->GetInnerIter();
3482  bool Update_BCThrust_Bool = false;
3483  bool restart = (config->GetRestart() || config->GetRestart_Flow());
3484  su2double Fan_Poly_Eff = config->GetFan_Poly_Eff();
3485  su2double PolyCoeff = 1.0/(1.0-((Gamma-1.0)/Gamma)/Fan_Poly_Eff);
3486 
3487  RefDensity = Density_Inf;
3488  RefArea = config->GetRefArea();
3489  RefVel2 = 0.0; for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) RefVel2 += Velocity_Inf[iDim]*Velocity_Inf[iDim];
3490 
3491  Factor = (0.5*RefDensity*RefArea*RefVel2);
3492  Ref = config->GetDensity_Ref() * config->GetVelocity_Ref() * config->GetVelocity_Ref() * 1.0 * 1.0;
3493 
3494  /*--- Blade element distribution is in input file. ---*/
3495  if (Kind_ActDisk == BLADE_ELEMENT) {
3496  SetActDisk_BEM_VLAD(geometry, solver_container, config, iMesh, Output);
3497  }
3498 
3499  /*--- Variable load distribution is in input file. ---*/
3500  if (Kind_ActDisk == VARIABLE_LOAD) {
3501  if(InnerIter == 0) {
3502  ReadActDisk_InputFile(geometry, solver_container, config, iMesh, Output);
3503  }
3504  }
3505  /*--- Delta P and delta T are inputs ---*/
3506 
3507  else if (Kind_ActDisk == VARIABLES_JUMP) {
3508 
3509  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < config->GetnMarker_All(); iMarker++) {
3510 
3511  if ((config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ACTDISK_INLET) ||
3512  (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ACTDISK_OUTLET)) {
3513 
3514  Marker_Tag = config->GetMarker_All_TagBound(iMarker);
3515 
3516  if (ratio) {
3517  if (config->GetMach() < 0.5) {
3518  DeltaP = config->GetActDisk_PressJump(Marker_Tag, 0);
3519  DeltaT = config->GetActDisk_TempJump(Marker_Tag, 0);
3520  }
3521  else {
3522  DeltaP = config->GetActDisk_PressJump(Marker_Tag, 1);
3523  DeltaT = config->GetActDisk_TempJump(Marker_Tag, 1);
3524  }
3525  }
3526  else {
3527  if (config->GetMach() < 0.5) {
3528  DeltaP = max(0.0, config->GetActDisk_PressJump(Marker_Tag, 0) / config->GetPressure_Ref());
3529  DeltaT = max(0.0, config->GetActDisk_TempJump(Marker_Tag, 0) / config->GetTemperature_Ref());
3530  }
3531  else {
3532  DeltaP = max(0.0, config->GetActDisk_PressJump(Marker_Tag, 1) / config->GetPressure_Ref());
3533  DeltaT = max(0.0, config->GetActDisk_TempJump(Marker_Tag, 1) / config->GetTemperature_Ref());
3534  }
3535  }
3536 
3537  /*--- Set the Delta P, Delta T values at each discrete point (uniform distribution) ---*/
3538 
3539  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[iMarker]; iVertex++) {
3540  iPoint = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNode();
3541  ActDisk_DeltaP[iMarker][iVertex] = DeltaP;
3542  ActDisk_DeltaT[iMarker][iVertex] = DeltaT;
3543  }
3544  }
3545  }
3546  }
3547 
3548  /*--- Iteration using BCThrust ---*/
3549 
3550  else {
3551 
3552  if (InnerIter == 0) BCThrust_Counter = 0;
3553 
3554  /*--- Only the fine mesh level should check the convergence criteria ---*/
3555 
3556  if ((iMesh == MESH_0) && Output) {
3557 
3558  /*--- Initialize the update flag to false ---*/
3559 
3560  Update_BCThrust_Bool = false;
3561 
3562  /*--- Reevaluate BCThrust at a fix number of iterations ---*/
3563 
3564  if ((InnerIter % Iter_Fixed_NetThrust == 0) && (InnerIter != 0)) {
3565  BCThrust_Counter++;
3566  Update_BCThrust_Bool = (BCThrust_Counter != 0) &&
3567  (BCThrust_Counter != 1) &&
3568  (BCThrust_Counter != Update_BCThrust) &&
3569  (BCThrust_Counter != Update_BCThrust + 2) &&
3570  (BCThrust_Counter != Update_BCThrust + 4);
3571  }
3572 
3573  /*--- Store the update boolean for use on other mesh levels in the MG ---*/
3574 
3575  config->SetUpdate_BCThrust_Bool(Update_BCThrust_Bool);
3576 
3577  }
3578 
3579  else {
3580  Update_BCThrust_Bool = config->GetUpdate_BCThrust_Bool();
3581  }
3582 
3583 
3584  /*--- If it is the first iteration, set the BCThrust to a meaning full target value,
3585  * this can be done at an initialization level, for the time being it is OK here ---*/
3586 
3587  if (InnerIter == 0) {
3588  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < config->GetnMarker_All(); iMarker++) {
3589  if ((config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ACTDISK_INLET) ||
3590  (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ACTDISK_OUTLET)) {
3591  Marker_Tag = config->GetMarker_All_TagBound(iMarker);
3592 
3593  if (Kind_ActDisk == NET_THRUST) {
3594  if (restart)
3595  Initial_BCThrust = config->GetInitial_BCThrust() / Ref;
3596  else {
3597  if (config->GetMach() < 0.5) Initial_BCThrust = fabs( config->GetActDisk_PressJump(Marker_Tag, 0) / Ref);
3598  else Initial_BCThrust = fabs( config->GetActDisk_PressJump(Marker_Tag, 1) / Ref);
3599  }
3600  config->SetActDisk_BCThrust(Marker_Tag, Initial_BCThrust);
3601  config->SetActDisk_BCThrust_Old(Marker_Tag, Initial_BCThrust);
3602  }
3603 
3604  if (Kind_ActDisk == BC_THRUST) {
3605  if (restart)
3606  Initial_BCThrust = config->GetInitial_BCThrust() / Ref;
3607  else {
3608  if (config->GetMach() < 0.5) Initial_BCThrust = fabs( config->GetActDisk_PressJump(Marker_Tag, 0) / Ref);
3609  else Initial_BCThrust = fabs( config->GetActDisk_PressJump(Marker_Tag, 1) / Ref);
3610  }
3611  config->SetActDisk_BCThrust(Marker_Tag, Initial_BCThrust);
3612  config->SetActDisk_BCThrust_Old(Marker_Tag, Initial_BCThrust);
3613  }
3614 
3615  if (Kind_ActDisk == POWER) {
3616  Initial_BCThrust = config->GetInitial_BCThrust() / Ref;
3617  config->SetActDisk_BCThrust(Marker_Tag, Initial_BCThrust);
3618  config->SetActDisk_BCThrust_Old(Marker_Tag, Initial_BCThrust);
3619  }
3620 
3621  if (Kind_ActDisk == DRAG_MINUS_THRUST) {
3622  Initial_BCThrust = config->GetInitial_BCThrust() / Ref;
3623  config->SetActDisk_BCThrust(Marker_Tag, Initial_BCThrust);
3624  config->SetActDisk_BCThrust_Old(Marker_Tag, Initial_BCThrust);
3625  }
3626 
3627  if (Kind_ActDisk == MASSFLOW) {
3628  Initial_BCThrust = config->GetInitial_BCThrust() / Ref;
3629  config->SetActDisk_BCThrust(Marker_Tag, Initial_BCThrust);
3630  config->SetActDisk_BCThrust_Old(Marker_Tag, Initial_BCThrust);
3631  }
3632 
3633  }
3634  }
3635  }
3636 
3637  /*--- Typical iteration to set the value of BC Thrust at each actuator disk ---*/
3638 
3639  if (Update_BCThrust_Bool && Output) {
3640 
3641  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < config->GetnMarker_All(); iMarker++) {
3642 
3643  if ((config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ACTDISK_INLET) ||
3644  (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ACTDISK_OUTLET)) {
3645 
3646  Marker_Tag = config->GetMarker_All_TagBound(iMarker);
3647 
3648  if (Kind_ActDisk == NET_THRUST) {
3649 
3650  if (config->GetMach() < 0.5) Target_NetThrust = fabs( config->GetActDisk_PressJump(Marker_Tag, 0) / Ref);
3651  else Target_NetThrust = fabs( config->GetActDisk_PressJump(Marker_Tag, 1) / Ref);
3652  NetThrust = config->GetActDisk_NetThrust(Marker_Tag);
3653  BCThrust_old = config->GetActDisk_BCThrust_Old(Marker_Tag);
3654  BCThrust_inc = (1.0/dNetThrust_dBCThrust)*(Target_NetThrust - NetThrust);
3655 
3656  if (iMesh == MESH_0) BCThrust = max(0.0,(BCThrust_old + BCThrust_inc));
3657  else BCThrust = config->GetActDisk_BCThrust(Marker_Tag);
3658 
3659  if (iMesh == MESH_0) {
3660  config->SetActDisk_BCThrust(Marker_Tag, BCThrust);
3661  BCThrust_Init = BCThrust*Ref;
3662  config->SetInitial_BCThrust(BCThrust_Init);
3663  }
3664 
3665  }
3666 
3667  if (Kind_ActDisk == BC_THRUST) {
3668 
3669  if (config->GetMach() < 0.5) Target_Force = fabs( config->GetActDisk_PressJump(Marker_Tag, 0) / Ref);
3670  else Target_Force = fabs( config->GetActDisk_PressJump(Marker_Tag, 1) / Ref);
3671  Force = -config->GetActDisk_Force(Marker_Tag);
3672  BCThrust_old = config->GetActDisk_BCThrust_Old(Marker_Tag);
3673  BCThrust_inc = (1.0/dNetThrust_dBCThrust)*(Target_Force - Force);
3674 
3675  if (iMesh == MESH_0) BCThrust = max(0.0,(BCThrust_old + BCThrust_inc));
3676  else BCThrust = config->GetActDisk_BCThrust(Marker_Tag);
3677 
3678  if (iMesh == MESH_0) {
3679  config->SetActDisk_BCThrust(Marker_Tag, BCThrust);
3680  BCThrust_Init = BCThrust*Ref;
3681  config->SetInitial_BCThrust(BCThrust_Init);
3682  }
3683 
3684  }
3685 
3686  if (Kind_ActDisk == POWER) {
3687 
3688  if (config->GetMach() < 0.5) Target_Power = fabs( config->GetActDisk_PressJump(Marker_Tag, 0) / (Ref * config->GetVelocity_Ref() / 550.0));
3689  else Target_Power = fabs( config->GetActDisk_PressJump(Marker_Tag, 1) / (Ref * config->GetVelocity_Ref() / 550.0));
3690  Power = config->GetActDisk_Power(Marker_Tag);
3691  BCThrust_old = config->GetActDisk_BCThrust_Old(Marker_Tag);
3692  BCThrust_inc = (1.0/dNetThrust_dBCThrust)*(Target_Power - Power);
3693 
3694  if (iMesh == MESH_0) BCThrust = max(0.0,(BCThrust_old + BCThrust_inc));
3695  else BCThrust = config->GetActDisk_BCThrust(Marker_Tag);
3696 
3697  if (iMesh == MESH_0) {
3698  config->SetActDisk_BCThrust(Marker_Tag, BCThrust);
3699  BCThrust_Init = BCThrust*Ref;
3700  config->SetInitial_BCThrust(BCThrust_Init);
3701  }
3702 
3703  }
3704 
3705  if (Kind_ActDisk == DRAG_MINUS_THRUST) {
3706 
3707  if (config->GetMach() < 0.5) Target_DragMinusThrust = -fabs(config->GetActDisk_PressJump(Marker_Tag, 0)) * Factor;
