3708  else Target_DragMinusThrust = -fabs(config->GetActDisk_PressJump(Marker_Tag, 1)) * Factor;
3709  DragMinusThrust = GetTotal_CD() * Factor;
3710  BCThrust_old = config->GetActDisk_BCThrust_Old(Marker_Tag);
3711  BCThrust_inc = -(1.0/dNetThrust_dBCThrust)*(Target_DragMinusThrust - DragMinusThrust);
3712 
3713  if (iMesh == MESH_0) BCThrust = max(0.0,(BCThrust_old + BCThrust_inc));
3714  else BCThrust = config->GetActDisk_BCThrust(Marker_Tag);
3715 
3716  if (iMesh == MESH_0) {
3717  config->SetActDisk_BCThrust(Marker_Tag, BCThrust);
3718  BCThrust_Init = BCThrust*Ref;
3719  config->SetInitial_BCThrust(BCThrust_Init);
3720  }
3721 
3722  }
3723 
3724  if (Kind_ActDisk == MASSFLOW) {
3725 
3726  if (config->GetMach() < 0.5) {
3727  Target_Massflow = fabs(config->GetActDisk_PressJump(Marker_Tag, 0) / (config->GetDensity_Ref() * config->GetVelocity_Ref()));
3728  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) Target_Massflow /= 32.174;
3729  }
3730  else {
3731  Target_Massflow = fabs(config->GetActDisk_PressJump(Marker_Tag, 1) / (config->GetDensity_Ref() * config->GetVelocity_Ref()));
3732  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) Target_Massflow /= 32.174;
3733  }
3734 
3735  Massflow = config->GetActDisk_MassFlow(Marker_Tag);
3736  BCThrust_old = config->GetActDisk_BCThrust_Old(Marker_Tag);
3737  BCThrust_inc = (1.0/dNetThrust_dBCThrust)*(Target_Massflow - Massflow);
3738  if (iMesh == MESH_0) BCThrust = max(0.0,(BCThrust_old + BCThrust_inc));
3739  else BCThrust = config->GetActDisk_BCThrust(Marker_Tag);
3740  if (iMesh == MESH_0) {
3741  config->SetActDisk_BCThrust(Marker_Tag, BCThrust);
3742  BCThrust_Init = BCThrust*Ref;
3743  config->SetInitial_BCThrust(BCThrust_Init);
3744  }
3745 
3746  }
3747 
3748  }
3749 
3750  }
3751 
3752  /*--- After a complete update of BC_Thrust
3753  update the value of BC Thrust (old) for future iterations ---*/
3754 
3755  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < config->GetnMarker_All(); iMarker++) {
3756  if ((config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ACTDISK_INLET) ||
3757  (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ACTDISK_OUTLET)) {
3758  Marker_Tag = config->GetMarker_All_TagBound(iMarker);
3759  if ((Kind_ActDisk == NET_THRUST) || (Kind_ActDisk == BC_THRUST) ||
3760  (Kind_ActDisk == POWER) || (Kind_ActDisk == DRAG_MINUS_THRUST) ||
3761  (Kind_ActDisk == MASSFLOW)) {
3762  BCThrust = config->GetActDisk_BCThrust(Marker_Tag);
3763  config->SetActDisk_BCThrust_Old(Marker_Tag, BCThrust);
3764  }
3765  }
3766  }
3767  }
3768 
3769  /*--- Evaluate the pressure jump at each node using the total thrust ---*/
3770 
3771  if ((Update_BCThrust_Bool && Output) || (InnerIter == 0)) {
3772 
3773  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < config->GetnMarker_All(); iMarker++) {
3774 
3775  if ((config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ACTDISK_INLET) ||
3776  (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ACTDISK_OUTLET)) {
3777 
3778  Marker_Tag = config->GetMarker_All_TagBound(iMarker);
3779  RefDensity = Density_Inf;
3780  RefArea = config->GetRefArea();
3781  RefVel2 = 0.0; for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) RefVel2 += Velocity_Inf[iDim]*Velocity_Inf[iDim];
3782 
3783  Factor = (0.5*RefDensity*RefArea*RefVel2);
3784  Ref = config->GetDensity_Ref() * config->GetVelocity_Ref() * config->GetVelocity_Ref() * 1.0 * 1.0;
3785  BCThrust = config->GetActDisk_BCThrust(Marker_Tag);
3786 
3787  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[iMarker]; iVertex++) {
3788 
3789  iPoint = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNode();
3790 
3791  if (geometry->nodes->GetDomain(iPoint)) {
3792 
3793  geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNormal(Vector);
3794 
3795  if (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ACTDISK_INLET) {
3796  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) { Vector[iDim] = -Vector[iDim]; }
3797  }
3798 
3799  Area = GeometryToolbox::Norm(nDim, Vector);
3800 
3801  /*--- Use the inlet state to compute the Pressure and Temperature jumps ---*/
3802 
3803  if (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ACTDISK_INLET)
3804  V_inlet = nodes->GetPrimitive(iPoint);
3805  if (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ACTDISK_OUTLET)
3806  V_inlet = DonorPrimVar[iMarker][iVertex];
3807 
3808  Density = V_inlet[nDim+2];
3809  Pressure = V_inlet[nDim+1];
3810  SoundSpeed2 = Pressure*Gamma/Density;
3811  TotalArea = config->GetActDisk_Area(Marker_Tag);
3812  Force_Normal = Area*(BCThrust/TotalArea);
3813 
3814 
3815  Velocity_Normal = 0.0;
3816  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
3817  Velocity_Normal += V_inlet[iDim+1]*Vector[iDim]/Area;
3818  }
3819 
3820 
3821  if (Velocity_Normal > EPS) {
3822 
3823  /*--- Ratio of the total temperature to the temperature at the inflow ---*/
3824 
3825  T0_Ti = 1.0 + ((Gamma-1.0)/SoundSpeed2)*(0.5*Velocity_Normal*Velocity_Normal + Force_Normal/(Density*Area));
3826 
3827 
3828  ATerm = 2.0*T0_Ti/(Gamma+1.0);
3829  BTerm = 0.5*(Gamma+1.0)/(Gamma-1.0);
3830  LHS = fabs(Velocity_Normal)/(sqrt(SoundSpeed2)*pow(ATerm,BTerm));
3831 
3832  CTerm_ = (PolyCoeff-1.0)/(PolyCoeff+1.0);
3833  DTerm_ = 1.0/(PolyCoeff-1.0);
3834 
3835  La = EPS; La_old = EPS;
3836 
3837  for (iter = 0; iter < 100; iter++) {
3838 
3839  ETerm = ((1.0-CTerm_*La*La)/(1.0-CTerm_+EPS));
3840 
3841  RHS = La*pow(ETerm, DTerm_);
3842 
3843  ETerm = ((1.0-CTerm_*(La+1E-6)*(La+1E-6))/(1.0-CTerm_+EPS));
3844  RHS_PDelta = (La+1E-6)*pow(ETerm, DTerm_);
3845 
3846  ETerm = ((1.0-CTerm_*(La-1E-6)*(La-1E-6))/(1.0-CTerm_+EPS));
3847  RHS_MDelta = (La-1E-6)*pow(ETerm, DTerm_);
3848 
3849  /*--- Objective function and finitte differences derivative ---*/
3850 
3851  F = RHS - LHS;
3852  DF_DLa = (RHS_PDelta - RHS_MDelta)/2E-6;
3853 
3854  /*--- Newton's step ---*/
3855 
3856  La_old = La;
3857  La = La_old - 0.75*(F/DF_DLa);
3858 
3859  if (fabs(F) < 1E-10) break;
3860 
3861  }
3862 
3863  if (iter == 99) cout << "The laval number evaluation is not converging." << endl;
3864 
3865  /*--- Laval is bounded ---*/
3866 
3867  La = min(La, sqrt(6.0)); La = max(La, 0.0);
3868 
3869  To_Ti = max(1.0, T0_Ti*(1.0-CTerm_*La*La));
3870  ActDisk_DeltaT[iMarker][iVertex] = To_Ti;
3871 
3872  Po_Pi = max(1.0, pow(To_Ti, PolyCoeff*DTerm_));
3873  ActDisk_DeltaP[iMarker][iVertex] = Po_Pi;
3874 
3875  }
3876  else {
3877  ActDisk_DeltaT[iMarker][iVertex] = 1.0;
3878  ActDisk_DeltaP[iMarker][iVertex] = 1.0;
3879  }
3880  }
3881  }
3882  }
3883  }
3884  }
3885  }
3886 
3887  /*--- Broadcast some information to the master node ---*/
3888 
3889  ActDisk_Info = false;
3890  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < config->GetnMarker_All(); iMarker++) {
3891  if ((config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ACTDISK_INLET) ||
3892  (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ACTDISK_OUTLET)) {
3893  ActDisk_Info = true;
3894  }
3895  }
3896  if (!ActDisk_Info) config->SetInitial_BCThrust(0.0);
3897 
3898  MyBCThrust = config->GetInitial_BCThrust();
3899  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(&MyBCThrust, &BCThrust, 1, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_MAX, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
3900  config->SetInitial_BCThrust(BCThrust);
3901 
3902 }
3903 
3904 void CEulerSolver::ReadActDisk_InputFile(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver_container,
3905  CConfig *config, unsigned short iMesh, bool Output) {
3906  /*--- Input file provides force coefficients distributions along disk radius. Initialization
3907  necessary only at initial iteration. ---*/
3908 
3909  unsigned short iDim, iMarker;
3910  unsigned long iVertex, iPoint;
3911  string Marker_Tag;
3912  int iRow, nRow, iEl;
3913  std::vector<su2double> rad_v, dCt_v, dCp_v, dCr_v;
3914  su2double r_ = 0.0, r[MAXNDIM] = {0.0},
3915  AD_Center[MAXNDIM] = {0.0}, AD_Axis[MAXNDIM] = {0.0}, AD_Radius = 0.0, AD_J = 0.0;
3916  std::vector<su2double> Fa, Ft, Fr;
3917  su2double Fx = 0.0, Fy = 0.0, Fz = 0.0,
3918  Fx_inf = 0.0, Fy_inf = 0.0, Fz_inf = 0.0, Fx_sup = 0.0, Fy_sup = 0.0, Fz_sup = 0.0, h = 0.0;
3919  const su2double *P = nullptr;
3920 
3921  su2double Dens_FreeStream = config->GetDensity_FreeStream();
3922  const su2double *Vel_FreeStream = config->GetVelocity_FreeStream();
3923 
3924  /*--- Get the file name that contains the propeller data. ---*/
3925  string ActDisk_filename = config->GetActDisk_FileName();
3926  /*--- Loop over the markers. ---*/
3927  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < config->GetnMarker_All(); iMarker++) {
3928  if ((config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ACTDISK_INLET) ||
3929  (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ACTDISK_OUTLET)) {
3930 
3931  /*--- Get the marker tag of the current BC marker. ---*/
3932  Marker_Tag = config->GetMarker_All_TagBound(iMarker);
3933  ifstream ActDisk_file;
3934  /*--- Open the file that contains the propeller data. ---*/
3935  ActDisk_file.open(ActDisk_filename.data(), ios::in);
3936 
3937  /*--- Error message if the propeller data input file fails to open. ---*/
3938  if (ActDisk_file.fail()) SU2_MPI::Error("Unable to open Actuator Disk Input File", CURRENT_FUNCTION);
3939 
3940  string text_line, text_line_appo, name[2];
3941  string::size_type position;
3942 
3943  while (getline (ActDisk_file, text_line)) {
3944  /*--- Check if there is the "MARKER_ACTDISK=" string in the current line. If not keep on reading. ---*/
3945  position = text_line.find ("MARKER_ACTDISK=");
3946  if(position == string::npos){continue;}
3947  text_line.erase (0,15);
3948  /*--- Read the names of the two faces of the actuator disk and assign them to the name[] array. ---*/
3949  istringstream NameID(text_line);
3950  for (int i = 0; i < 2; i++){
3951  NameID >> name[i];
3952  }
3953 
3954  /*--- Check if the propeller data correspond to the actual BC marker. ---*/
3955  if (Marker_Tag == name[0] || Marker_Tag == name[1]){
3956  /*--- Read and assign the coordinates of the actuator disk center. ---*/
3957  getline (ActDisk_file, text_line_appo);
3958  text_line_appo.erase (0,7);
3959  istringstream C_value(text_line_appo);
3960  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++){
3961  C_value >> AD_Center[iDim];
3962  }
3963 
3964  /*--- Read and assign the components of the actuator disk axis versor pointing backward. ---*/
3965  getline (ActDisk_file, text_line_appo);
3966  text_line_appo.erase (0,5);
3967  istringstream axis_value(text_line_appo);
3968  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++){
3969  axis_value >> AD_Axis[iDim];
3970  }
3971 
3972  /*--- Read and assign the value of the actuator disk radius. ---*/
3973  getline (ActDisk_file, text_line_appo);
3974  text_line_appo.erase (0,7);
3975  istringstream R_value(text_line_appo);
3976  R_value >> AD_Radius;
3977 
3978  /*--- Read and assign the value of the actuator disk advance ratio. ---*/
3979  getline (ActDisk_file, text_line_appo);
3980  text_line_appo.erase (0,10);
3981  istringstream J_value(text_line_appo);
3982  J_value >> AD_J;
3983 
3984  /*--- Read and assign the number of radial stations contained in the propeller data file. ---*/
3985  getline (ActDisk_file, text_line_appo);
3986  text_line_appo.erase (0,5);
3987  istringstream row_value(text_line_appo);
3988  row_value >> nRow;
3989 
3990  /*--- Assign the vectors dimension. ---*/
3991  rad_v.resize(nRow);
3992  dCt_v.resize(nRow);
3993  dCp_v.resize(nRow);
3994  dCr_v.resize(nRow);
3995 
3996  Fa.resize(nRow);
3997  Ft.resize(nRow);
3998  Fr.resize(nRow);
3999 
4000  /*--- Read and assign the values of the non-dimensional radius, thrust coefficient, power coefficient
4001  and radial force coefficient. ---*/
4002  getline (ActDisk_file, text_line_appo);
4003  for (iRow = 0; iRow < nRow; iRow++){
4004  getline (ActDisk_file, text_line_appo);
4005  istringstream row_val_value(text_line_appo);
4006  row_val_value >> rad_v[iRow] >> dCt_v[iRow] >> dCp_v[iRow] >> dCr_v[iRow];
4007  }
4008 
4009  /*--- Set the actuator disk radius value, center coordiantes values and axis coordinates values. ---*/
4010  ActDisk_R(iMarker) = AD_Radius;
4011  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++){
4012  ActDisk_C(iMarker, iDim) = AD_Center[iDim];
4013  ActDisk_Axis(iMarker, iDim) = AD_Axis[iDim];
4014  }
4015 
4016  /*--- If the first radial station corresponds to the actuator disk center, the radial and tangential forces
4017  per unit area (Fr and Ft) are equal to zero, while the axial force per unit area (Fa) is computed using
4018  a linear interpolation in order to avoid a mathematical singularity at actuator disk center. ---*/
4019  if (rad_v[0] == 0.0){
4020  Fa[0] = (((2*Dens_FreeStream*pow(Vel_FreeStream[0],2))/
4021  (pow(AD_J,2)*PI_NUMBER))*((dCt_v[1] - dCt_v[0])/rad_v[1])) / config->GetPressure_Ref();
4022  Ft[0] = 0.0;
4023  Fr[0] = 0.0;
4024  }
4025  else {
4026  Fa[0] = (dCt_v[0]*(2*Dens_FreeStream*pow(Vel_FreeStream[0],2))/
4027  (pow(AD_J,2)*PI_NUMBER*rad_v[0])) / config->GetPressure_Ref();
4028  Ft[0] = (dCp_v[0]*(2*Dens_FreeStream*pow(Vel_FreeStream[0],2))/
4029  ((AD_J*PI_NUMBER*rad_v[0])*(AD_J*PI_NUMBER*rad_v[0]))) / config->GetPressure_Ref();
4030  Fr[0] = (dCr_v[0]*(2*Dens_FreeStream*pow(Vel_FreeStream[0],2))/
4031  (pow(AD_J,2)*PI_NUMBER*rad_v[0])) / config->GetPressure_Ref();
4032  }
4033 
4034  /*--- Loop over the radial stations. Computation of Fa (axial force per unit area), Ft (tangential force per unit area)
4035  and Fr (radial force per unit area).
4036  These equations are not valid if the freestream velocity is equal to zero (hovering condition not enabled yet). ---*/
4037  for (iEl = 1; iEl < nRow; iEl++){
4038  Fa[iEl] = (dCt_v[iEl]*(2*Dens_FreeStream*pow(Vel_FreeStream[0],2))/
4039  (pow(AD_J,2)*PI_NUMBER*rad_v[iEl])) / config->GetPressure_Ref();
4040  Ft[iEl] = (dCp_v[iEl]*(2*Dens_FreeStream*pow(Vel_FreeStream[0],2))/
4041  ((AD_J*PI_NUMBER*rad_v[iEl])*(AD_J*PI_NUMBER*rad_v[iEl]))) / config->GetPressure_Ref();
4042  Fr[iEl] = (dCr_v[iEl]*(2*Dens_FreeStream*pow(Vel_FreeStream[0],2))/
4043  (pow(AD_J,2)*PI_NUMBER*rad_v[iEl])) / config->GetPressure_Ref();
4044  }
4045 
4046  /*--- Loop over the marker nodes. ---*/
4047  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[iMarker]; iVertex++) {
4048  /*--- Get the coordinates of the current node. ---*/
4049  iPoint = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNode();
4050  P = geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint);
4051 
4052  /*--- Computation of the radius coordinates for the current node. ---*/
4053  GeometryToolbox::Distance(nDim, P, AD_Center, r);
4054 
4055  /*--- Computation of the non-dimensional radius for the current node. ---*/
4056  r_ = GeometryToolbox::Norm(nDim, r) / AD_Radius;
4057 
4058  /*--- Loop over the actuator disk radial stations. ---*/
4059  for (iEl = 0; iEl < nRow; iEl++){
4060  /*--- Check if the current node is located between rad_v[iEl] and rad_v[iEl-1]. ---*/
4061  if (r_ <= rad_v[iEl]){
4062  /*--- h is the dinstance of the current node from the previous radial element (iEl-1)
4063  divided by the length of the radial element in which the node is contained. ---*/
4064  h = (r_-rad_v[iEl-1])/(rad_v[iEl]-rad_v[iEl-1]);
4065  /*--- Fx, Fy and Fz are the x, y and z components of the tangential and radial forces
4066  per unit area resultant. ---*/
4067  if(r_ == 0.0){
4068  Fx = 0.0;
4069  Fy = 0.0;
4070  Fz = 0.0;
4071  }
4072  /*--- _inf is the value of the previous radial element. _sup is the value of the
4073  following radial element. ---*/
4074  else{
4075  Fx_inf = (Ft[iEl-1]+Fr[iEl-1])*(r[0]/(r_*AD_Radius));
4076  Fy_inf = (Ft[iEl-1]+Fr[iEl-1])*(r[2]/(r_*AD_Radius));
4077  Fz_inf = -(Ft[iEl-1]+Fr[iEl-1])*(r[1]/(r_*AD_Radius));
4078  Fx_sup = (Ft[iEl]+Fr[iEl])*(r[0]/(r_*AD_Radius));
4079  Fy_sup = (Ft[iEl]+Fr[iEl])*(r[2]/(r_*AD_Radius));
4080  Fz_sup = -(Ft[iEl]+Fr[iEl])*(r[1]/(r_*AD_Radius));
4081 
4082  /*--- Fx, Fy and Fz at the current node are evaluated using a linear interpolation between
4083  the end vaues of the radial element in which the current node is contained. ---*/
4084  Fx = Fx_inf + (Fx_sup - Fx_inf)*h;
4085  Fy = Fy_inf + (Fy_sup - Fy_inf)*h;
4086  Fz = Fz_inf + (Fz_sup - Fz_inf)*h;
4087  }
4088  /*--- Set the values of Fa, Fx, Fy and Fz. Fa is evaluated using a linear interpolation. ---*/
4089  ActDisk_Fa[iMarker][iVertex] = Fa[iEl-1] + (Fa[iEl]-Fa[iEl-1])*h;
4090  ActDisk_Fx[iMarker][iVertex] = Fx;
4091  ActDisk_Fy[iMarker][iVertex] = Fy;
4092  ActDisk_Fz[iMarker][iVertex] = Fz;
4093 
4094  break;
4095  }
4096  }
4097  }
4098  }
4099  }
4100  }
4101  }
4102 }
4103 
4104 void CEulerSolver::SetActDisk_BEM_VLAD(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver_container,
4105  CConfig *config, unsigned short iMesh, bool Output) {
4106 
4107  /*!
4108  * \function SetActDisk_BEM_VLAD
4109  * \brief Actuator disk model with Blade Element Method (BEM)
4110  * \author: Chandukrishna Y., T. N. Venkatesh and Josy Pullockara
4111  * Institution: Computational and Theoretical Fluid Dynamics (CTFD),
4112  * CSIR - National Aerospace Laboratories, Bangalore
4113  * Academy of Scientific and Innovative Research, Ghaziabad
4114  * \version 8.1.0 "Harrier"
4115  * First release date : September 26 2023
4116  * modified on:
4117  *
4118  * Section properties of the propeller given in an input file.
4119  * Cl, Cd of propeller sections need to be generated earlier and saved in this file
4120  * Actuator disk data initialized in function SetActDisk_BCThrust.
4121  * Propeller load calculated with Blade Element Method
4122  * Interpolated load at each point on the actuator disk is set in SetActDisk_BEM_VLAD function
4123  * Rest calculations follows the Variable Load (BC_ActDisk_VariableLoad) approach
4124  *
4125  */
4126 
4127  /*--- InputFile reading ---*/
4128  static int ADBem_NBlade = 0, ADBem_NSection = 0, ADBem_NAlpha = 0;
4129  static su2double ADBem_Diameter = 0.0, ADBem_HubRadius = 0.0, ADBem_Angle75R = 0.0;
4130  static std::vector<su2double> i_v, radius_v, chord_v, angle75r_v;
4131  static std::vector<std::vector<su2double> > alpha_m, cl_m, cd_m;
4132 
4133  static su2double ADBem_Omega = 0.0;
4134  static su2double ADBem_CG[MAXNDIM] = {0.0, 0.0, 0.0};
4135  static su2double ADBem_Axis[MAXNDIM] = {0.0}, ADBem_J = 0.0;
4136  static unsigned short ADBem_Frequency = 0;
4137 
4138  /*--- BEM VLAD ---*/
4139  const int BEM_MAX_ITER = 20;
4140 
4141  unsigned long InnerIter = config->GetInnerIter();
4142  su2double Dens_FreeStream = config->GetDensity_FreeStream();
4143  const su2double* Vel_FreeStream = config->GetVelocity_FreeStream();
4144 
4145  /*--- Input file provides force coefficients distributions along disk radius.
4146  Initialization necessary only at initial iteration (InnerIter == 0)
4147  when the tables (radius_v, chord_v, ...) are empty. ---*/
4148  if (radius_v.empty()) {
4149  /*--- Get the RPM, CG, Axis and Frequency from config. ---*/
4150  for (unsigned short iMarker = 0; iMarker < config->GetnMarker_All(); iMarker++) {
4151 
4152  if ((config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ACTDISK_INLET) ||
4153  (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ACTDISK_OUTLET)) {
4154 
4155  const string Marker_Tag = config->GetMarker_All_TagBound(iMarker);
4156  ADBem_Omega = config->GetActDisk_Omega(Marker_Tag, 0);
4157  for (unsigned short iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
4158  ADBem_CG[iDim] = config->GetActDiskBem_CG(iDim, Marker_Tag, 0);
4159  ADBem_Axis[iDim] = config->GetActDiskBem_Axis(iDim, Marker_Tag, 0);
4160  }
4161  }
4162  }
4163  ADBem_Frequency = config->GetActDiskBem_Frequency();
4164 
4165  /*--- Get the file name that contains the propeller data. ---*/
4166  string ActDiskBem_filename = config->GetBEM_prop_filename();
4167  ifstream ActDiskBem_file;
4168 
4169  /*--- Open the file that contains the propeller data. ---*/
4170  ActDiskBem_file.open(ActDiskBem_filename.data(), ios::in);
4171 
4172  /*--- Error message if the propeller data input file fails to open. ---*/
4173  if (ActDiskBem_file.fail()) SU2_MPI::Error("Unable to open Actuator Disk BEM Input File", CURRENT_FUNCTION);
4174 
4175  string text_line_appo;
4176 
4177  getline(ActDiskBem_file, text_line_appo);
4178  /*--- Read and assign the value of the number of propeller blades. ---*/
4179  getline(ActDiskBem_file, text_line_appo);
4180  istringstream NBlade_value(text_line_appo);
4181  NBlade_value >> ADBem_NBlade;
4182 
4183  /*--- Read and assign the value of the propeller diameter. ---*/
4184  getline(ActDiskBem_file, text_line_appo);
4185  istringstream Diameter_value(text_line_appo);
4186  Diameter_value >> ADBem_Diameter;
4187 
4188  /*--- Read and assign the value of the propeller hub radius. ---*/
4189  getline(ActDiskBem_file, text_line_appo);
4190  istringstream HubR_value(text_line_appo);
4191  HubR_value >> ADBem_HubRadius;
4192 
4193  /*--- Read and assign the value of the blade angle at 75% of R. ---*/
4194  getline(ActDiskBem_file, text_line_appo);
4195  istringstream Angle75R_value(text_line_appo);
4196  Angle75R_value >> ADBem_Angle75R;
4197 
4198  getline(ActDiskBem_file, text_line_appo);
4199  /*--- Read and assign the value of the number of radial propeller blade sections and alphas for each. ---*/
4200  getline(ActDiskBem_file, text_line_appo);
4201  istringstream NSection_NAlpha_value(text_line_appo);
4202  NSection_NAlpha_value >> ADBem_NSection >> ADBem_NAlpha;
4203 
4204  /*--- Assign the vector dimensions. ---*/
4205  i_v.resize(ADBem_NSection, 0.0);
4206  radius_v.resize(ADBem_NSection, 0.0);
4207  chord_v.resize(ADBem_NSection, 0.0);
4208  angle75r_v.resize(ADBem_NSection, 0.0);
4209 
4210  getline(ActDiskBem_file, text_line_appo);
4211  /*--- Read and assign the values of the propeller blade section's id, radius, chord, angle75R. ---*/
4212  for (int iSection = 0; iSection < ADBem_NSection; iSection++) {
4213  getline(ActDiskBem_file, text_line_appo);
4214  istringstream sectionStream(text_line_appo);
4215  sectionStream >> i_v[iSection] >> radius_v[iSection] >> chord_v[iSection] >> angle75r_v[iSection];
4216  }
4217 
4218  /*--- Assign the matrix dimensions. ---*/
4219  alpha_m.resize(ADBem_NAlpha, std::vector<su2double>(ADBem_NSection, 0.0));
4220  cl_m.resize(ADBem_NAlpha, std::vector<su2double>(ADBem_NSection, 0.0));
4221  cd_m.resize(ADBem_NAlpha, std::vector<su2double>(ADBem_NSection, 0.0));
4222 
4223  /*--- Read and assign the values for each of the propeller blade section's alpha, cl, cd. ---*/
4224  for (int iSection = 0; iSection < ADBem_NSection; iSection++) {
4225  getline(ActDiskBem_file, text_line_appo);
4226  for (int iAlpha = 0; iAlpha < ADBem_NAlpha; iAlpha++) {
4227  getline(ActDiskBem_file, text_line_appo);
4228  istringstream alphaStream(text_line_appo);
4229  alphaStream >> alpha_m[iAlpha][iSection] >> cl_m[iAlpha][iSection] >> cd_m[iAlpha][iSection];
4230  }
4231  }
4232  }
4233 
4234  /*--- Update the propeller load according to the modified flow field after every ADBem_Frequency inner iterations. ---*/
4235  if (InnerIter % ADBem_Frequency != 0) return;
4236  const su2double dia = ADBem_Diameter;
4237  const su2double r_tip = 0.5 * dia;
4238  su2double loc_Torque = 0.0;
4239  su2double loc_thrust = 0.0;
4240  su2double tot_area = 0.0, tot_tq = 0.0;
4241 
4242  su2double Normal[MAXNDIM];
4243  for (unsigned short iMarker = 0; iMarker < config->GetnMarker_All(); iMarker++) {
4244  if ((config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ACTDISK_INLET) ||
4245  (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ACTDISK_OUTLET)) {
4246  for (unsigned long iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[iMarker]; iVertex++) {
4247  const unsigned long iPoint = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNode();
4248 
4249  /*--- Read Swirl params. ---*/
4250  const su2double Omega_RPM = ADBem_Omega;
4251  const su2double omega_ref = config->GetOmega_Ref();
4252  const su2double Lref = config->GetLength_Ref();
4253  const su2double Omega_sw = Omega_RPM * (PI_NUMBER / 30.0) / (omega_ref); // Swirl rate
4254 
4255  /*--- Center of the rotor ---*/
4256  su2double Origin[3] = {0.0, 0.0, 0.0};
4257  for (unsigned short iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
4258  Origin[iDim] = ADBem_CG[iDim] / Lref;
4259  }
4260 
4261  /*--- Compute the distance to the center of the rotor ---*/
4262  geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNormal(Normal);
4263  for (unsigned short iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
4264  Normal[iDim] = -Normal[iDim];
4265  }
4266 
4267  /*--- Get propeller axis from config file. ---*/
4268  for (unsigned short iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++){
4269  ActDisk_Axis(iMarker, iDim) = ADBem_Axis[iDim];
4270  }
4271  su2double Area = 0.0;
4272  for (unsigned short iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
4273  Area += Normal[iDim] * Normal[iDim];
4274  }
4275  Area = sqrt(Area);
4276 
4277  su2double UnitNormal[3] = {0.0, 0.0, 0.0};
4278  for (unsigned short iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
4279  UnitNormal[iDim] = Normal[iDim] / Area;
4280  }
4281 
4282  const su2double* Coord = geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint);
4283 
4284  su2double radius = 0.0;
4285  su2double radius_[3] = {0.0, 0.0, 0.0};
4286  for (unsigned short iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
4287  radius += (Coord[iDim] - Origin[iDim]) * (Coord[iDim] - Origin[iDim]);
4288  radius_[iDim] = (Coord[iDim] - Origin[iDim]);
4289  }
4290  radius = sqrt(radius);
4291 
4292  /*--- Current solution at this boundary node and jumps values ---*/
4293  const su2double* V_domain = nodes->GetPrimitive(iPoint);
4294 
4295  if (abs(Omega_sw) > 1.0e-1) {
4296  su2double Vn = 0.0;
4297  for (unsigned short iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
4298  Vn += V_domain[iDim + 1] * UnitNormal[iDim];
4299  }
4300 
4301  const su2double RPM = abs(Omega_RPM);
4302  const su2double rps = RPM / 60.0;
4303  ADBem_J = Vel_FreeStream[0] / (rps * dia);
4304  const su2double rho = V_domain[nDim + 2];
4305  const su2double T = V_domain[0];
4306  const su2double blade_angle = config->GetBEM_blade_angle();
4307  const su2double V = fabs(Vn);
4308 
4309  /*--- BEM model without parameter 'a' (ref?) ---*/
4310  su2double Torque = 0.0, dp_av = 0.0, dp_at_r = 0.0;
4311  {
4312  std::vector<su2double> DtDr(ADBem_NSection, 0.0);
4313 
4314  int s_prop_nblades = ADBem_NBlade;
4315  int sprop_sec_nalf = ADBem_NAlpha;
4316  int sprop_sec_nrad = ADBem_NSection;
4317  std::vector<su2double>& sprop_sec_r1 = radius_v;
4318  std::vector<su2double>& sprop_sec_chord = chord_v;
4319  std::vector<su2double>& sprop_sec_setangle = angle75r_v;
4320  std::vector<std::vector<su2double> >& sprop_sec_alf = alpha_m;
4321  std::vector<std::vector<su2double> >& sprop_sec_cl_arr = cl_m;
4322  std::vector<std::vector<su2double> >& sprop_sec_cd_arr = cd_m;
4323 
4324  su2double rad_p = radius;
4325 
4326  int j, isec, converged, n_iter;
4327  int NR = sprop_sec_nrad;
4328  su2double r_hub, alpha_corr, cl_corr_fac;
4329  su2double base_mach, s_mach, b_num, thrust, torque;
4330  su2double r_dash, t_loss, c_phi, rad, phi, alpha, radtodeg;
4331  su2double bnew, V0, V2, cl = 0.0, cd = 0.0, Vlocal, DqDr = 0.0, tem1, tem2, q;
4332  std::vector<su2double> delta_r(ADBem_NSection, 0.0);
4333  std::vector<su2double> b(ADBem_NSection, 0.0);
4334  static std::vector<su2double> Dtorq(ADBem_NSection, 0.0);
4335 
4336  su2double n, omega, a0, den;
4337  su2double ang_offset = 0.0;
4338 
4339  radtodeg = 180.0 / PI_NUMBER;
4340  r_hub = ADBem_HubRadius;
4341  ang_offset = blade_angle - ADBem_Angle75R;
4342 
4343  alpha_corr = 0.0;
4344  base_mach = 0.22;
4345  b_num = sqrt(1.0 - base_mach * base_mach);
4346  a0 = sqrt(1.4 * 287 * T);
4347  /*--- Change pitch by ang_offset and calculate delta_r for integration by trapezoidal rule. ---*/
4348  n = RPM / 60.0;
4349  omega = n * 2.0 * PI_NUMBER;
4350 
4351  for (j = 0; j < NR; j++) {
4352  if (j < 1) {
4353  delta_r[j] = sprop_sec_r1[j + 1] - r_hub;
4354  } else {
4355  if (j < NR - 1) {
4356  delta_r[j] = sprop_sec_r1[j + 1] - sprop_sec_r1[j - 1];
4357  } else {
4358  delta_r[j] = r_tip - sprop_sec_r1[j - 1];
4359  }
4360  }
4361  delta_r[j] *= 0.5;
4362  }
4363 
4364  thrust = 0.0;
4365  torque = 0.0;
4366 
4367  for (j = 0; j < NR; j++) {
4368  b[j] = 0.01;
4369  converged = 0;
4370  n_iter = 1;
4371  while (converged == 0) {
4372  V2 = omega * sprop_sec_r1[j] * (1 - b[j]);
4373  V0 = V;
4374 
4375  phi = atan2(V0, V2);
4376 
4377  alpha = sprop_sec_setangle[j] + ang_offset - radtodeg * phi + alpha_corr;
4378  rad = sprop_sec_r1[j];
4379 
4380  /*--- get cl, cd from lookup table. ---*/
4381  isec = j + 1;
4382  {
4383  int i, salf = 0;
4384  su2double fact;
4385 
4386  /*--- interpolating values of cl and cd for given alpha. ---*/
4387  if (alpha >= sprop_sec_alf[salf][isec - 1] &&
4388  alpha <= sprop_sec_alf[sprop_sec_nalf - 1][isec - 1]) {
4389  for (i = 0; i < sprop_sec_nalf - 1; i++) {
4390  if (alpha >= sprop_sec_alf[i][isec - 1] && alpha <= sprop_sec_alf[i + 1][isec - 1]) {
4391  fact = (alpha - sprop_sec_alf[i][isec - 1])
4392  / (sprop_sec_alf[i + 1][isec - 1] - sprop_sec_alf[i][isec - 1]);
4393  cl = sprop_sec_cl_arr[i][isec - 1]
4394  + fact * (sprop_sec_cl_arr[i + 1][isec - 1] - sprop_sec_cl_arr[i][isec - 1]);
4395  cd = sprop_sec_cd_arr[i][isec - 1]
4396  + fact * (sprop_sec_cd_arr[i + 1][isec - 1] - sprop_sec_cd_arr[i][isec - 1]);
4397  }
4398  }
4399  } else {
4400  if (alpha < sprop_sec_alf[salf][isec - 1]) {
4401  cl = sprop_sec_cl_arr[0][isec - 1];
4402  cd = sprop_sec_cd_arr[0][isec - 1];
4403  }
4404  if (alpha > sprop_sec_alf[sprop_sec_nalf - 1][isec - 1]) {
4405  cl = sprop_sec_cl_arr[sprop_sec_nalf - 1][isec - 1];
4406  cd = sprop_sec_cd_arr[sprop_sec_nalf - 1][isec - 1];
4407  }
4408  }
4409  }
4410 
4411  Vlocal = sqrt(V0 * V0 + V2 * V2);
4412  q = 0.5 * rho * Vlocal * Vlocal;
4413  s_mach = Vlocal / a0;
4414  cl_corr_fac = 1.0;
4415  if (s_mach > base_mach) {
4416  den = 1.0 - s_mach * s_mach;
4417  if (den > 0.0) cl_corr_fac = b_num / sqrt(den);
4418  }
4419  cl *= cl_corr_fac;
4420 
4421  /*--- tip loss factor. ---*/
4422  r_dash = rad / r_tip + 1.0e-5;
4423  c_phi = cos(phi);
4424  t_loss = 1.0;
4425  if (r_dash > 0.90) {
4426  t_loss = (2.0 / PI_NUMBER) * acos(exp(-(1.0 * s_prop_nblades * (1 - r_dash) / (r_dash * c_phi))));
4427  }
4428 
4429  DtDr[j] = q * s_prop_nblades * sprop_sec_chord[j] * (cl * cos(phi) - cd * sin(phi));
4430  DqDr = q * s_prop_nblades * sprop_sec_chord[j] * rad * (cd * cos(phi) + cl * sin(phi));
4431 
4432  DtDr[j] *= t_loss;
4433  DqDr *= t_loss;
4434 
4435  tem2 = DqDr / (4.0 * PI_NUMBER * rad * rad * rad * rho * V * omega);
4436  bnew = 0.6 * b[j] + 0.4 * tem2;
4437  if (bnew > 0.9) bnew = 0.9;
4438  if (fabs(bnew - b[j]) < 1.0e-5) {
4439  converged = 1;
4440  }
4441  if (bnew < 0.1) {
4442  b[j] = bnew;
4443  }
4444  n_iter++;
4445  if (n_iter > BEM_MAX_ITER) {
4446  converged = 1;
4447  }
4448  }
4449  thrust = thrust + DtDr[j] * delta_r[j];
4450  torque = torque + DqDr * delta_r[j];
4451  Dtorq[j] = DqDr;
4452  }
4453 
4454  tem1 = rho * n * n * dia * dia * dia * dia;
4455  tem2 = tem1 * dia;
4456 
4457  Torque = 2.0 * PI_NUMBER * torque;
4458  dp_av = 2.0 * PI_NUMBER * torque;
4459 
4460  for (j = 0; j < NR; j++) {
4461  DtDr[j] /= (2.0 * PI_NUMBER * sprop_sec_r1[j]);
4462  Dtorq[j] = Dtorq[j];
4463  }
4464 
4465  if (rad_p < sprop_sec_r1[0]) {
4466  tem2 = sprop_sec_r1[0] - r_hub;
4467  tem1 = (rad_p - r_hub) / tem2;
4468  tem2 = 1.0 - tem1;
4469  dp_at_r = DtDr[0] * tem1;
4470  Torque = Dtorq[0] * tem1;
4471  } else {
4472  if (rad_p > r_tip) {
4473  dp_at_r = 0.0;
4474  Torque = 0.0;
4475  } else {
4476  if (rad_p > sprop_sec_r1[NR - 1]) {
4477  tem2 = r_tip - sprop_sec_r1[NR - 1];
4478  tem1 = (rad_p - sprop_sec_r1[NR - 1]) / tem2;
4479  tem2 = 1.0 - tem1;
4480  dp_at_r = DtDr[NR - 1] * tem2;
4481  Torque = Dtorq[NR - 1] * tem2;
4482  } else {
4483  for (j = 0; j < NR - 1; j++) {
4484  if ((sprop_sec_r1[j] < rad_p) && (sprop_sec_r1[j + 1] >= rad_p)) {
4485  tem2 = sprop_sec_r1[j + 1] - sprop_sec_r1[j];
4486  tem1 = (rad_p - sprop_sec_r1[j]) / tem2;
4487  tem2 = 1.0 - tem1;
4488  dp_at_r = DtDr[j] * tem2 + DtDr[j + 1] * tem1;
4489  Torque = Dtorq[j] * tem2 + Dtorq[j + 1] * tem1;
4490  }
4491  }
4492  }
4493  }
4494  }
4495  }
4496 
4497  tot_area += Area;
4498  loc_Torque += Torque * Area;
4499  tot_tq += dp_av;
4500  loc_thrust += dp_at_r * Area;
4501  const su2double Target_Press_Jump = dp_at_r;
4502 
4503  ActDisk_DeltaP_r[iMarker][iVertex] = Target_Press_Jump;
4504  ActDisk_Thrust_r[iMarker][iVertex] = dp_at_r;
4505  ActDisk_Torque_r[iMarker][iVertex] = Torque / (2 * PI_NUMBER * radius);
4506  /*--- Non-dimensionalize the elemental load. ---*/
4507  const su2double dCp_v = Torque * ((Omega_sw * r_tip) / (rho * rps * rps * rps * pow(dia, 5)));
4508  /*--- Force radial load to 0 as there is no information of radial load from BEM. ---*/
4509  const su2double dCr_v = 0.0;
4510  const su2double rad_v = radius / r_tip;
4511  const su2double Fa = dp_at_r;
4512  const su2double Ft = (dCp_v * (2 * Dens_FreeStream * pow(Vel_FreeStream[0], 2)) /
4513  ((ADBem_J * PI_NUMBER * rad_v) * (ADBem_J * PI_NUMBER * rad_v))) /
4514  config->GetPressure_Ref();
4515  const su2double Fr = (dCr_v * (2 * Dens_FreeStream * pow(Vel_FreeStream[0], 2)) /
4516  (pow(ADBem_J, 2) * PI_NUMBER * rad_v)) / config->GetPressure_Ref();
4517  const su2double Fx = (Ft + Fr) * (radius_[0] / (radius));
4518  const su2double Fy = (Ft + Fr) * (radius_[2] / (radius));
4519  const su2double Fz = -(Ft + Fr) * (radius_[1] / (radius));
4520  ActDisk_Fa_BEM[iMarker][iVertex] = Fa;
4521  ActDisk_Fx_BEM[iMarker][iVertex] = Fx;
4522  ActDisk_Fy_BEM[iMarker][iVertex] = Fy;
4523  ActDisk_Fz_BEM[iMarker][iVertex] = Fz;
4524  }
4525  }
4526  }
4527  }
4528 }
4529 
4530 void CEulerSolver::SetFarfield_AoA(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver_container,
4531  CConfig *config, unsigned short iMesh, bool Output) {
4532 
4533  const auto InnerIter = config->GetInnerIter();
4534  /* --- Initialize values at first iteration --- */
4535 
4536  if (InnerIter == 0) {
4537  Total_CD_Prev = 0.0;
4538  Total_CL_Prev = 0.0;
4539  Total_CMx_Prev = 0.0;
4540  Total_CMy_Prev = 0.0;
4541  Total_CMz_Prev = 0.0;
4542  AoA_Prev = config->GetAoA();
4543  dCL_dAlpha = config->GetdCL_dAlpha();
4544  AoA_inc = 0.0;
4545  }
4546 
4547  /*--- Retrieve the AoA (degrees) ---*/
4548 
4549  su2double AoA = config->GetAoA();
4550 
4551  /* --- Set new AoA if needed --- */
4552 
4553  if (fabs(AoA_inc) > 0.0 && Output) {
4554 
4555  /* --- Update *_Prev values with current coefficients --- */
4556 
4557  SetCoefficient_Gradients(config);
4558 
4559  Total_CD_Prev = TotalCoeff.CD;
4560  Total_CL_Prev = TotalCoeff.CL;
4561  Total_CMx_Prev = TotalCoeff.CMx;
4562  Total_CMy_Prev = TotalCoeff.CMy;
4563  Total_CMz_Prev = TotalCoeff.CMz;
4564  AoA_Prev = AoA;
4565 
4566  /*--- Compute a new value for AoA on the fine mesh only (degrees)---*/
4567 
4568  if (iMesh == MESH_0) {
4569  AoA = AoA + AoA_inc;
4570  config->SetAoA(AoA);
4571  }
4572  UpdateFarfieldVelocity(config);
4573  }
4574 }
4575 
4576 bool CEulerSolver::FixedCL_Convergence(CConfig* config, bool convergence) {
4577  const su2double Target_CL = config->GetTarget_CL();
4578  const auto curr_iter = config->GetInnerIter();
4579  const auto Iter_dCL_dAlpha = config->GetIter_dCL_dAlpha();
4580  bool fixed_cl_conv = false;
4581  AoA_inc = 0.0;
4582 
4583  /*--- if in Fixed CL mode, before finite differencing --- */
4584 
4585  if (!Start_AoA_FD){
4586  if (convergence){
4587 
4588  /* --- C_L and solution are converged, start finite differencing --- */
4589 
4590  if (fabs(TotalCoeff.CL-Target_CL) < (config->GetCauchy_Eps()/2)) {
4591 
4592  /* --- If no finite differencing required --- */
4593 
4594  if (Iter_dCL_dAlpha == 0){
4595  fixed_cl_conv = true;
4596  return fixed_cl_conv;
4597  }
4598 
4599  /* --- Else, set up finite differencing routine ---*/
4600 
4601  Iter_Update_AoA = curr_iter;
4602  Start_AoA_FD = true;
4603  fixed_cl_conv = false;
4604  AoA_inc = 0.001;
4605  }
4606 
4607  /* --- C_L is not converged to target value and some iterations
4608  have passed since last update, so update AoA --- */
4609 
4610  else if ((curr_iter - Iter_Update_AoA) > config->GetStartConv_Iter()){
4611  Iter_Update_AoA = curr_iter;
4612  fixed_cl_conv = false;
4613  if (fabs(TotalCoeff.CL-Target_CL) > (config->GetCauchy_Eps()/2)) {
4614  AoA_inc = (1.0/dCL_dAlpha)*(Target_CL - TotalCoeff.CL);
4615  }
4616  }
4617  }
4618 
4619  /* --- If the iteration limit between AoA updates is met, so update AoA --- */
4620 
4621  else if ((curr_iter - Iter_Update_AoA) == config->GetUpdate_AoA_Iter_Limit()) {
4622  Iter_Update_AoA = curr_iter;
4623  fixed_cl_conv = false;
4624  if (fabs(TotalCoeff.CL-Target_CL) > (config->GetCauchy_Eps()/2)) {
4625  AoA_inc = (1.0/dCL_dAlpha)*(Target_CL - TotalCoeff.CL);
4626  }
4627  }
4628 
4629  /* --- If the total iteration limit is reached, start finite differencing --- */
4630 
4631  if (curr_iter == config->GetnInner_Iter() - Iter_dCL_dAlpha){
4632  if (Iter_dCL_dAlpha == 0){
4633  End_AoA_FD = true;
4634  }
4635  Iter_Update_AoA = curr_iter;
4636  Start_AoA_FD = true;
4637  fixed_cl_conv = false;
4638  AoA_inc = 0.001;
4639  }
4640  }
4641 
4642  /* --- If Finite Difference Mode has ended, end simulation --- */
4643 
4644  if (End_AoA_FD){
4645  //fixed_cl_conv = true;
4646  return true;
4647  }
4648 
4649  /* --- If starting Finite Difference Mode --- */
4650 
4651  if (Start_AoA_FD){
4652 
4653  /* --- Disable history writing --- */
4654 
4655  config->SetHistory_Wrt_Freq(2, 0);
4656 
4657  /* --- End Finite Difference Mode if iteration limit is reached, so simualtion is converged --- */
4658 
4659  End_AoA_FD = ((curr_iter - Iter_Update_AoA - 2) == Iter_dCL_dAlpha ||
4660  curr_iter == config->GetnInner_Iter()- 2 );
4661 
4662  if (convergence && (curr_iter - Iter_Update_AoA) > config->GetStartConv_Iter())
4663  End_AoA_FD = true;
4664 
4665  /* --- If Finite Difference mode is ending, reset AoA and calculate Coefficient Gradients --- */
4666 
4667  if (End_AoA_FD){
4668  SetCoefficient_Gradients(config);
4669  config->SetAoA(AoA_Prev);
4670  }
4671  }
4672 
4673  return fixed_cl_conv;
4674 
4675 }
4676 
4677 void CEulerSolver::SetCoefficient_Gradients(CConfig *config) const{
4678 
4679  const su2double AoA = config->GetAoA();
4680 
4681  if (AoA == AoA_Prev) return;
4682 
4683  /*--- Calculate gradients of coefficients w.r.t. CL ---*/
4684 
4685  const su2double dCL = TotalCoeff.CL - Total_CL_Prev;
4686  const su2double dCL_dAlpha_ = dCL / (AoA - AoA_Prev);
4687  const su2double dCD_dCL_ = (TotalCoeff.CD-Total_CD_Prev) / dCL;
4688  const su2double dCMx_dCL_ = (TotalCoeff.CMx-Total_CMx_Prev) / dCL;
4689  const su2double dCMy_dCL_ = (TotalCoeff.CMy-Total_CMy_Prev) / dCL;
4690  const su2double dCMz_dCL_ = (TotalCoeff.CMz-Total_CMz_Prev) / dCL;
4691 
4692  /*--- Set the value of the dOF/dCL in the config file ---*/
4693 
4694  config->SetdCD_dCL(dCD_dCL_);
4695  config->SetdCMx_dCL(dCMx_dCL_);
4696  config->SetdCMy_dCL(dCMy_dCL_);
4697  config->SetdCMz_dCL(dCMz_dCL_);
4698  config->SetdCL_dAlpha(dCL_dAlpha_);
4699 }
4700 
4701 void CEulerSolver::Evaluate_ObjFunc(const CConfig *config, CSolver**) {
4702 
4703  unsigned short iMarker_Monitoring, Kind_ObjFunc;
4704  su2double Weight_ObjFunc;
4705 
4706  Total_ComboObj = EvaluateCommonObjFunc(*config);
4707 
4708  /*--- Loop over all monitored markers, add to the 'combo' objective ---*/
4709 
4710  if (config->GetFixed_CL_Mode()) {
4711  for (iMarker_Monitoring = 0; iMarker_Monitoring < config->GetnMarker_Monitoring(); iMarker_Monitoring++) {
4712 
4713  Weight_ObjFunc = config->GetWeight_ObjFunc(iMarker_Monitoring);
4714  Kind_ObjFunc = config->GetKind_ObjFunc(iMarker_Monitoring);
4715 
4716  switch(Kind_ObjFunc) {
4717  case DRAG_COEFFICIENT:
4718  Total_ComboObj -= Weight_ObjFunc*config->GetdCD_dCL()*(SurfaceCoeff.CL[iMarker_Monitoring]);
4719  break;
4720  case MOMENT_X_COEFFICIENT:
4721  Total_ComboObj -= Weight_ObjFunc*config->GetdCMx_dCL()*(SurfaceCoeff.CL[iMarker_Monitoring]);
4722  break;
4723  case MOMENT_Y_COEFFICIENT:
4724  Total_ComboObj -= Weight_ObjFunc*config->GetdCMy_dCL()*(SurfaceCoeff.CL[iMarker_Monitoring]);
4725  break;
4726  case MOMENT_Z_COEFFICIENT:
4727  Total_ComboObj -= Weight_ObjFunc*config->GetdCMz_dCL()*(SurfaceCoeff.CL[iMarker_Monitoring]);
4728  break;
4729  default:
4730  break;
4731  }
4732  }
4733  }
4734 
4735  /*--- The following are not per-surface, and so to avoid that they are
4736  double-counted when multiple surfaces are specified, they have been
4737  placed outside of the loop above. In addition, multi-objective mode is
4738  also disabled for these objective functions (error thrown at start). ---*/
4739 
4740  Weight_ObjFunc = config->GetWeight_ObjFunc(0);
4741  Kind_ObjFunc = config->GetKind_ObjFunc(0);
4742 
4743  switch(Kind_ObjFunc) {
4744  case NEARFIELD_PRESSURE:
4745  Total_ComboObj+=Weight_ObjFunc*Total_CNearFieldOF;
4746  break;
4747  case SURFACE_MACH:
4748  Total_ComboObj+=Weight_ObjFunc*config->GetSurface_Mach(0);
4749  break;
4750  default:
4751  break;
4752  }
4753 }
4754 
4755 void CEulerSolver::BC_Far_Field(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver_container, CNumerics *conv_numerics,
4756  CNumerics *visc_numerics, CConfig *config, unsigned short val_marker) {
4757 
4758  unsigned short iDim;
4759  unsigned long iVertex, iPoint, Point_Normal;
4760 
4761  su2double *GridVel;
4762  su2double Area, UnitNormal[MAXNDIM] = {0.0};
4763  su2double Density, Pressure, Energy, Velocity[MAXNDIM] = {0.0};
4764  su2double Density_Bound, Pressure_Bound, Vel_Bound[MAXNDIM] = {0.0};
4765  su2double Density_Infty, Pressure_Infty, Vel_Infty[MAXNDIM] = {0.0};
4766  su2double SoundSpeed, Entropy, Velocity2, Vn;
4767  su2double SoundSpeed_Bound, Entropy_Bound, Vel2_Bound, Vn_Bound;
4768  su2double SoundSpeed_Infty, Entropy_Infty, Vel2_Infty, Vn_Infty, Qn_Infty;
4769  su2double RiemannPlus, RiemannMinus;
4770  su2double *V_infty, *V_domain;
4771 
4772  su2double Gas_Constant = config->GetGas_ConstantND();
4773 
4774  bool implicit = config->GetKind_TimeIntScheme() == EULER_IMPLICIT;
4775  bool viscous = config->GetViscous();
4776  bool tkeNeeded = config->GetKind_Turb_Model() == TURB_MODEL::SST;
4777 
4778  auto *Normal = new su2double[nDim];
4779 
4780  /*--- Loop over all the vertices on this boundary marker ---*/
4781 
4782  SU2_OMP_FOR_DYN(OMP_MIN_SIZE)
4783  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[val_marker]; iVertex++) {
4784  iPoint = geometry->vertex[val_marker][iVertex]->GetNode();
4785 
4786  /*--- Allocate the value at the infinity ---*/
4787  V_infty = GetCharacPrimVar(val_marker, iVertex);
4788 
4789  /*--- Check if the node belongs to the domain (i.e, not a halo node) ---*/
4790 
4791  if (geometry->nodes->GetDomain(iPoint)) {
4792 
4793  /*--- Index of the closest interior node ---*/
4794 
4795  Point_Normal = geometry->vertex[val_marker][iVertex]->GetNormal_Neighbor();
4796 
4797  /*--- Normal vector for this vertex (negate for outward convention) ---*/
4798 
4799  geometry->vertex[val_marker][iVertex]->GetNormal(Normal);
4800  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) Normal[iDim] = -Normal[iDim];
4801  conv_numerics->SetNormal(Normal);
4802 
4803  /*--- Retrieve solution at the farfield boundary node ---*/
4804  V_domain = nodes->GetPrimitive(iPoint);
4805 
4806  /*--- Construct solution state at infinity for compressible flow by
4807  using Riemann invariants, and then impose a weak boundary condition
4808  by computing the flux using this new state for U. See CFD texts by
4809  Hirsch or Blazek for more detail. Adapted from an original
4810  implementation in the Stanford University multi-block (SUmb) solver
4811  in the routine bcFarfield.f90 written by Edwin van der Weide,
4812  last modified 06-12-2005. First, compute the unit normal at the
4813  boundary nodes. ---*/
4814 
4815  Area = GeometryToolbox::Norm(nDim, Normal);
4816  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
4817  UnitNormal[iDim] = Normal[iDim]/Area;
4818 
4819  /*--- Store primitive variables (density, velocities, velocity squared,
4820  energy, pressure, and sound speed) at the boundary node, and set some
4821  other quantities for clarity. Project the current flow velocity vector
4822  at this boundary node into the local normal direction, i.e. compute
4823  v_bound.n. ---*/
4824 
4825  Density_Bound = V_domain[nDim+2];
4826  Vel2_Bound = 0.0; Vn_Bound = 0.0;
4827  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
4828  Vel_Bound[iDim] = V_domain[iDim+1];
4829  Vel2_Bound += Vel_Bound[iDim]*Vel_Bound[iDim];
4830  Vn_Bound += Vel_Bound[iDim]*UnitNormal[iDim];
4831  }
4832  Pressure_Bound = nodes->GetPressure(iPoint);
4833  SoundSpeed_Bound = sqrt(Gamma*Pressure_Bound/Density_Bound);
4834  Entropy_Bound = pow(Density_Bound, Gamma)/Pressure_Bound;
4835 
4836  /*--- Store the primitive variable state for the freestream. Project
4837  the freestream velocity vector into the local normal direction,
4838  i.e. compute v_infty.n. ---*/
4839 
4840  Density_Infty = GetDensity_Inf();
4841  Vel2_Infty = 0.0; Vn_Infty = 0.0;
4842  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
4843  Vel_Infty[iDim] = GetVelocity_Inf(iDim);
4844  Vel2_Infty += Vel_Infty[iDim]*Vel_Infty[iDim];
4845  Vn_Infty += Vel_Infty[iDim]*UnitNormal[iDim];
4846  }
4847  Pressure_Infty = GetPressure_Inf();
4848  SoundSpeed_Infty = sqrt(Gamma*Pressure_Infty/Density_Infty);
4849  Entropy_Infty = pow(Density_Infty, Gamma)/Pressure_Infty;
4850 
4851  /*--- Adjust the normal freestream velocity for grid movement ---*/
4852 
4853  Qn_Infty = Vn_Infty;
4854  if (dynamic_grid) {
4855  GridVel = geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint);
4856  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
4857  Qn_Infty -= GridVel[iDim]*UnitNormal[iDim];
4858  }
4859 
4860  /*--- Compute acoustic Riemann invariants: R = u.n +/- 2c/(gamma-1).
4861  These correspond with the eigenvalues (u+c) and (u-c), respectively,
4862  which represent the acoustic waves. Positive characteristics are
4863  incoming, and a physical boundary condition is imposed (freestream
4864  state). This occurs when either (u.n+c) > 0 or (u.n-c) > 0. Negative
4865  characteristics are leaving the domain, and numerical boundary
4866  conditions are required by extrapolating from the interior state
4867  using the Riemann invariants. This occurs when (u.n+c) < 0 or
4868  (u.n-c) < 0. Note that grid movement is taken into account when
4869  checking the sign of the eigenvalue. ---*/
4870 
4871  /*--- Check whether (u.n+c) is greater or less than zero ---*/
4872 
4873  if (Qn_Infty > -SoundSpeed_Infty) {
4874  /*--- Subsonic inflow or outflow ---*/
4875  RiemannPlus = Vn_Bound + 2.0*SoundSpeed_Bound/Gamma_Minus_One;
4876  } else {
4877  /*--- Supersonic inflow ---*/
4878  RiemannPlus = Vn_Infty + 2.0*SoundSpeed_Infty/Gamma_Minus_One;
4879  }
4880 
4881  /*--- Check whether (u.n-c) is greater or less than zero ---*/
4882 
4883  if (Qn_Infty > SoundSpeed_Infty) {
4884  /*--- Supersonic outflow ---*/
4885  RiemannMinus = Vn_Bound - 2.0*SoundSpeed_Bound/Gamma_Minus_One;
4886  } else {
4887  /*--- Subsonic outflow ---*/
4888  RiemannMinus = Vn_Infty - 2.0*SoundSpeed_Infty/Gamma_Minus_One;
4889  }
4890 
4891  /*--- Compute a new value for the local normal velocity and speed of
4892  sound from the Riemann invariants. ---*/
4893 
4894  Vn = 0.5 * (RiemannPlus + RiemannMinus);
4895  SoundSpeed = 0.25 * (RiemannPlus - RiemannMinus)*Gamma_Minus_One;
4896 
4897  /*--- Construct the primitive variable state at the boundary for
4898  computing the flux for the weak boundary condition. The values
4899  that we choose to construct the solution (boundary or freestream)
4900  depend on whether we are at an inflow or outflow. At an outflow, we
4901  choose boundary information (at most one characteristic is incoming),
4902  while at an inflow, we choose infinity values (at most one
4903  characteristic is outgoing). ---*/
4904 
4905  if (Qn_Infty > 0.0) {
4906  /*--- Outflow conditions ---*/
4907  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
4908  Velocity[iDim] = Vel_Bound[iDim] + (Vn-Vn_Bound)*UnitNormal[iDim];
4909  Entropy = Entropy_Bound;
4910  } else {
4911  /*--- Inflow conditions ---*/
4912  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
4913  Velocity[iDim] = Vel_Infty[iDim] + (Vn-Vn_Infty)*UnitNormal[iDim];
4914  Entropy = Entropy_Infty;
4915  }
4916 
4917  /*--- Recompute the primitive variables. ---*/
4918 
4919  Density = pow(Entropy*SoundSpeed*SoundSpeed/Gamma,1.0/Gamma_Minus_One);
4920  Velocity2 = 0.0;
4921  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
4922  Velocity2 += Velocity[iDim]*Velocity[iDim];
4923  }
4924  Pressure = Density*SoundSpeed*SoundSpeed/Gamma;
4925  Energy = Pressure/(Gamma_Minus_One*Density) + 0.5*Velocity2;
4926  if (tkeNeeded) Energy += GetTke_Inf();
4927 
4928  /*--- Store new primitive state for computing the flux. ---*/
4929 
4930  V_infty[0] = Pressure/(Gas_Constant*Density);
4931  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
4932  V_infty[iDim+1] = Velocity[iDim];
4933  V_infty[nDim+1] = Pressure;
4934  V_infty[nDim+2] = Density;
4935  V_infty[nDim+3] = Energy + Pressure/Density;
4936 
4937 
4938 
4939  /*--- Set various quantities in the numerics class ---*/
4940 
4941  conv_numerics->SetPrimitive(V_domain, V_infty);
4942 
4943  if (dynamic_grid) {
4944  conv_numerics->SetGridVel(geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint),
4945  geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint));
4946  }
4947 
4948  /*--- Compute the convective residual using an upwind scheme ---*/
4949 
4950  auto residual = conv_numerics->ComputeResidual(config);
4951 
4952  /*--- Update residual value ---*/
4953 
4954  LinSysRes.AddBlock(iPoint, residual);
4955 
4956  /*--- Convective Jacobian contribution for implicit integration ---*/
4957 
4958  if (implicit)
4959  Jacobian.AddBlock2Diag(iPoint, residual.jacobian_i);
4960 
4961  /*--- Viscous residual contribution ---*/
4962 
4963  if (viscous) {
4964 
4965  /*--- Set laminar and eddy viscosity at the infinity ---*/
4966 
4967  V_infty[nDim+5] = nodes->GetLaminarViscosity(iPoint);
4968  V_infty[nDim+6] = nodes->GetEddyViscosity(iPoint);
4969 
4970  /*--- Set the normal vector and the coordinates ---*/
4971 
4972  visc_numerics->SetNormal(Normal);
4973  su2double Coord_Reflected[MAXNDIM];
4974  GeometryToolbox::PointPointReflect(nDim, geometry->nodes->GetCoord(Point_Normal),
4975  geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint), Coord_Reflected);
4976  visc_numerics->SetCoord(geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint), Coord_Reflected);
4977 
4978  /*--- Primitive variables, and gradient ---*/
4979 
4980  visc_numerics->SetPrimitive(V_domain, V_infty);
4981  visc_numerics->SetPrimVarGradient(nodes->GetGradient_Primitive(iPoint),
4982  nodes->GetGradient_Primitive(iPoint));
4983 
4984  /*--- Turbulent kinetic energy ---*/
4985 
4986  if (config->GetKind_Turb_Model() == TURB_MODEL::SST)
4987  visc_numerics->SetTurbKineticEnergy(solver_container[TURB_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetSolution(iPoint,0),
4988  solver_container[TURB_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetSolution(iPoint,0));
4989 
4990  /*--- Compute and update viscous residual ---*/
4991 
4992  auto residual = visc_numerics->ComputeResidual(config);
4993  LinSysRes.SubtractBlock(iPoint, residual);
4994 
4995  /*--- Viscous Jacobian contribution for implicit integration ---*/
4996 
4997  if (implicit)
4998  Jacobian.SubtractBlock2Diag(iPoint, residual.jacobian_i);
4999 
5000  }
5001 
5002  }
5003  }
5004  END_SU2_OMP_FOR
5005 
5006  /*--- Free locally allocated memory ---*/
5007  delete [] Normal;
5008 
5009 }
5010 
5011 void CEulerSolver::BC_Riemann(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver_container,
5012  CNumerics *conv_numerics, CNumerics *visc_numerics,
5013  CConfig *config, unsigned short val_marker) {
5014 
5015  const string Marker_Tag = config->GetMarker_All_TagBound(val_marker);
5016  const bool viscous = config->GetViscous(),
5017  implicit = (config->GetKind_TimeIntScheme() == EULER_IMPLICIT),
5018  gravity = config->GetGravityForce(),
5019  tkeNeeded = (config->GetKind_Turb_Model() == TURB_MODEL::SST);
5020 
5021  su2double **P_Tensor = new su2double*[nVar],
5022  **invP_Tensor = new su2double*[nVar];
5023  for (auto iVar = 0u; iVar < nVar; iVar++){
5024  P_Tensor[iVar] = new su2double[nVar];
5025  invP_Tensor[iVar] = new su2double[nVar];
5026  }
5027 
5028  /*--- Loop over all the vertices on this boundary marker ---*/
5029 
5030  SU2_OMP_FOR_DYN(OMP_MIN_SIZE)
5031  for (auto iVertex = 0u; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[val_marker]; iVertex++) {
5032 
5033  auto iPoint = geometry->vertex[val_marker][iVertex]->GetNode();
5034 
5035  /*--- Check if the node belongs to the domain (i.e., not a halo node) ---*/
5036  if (geometry->nodes->GetDomain(iPoint)) {
5037 
5038  /*--- Index of the closest interior node ---*/
5039  const auto Point_Normal = geometry->vertex[val_marker][iVertex]->GetNormal_Neighbor();
5040 
5041  /*--- Normal vector for this vertex (negate for outward convention) ---*/
5042  su2double Normal[MAXNDIM] = {0};
5043  geometry->vertex[val_marker][iVertex]->GetNormal(Normal);
5044  for (auto iDim = 0u; iDim < nDim; iDim++) Normal[iDim] = -Normal[iDim];
5045  conv_numerics->SetNormal(Normal);
5046 
5047  const auto Area = GeometryToolbox::Norm(nDim, Normal);
5048 
5049  su2double UnitNormal[MAXNDIM] = {0};
5050  for (auto iDim = 0u; iDim < nDim; iDim++) UnitNormal[iDim] = Normal[iDim]/Area;
5051 
5052  /*--- Retrieve solution at this boundary node ---*/
5053  const auto V_domain = nodes->GetPrimitive(iPoint);
5054 
5055  /*--- Compute the internal state u_i ---*/
5056  su2double Velocity_i[MAXNDIM]={0};
5057  for (auto iDim=0u; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
5058  Velocity_i[iDim] = nodes->GetVelocity(iPoint,iDim);
5059 
5060  const auto Velocity2_i = GeometryToolbox::SquaredNorm(nDim, Velocity_i);
5061 
5062  const auto Density_i = nodes->GetDensity(iPoint);
5063 
5064  const auto Energy_i = nodes->GetEnergy(iPoint);
5065  const su2double StaticEnergy_i = Energy_i - 0.5*Velocity2_i;
5066 
5067  GetFluidModel()->SetTDState_rhoe(Density_i, StaticEnergy_i);
5068 
5069  const auto Pressure_i = GetFluidModel()->GetPressure();
5070  const su2double Enthalpy_i = Energy_i + Pressure_i/Density_i;
5071 
5072  const auto SoundSpeed_i = GetFluidModel()->GetSoundSpeed();
5073 
5074  const su2double Kappa_i = GetFluidModel()->GetdPde_rho() / Density_i;
5075  const su2double Chi_i = GetFluidModel()->GetdPdrho_e() - Kappa_i * StaticEnergy_i;
5076 
5077  /*--- Build the external state u_e from boundary data and internal node ---*/
5078  su2double T_static{0}, P_static{0}, Pressure_e{0}, Density_static{0}, Enthalpy_e{0}, Energy_e{0}, Entropy_e{0},
5079  T_Total{0}, P_Total{0}, Density_e{0}, StaticEnthalpy_e{0}, StaticEnergy_e{0};
5080 
5081  su2double Velocity2_e{0}, NormalVelocity{0}, TangVelocity{0}, VelMag_e{0};
5082  su2double Velocity_e[MAXNDIM] = {0};
5083  const su2double * Flow_Dir, * Mach;
5084  switch(config->GetKind_Data_Riemann(Marker_Tag))
5085  {
5086  case TOTAL_CONDITIONS_PT:
5087 
5088  /*--- Retrieve the specified total conditions for this boundary. ---*/
5089  if (gravity) P_Total = config->GetRiemann_Var1(Marker_Tag) - geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint, nDim-1)*STANDARD_GRAVITY;/// check in which case is true (only freesurface?)
5090  else P_Total = config->GetRiemann_Var1(Marker_Tag);
5091  T_Total = config->GetRiemann_Var2(Marker_Tag);
5092  Flow_Dir = config->GetRiemann_FlowDir(Marker_Tag);
5093 
5094  /*--- Non-dim. the inputs if necessary. ---*/
5095  P_Total /= config->GetPressure_Ref();
5096  T_Total /= config->GetTemperature_Ref();
5097 
5098  /* --- Computes the total state --- */
5099  GetFluidModel()->SetTDState_PT(P_Total, T_Total);
5100  Enthalpy_e = GetFluidModel()->GetStaticEnergy()+ GetFluidModel()->GetPressure()/GetFluidModel()->GetDensity();
5101  Entropy_e = GetFluidModel()->GetEntropy();
5102 
5103  /* --- Compute the boundary state u_e --- */
5104  Velocity2_e = Velocity2_i;
5105  if (nDim == 2){
5106  NormalVelocity= -sqrt(Velocity2_e)*Flow_Dir[0];
5107  TangVelocity= -sqrt(Velocity2_e)*Flow_Dir[1];
5108  Velocity_e[0]= UnitNormal[0]*NormalVelocity - UnitNormal[1]*TangVelocity;
5109  Velocity_e[1]= UnitNormal[1]*NormalVelocity + UnitNormal[0]*TangVelocity;
5110  }else{
5111  for (auto iDim = 0u; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
5112  Velocity_e[iDim] = sqrt(Velocity2_e)*Flow_Dir[iDim];
5113  }
5114  StaticEnthalpy_e = Enthalpy_e - 0.5 * Velocity2_e;
5115  GetFluidModel()->SetTDState_hs(StaticEnthalpy_e, Entropy_e);
5116  Density_e = GetFluidModel()->GetDensity();
5117  StaticEnergy_e = GetFluidModel()->GetStaticEnergy();
5118  Energy_e = StaticEnergy_e + 0.5 * Velocity2_e;
5119  if (tkeNeeded) Energy_e += GetTke_Inf();
5120  break;
5121 
5122  case STATIC_SUPERSONIC_INFLOW_PT:
5123 
5124  /*--- Retrieve the specified total conditions for this boundary. ---*/
5125  if (gravity) P_static = config->GetRiemann_Var1(Marker_Tag) - geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint, nDim-1)*STANDARD_GRAVITY;/// check in which case is true (only freesurface?)
5126  else P_static = config->GetRiemann_Var1(Marker_Tag);
5127  T_static = config->GetRiemann_Var2(Marker_Tag);
5128  Mach = config->GetRiemann_FlowDir(Marker_Tag);
5129 
5130  /*--- Non-dim. the inputs if necessary. ---*/
5131  P_static /= config->GetPressure_Ref();
5132  T_static /= config->GetTemperature_Ref();
5133 
5134  /* --- Computes the total state --- */
5135  GetFluidModel()->SetTDState_PT(P_static, T_static);
5136 
5137  /* --- Compute the boundary state u_e --- */
5138  for (auto iDim = 0u; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
5139  Velocity_e[iDim] = Mach[iDim]*GetFluidModel()->GetSoundSpeed();
5140 
5141  Velocity2_e = GeometryToolbox::SquaredNorm(nDim, Velocity_e);
5142  Density_e = GetFluidModel()->GetDensity();
5143  StaticEnergy_e = GetFluidModel()->GetStaticEnergy();
5144  Energy_e = StaticEnergy_e + 0.5 * Velocity2_e;
5145  if (tkeNeeded) Energy_e += GetTke_Inf();
5146  break;
5147 
5148  case STATIC_SUPERSONIC_INFLOW_PD:
5149 
5150  /*--- Retrieve the specified total conditions for this boundary. ---*/
5151 
5152  if (gravity) P_static = config->GetRiemann_Var1(Marker_Tag) - geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint, nDim-1)*STANDARD_GRAVITY;/// check in which case is true (only freesurface?)
5153  else P_static = config->GetRiemann_Var1(Marker_Tag);
5154  Density_static = config->GetRiemann_Var2(Marker_Tag);
5155  Mach = config->GetRiemann_FlowDir(Marker_Tag);
5156 
5157  /*--- Non-dim. the inputs if necessary. ---*/
5158  P_static /= config->GetPressure_Ref();
5159  Density_static /= config->GetDensity_Ref();
5160 
5161  /* --- Computes the total state --- */
5162  GetFluidModel()->SetTDState_Prho(P_static, Density_static);
5163 
5164  /* --- Compute the boundary state u_e --- */
5165  for (auto iDim = 0u; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
5166  Velocity_e[iDim] = Mach[iDim]*GetFluidModel()->GetSoundSpeed();
5167 
5168  Velocity2_e = GeometryToolbox::SquaredNorm(nDim, Velocity_e);
5169  Density_e = GetFluidModel()->GetDensity();
5170  StaticEnergy_e = GetFluidModel()->GetStaticEnergy();
5171  Energy_e = StaticEnergy_e + 0.5 * Velocity2_e;
5172  if (tkeNeeded) Energy_e += GetTke_Inf();
5173  break;
5174 
5175  case DENSITY_VELOCITY:
5176 
5177  /*--- Retrieve the specified density and velocity magnitude ---*/
5178  Density_e = config->GetRiemann_Var1(Marker_Tag);
5179  VelMag_e = config->GetRiemann_Var2(Marker_Tag);
5180  Flow_Dir = config->GetRiemann_FlowDir(Marker_Tag);
5181 
5182  /*--- Non-dim. the inputs if necessary. ---*/
5183  Density_e /= config->GetDensity_Ref();
5184  VelMag_e /= config->GetVelocity_Ref();
5185 
5186  for (auto iDim = 0u; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
5187  Velocity_e[iDim] = VelMag_e*Flow_Dir[iDim];
5188  Energy_e = Energy_i;
5189  break;
5190 
5191  case STATIC_PRESSURE:
5192 
5193  /*--- Retrieve the static pressure for this boundary. ---*/
5194  Pressure_e = config->GetRiemann_Var1(Marker_Tag);
5195  Pressure_e /= config->GetPressure_Ref();
5196  Density_e = Density_i;
5197 
5198  /* --- Compute the boundary state u_e --- */
5199  GetFluidModel()->SetTDState_Prho(Pressure_e, Density_e);
5200  for (auto iDim = 0u; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
5201  Velocity_e[iDim] = Velocity_i[iDim];
5202 
5203  Velocity2_e = GeometryToolbox::SquaredNorm(nDim, Velocity_e);
5204  Energy_e = GetFluidModel()->GetStaticEnergy() + 0.5*Velocity2_e;
5205  break;
5206 
5207  default:
5208  SU2_MPI::Error("Invalid Riemann input!", CURRENT_FUNCTION);
5209  break;
5210  }
5211 
5212  /*--- Compute P (matrix of right eigenvectors) ---*/
5213  conv_numerics->GetPMatrix(&Density_i, Velocity_i, &SoundSpeed_i, &Enthalpy_i, &Chi_i, &Kappa_i, UnitNormal, P_Tensor);
5214 
5215  /*--- Compute inverse P (matrix of left eigenvectors)---*/
5216  conv_numerics->GetPMatrix_inv(invP_Tensor, &Density_i, Velocity_i, &SoundSpeed_i, &Chi_i, &Kappa_i, UnitNormal);
5217 
5218  /*--- eigenvalues contribution due to grid motion ---*/
5219  su2double ProjVelocity_i = GeometryToolbox::DotProduct(nDim, Velocity_i, UnitNormal);
5220  if (dynamic_grid) {
5221  const auto gridVel = geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint);
5222  const su2double ProjGridVel = GeometryToolbox::DotProduct(nDim, gridVel, UnitNormal);
5223  ProjVelocity_i -= ProjGridVel;
5224  }
5225 
5226  /*--- Flow eigenvalues, boundary state u_e and u_i ---*/
5227  su2double Lambda_i[MAXNVAR] = {0}, u_e[MAXNVAR] = {0}, u_i[MAXNVAR]={0}, u_b[MAXNVAR]={0},
5228  dw[MAXNVAR]={0};
5229  u_e[0] = Density_e;
5230  u_i[0] = Density_i;
5231  for (auto iDim = 0u; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
5232  Lambda_i[iDim] = ProjVelocity_i;
5233  u_e[iDim+1] = Velocity_e[iDim]*Density_e;
5234  u_i[iDim+1] = Velocity_i[iDim]*Density_i;
5235  }
5236  Lambda_i[nVar-2] = ProjVelocity_i + SoundSpeed_i;
5237  Lambda_i[nVar-1] = ProjVelocity_i - SoundSpeed_i;
5238  u_e[nVar-1] = Energy_e*Density_e;
5239  u_i[nVar-1] = Energy_i*Density_i;
5240 
5241  /*--- Compute the characteristic jumps ---*/
5242  for (auto iVar = 0u; iVar < nVar; iVar++){
5243  dw[iVar] = 0;
5244  for (auto jVar = 0u; jVar < nVar; jVar++)
5245  dw[iVar] += invP_Tensor[iVar][jVar] * (u_e[jVar] - u_i[jVar]);
5246  }
5247 
5248  /*--- Compute the boundary state u_b using characteristics ---*/
5249  for (auto iVar = 0u; iVar < nVar; iVar++) {
5250  u_b[iVar] = u_i[iVar];
5251  for (auto jVar = 0u; jVar < nVar; jVar++) {
5252  if (Lambda_i[jVar] < 0)
5253  u_b[iVar] += P_Tensor[iVar][jVar]*dw[jVar];
5254  }
5255  }
5256 
5257  /*--- Compute the thermodynamic state in u_b ---*/
5258  su2double Velocity_b[MAXNDIM] = {0};
5259  const auto Density_b = u_b[0];
5260  for (auto iDim = 0u; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
5261  Velocity_b[iDim] = u_b[iDim+1]/Density_b;
5262  const auto Velocity2_b = GeometryToolbox::SquaredNorm(nDim, Velocity_b);
5263 
5264  const su2double Energy_b = u_b[nVar-1]/Density_b;
5265  const su2double StaticEnergy_b = Energy_b - 0.5*Velocity2_b;
5266  GetFluidModel()->SetTDState_rhoe(Density_b, StaticEnergy_b);
5267 
5268  /*--- Store number of Newton iterations at BC ---*/
5269  if(config->GetKind_FluidModel() == DATADRIVEN_FLUID)
5270  nodes->SetNewtonSolverIterations(iPoint, GetFluidModel()->GetnIter_Newton());
5271 
5272  const auto Pressure_b = GetFluidModel()->GetPressure();
5273  const auto Temperature_b = GetFluidModel()->GetTemperature();
5274  const su2double Enthalpy_b = Energy_b + Pressure_b/Density_b;
5275  const su2double Kappa_b = GetFluidModel()->GetdPde_rho() / Density_b;
5276  const su2double Chi_b = GetFluidModel()->GetdPdrho_e() - Kappa_b * StaticEnergy_b;
5277 
5278  /*--- Compute the residuals ---*/
5279  su2double Residual[MAXNVAR] = {0};
5280  conv_numerics->GetInviscidProjFlux(&Density_b, Velocity_b, &Pressure_b, &Enthalpy_b, Normal, Residual);
5281 
5282  /*--- Residual contribution due to grid motion ---*/
5283  if (dynamic_grid) {
5284  const auto gridVel = geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint);
5285  const auto projVelocity = GeometryToolbox::DotProduct(nDim, gridVel, Normal);
5286  for (auto iVar = 0u; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
5287  Residual[iVar] -= projVelocity *u_b[iVar];
5288  }
5289 
5290  /*--- Update residual value ---*/
5291  LinSysRes.AddBlock(iPoint, Residual);
5292 
5293  if (implicit) {
5294  su2double **Jacobian_b = new su2double*[nVar],
5295  **Jacobian_i = new su2double*[nVar];
5296  su2double **DubDu = new su2double*[nVar];
5297  for (auto iVar = 0u; iVar < nVar; iVar++){
5298  Jacobian_b[iVar] = new su2double[nVar];
5299  Jacobian_i[iVar] = new su2double[nVar];
5300  /*--- Initialize DubDu to unit matrix---*/
5301  DubDu[iVar] = new su2double[nVar];
5302  for (auto jVar=0u; jVar < nVar; jVar++)
5303  DubDu[iVar][jVar] = 0;
5304 
5305  DubDu[iVar][iVar]=1;
5306  }
5307 
5308  /*--- Compute DubDu -= RNL---*/
5309  for (auto iVar=0u; iVar<nVar; iVar++){
5310  for (auto jVar=0u; jVar<nVar; jVar++){
5311  for (auto kVar=0u; kVar<nVar; kVar++){
5312  if (Lambda_i[kVar]<0)
5313  DubDu[iVar][jVar] -= P_Tensor[iVar][kVar] * invP_Tensor[kVar][jVar];
5314  }
5315  }
5316  }
5317 
5318  /*--- Compute flux Jacobian in state b ---*/
5319  conv_numerics->GetInviscidProjJac(Velocity_b, &Enthalpy_b, &Chi_b, &Kappa_b, Normal, 1.0, Jacobian_b);
5320 
5321  /*--- Jacobian contribution due to grid motion ---*/
5322  if (dynamic_grid){
5323  const auto gridVel = geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint);
5324  const auto projVelocity = GeometryToolbox::DotProduct(nDim, gridVel, Normal);
5325  for (auto iVar = 0u; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
5326  Jacobian_b[iVar][iVar] -= projVelocity;
5327  }
5328 
5329  /*--- initiate Jacobian_i to zero matrix ---*/
5330  for (auto iVar=0u; iVar<nVar; iVar++) {
5331  for (auto jVar=0u; jVar<nVar; jVar++) {
5332  Jacobian_i[iVar][jVar] = 0.0;
5333  /*--- Compute numerical flux Jacobian at node i ---*/
5334  for (auto kVar=0u; kVar<nVar; kVar++)
5335  Jacobian_i[iVar][jVar] += Jacobian_b[iVar][kVar] * DubDu[kVar][jVar];
5336  }
5337  }
5338 
5339  /*--- Jacobian contribution for implicit integration ---*/
5340  Jacobian.AddBlock2Diag(iPoint, Jacobian_i);
5341 
5342  for (auto iVar = 0u; iVar < nVar; iVar++) {
5343  delete [] Jacobian_b[iVar];
5344  delete [] DubDu[iVar];
5345  delete [] Jacobian_i[iVar];
5346  }
5347  delete [] Jacobian_b;
5348  delete [] DubDu;
5349  delete [] Jacobian_i;
5350  }
5351 
5352  /*--- Viscous contribution ---*/
5353 
5354  if (viscous) {
5355 
5356  /*--- Primitive variables, using the derived quantities ---*/
5357  auto V_boundary= GetCharacPrimVar(val_marker, iVertex);
5358  V_boundary[prim_idx.Temperature()] = Temperature_b;
5359  for (auto iDim = 0u; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
5360  V_boundary[prim_idx.Velocity() + iDim] = Velocity_b[iDim];
5361  V_boundary[prim_idx.Pressure()] = Pressure_b;
5362  V_boundary[prim_idx.Density()] = Density_b;
5363  V_boundary[prim_idx.Enthalpy()] = Enthalpy_b;
5364 
5365  /*--- Set laminar and eddy viscosity at the infinity ---*/
5366 
5367  V_boundary[prim_idx.LaminarViscosity()] = GetFluidModel()->GetLaminarViscosity();
5368  V_boundary[prim_idx.EddyViscosity()] = nodes->GetEddyViscosity(iPoint);
5369  V_boundary[prim_idx.ThermalConductivity()] = GetFluidModel()->GetThermalConductivity();
5370  V_boundary[prim_idx.CpTotal()] = GetFluidModel()->GetCp();
5371 
5372  /*--- Set the normal vector and the coordinates ---*/
5373 
5374  visc_numerics->SetNormal(Normal);
5375  su2double Coord_Reflected[MAXNDIM];
5376  GeometryToolbox::PointPointReflect(nDim, geometry->nodes->GetCoord(Point_Normal),
5377  geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint), Coord_Reflected);
5378  visc_numerics->SetCoord(geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint), Coord_Reflected);
5379 
5380  /*--- Primitive variables, and gradient ---*/
5381 
5382  visc_numerics->SetPrimitive(V_domain, V_boundary);
5383  visc_numerics->SetPrimVarGradient(nodes->GetGradient_Primitive(iPoint), nodes->GetGradient_Primitive(iPoint));
5384 
5385  /*--- Secondary variables ---*/
5386 
5387  auto S_domain = nodes->GetSecondary(iPoint);
5388 
5389  /*--- Compute secondary thermodynamic properties (partial derivatives...) ---*/
5390  su2double S_boundary[8];
5391  S_boundary[0]= GetFluidModel()->GetdPdrho_e();
5392  S_boundary[1]= GetFluidModel()->GetdPde_rho();
5393 
5394  S_boundary[2]= GetFluidModel()->GetdTdrho_e();
5395  S_boundary[3]= GetFluidModel()->GetdTde_rho();
5396 
5397  /*--- Compute secondary thermo-physical properties (partial derivatives...) ---*/
5398 
5399  S_boundary[4]= GetFluidModel()->Getdmudrho_T();
5400  S_boundary[5]= GetFluidModel()->GetdmudT_rho();
5401 
5402  S_boundary[6]= GetFluidModel()->Getdktdrho_T();
5403  S_boundary[7]= GetFluidModel()->GetdktdT_rho();
5404 
5405  visc_numerics->SetSecondary(S_domain, S_boundary);
5406 
5407  /*--- Turbulent kinetic energy ---*/
5408 
5409  if (config->GetKind_Turb_Model() == TURB_MODEL::SST)
5410  visc_numerics->SetTurbKineticEnergy(solver_container[TURB_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetSolution(iPoint,0),
5411  solver_container[TURB_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetSolution(iPoint,0));
5412 
5413  /*--- Compute and update residual ---*/
5414  auto residual = visc_numerics->ComputeResidual(config);
5415  LinSysRes.SubtractBlock(iPoint, residual);
5416 
5417  /*--- Jacobian contribution for implicit integration ---*/
5418  if (implicit)
5419  Jacobian.SubtractBlock2Diag(iPoint, residual.jacobian_i);
5420 
5421  }
5422  /*--- Store number of Newton iterations at BC ---*/
5423  if(config->GetKind_FluidModel() == DATADRIVEN_FLUID)
5424  nodes->SetNewtonSolverIterations(iPoint, GetFluidModel()->GetnIter_Newton());
5425 
5426  }
5427  }
5428  END_SU2_OMP_FOR
5429 
5430  for(auto iVar=0u; iVar<nVar; iVar++) {
5431  delete [] P_Tensor[iVar];
5432  delete [] invP_Tensor[iVar];
5433  }
5434  delete[] P_Tensor;
5435  delete[] invP_Tensor;
5436 }
5437 
5438 
5439 void CEulerSolver::BC_TurboRiemann(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver_container,
5440  CNumerics *conv_numerics, CNumerics *visc_numerics,
5441  CConfig *config, unsigned short val_marker) {
5442 
5443  unsigned short iDim, iVar, jVar, kVar, iSpan;
5444  unsigned long iPoint, Point_Normal, oldVertex, iVertex;
5445  const su2double *Flow_Dir;
5446  su2double P_Total, T_Total;
5447  su2double *Velocity_b, Velocity2_b, Enthalpy_b, Energy_b, StaticEnergy_b, Density_b, Kappa_b, Chi_b, Pressure_b, Temperature_b;
5448  su2double *Velocity_e, Velocity2_e, Enthalpy_e, Entropy_e, Energy_e = 0.0, StaticEnthalpy_e, StaticEnergy_e, Density_e = 0.0, Pressure_e;
5449  su2double *Velocity_i, Velocity2_i, Enthalpy_i, Energy_i, StaticEnergy_i, Density_i, Kappa_i, Chi_i, Pressure_i, SoundSpeed_i;
5450  su2double ProjVelocity_i;
5451  su2double **P_Tensor, **invP_Tensor, *Lambda_i, **Jacobian_b, **Jacobian_i, **DubDu, *dw, *u_e, *u_i, *u_b;
5452  su2double *gridVel, *Residual;
5453  su2double *V_boundary, *V_domain, *S_boundary, *S_domain;
5454  su2double AverageEnthalpy, AverageEntropy;
5455  unsigned short iZone = config->GetiZone();
5456  bool implicit = (config->GetKind_TimeIntScheme() == EULER_IMPLICIT);
5457  string Marker_Tag = config->GetMarker_All_TagBound(val_marker);
5458  unsigned short nSpanWiseSections = geometry->GetnSpanWiseSections(config->GetMarker_All_TurbomachineryFlag(val_marker));
5459  bool viscous = config->GetViscous();
5460  bool gravity = (config->GetGravityForce());
5461  bool tkeNeeded = (config->GetKind_Turb_Model() == TURB_MODEL::SST);
5462 
5463  su2double *Normal, *turboNormal, *UnitNormal, *FlowDirMix, FlowDirMixMag, *turboVelocity;
5464  Normal = new su2double[nDim];
5465  turboNormal = new su2double[nDim];
5466  UnitNormal = new su2double[nDim];
5467 
5468  Velocity_i = new su2double[nDim];
5469  Velocity_b = new su2double[nDim];
5470  Velocity_e = new su2double[nDim];
5471  turboVelocity = new su2double[nDim];
5472  FlowDirMix = new su2double[nDim];
5473  Lambda_i = new su2double[nVar];
5474  u_i = new su2double[nVar];
5475  u_e = new su2double[nVar];
5476  u_b = new su2double[nVar];
5477  dw = new su2double[nVar];
5478 
5479  Residual = new su2double[nVar];
5480 
5481  S_boundary = new su2double[8];
5482 
5483  P_Tensor = new su2double*[nVar];
5484  invP_Tensor = new su2double*[nVar];
5485  Jacobian_i = new su2double*[nVar];
5486  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
5487  {
5488  P_Tensor[iVar] = new su2double[nVar];
5489  invP_Tensor[iVar] = new su2double[nVar];
5490  Jacobian_i[iVar] = new su2double[nVar];
5491  }
5492 
5493  /*--- Loop over all the vertices on this boundary marker ---*/
5494  for (iSpan= 0; iSpan < nSpanWiseSections; iSpan++){
5495 
5496  SU2_OMP_FOR_DYN(OMP_MIN_SIZE)
5497  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->GetnVertexSpan(val_marker,iSpan); iVertex++) {
5498 
5499  /*--- using the other vertex information for retrieving some information ---*/
5500  oldVertex = geometry->turbovertex[val_marker][iSpan][iVertex]->GetOldVertex();
5501  V_boundary= GetCharacPrimVar(val_marker, oldVertex);
5502 
5503  /*--- Index of the closest interior node ---*/
5504  Point_Normal = geometry->vertex[val_marker][oldVertex]->GetNormal_Neighbor();
5505 
5506  /*--- Normal vector for this vertex (negate for outward convention),
5507  * this normal is scaled with the area of the face of the element ---*/
5508  geometry->vertex[val_marker][oldVertex]->GetNormal(Normal);
5509  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) Normal[iDim] = -Normal[iDim];
5510  conv_numerics->SetNormal(Normal);
5511 
5512  /*--- find the node related to the vertex ---*/
5513  iPoint = geometry->turbovertex[val_marker][iSpan][iVertex]->GetNode();
5514  if (geometry->nodes->GetDomain(iPoint)){
5515 
5516  /*--- Normalize Normal vector for this vertex (already for outward convention) ---*/
5517  geometry->turbovertex[val_marker][iSpan][iVertex]->GetNormal(UnitNormal);
5518  geometry->turbovertex[val_marker][iSpan][iVertex]->GetTurboNormal(turboNormal);
5519 
5520  /*--- Retrieve solution at this boundary node ---*/
5521  V_domain = nodes->GetPrimitive(iPoint);
5522 
5523  /* --- Compute the internal state u_i --- */
5524  Velocity2_i = 0;
5525  for (iDim=0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
5526  {
5527  Velocity_i[iDim] = nodes->GetVelocity(iPoint,iDim);
5528  Velocity2_i += Velocity_i[iDim]*Velocity_i[iDim];
5529  }
5530 
5531  Density_i = nodes->GetDensity(iPoint);
5532 
5533  Energy_i = nodes->GetEnergy(iPoint);
5534  StaticEnergy_i = Energy_i - 0.5*Velocity2_i;
5535 
5536  GetFluidModel()->SetTDState_rhoe(Density_i, StaticEnergy_i);
5537 
5538  Pressure_i = GetFluidModel()->GetPressure();
5539  Enthalpy_i = Energy_i + Pressure_i/Density_i;
5540 
5541  SoundSpeed_i = GetFluidModel()->GetSoundSpeed();
5542 
5543  Kappa_i = GetFluidModel()->GetdPde_rho() / Density_i;
5544  Chi_i = GetFluidModel()->GetdPdrho_e() - Kappa_i * StaticEnergy_i;
5545 
5546  ProjVelocity_i = 0.0;
5547  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
5548  ProjVelocity_i += Velocity_i[iDim]*UnitNormal[iDim];
5549 
5550  /*--- Build the external state u_e from boundary data and internal node ---*/
5551 
5552  switch(config->GetKind_Data_Riemann(Marker_Tag))
5553  {
5554  //TODO(turbo), generilize for 3D case
5555  //TODO(turbo), generilize for Inlet and Outlet in for backflow treatment
5556  //TODO(turbo), implement not uniform inlet and radial equilibrium for the outlet
5557  case TOTAL_CONDITIONS_PT:
5558 
5559  /*--- Retrieve the specified total conditions for this boundary. ---*/
5560  if (gravity) P_Total = config->GetRiemann_Var1(Marker_Tag) - geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint, nDim-1)*STANDARD_GRAVITY;/// check in which case is true (only freesurface?)
5561  else P_Total = config->GetRiemann_Var1(Marker_Tag);
5562  T_Total = config->GetRiemann_Var2(Marker_Tag);
5563  Flow_Dir = config->GetRiemann_FlowDir(Marker_Tag);
5564 
5565  /*--- Non-dim. the inputs if necessary. ---*/
5566  P_Total /= config->GetPressure_Ref();
5567  T_Total /= config->GetTemperature_Ref();
5568 
5569  /* --- Computes the total state --- */
5570  GetFluidModel()->SetTDState_PT(P_Total, T_Total);
5571  Enthalpy_e = GetFluidModel()->GetStaticEnergy()+ GetFluidModel()->GetPressure()/GetFluidModel()->GetDensity();
5572  Entropy_e = GetFluidModel()->GetEntropy();
5573 
5574  /* --- Compute the boundary state u_e --- */
5575  Velocity2_e = Velocity2_i;
5576  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
5577  turboVelocity[iDim] = sqrt(Velocity2_e)*Flow_Dir[iDim];
5578  ComputeBackVelocity(turboVelocity,turboNormal, Velocity_e, config->GetMarker_All_TurbomachineryFlag(val_marker),config->GetKind_TurboMachinery(iZone));
5579  StaticEnthalpy_e = Enthalpy_e - 0.5 * Velocity2_e;
5580  GetFluidModel()->SetTDState_hs(StaticEnthalpy_e, Entropy_e);
5581  Density_e = GetFluidModel()->GetDensity();
5582  StaticEnergy_e = GetFluidModel()->GetStaticEnergy();
5583  Energy_e = StaticEnergy_e + 0.5 * Velocity2_e;
5584  if (tkeNeeded) Energy_e += GetTke_Inf();
5585  break;
5586 
5587  case MIXING_IN:
5588 
5589  /* --- compute total averaged quantities ---*/
5590  GetFluidModel()->SetTDState_Prho(ExtAveragePressure[val_marker][iSpan], ExtAverageDensity[val_marker][iSpan]);
5591  AverageEnthalpy = GetFluidModel()->GetStaticEnergy() + ExtAveragePressure[val_marker][iSpan]/ExtAverageDensity[val_marker][iSpan];
5592  AverageEntropy = GetFluidModel()->GetEntropy();
5593 
5594  FlowDirMixMag = 0;
5595  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
5596  FlowDirMixMag += ExtAverageTurboVelocity[val_marker][iSpan][iDim]*ExtAverageTurboVelocity[val_marker][iSpan][iDim];
5597  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++){
5598  FlowDirMix[iDim] = ExtAverageTurboVelocity[val_marker][iSpan][iDim]/sqrt(FlowDirMixMag);
5599  }
5600 
5601 
5602  /* --- Computes the total state --- */
5603  Enthalpy_e = AverageEnthalpy;
5604  Entropy_e = AverageEntropy;
5605 
5606  /* --- Compute the boundary state u_e --- */
5607  Velocity2_e = Velocity2_i;
5608  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++){
5609  turboVelocity[iDim] = sqrt(Velocity2_e)*FlowDirMix[iDim];
5610 
5611  }
5612  ComputeBackVelocity(turboVelocity,turboNormal, Velocity_e, config->GetMarker_All_TurbomachineryFlag(val_marker),config->GetKind_TurboMachinery(iZone));
5613 
5614  StaticEnthalpy_e = Enthalpy_e - 0.5 * Velocity2_e;
5615  GetFluidModel()->SetTDState_hs(StaticEnthalpy_e, Entropy_e);
5616  Density_e = GetFluidModel()->GetDensity();
5617  StaticEnergy_e = GetFluidModel()->GetStaticEnergy();
5618  Energy_e = StaticEnergy_e + 0.5 * Velocity2_e;
5619  // if (tkeNeeded) Energy_e += GetTke_Inf();
5620  break;
5621 
5622 
5623  case MIXING_OUT:
5624 
5625  /*--- Retrieve the static pressure for this boundary. ---*/
5626  Pressure_e = ExtAveragePressure[val_marker][iSpan];
5627  Density_e = Density_i;
5628 
5629  /* --- Compute the boundary state u_e --- */
5630  GetFluidModel()->SetTDState_Prho(Pressure_e, Density_e);
5631  Velocity2_e = 0.0;
5632  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
5633  Velocity_e[iDim] = Velocity_i[iDim];
5634  Velocity2_e += Velocity_e[iDim]*Velocity_e[iDim];
5635  }
5636  Energy_e = GetFluidModel()->GetStaticEnergy() + 0.5*Velocity2_e;
5637  break;
5638 
5639  case STATIC_PRESSURE:
5640 
5641  /*--- Retrieve the static pressure for this boundary. ---*/
5642  Pressure_e = config->GetRiemann_Var1(Marker_Tag);
5643  Pressure_e /= config->GetPressure_Ref();
5644  Density_e = Density_i;
5645 
5646  /* --- Compute the boundary state u_e --- */
5647  GetFluidModel()->SetTDState_Prho(Pressure_e, Density_e);
5648  Velocity2_e = 0.0;
5649  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
5650  Velocity_e[iDim] = Velocity_i[iDim];
5651  Velocity2_e += Velocity_e[iDim]*Velocity_e[iDim];
5652  }
5653  Energy_e = GetFluidModel()->GetStaticEnergy() + 0.5*Velocity2_e;
5654  break;
5655 
5656 
5657  case RADIAL_EQUILIBRIUM:
5658 
5659  /*--- Retrieve the static pressure for this boundary. ---*/
5660  Pressure_e = RadialEquilibriumPressure[val_marker][iSpan];
5661  Density_e = Density_i;
5662 
5663  /* --- Compute the boundary state u_e --- */
5664  GetFluidModel()->SetTDState_Prho(Pressure_e, Density_e);
5665  Velocity2_e = 0.0;
5666  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
5667  Velocity_e[iDim] = Velocity_i[iDim];
5668  Velocity2_e += Velocity_e[iDim]*Velocity_e[iDim];
5669  }
5670  Energy_e = GetFluidModel()->GetStaticEnergy() + 0.5*Velocity2_e;
5671  break;
5672 
5673  default:
5674  SU2_MPI::Error("Invalid Riemann input!", CURRENT_FUNCTION);
5675  break;
5676  }
5677 
5678  /*--- Compute P (matrix of right eigenvectors) ---*/
5679  conv_numerics->GetPMatrix(&Density_i, Velocity_i, &SoundSpeed_i, &Enthalpy_i, &Chi_i, &Kappa_i, UnitNormal, P_Tensor);
5680 
5681  /*--- Compute inverse P (matrix of left eigenvectors)---*/
5682  conv_numerics->GetPMatrix_inv(invP_Tensor, &Density_i, Velocity_i, &SoundSpeed_i, &Chi_i, &Kappa_i, UnitNormal);
5683 
5684  /*--- eigenvalues contribution due to grid motion ---*/
5685  if (dynamic_grid){
5686  gridVel = geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint);
5687
