5688  su2double ProjGridVel = 0.0;
5689  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
5690  ProjGridVel += gridVel[iDim]*UnitNormal[iDim];
5691  ProjVelocity_i -= ProjGridVel;
5692  }
5693 
5694  /*--- Flow eigenvalues ---*/
5695  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
5696  Lambda_i[iDim] = ProjVelocity_i;
5697  Lambda_i[nVar-2] = ProjVelocity_i + SoundSpeed_i;
5698  Lambda_i[nVar-1] = ProjVelocity_i - SoundSpeed_i;
5699 
5700  /* --- Compute the boundary state u_e --- */
5701  u_e[0] = Density_e;
5702  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
5703  u_e[iDim+1] = Velocity_e[iDim]*Density_e;
5704  u_e[nVar-1] = Energy_e*Density_e;
5705 
5706  /* --- Compute the boundary state u_i --- */
5707  u_i[0] = Density_i;
5708  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
5709  u_i[iDim+1] = Velocity_i[iDim]*Density_i;
5710  u_i[nVar-1] = Energy_i*Density_i;
5711 
5712  /*--- Compute the characteristic jumps ---*/
5713  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
5714  {
5715  dw[iVar] = 0;
5716  for (jVar = 0; jVar < nVar; jVar++)
5717  dw[iVar] += invP_Tensor[iVar][jVar] * (u_e[jVar] - u_i[jVar]);
5718 
5719  }
5720 
5721  /*--- Compute the boundary state u_b using characteristics ---*/
5722  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
5723  {
5724  u_b[iVar] = u_i[iVar];
5725 
5726  for (jVar = 0; jVar < nVar; jVar++)
5727  {
5728  if (Lambda_i[jVar] < 0)
5729  {
5730  u_b[iVar] += P_Tensor[iVar][jVar]*dw[jVar];
5731 
5732  }
5733  }
5734  }
5735 
5736 
5737  /*--- Compute the thermodynamic state in u_b ---*/
5738  Density_b = u_b[0];
5739  Velocity2_b = 0;
5740  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
5741  {
5742  Velocity_b[iDim] = u_b[iDim+1]/Density_b;
5743  Velocity2_b += Velocity_b[iDim]*Velocity_b[iDim];
5744  }
5745  Energy_b = u_b[nVar-1]/Density_b;
5746  StaticEnergy_b = Energy_b - 0.5*Velocity2_b;
5747  GetFluidModel()->SetTDState_rhoe(Density_b, StaticEnergy_b);
5748  Pressure_b = GetFluidModel()->GetPressure();
5749  Temperature_b = GetFluidModel()->GetTemperature();
5750  Enthalpy_b = Energy_b + Pressure_b/Density_b;
5751  Kappa_b = GetFluidModel()->GetdPde_rho() / Density_b;
5752  Chi_b = GetFluidModel()->GetdPdrho_e() - Kappa_b * StaticEnergy_b;
5753 
5754  /*--- Compute the residuals ---*/
5755  conv_numerics->GetInviscidProjFlux(&Density_b, Velocity_b, &Pressure_b, &Enthalpy_b, Normal, Residual);
5756 
5757  /*--- Residual contribution due to grid motion ---*/
5758  if (dynamic_grid) {
5759  gridVel = geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint);
5760  su2double projVelocity = 0.0;
5761 
5762  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
5763  projVelocity += gridVel[iDim]*Normal[iDim];
5764  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
5765  Residual[iVar] -= projVelocity *(u_b[iVar]);
5766  }
5767 
5768  if (implicit) {
5769 
5770  Jacobian_b = new su2double*[nVar];
5771  DubDu = new su2double*[nVar];
5772  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
5773  {
5774  Jacobian_b[iVar] = new su2double[nVar];
5775  DubDu[iVar] = new su2double[nVar];
5776  }
5777 
5778  /*--- Initialize DubDu to unit matrix---*/
5779 
5780  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
5781  {
5782  for (jVar = 0; jVar < nVar; jVar++)
5783  DubDu[iVar][jVar]= 0;
5784 
5785  DubDu[iVar][iVar]= 1;
5786  }
5787 
5788  /*--- Compute DubDu -= RNL---*/
5789  for (iVar=0; iVar<nVar; iVar++)
5790  {
5791  for (jVar=0; jVar<nVar; jVar++)
5792  {
5793  for (kVar=0; kVar<nVar; kVar++)
5794  {
5795  if (Lambda_i[kVar]<0)
5796  DubDu[iVar][jVar] -= P_Tensor[iVar][kVar] * invP_Tensor[kVar][jVar];
5797  }
5798  }
5799  }
5800 
5801  /*--- Compute flux Jacobian in state b ---*/
5802  conv_numerics->GetInviscidProjJac(Velocity_b, &Enthalpy_b, &Chi_b, &Kappa_b, Normal, 1.0, Jacobian_b);
5803 
5804  /*--- Jacobian contribution due to grid motion ---*/
5805  if (dynamic_grid)
5806  {
5807  gridVel = geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint);
5808  su2double projVelocity = 0.0;
5809  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
5810  projVelocity += gridVel[iDim]*Normal[iDim];
5811  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++){
5812  Residual[iVar] -= projVelocity *(u_b[iVar]);
5813  Jacobian_b[iVar][iVar] -= projVelocity;
5814  }
5815 
5816  }
5817 
5818  /*--- initiate Jacobian_i to zero matrix ---*/
5819  for (iVar=0; iVar<nVar; iVar++)
5820  for (jVar=0; jVar<nVar; jVar++)
5821  Jacobian_i[iVar][jVar] = 0.0;
5822 
5823  /*--- Compute numerical flux Jacobian at node i ---*/
5824  for (iVar=0; iVar<nVar; iVar++) {
5825  for (jVar=0; jVar<nVar; jVar++) {
5826  for (kVar=0; kVar<nVar; kVar++) {
5827  Jacobian_i[iVar][jVar] += Jacobian_b[iVar][kVar] * DubDu[kVar][jVar];
5828  }
5829  }
5830  }
5831 
5832  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++) {
5833  delete [] Jacobian_b[iVar];
5834  delete [] DubDu[iVar];
5835  }
5836  delete [] Jacobian_b;
5837  delete [] DubDu;
5838  }
5839 
5840  /*--- Update residual value ---*/
5841  LinSysRes.AddBlock(iPoint, Residual);
5842 
5843  /*--- Jacobian contribution for implicit integration ---*/
5844  if (implicit)
5845  Jacobian.AddBlock2Diag(iPoint, Jacobian_i);
5846 
5847  /*--- Viscous contribution ---*/
5848 
5849  if (viscous) {
5850 
5851  /*--- Primitive variables, using the derived quantities ---*/
5852 
5853  V_boundary[0] = Temperature_b;
5854  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
5855  V_boundary[iDim+1] = Velocity_b[iDim];
5856  V_boundary[nDim+1] = Pressure_b;
5857  V_boundary[nDim+2] = Density_b;
5858  V_boundary[nDim+3] = Enthalpy_b;
5859 
5860  /*--- Set laminar and eddy viscosity at the infinity ---*/
5861 
5862  V_boundary[nDim+5] = GetFluidModel()->GetLaminarViscosity();
5863  V_boundary[nDim+6] = nodes->GetEddyViscosity(iPoint);
5864  V_boundary[nDim+7] = GetFluidModel()->GetThermalConductivity();
5865  V_boundary[nDim+8] = GetFluidModel()->GetCp();
5866 
5867  /*--- Set the normal vector and the coordinates ---*/
5868 
5869  visc_numerics->SetNormal(Normal);
5870  su2double Coord_Reflected[MAXNDIM];
5871  GeometryToolbox::PointPointReflect(nDim, geometry->nodes->GetCoord(Point_Normal),
5872  geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint), Coord_Reflected);
5873  visc_numerics->SetCoord(geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint), Coord_Reflected);
5874 
5875  /*--- Primitive variables, and gradient ---*/
5876 
5877  visc_numerics->SetPrimitive(V_domain, V_boundary);
5878  visc_numerics->SetPrimVarGradient(nodes->GetGradient_Primitive(iPoint), nodes->GetGradient_Primitive(iPoint));
5879 
5880  /*--- Secondary variables ---*/
5881 
5882  S_domain = nodes->GetSecondary(iPoint);
5883 
5884  /*--- Compute secondary thermodynamic properties (partial derivatives...) ---*/
5885 
5886  S_boundary[0]= GetFluidModel()->GetdPdrho_e();
5887  S_boundary[1]= GetFluidModel()->GetdPde_rho();
5888 
5889  S_boundary[2]= GetFluidModel()->GetdTdrho_e();
5890  S_boundary[3]= GetFluidModel()->GetdTde_rho();
5891 
5892  /*--- Compute secondary thermo-physical properties (partial derivatives...) ---*/
5893 
5894  S_boundary[4]= GetFluidModel()->Getdmudrho_T();
5895  S_boundary[5]= GetFluidModel()->GetdmudT_rho();
5896 
5897  S_boundary[6]= GetFluidModel()->Getdktdrho_T();
5898  S_boundary[7]= GetFluidModel()->GetdktdT_rho();
5899 
5900  visc_numerics->SetSecondary(S_domain, S_boundary);
5901 
5902  /*--- Turbulent kinetic energy ---*/
5903 
5904  if (config->GetKind_Turb_Model() == TURB_MODEL::SST)
5905  visc_numerics->SetTurbKineticEnergy(solver_container[TURB_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetSolution(iPoint,0),
5906  solver_container[TURB_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetSolution(iPoint,0));
5907 
5908  /*--- Compute and update residual ---*/
5909 
5910  auto residual = visc_numerics->ComputeResidual(config);
5911  LinSysRes.SubtractBlock(iPoint, residual);
5912 
5913  /*--- Jacobian contribution for implicit integration ---*/
5914 
5915  if (implicit)
5916  Jacobian.SubtractBlock2Diag(iPoint, residual.jacobian_i);
5917 
5918  }
5919  }
5920  }
5921  END_SU2_OMP_FOR
5922  }
5923 
5924  /*--- Free locally allocated memory ---*/
5925  delete [] Normal;
5926  delete [] UnitNormal;
5927  delete [] turboNormal;
5928  delete [] turboVelocity;
5929  delete [] Velocity_e;
5930  delete [] Velocity_b;
5931  delete [] Velocity_i;
5932  delete [] FlowDirMix;
5933 
5934  delete [] S_boundary;
5935  delete [] Lambda_i;
5936  delete [] u_i;
5937  delete [] u_e;
5938  delete [] u_b;
5939  delete [] dw;
5940 
5941  delete [] Residual;
5942 
5943  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
5944  {
5945  delete [] P_Tensor[iVar];
5946  delete [] invP_Tensor[iVar];
5947  delete [] Jacobian_i[iVar];
5948  }
5949  delete [] P_Tensor;
5950  delete [] invP_Tensor;
5951  delete [] Jacobian_i;
5952 
5953 }

5955 void CEulerSolver::PreprocessBC_Giles(CGeometry *geometry, CConfig *config, CNumerics *conv_numerics, unsigned short marker_flag) {
5956  /* Implementation of Fuorier Transformations for non-regfelcting BC will come soon */
5957  su2double cj_inf,cj_out1, cj_out2, Density_i, Pressure_i, *turboNormal, *turboVelocity, *Velocity_i, AverageSoundSpeed;
5958  su2double *deltaprim, *cj, TwoPiThetaFreq_Pitch, pitch, theta, deltaTheta;
5959  unsigned short iMarker, iSpan, iMarkerTP, iDim;
5960  unsigned long iPoint, kend_max, k, iVertex;
5961  long freq;
5962  unsigned short iZone = config->GetiZone();
5963  unsigned short nSpanWiseSections = geometry->GetnSpanWiseSections(marker_flag);
5964  turboNormal = new su2double[nDim];
5965  turboVelocity = new su2double[nDim];
5966  Velocity_i = new su2double[nDim];
5967  deltaprim = new su2double[nVar];
5968  cj = new su2double[nVar];
5969  complex<su2double> I, expArg;
5970  static complex<su2double> cktemp_inf, cktemp_out1, cktemp_out2;
5971  I = complex<su2double>(0.0,1.0);
5972 
5973  kend_max = geometry->GetnFreqSpanMax(marker_flag);
5974  for (iSpan= 0; iSpan < nSpanWiseSections ; iSpan++){
5975  for(k=0; k < 2*kend_max+1; k++){
5976  freq = k - kend_max;
5977  SU2_OMP_MASTER
5978  {
5979  cktemp_inf = complex<su2double>(0.0,0.0);
5980  cktemp_out1 = complex<su2double>(0.0,0.0);
5981  cktemp_out2 = complex<su2double>(0.0,0.0);
5982  } END_SU2_OMP_MASTER
5983  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < config->GetnMarker_All(); iMarker++){
5984  for (iMarkerTP=1; iMarkerTP < config->GetnMarker_Turbomachinery()+1; iMarkerTP++){
5985  if (config->GetMarker_All_Turbomachinery(iMarker) == iMarkerTP){
5986  if (config->GetMarker_All_TurbomachineryFlag(iMarker) == marker_flag){
5987  complex<su2double> cktemp_inf_local{0.,0.},cktemp_out1_local{0.,0.}, cktemp_out2_local{0.,0.};
5988  SU2_OMP_FOR_DYN(roundUpDiv(geometry->GetnVertexSpan(iMarker,iSpan), 2*omp_get_max_threads()))
5989  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->GetnVertexSpan(iMarker,iSpan); iVertex++) {
5990 
5991  /*--- find the node related to the vertex ---*/
5992  iPoint = geometry->turbovertex[iMarker][iSpan][iVertex]->GetNode();
5993 
5994  geometry->turbovertex[iMarker][iSpan][iVertex]->GetTurboNormal(turboNormal);
5995  /*--- Compute the internal state _i ---*/
5996 
5997  Pressure_i = nodes->GetPressure(iPoint);
5998  Density_i = nodes->GetDensity(iPoint);
5999  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
6000  {
6001  Velocity_i[iDim] = nodes->GetVelocity(iPoint,iDim);
6002  }
6003 
6004  ComputeTurboVelocity(Velocity_i, turboNormal, turboVelocity, marker_flag, config->GetKind_TurboMachinery(iZone));
6005 
6006  if(nDim ==2){
6007  deltaprim[0] = Density_i - AverageDensity[iMarker][iSpan];
6008  deltaprim[1] = turboVelocity[0] - AverageTurboVelocity[iMarker][iSpan][0];
6009  deltaprim[2] = turboVelocity[1] - AverageTurboVelocity[iMarker][iSpan][1];
6010  deltaprim[3] = Pressure_i - AveragePressure[iMarker][iSpan];
6011  }
6012  else{
6013  //Here 3d
6014  deltaprim[0] = Density_i - AverageDensity[iMarker][iSpan];
6015  deltaprim[1] = turboVelocity[0] - AverageTurboVelocity[iMarker][iSpan][0];
6016  deltaprim[2] = turboVelocity[1] - AverageTurboVelocity[iMarker][iSpan][1];
6017  deltaprim[3] = turboVelocity[2] - AverageTurboVelocity[iMarker][iSpan][2]; //New char
6018  deltaprim[4] = Pressure_i - AveragePressure[iMarker][iSpan];
6019  }
6020 
6021  GetFluidModel()->SetTDState_Prho(AveragePressure[iMarker][iSpan], AverageDensity[iMarker][iSpan]);
6022  AverageSoundSpeed = GetFluidModel()->GetSoundSpeed();
6023  conv_numerics->GetCharJump(AverageSoundSpeed, AverageDensity[iMarker][iSpan], deltaprim, cj);
6024 
6025  /*-----this is only valid 2D ----*/
6026  if(nDim ==2){
6027  cj_out1 = cj[1];
6028  cj_out2 = cj[2];
6029  cj_inf = cj[3];
6030  }
6031  else{
6032  //Here 3D
6033  cj_out1 = cj[1];
6034  cj_out2 = cj[3];
6035  cj_inf = cj[4];
6036  }
6037  pitch = geometry->GetMaxAngularCoord(iMarker, iSpan) - geometry->GetMinAngularCoord(iMarker,iSpan);
6038  theta = geometry->turbovertex[iMarker][iSpan][iVertex]->GetRelAngularCoord();
6039  deltaTheta = geometry->turbovertex[iMarker][iSpan][iVertex]->GetDeltaAngularCoord();
6040  TwoPiThetaFreq_Pitch = 2*PI_NUMBER*freq*theta/pitch;
6041 
6042  expArg = complex<su2double>(cos(TwoPiThetaFreq_Pitch)) - I*complex<su2double>(sin(TwoPiThetaFreq_Pitch));
6043  if (freq != 0){
6044  cktemp_out1_local += cj_out1*expArg*deltaTheta/pitch;
6045  cktemp_out2_local += cj_out2*expArg*deltaTheta/pitch;
6046  cktemp_inf_local += cj_inf*expArg*deltaTheta/pitch;
6047  }
6048  else{
6049  cktemp_inf_local += complex<su2double>(0.0,0.0);
6050  cktemp_out1_local += complex<su2double>(0.0,0.0);
6051  cktemp_out2_local += complex<su2double>(0.0,0.0);
6052  }
6053  }
6054  END_SU2_OMP_FOR
6055  SU2_OMP_CRITICAL
6056  {
6057  cktemp_inf += cktemp_inf_local;
6058  cktemp_out1 += cktemp_out1_local;
6059  cktemp_out2 += cktemp_out2_local;
6060  } END_SU2_OMP_CRITICAL
6061  }
6062  }
6063  }
6064  }
6065 
6066  BEGIN_SU2_OMP_SAFE_GLOBAL_ACCESS
6067  {
6068 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
6069  su2double MyRe_inf = cktemp_inf.real(); su2double Re_inf = 0.0;
6070  su2double MyIm_inf = cktemp_inf.imag(); su2double Im_inf = 0.0;
6071  cktemp_inf = complex<su2double>(0.0,0.0);
6072 
6073  su2double MyRe_out1 = cktemp_out1.real(); su2double Re_out1 = 0.0;
6074  su2double MyIm_out1 = cktemp_out1.imag(); su2double Im_out1 = 0.0;
6075  cktemp_out1 = complex<su2double>(0.0,0.0);
6076 
6077  su2double MyRe_out2 = cktemp_out2.real(); su2double Re_out2 = 0.0;
6078  su2double MyIm_out2 = cktemp_out2.imag(); su2double Im_out2 = 0.0;
6079  cktemp_out2 = complex<su2double>(0.0,0.0);
6080 
6081 
6082  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(&MyRe_inf, &Re_inf, 1, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
6083  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(&MyIm_inf, &Im_inf, 1, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
6084  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(&MyRe_out1, &Re_out1, 1, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
6085  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(&MyIm_out1, &Im_out1, 1, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
6086  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(&MyRe_out2, &Re_out2, 1, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
6087  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(&MyIm_out2, &Im_out2, 1, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
6088 
6089  cktemp_inf = complex<su2double>(Re_inf,Im_inf);
6090  cktemp_out1 = complex<su2double>(Re_out1,Im_out1);
6091  cktemp_out2 = complex<su2double>(Re_out2,Im_out2);
6092 #endif
6093 
6094  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < config->GetnMarker_All(); iMarker++){
6095  for (iMarkerTP=1; iMarkerTP < config->GetnMarker_Turbomachinery()+1; iMarkerTP++){
6096  if (config->GetMarker_All_Turbomachinery(iMarker) == iMarkerTP){
6097  if (config->GetMarker_All_TurbomachineryFlag(iMarker) == marker_flag){
6098  /*-----this is only valid 2D ----*/
6099  if (marker_flag == INFLOW){
6100  CkInflow[iMarker][iSpan][k]= cktemp_inf;
6101  }else{
6102  CkOutflow1[iMarker][iSpan][k]=cktemp_out1;
6103  CkOutflow2[iMarker][iSpan][k]=cktemp_out2;
6104  }
6105  }
6106  }
6107  }
6108  }
6109  } END_SU2_OMP_SAFE_GLOBAL_ACCESS
6110  }
6111  }
6112 
6113  delete [] turboVelocity;
6114  delete [] turboNormal;
6115  delete [] Velocity_i;
6116  delete [] deltaprim;
6117  delete [] cj;
6118 
6119 }

6121 void CEulerSolver::BC_Giles(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver_container, CNumerics *conv_numerics,
6122  CNumerics *visc_numerics, CConfig *config, unsigned short val_marker) {
6123 
6124  unsigned short iDim, iVar, jVar, iSpan;
6125  unsigned long iPoint, Point_Normal, oldVertex, k, kend, kend_max, iVertex;
6126  su2double *UnitNormal, *turboVelocity, *turboNormal;
6127 
6128  su2double *Velocity_b, Velocity2_b, Enthalpy_b, Energy_b, Density_b, Pressure_b, Temperature_b;
6129  su2double *Velocity_i, Velocity2_i, Energy_i, StaticEnergy_i, Density_i, Pressure_i;
6130  su2double Pressure_e;
6131  su2double *V_boundary, *V_domain, *S_boundary, *S_domain;
6132  unsigned short iZone = config->GetiZone();
6133  bool implicit = (config->GetKind_TimeIntScheme() == EULER_IMPLICIT);
6134  string Marker_Tag = config->GetMarker_All_TagBound(val_marker);
6135  bool viscous = config->GetViscous();
6136  unsigned short nSpanWiseSections = geometry->GetnSpanWiseSections(config->GetMarker_All_TurbomachineryFlag(val_marker));
6137  su2double relfacAvgCfg = config->GetGiles_RelaxFactorAverage(Marker_Tag);
6138  su2double relfacFouCfg = config->GetGiles_RelaxFactorFourier(Marker_Tag);
6139  su2double *Normal;
6140  su2double TwoPiThetaFreq_Pitch, pitch,theta;
6141  const su2double *SpanWiseValues = nullptr, *FlowDir;
6142  su2double spanPercent, extrarelfacAvg = 0.0, deltaSpan = 0.0, relfacAvg, relfacFou, coeffrelfacAvg = 0.0;
6143  unsigned short Turbo_Flag;
6144 
6145  Normal = new su2double[nDim];
6146  turboNormal = new su2double[nDim];
6147  UnitNormal = new su2double[nDim];
6148  turboVelocity = new su2double[nDim];
6149  Velocity_i = new su2double[nDim];
6150  Velocity_b = new su2double[nDim];
6151 
6152 
6153  su2double AverageSoundSpeed, *AverageTurboMach, AverageEntropy, AverageEnthalpy;
6154  AverageTurboMach = new su2double[nDim];
6155  S_boundary = new su2double[8];
6156 
6157  su2double AvgMach , *cj, GilesBeta, *delta_c, **R_Matrix, *deltaprim, **R_c_inv,**R_c, alphaIn_BC, gammaIn_BC = 0,
6158  P_Total, T_Total, Enthalpy_BC, Entropy_BC, *R, *c_avg,*dcjs, Beta_inf2, c2js_Re, c3js_Re, cOutjs_Re, avgVel2 =0.0;
6159 
6160  long freq;
6161 
6162  delta_c = new su2double[nVar];
6163  deltaprim = new su2double[nVar];
6164  cj = new su2double[nVar];
6165  R_Matrix = new su2double*[nVar];
6166  R_c = new su2double*[nVar-1];
6167  R_c_inv = new su2double*[nVar-1];
6168  R = new su2double[nVar-1];
6169  c_avg = new su2double[nVar];
6170  dcjs = new su2double[nVar];
6171 
6172  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
6173  {
6174  R_Matrix[iVar] = new su2double[nVar];
6175  c_avg[iVar] = 0.0;
6176  dcjs[iVar] = 0.0;
6177  }
6178  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar-1; iVar++)
6179  {
6180  R_c[iVar] = new su2double[nVar-1];
6181  R_c_inv[iVar] = new su2double[nVar-1];
6182  }
6183 
6184 
6185  complex<su2double> I, c2ks, c2js, c3ks, c3js, cOutks, cOutjs, Beta_inf;
6186  I = complex<su2double>(0.0,1.0);
6187 
6188  /*--- Compute coeff for under relaxation of Avg and Fourier Coefficient for hub and shroud---*/
6189  if (nDim == 3){
6190  extrarelfacAvg = config->GetExtraRelFacGiles(0);
6191  spanPercent = config->GetExtraRelFacGiles(1);
6192  Turbo_Flag = config->GetMarker_All_TurbomachineryFlag(val_marker);
6193  SpanWiseValues = geometry->GetSpanWiseValue(Turbo_Flag);
6194  deltaSpan = SpanWiseValues[nSpanWiseSections-1]*spanPercent;
6195  coeffrelfacAvg = (relfacAvgCfg - extrarelfacAvg)/deltaSpan;
6196  }
6197 
6198  for (iSpan= 0; iSpan < nSpanWiseSections ; iSpan++){
6199  /*--- Compute under relaxation for the Hub and Shroud Avg and Fourier Coefficient---*/
6200  if(nDim == 3){
6201  if(SpanWiseValues[iSpan] <= SpanWiseValues[0] + deltaSpan){
6202  relfacAvg = extrarelfacAvg + coeffrelfacAvg*(SpanWiseValues[iSpan] - SpanWiseValues[0]);
6203  relfacFou = 0.0;
6204  }
6205  else if(SpanWiseValues[iSpan] >= SpanWiseValues[nSpanWiseSections -1] - deltaSpan){
6206  relfacAvg = extrarelfacAvg - coeffrelfacAvg*(SpanWiseValues[iSpan] - SpanWiseValues[nSpanWiseSections -1]);
6207  relfacFou = 0.0;
6208  }
6209  else{
6210  relfacAvg = relfacAvgCfg;
6211  relfacFou = relfacFouCfg;
6212  }
6213  }
6214  else{
6215  {
6216  relfacAvg = relfacAvgCfg;
6217  relfacFou = relfacFouCfg;
6218  }
6219  }
6220 
6221  GetFluidModel()->SetTDState_Prho(AveragePressure[val_marker][iSpan], AverageDensity[val_marker][iSpan]);
6222  AverageSoundSpeed = GetFluidModel()->GetSoundSpeed();
6223  AverageTurboMach[0] = AverageTurboVelocity[val_marker][iSpan][0]/AverageSoundSpeed;
6224  AverageTurboMach[1] = AverageTurboVelocity[val_marker][iSpan][1]/AverageSoundSpeed;
6225 
6226  if(dynamic_grid){
6227  AverageTurboMach[1] -= geometry->GetAverageTangGridVel(val_marker,iSpan)/AverageSoundSpeed;
6228  }
6229 
6230  AvgMach = AverageTurboMach[0]*AverageTurboMach[0] + AverageTurboMach[1]*AverageTurboMach[1];
6231

6234  conv_numerics->GetRMatrix(AverageSoundSpeed, AverageDensity[val_marker][iSpan], R_Matrix);
6235 
6236  switch(config->GetKind_Data_Giles(Marker_Tag)){
6237 
6238  case TOTAL_CONDITIONS_PT:
6239 
6240  /*--- Retrieve the specified total conditions for this inlet. ---*/
6241  P_Total = config->GetGiles_Var1(Marker_Tag);
6242  T_Total = config->GetGiles_Var2(Marker_Tag);
6243  FlowDir = config->GetGiles_FlowDir(Marker_Tag);
6244  alphaIn_BC = atan(FlowDir[1]/FlowDir[0]);
6245 
6246  gammaIn_BC = 0;
6247  if (nDim == 3){
6248  gammaIn_BC = FlowDir[2]; //atan(FlowDir[2]/FlowDir[0]);
6249  }
6250 
6251  /*--- Non-dim. the inputs---*/
6252  P_Total /= config->GetPressure_Ref();
6253  T_Total /= config->GetTemperature_Ref();
6254

6256  GetFluidModel()->SetTDState_PT(P_Total, T_Total);
6257  Enthalpy_BC = GetFluidModel()->GetStaticEnergy()+ GetFluidModel()->GetPressure()/GetFluidModel()->GetDensity();
6258  Entropy_BC = GetFluidModel()->GetEntropy();
6259 
6260 
6261  /* --- Computes the inverse matrix R_c --- */
6262  conv_numerics->ComputeResJacobianGiles(GetFluidModel(), AveragePressure[val_marker][iSpan], AverageDensity[val_marker][iSpan],
6263  AverageTurboVelocity[val_marker][iSpan], alphaIn_BC, gammaIn_BC, R_c, R_c_inv);
6264 
6265  GetFluidModel()->SetTDState_Prho(AveragePressure[val_marker][iSpan], AverageDensity[val_marker][iSpan]);
6266  AverageEnthalpy = GetFluidModel()->GetStaticEnergy() + AveragePressure[val_marker][iSpan]/AverageDensity[val_marker][iSpan];
6267  AverageEntropy = GetFluidModel()->GetEntropy();
6268 
6269  avgVel2 = 0.0;
6270  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) avgVel2 += AverageVelocity[val_marker][iSpan][iDim]*AverageVelocity[val_marker][iSpan][iDim];
6271  if (nDim == 2){
6272  R[0] = -(AverageEntropy - Entropy_BC);
6273  R[1] = -(AverageTurboVelocity[val_marker][iSpan][1] - tan(alphaIn_BC)*AverageTurboVelocity[val_marker][iSpan][0]);
6274  R[2] = -(AverageEnthalpy + 0.5*avgVel2 - Enthalpy_BC);
6275  }
6276 
6277  else{
6278  R[0] = -(AverageEntropy - Entropy_BC);
6279  R[1] = -(AverageTurboVelocity[val_marker][iSpan][1] - tan(alphaIn_BC)*AverageTurboVelocity[val_marker][iSpan][0]);
6280  R[2] = -(AverageTurboVelocity[val_marker][iSpan][2] - tan(gammaIn_BC)*AverageTurboVelocity[val_marker][iSpan][0]);
6281  R[3] = -(AverageEnthalpy + 0.5*avgVel2 - Enthalpy_BC);
6282 
6283  }
6284  /* --- Compute the avg component c_avg = R_c^-1 * R --- */
6285  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar-1; iVar++){
6286  c_avg[iVar] = 0.0;
6287  for (jVar = 0; jVar < nVar-1; jVar++){
6288  c_avg[iVar] += R_c_inv[iVar][jVar]*R[jVar];
6289  }
6290  }
6291  break;
6292 
6293  case TOTAL_CONDITIONS_PT_1D:
6294 
6295  /*--- Retrieve the specified total conditions for this inlet. ---*/
6296  P_Total = config->GetGiles_Var1(Marker_Tag);
6297  T_Total = config->GetGiles_Var2(Marker_Tag);
6298  FlowDir = config->GetGiles_FlowDir(Marker_Tag);
6299  alphaIn_BC = atan(FlowDir[1]/FlowDir[0]);
6300 
6301  gammaIn_BC = 0;
6302  if (nDim == 3){
6303  // Review definition of angle
6304  gammaIn_BC = FlowDir[2]; //atan(FlowDir[2]/FlowDir[0]);
6305  }
6306 
6307  /*--- Non-dim. the inputs---*/
6308  P_Total /= config->GetPressure_Ref();
6309  T_Total /= config->GetTemperature_Ref();
6310 
6311  /* --- Computes the total state --- */
6312  GetFluidModel()->SetTDState_PT(P_Total, T_Total);
6313  Enthalpy_BC = GetFluidModel()->GetStaticEnergy()+ GetFluidModel()->GetPressure()/GetFluidModel()->GetDensity();
6314  Entropy_BC = GetFluidModel()->GetEntropy();

6318  conv_numerics->ComputeResJacobianGiles(GetFluidModel(), AveragePressure[val_marker][iSpan], AverageDensity[val_marker][iSpan],
6319  AverageTurboVelocity[val_marker][iSpan], alphaIn_BC, gammaIn_BC, R_c, R_c_inv);
6320 
6321  GetFluidModel()->SetTDState_Prho(AveragePressure[val_marker][nSpanWiseSections], AverageDensity[val_marker][nSpanWiseSections]);
6322  AverageEnthalpy = GetFluidModel()->GetStaticEnergy() + AveragePressure[val_marker][nSpanWiseSections]/AverageDensity[val_marker][nSpanWiseSections];
6323  AverageEntropy = GetFluidModel()->GetEntropy();
6324 
6325 
6326  avgVel2 = 0.0;
6327  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) avgVel2 += AverageVelocity[val_marker][iSpan][iDim]*AverageVelocity[val_marker][iSpan][iDim];
6328  if (nDim == 2){
6329  R[0] = -(AverageEntropy - Entropy_BC);
6330  R[1] = -(AverageTurboVelocity[val_marker][nSpanWiseSections][1] - tan(alphaIn_BC)*AverageTurboVelocity[val_marker][nSpanWiseSections][0]);
6331  R[2] = -(AverageEnthalpy + 0.5*avgVel2 - Enthalpy_BC);
6332  }
6333 
6334  else{
6335  R[0] = -(AverageEntropy - Entropy_BC);
6336  R[1] = -(AverageTurboVelocity[val_marker][nSpanWiseSections][1] - tan(alphaIn_BC)*AverageTurboVelocity[val_marker][nSpanWiseSections][0]);
6337  R[2] = -(AverageTurboVelocity[val_marker][nSpanWiseSections][2] - tan(gammaIn_BC)*AverageTurboVelocity[val_marker][nSpanWiseSections][0]);
6338  R[3] = -(AverageEnthalpy + 0.5*avgVel2 - Enthalpy_BC);
6339 
6340  }
6341  /* --- Compute the avg component c_avg = R_c^-1 * R --- */
6342  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar-1; iVar++){
6343  c_avg[iVar] = 0.0;
6344  for (jVar = 0; jVar < nVar-1; jVar++){
6345  c_avg[iVar] += R_c_inv[iVar][jVar]*R[jVar];
6346  }
6347  }
6348  break;
6349 
6350  case MIXING_IN: case MIXING_OUT:
6351 
6352  /* --- Compute average jump of primitive at the mixing-plane interface--- */
6353  deltaprim[0] = ExtAverageDensity[val_marker][iSpan] - AverageDensity[val_marker][iSpan];
6354  deltaprim[1] = ExtAverageTurboVelocity[val_marker][iSpan][0] - AverageTurboVelocity[val_marker][iSpan][0];
6355  deltaprim[2] = ExtAverageTurboVelocity[val_marker][iSpan][1] - AverageTurboVelocity[val_marker][iSpan][1];
6356  if (nDim == 2){
6357  deltaprim[3] = ExtAveragePressure[val_marker][iSpan] - AveragePressure[val_marker][iSpan];
6358  }
6359  else
6360  {
6361  deltaprim[3] = ExtAverageTurboVelocity[val_marker][iSpan][2] - AverageTurboVelocity[val_marker][iSpan][2];
6362  deltaprim[4] = ExtAveragePressure[val_marker][iSpan] - AveragePressure[val_marker][iSpan];
6363  }
6364

6367  GetFluidModel()->SetTDState_Prho(AveragePressure[val_marker][iSpan], AverageDensity[val_marker][iSpan]);

6391  break;
6392

6395  Pressure_e = config->GetGiles_Var1(Marker_Tag);
6396  Pressure_e /= config->GetPressure_Ref();
6397 
6398  /* --- Compute avg characteristic jump --- */
6399  if (nDim == 2){
6400  c_avg[3] = -2.0*(AveragePressure[val_marker][iSpan]-Pressure_e);
6401  }
6402  else
6403  {
6404  c_avg[4] = -2.0*(AveragePressure[val_marker][iSpan]-Pressure_e);
6405  }

6407

6409  Pressure_e = config->GetGiles_Var1(Marker_Tag);
6410  Pressure_e /= config->GetPressure_Ref();

6413  if (nDim == 2){
6414  c_avg[3] = -2.0*(AveragePressure[val_marker][nSpanWiseSections]-Pressure_e);
6415  }
6416  else
6417  {
6418  c_avg[4] = -2.0*(AveragePressure[val_marker][nSpanWiseSections]-Pressure_e);
6419  }
6420  break;
6421

6423  Pressure_e = RadialEquilibriumPressure[val_marker][iSpan];
6424 
6425  /* --- Compute avg characteristic jump --- */
6426  c_avg[4] = -2.0*(AveragePressure[val_marker][iSpan]-Pressure_e);
6427 
6428  break;
6429 
6430  case MASS_FLOW_OUTLET:
6431  auto const MassFlowRate_e = config->GetGiles_Var1(Marker_Tag);
6432  auto const relFacMassFlowRate = config->GetGiles_Var2(Marker_Tag);
6433

6435

6437  c_avg[nDim + 1] = -2.0*(AveragePressure[val_marker][iSpan]-Pressure_e);
6438  break;
6439 
6440  }
6441 
6442  /*--- Loop over all the vertices on this boundary marker ---*/
6443 
6444  SU2_OMP_FOR_DYN(OMP_MIN_SIZE)
6445  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->GetnVertexSpan(val_marker,iSpan); iVertex++) {
6446 
6447  /*--- using the other vertex information for retrieving some information ---*/
6448  oldVertex = geometry->turbovertex[val_marker][iSpan][iVertex]->GetOldVertex();
6449  V_boundary= GetCharacPrimVar(val_marker, oldVertex);
6450 
6451  /*--- Index of the closest interior node ---*/
6452  Point_Normal = geometry->vertex[val_marker][oldVertex]->GetNormal_Neighbor();
6453 
6454  /*--- Normal vector for this vertex (negate for outward convention),
6455  * this normal is scaled with the area of the face of the element ---*/
6456  geometry->vertex[val_marker][oldVertex]->GetNormal(Normal);
6457  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) Normal[iDim] = -Normal[iDim];
6458  conv_numerics->SetNormal(Normal);
6459 
6460  /*--- find the node related to the vertex ---*/
6461  iPoint = geometry->turbovertex[val_marker][iSpan][iVertex]->GetNode();
6462 
6463  /*--- Normalize Normal vector for this vertex (already for outward convention) ---*/
6464  geometry->turbovertex[val_marker][iSpan][iVertex]->GetNormal(UnitNormal);
6465  geometry->turbovertex[val_marker][iSpan][iVertex]->GetTurboNormal(turboNormal);
6466
