6468  V_domain = nodes->GetPrimitive(iPoint);
6469 
6470  /*--- Retrieve domain Secondary variables ---*/
6471  S_domain = nodes->GetSecondary(iPoint);
6472 
6473 
6474  /*--- Compute the internal state u_i ---*/
6475  Velocity2_i = 0;
6476  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
6477  {
6478  Velocity_i[iDim] = nodes->GetVelocity(iPoint,iDim);
6479  Velocity2_i += Velocity_i[iDim]*Velocity_i[iDim];
6480  }
6481 
6482 
6483  Density_i = nodes->GetDensity(iPoint);
6484 
6485  Energy_i = nodes->GetEnergy(iPoint);
6486  StaticEnergy_i = Energy_i - 0.5*Velocity2_i;
6487 
6488  GetFluidModel()->SetTDState_rhoe(Density_i, StaticEnergy_i);
6489 
6490  Pressure_i = GetFluidModel()->GetPressure();
6491 
6492  ComputeTurboVelocity(Velocity_i, turboNormal, turboVelocity, config->GetMarker_All_TurbomachineryFlag(val_marker),config->GetKind_TurboMachinery(iZone));
6493  if (nDim == 2){
6494  deltaprim[0] = Density_i - AverageDensity[val_marker][iSpan];
6495  deltaprim[1] = turboVelocity[0] - AverageTurboVelocity[val_marker][iSpan][0];
6496  deltaprim[2] = turboVelocity[1] - AverageTurboVelocity[val_marker][iSpan][1];
6497  deltaprim[3] = Pressure_i - AveragePressure[val_marker][iSpan];
6498  }
6499  else{
6500  deltaprim[0] = Density_i - AverageDensity[val_marker][iSpan];
6501  deltaprim[1] = turboVelocity[0] - AverageTurboVelocity[val_marker][iSpan][0];
6502  deltaprim[2] = turboVelocity[1] - AverageTurboVelocity[val_marker][iSpan][1];
6503  deltaprim[3] = turboVelocity[2] - AverageTurboVelocity[val_marker][iSpan][2];
6504  deltaprim[4] = Pressure_i - AveragePressure[val_marker][iSpan];
6505  }
6506 
6507  GetFluidModel()->SetTDState_Prho(AveragePressure[val_marker][iSpan], AverageDensity[val_marker][iSpan]);
6508  AverageSoundSpeed = GetFluidModel()->GetSoundSpeed();
6509  conv_numerics->GetCharJump(AverageSoundSpeed, AverageDensity[val_marker][iSpan], deltaprim, cj);
6510 
6511 
6512  pitch = geometry->GetMaxAngularCoord(val_marker, iSpan) - geometry->GetMinAngularCoord(val_marker,iSpan);
6513  theta = geometry->turbovertex[val_marker][iSpan][iVertex]->GetRelAngularCoord();
6514 
6515  switch(config->GetKind_Data_Giles(Marker_Tag))
6516  {
6517 
6518  //Done, generilize for 3D case
6519  //TODO(turbo), generilize for Inlet and Outlet in for backflow treatment
6520 
6521  case TOTAL_CONDITIONS_PT: case MIXING_IN:case TOTAL_CONDITIONS_PT_1D: case MIXING_IN_1D:
6522  if(config->GetSpatialFourier()){
6523  if (AvgMach <= 1.0){
6524  Beta_inf= I*complex<su2double>(sqrt(1.0 - AvgMach));
6525  c2js = complex<su2double>(0.0,0.0);
6526  c3js = complex<su2double>(0.0,0.0);
6527  for(k=0; k < 2*kend_max+1; k++){
6528  freq = k - kend_max;
6529  if(freq >= (long)(-kend) && freq <= (long)(kend) && AverageTurboMach[0] > config->GetAverageMachLimit()){
6530  TwoPiThetaFreq_Pitch = 2*PI_NUMBER*freq*theta/pitch;
6531 
6532  c2ks = -CkInflow[val_marker][iSpan][k]*complex<su2double>(Beta_inf + AverageTurboMach[1])/complex<su2double>( 1.0 + AverageTurboMach[0]);
6533  c3ks = CkInflow[val_marker][iSpan][k]*complex<su2double>(Beta_inf + AverageTurboMach[1])/complex<su2double>( 1.0 + AverageTurboMach[0]);
6534  c3ks *= complex<su2double>(Beta_inf + AverageTurboMach[1])/complex<su2double>( 1.0 + AverageTurboMach[0]);
6535  c2js += c2ks*(complex<su2double>(cos(TwoPiThetaFreq_Pitch))+I*complex<su2double>(sin(TwoPiThetaFreq_Pitch)));
6536  c3js += c3ks*(complex<su2double>(cos(TwoPiThetaFreq_Pitch))+I*complex<su2double>(sin(TwoPiThetaFreq_Pitch)));
6537  }
6538  else{
6539  c2js += complex<su2double>(0.0,0.0);
6540  c3js += complex<su2double>(0.0,0.0);
6541  }
6542  }
6543  c2js_Re = c2js.real();
6544  c3js_Re = c3js.real();
6545 
6546  if (nDim == 2){
6547  dcjs[0] = 0.0 - cj[0];
6548  dcjs[1] = c2js_Re - cj[1];
6549  dcjs[2] = c3js_Re - cj[2];
6550  }else{
6551  dcjs[0] = 0.0 - cj[0];
6552  dcjs[1] = c2js_Re - cj[1];
6553  dcjs[2] = 0.0 - cj[2];
6554  dcjs[3] = c3js_Re - cj[3];
6555  }
6556 
6557  }else{
6558  if (AverageTurboVelocity[val_marker][iSpan][1] >= 0.0){
6559  Beta_inf2= -sqrt(AvgMach - 1.0);
6560  }else{
6561  Beta_inf2= sqrt(AvgMach-1.0);
6562  }
6563  if (nDim == 2){
6564  c2js_Re = -cj[3]*(Beta_inf2 + AverageTurboMach[1])/( 1.0 + AverageTurboMach[0]);
6565  c3js_Re = cj[3]*(Beta_inf2 + AverageTurboMach[1])/( 1.0 + AverageTurboMach[0]);
6566  c3js_Re *= (Beta_inf2 + AverageTurboMach[1])/( 1.0 + AverageTurboMach[0]);
6567  }else{
6568  c2js_Re = -cj[4]*(Beta_inf2 + AverageTurboMach[1])/( 1.0 + AverageTurboMach[0]);
6569  c3js_Re = cj[4]*(Beta_inf2 + AverageTurboMach[1])/( 1.0 + AverageTurboMach[0]);
6570  c3js_Re *= (Beta_inf2 + AverageTurboMach[1])/( 1.0 + AverageTurboMach[0]);
6571  }
6572 
6573 
6574  if (nDim == 2){
6575  dcjs[0] = 0.0 - cj[0];
6576  dcjs[1] = c2js_Re - cj[1];
6577  dcjs[2] = c3js_Re - cj[2];
6578  }else{
6579  dcjs[0] = 0.0 - cj[0];
6580  dcjs[1] = c2js_Re - cj[1];
6581  dcjs[2] = 0.0 - cj[2];
6582  dcjs[3] = c3js_Re - cj[3];
6583  }
6584  }
6585  }
6586  else{
6587  if (nDim == 2){
6588  dcjs[0] = 0.0;
6589  dcjs[1] = 0.0;
6590  dcjs[2] = 0.0;
6591  }else{
6592  dcjs[0] = 0.0;
6593  dcjs[1] = 0.0;
6594  dcjs[2] = 0.0;
6595  dcjs[3] = 0.0;
6596  }
6597  }
6598  /* --- Impose Inlet BC Reflecting--- */
6599  delta_c[0] = relfacAvg*c_avg[0] + relfacFou*dcjs[0];
6600  delta_c[1] = relfacAvg*c_avg[1] + relfacFou*dcjs[1];
6601  delta_c[2] = relfacAvg*c_avg[2] + relfacFou*dcjs[2];
6602  if (nDim == 2){
6603  delta_c[3] = cj[3];
6604  }else{
6605  delta_c[3] = relfacAvg*c_avg[3] + relfacFou*dcjs[3];
6606  delta_c[4] = cj[4];
6607  }
6608  break;
6609 
6610 
6611  case STATIC_PRESSURE:case STATIC_PRESSURE_1D:case MIXING_OUT:case RADIAL_EQUILIBRIUM:case MIXING_OUT_1D: case MASS_FLOW_OUTLET:
6612 
6613  /* --- implementation of Giles BC---*/
6614  if(config->GetSpatialFourier()){
6615  if (AvgMach > 1.0){
6616  /* --- supersonic Giles implementation ---*/
6617  if (AverageTurboVelocity[val_marker][iSpan][1] >= 0.0){
6618  GilesBeta= -sqrt(AvgMach - 1.0);
6619 
6620  }else{
6621  GilesBeta= sqrt(AvgMach - 1.0);
6622  }
6623  if(nDim == 2){
6624  cOutjs_Re= (2.0 * AverageTurboMach[0])/(GilesBeta - AverageTurboMach[1])*cj[1] - (GilesBeta + AverageTurboMach[1])/(GilesBeta - AverageTurboMach[1])*cj[2];
6625  }
6626  else{
6627  cOutjs_Re= (2.0 * AverageTurboMach[0])/(GilesBeta - AverageTurboMach[1])*cj[1] - (GilesBeta + AverageTurboMach[1])/(GilesBeta - AverageTurboMach[1])*cj[3];
6628  }
6629  if (nDim == 2){
6630  dcjs[3] = cOutjs_Re - cj[3];
6631  }
6632  else{
6633  dcjs[4] = cOutjs_Re - cj[4];
6634  }
6635  }else{
6636 
6637  /* --- subsonic Giles implementation ---*/
6638  Beta_inf= I*complex<su2double>(sqrt(1.0 - AvgMach));
6639  cOutjs = complex<su2double>(0.0,0.0);
6640  for(k=0; k < 2*kend_max+1; k++){
6641  freq = k - kend_max;
6642  if(freq >= (long)(-kend) && freq <= (long)(kend) && AverageTurboMach[0] > config->GetAverageMachLimit()){
6643  TwoPiThetaFreq_Pitch = 2*PI_NUMBER*freq*theta/pitch;
6644  cOutks = complex<su2double>(2.0 * AverageTurboMach[0])/complex<su2double>(Beta_inf - AverageTurboMach[1])*CkOutflow1[val_marker][iSpan][k];
6645  cOutks -= complex<su2double>(Beta_inf + AverageTurboMach[1])/complex<su2double>(Beta_inf - AverageTurboMach[1])*CkOutflow2[val_marker][iSpan][k];
6646 
6647  cOutjs += cOutks*(complex<su2double>(cos(TwoPiThetaFreq_Pitch)) + I*complex<su2double>(sin(TwoPiThetaFreq_Pitch)));
6648  }
6649  else{
6650  cOutjs +=complex<su2double>(0.0,0.0);
6651  }
6652  }
6653  cOutjs_Re = cOutjs.real();
6654 
6655  if (nDim == 2){
6656  dcjs[3] = cOutjs_Re - cj[3];
6657  }
6658  else{
6659  dcjs[4] = cOutjs_Re - cj[4];
6660  }
6661  }
6662  }
6663  else{
6664  if (nDim == 2){
6665  dcjs[3] = 0.0;
6666  }
6667  else{
6668  dcjs[4] = 0.0;
6669  }
6670  }
6671  /* --- Impose Outlet BC Non-Reflecting --- */
6672  delta_c[0] = cj[0];
6673  delta_c[1] = cj[1];
6674  delta_c[2] = cj[2];
6675  if (nDim == 2){
6676  delta_c[3] = relfacAvg*c_avg[3] + relfacFou*dcjs[3];
6677  }
6678  else{
6679  delta_c[3] = cj[3];
6680  delta_c[4] = relfacAvg*c_avg[4] + relfacFou*dcjs[4];
6681  }
6682 
6683 
6684  /*--- Automatically impose supersonic autoflow ---*/
6685  if (abs(AverageTurboMach[0]) > 1.0000){
6686  delta_c[0] = 0.0;
6687  delta_c[1] = 0.0;
6688  delta_c[2] = 0.0;
6689  delta_c[2] = 0.0;
6690  if (nDim == 3)delta_c[4] = 0.0;
6691  }
6692 
6693  break;
6694 
6695  default:
6696  SU2_MPI::Error("Invalid Giles input!", CURRENT_FUNCTION);
6697  break;
6698  }
6699 
6700  /*--- Compute primitive jump from characteristic variables ---*/
6701  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
6702  {
6703  deltaprim[iVar]=0.0;
6704  for (jVar = 0; jVar < nVar; jVar++)
6705  {
6706  deltaprim[iVar] += R_Matrix[iVar][jVar]*delta_c[jVar];
6707  }
6708  }
6709 
6710  /*--- retrieve boundary variables ---*/
6711  Density_b = AverageDensity[val_marker][iSpan] + deltaprim[0];
6712  turboVelocity[0] = AverageTurboVelocity[val_marker][iSpan][0] + deltaprim[1];
6713  turboVelocity[1] = AverageTurboVelocity[val_marker][iSpan][1] + deltaprim[2];
6714  if(nDim == 2){
6715  Pressure_b = AveragePressure[val_marker][iSpan] + deltaprim[3];
6716  }
6717  else{
6718  turboVelocity[2] = AverageTurboVelocity[val_marker][iSpan][2] + deltaprim[3];
6719  Pressure_b = AveragePressure[val_marker][iSpan] + deltaprim[4];
6720  }
6721 
6722 
6723  ComputeBackVelocity(turboVelocity, turboNormal, Velocity_b, config->GetMarker_All_TurbomachineryFlag(val_marker), config->GetKind_TurboMachinery(iZone));
6724  Velocity2_b = 0.0;
6725  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
6726  Velocity2_b+= Velocity_b[iDim]*Velocity_b[iDim];
6727  }
6728 
6729  if(Pressure_b <= 0.0 || Density_b <= 0.0 ){
6730  Pressure_b = Pressure_i;
6731  Density_b = Density_i;
6732  Velocity2_b = 0.0;
6733  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
6734  Velocity_b[iDim] = Velocity_i[iDim];
6735  Velocity2_b+= Velocity_b[iDim]*Velocity_b[iDim];
6736  }
6737  }
6738 
6739  GetFluidModel()->SetTDState_Prho(Pressure_b, Density_b);
6740  Energy_b = GetFluidModel()->GetStaticEnergy() + 0.5*Velocity2_b;
6741  Temperature_b= GetFluidModel()->GetTemperature();
6742  Enthalpy_b = Energy_b + Pressure_b/Density_b;
6743 
6744  /*--- Primitive variables, using the derived quantities ---*/
6745  V_boundary[0] = Temperature_b;
6746  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
6747  V_boundary[iDim+1] = Velocity_b[iDim];
6748  V_boundary[nDim+1] = Pressure_b;
6749  V_boundary[nDim+2] = Density_b;
6750  V_boundary[nDim+3] = Enthalpy_b;
6751 
6752  S_boundary[0]= GetFluidModel()->GetdPdrho_e();
6753  S_boundary[1]= GetFluidModel()->GetdPde_rho();
6754 
6755 
6756 
6757  /*--- Set various quantities in the solver class ---*/
6758 
6759  conv_numerics->SetPrimitive(V_domain, V_boundary);
6760  conv_numerics->SetSecondary(S_domain, S_boundary);
6761 
6762 
6763  if (dynamic_grid)
6764  conv_numerics->SetGridVel(geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint), geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint));
6765 
6766  /*--- Compute the residual using an upwind scheme ---*/
6767 
6768  auto residual = conv_numerics->ComputeResidual(config);
6769 
6770  /*--- Update residual value ---*/
6771  LinSysRes.AddBlock(iPoint, residual);
6772 
6773  /*--- Jacobian contribution for implicit integration ---*/
6774  if (implicit)
6775  Jacobian.AddBlock2Diag(iPoint, residual.jacobian_i);
6776 
6777  /*--- Viscous contribution ---*/
6778 
6779  if (viscous) {
6780 
6781  /*--- Set laminar and eddy viscosity at the infinity ---*/
6782 
6783  V_boundary[nDim+5] = GetFluidModel()->GetLaminarViscosity();
6784  V_boundary[nDim+6] = nodes->GetEddyViscosity(iPoint);
6785  V_boundary[nDim+7] = GetFluidModel()->GetThermalConductivity();
6786  V_boundary[nDim+8] = GetFluidModel()->GetCp();
6787 
6788  /*--- Set the normal vector and the coordinates ---*/
6789 
6790  visc_numerics->SetNormal(Normal);
6791  su2double Coord_Reflected[MAXNDIM];
6792  GeometryToolbox::PointPointReflect(nDim, geometry->nodes->GetCoord(Point_Normal),
6793  geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint), Coord_Reflected);
6794  visc_numerics->SetCoord(geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint), Coord_Reflected);
6795 
6796  /*--- Primitive variables, and gradient ---*/
6797 
6798  visc_numerics->SetPrimitive(V_domain, V_boundary);
6799  visc_numerics->SetPrimVarGradient(nodes->GetGradient_Primitive(iPoint), nodes->GetGradient_Primitive(iPoint));
6800 
6801 
6802  /*--- Compute secondary thermodynamic properties (partial derivatives...) ---*/
6803 
6804  S_boundary[0]= GetFluidModel()->GetdPdrho_e();
6805  S_boundary[1]= GetFluidModel()->GetdPde_rho();
6806 
6807  S_boundary[2]= GetFluidModel()->GetdTdrho_e();
6808  S_boundary[3]= GetFluidModel()->GetdTde_rho();
6809 
6810  /*--- Compute secondary thermo-physical properties (partial derivatives...) ---*/
6811 
6812  S_boundary[4]= GetFluidModel()->Getdmudrho_T();
6813  S_boundary[5]= GetFluidModel()->GetdmudT_rho();
6814 
6815  S_boundary[6]= GetFluidModel()->Getdktdrho_T();
6816  S_boundary[7]= GetFluidModel()->GetdktdT_rho();
6817 
6818  visc_numerics->SetSecondary(S_domain, S_boundary);
6819 
6820  /*--- Turbulent kinetic energy ---*/
6821 
6822  if (config->GetKind_Turb_Model() == TURB_MODEL::SST)
6823  visc_numerics->SetTurbKineticEnergy(solver_container[TURB_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetSolution(iPoint,0),
6824  solver_container[TURB_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetSolution(iPoint,0));
6825 
6826  /*--- Compute and update residual ---*/
6827 
6828  auto residual = visc_numerics->ComputeResidual(config);
6829  LinSysRes.SubtractBlock(iPoint, residual);
6830 
6831  /*--- Jacobian contribution for implicit integration ---*/
6832 
6833  if (implicit)
6834  Jacobian.SubtractBlock2Diag(iPoint, residual.jacobian_i);
6835 
6836  }
6837  /*--- Store number of Newton iterations at BC ---*/
6838  if(config->GetKind_FluidModel() == DATADRIVEN_FLUID)
6839  nodes->SetNewtonSolverIterations(iPoint, GetFluidModel()->GetnIter_Newton());
6840 
6841  }
6842  END_SU2_OMP_FOR
6843  }
6844 
6845  /*--- Free locally allocated memory ---*/
6846  delete [] Normal;
6847 
6848  delete [] Velocity_b;
6849  delete [] Velocity_i;
6850 
6851  delete [] S_boundary;
6852  delete [] delta_c;
6853  delete [] deltaprim;
6854  delete [] cj;
6855  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
6856  {
6857  delete [] R_Matrix[iVar];
6858  }
6859  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar-1; iVar++)
6860  {
6861  delete [] R_c_inv[iVar];
6862  delete [] R_c[iVar];
6863  }
6864  delete [] R_Matrix;
6865  delete [] R_c;
6866  delete [] R_c_inv;
6867  delete [] R;
6868  delete [] c_avg;
6869  delete [] dcjs;
6870 
6871  delete [] AverageTurboMach;
6872  delete [] UnitNormal;
6873  delete [] turboNormal;
6874  delete [] turboVelocity;
6875 }
6876 
6877 void CEulerSolver::BC_Inlet(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver_container,
6878  CNumerics *conv_numerics, CNumerics *visc_numerics,
6879  CConfig *config, unsigned short val_marker) {
6880  unsigned short iDim;
6881  unsigned long iVertex, iPoint;
6882  su2double P_Total, T_Total, Velocity[MAXNDIM], Velocity2, H_Total, Temperature, Riemann,
6883  Pressure, Density, Energy, Flow_Dir[MAXNDIM], Mach2, SoundSpeed2, SoundSpeed_Total2, Vel_Mag,
6884  alpha, aa, bb, cc, dd, Area, UnitNormal[MAXNDIM], Normal[MAXNDIM];
6885  su2double *V_inlet, *V_domain;
6886 
6887  const bool implicit = (config->GetKind_TimeIntScheme() == EULER_IMPLICIT);
6888  const su2double Two_Gamma_M1 = 2.0 / Gamma_Minus_One;
6889  const su2double Gas_Constant = config->GetGas_ConstantND();
6890  const auto Kind_Inlet = config->GetKind_Inlet();
6891  const auto Marker_Tag = config->GetMarker_All_TagBound(val_marker);
6892  const bool tkeNeeded = (config->GetKind_Turb_Model() == TURB_MODEL::SST);
6893 
6894  /*--- Loop over all the vertices on this boundary marker ---*/
6895 
6896  SU2_OMP_FOR_DYN(OMP_MIN_SIZE)
6897  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[val_marker]; iVertex++) {
6898 
6899  /*--- Allocate the value at the inlet ---*/
6900 
6901  V_inlet = GetCharacPrimVar(val_marker, iVertex);
6902 
6903  iPoint = geometry->vertex[val_marker][iVertex]->GetNode();
6904 
6905  /*--- Check if the node belongs to the domain (i.e., not a halo node) ---*/
6906 
6907  if (geometry->nodes->GetDomain(iPoint)) {
6908 
6909  /*--- Normal vector for this vertex (negate for outward convention) ---*/
6910 
6911  geometry->vertex[val_marker][iVertex]->GetNormal(Normal);
6912  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) Normal[iDim] = -Normal[iDim];
6913  conv_numerics->SetNormal(Normal);
6914 
6915  Area = GeometryToolbox::Norm(nDim, Normal);
6916  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
6917  UnitNormal[iDim] = Normal[iDim]/Area;
6918 
6919  /*--- Retrieve solution at this boundary node ---*/
6920 
6921  V_domain = nodes->GetPrimitive(iPoint);
6922 
6923  /*--- Build the fictitious intlet state based on characteristics ---*/
6924 
6925 
6926  /*--- Subsonic inflow: there is one outgoing characteristic (u-c),
6927  therefore we can specify all but one state variable at the inlet.
6928  The outgoing Riemann invariant provides the final piece of info.
6929  Adapted from an original implementation in the Stanford University
6930  multi-block (SUmb) solver in the routine bcSubsonicInflow.f90
6931  written by Edwin van der Weide, last modified 04-20-2009. ---*/
6932 
6933  switch (Kind_Inlet) {
6934 
6935  /*--- Total properties have been specified at the inlet. ---*/
6936 
6937  case INLET_TYPE::TOTAL_CONDITIONS: {
6938 
6939  /*--- Retrieve the specified total conditions for this inlet. ---*/
6940 
6941  P_Total = Inlet_Ptotal[val_marker][iVertex];
6942  T_Total = Inlet_Ttotal[val_marker][iVertex];
6943  const su2double* dir = Inlet_FlowDir[val_marker][iVertex];
6944  const su2double mag = GeometryToolbox::Norm(nDim, dir);
6945  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
6946  Flow_Dir[iDim] = dir[iDim] / mag;
6947  }
6948 
6949  /*--- Non-dim. the inputs if necessary. ---*/
6950 
6951  P_Total /= config->GetPressure_Ref();
6952  T_Total /= config->GetTemperature_Ref();
6953 
6954  /*--- Store primitives and set some variables for clarity. ---*/
6955 
6956  Density = V_domain[nDim+2];
6957  Velocity2 = 0.0;
6958  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
6959  Velocity[iDim] = V_domain[iDim+1];
6960  Velocity2 += Velocity[iDim]*Velocity[iDim];
6961  }
6962  Energy = V_domain[nDim+3] - V_domain[nDim+1]/V_domain[nDim+2];
6963  Pressure = V_domain[nDim+1];
6964  H_Total = (Gamma*Gas_Constant/Gamma_Minus_One)*T_Total;
6965  SoundSpeed2 = Gamma*Pressure/Density;
6966 
6967  /*--- Compute the acoustic Riemann invariant that is extrapolated
6968  from the domain interior. ---*/
6969 
6970  Riemann = 2.0*sqrt(SoundSpeed2)/Gamma_Minus_One;
6971  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
6972  Riemann += Velocity[iDim]*UnitNormal[iDim];
6973 
6974  /*--- Total speed of sound ---*/
6975 
6976  SoundSpeed_Total2 = Gamma_Minus_One*(H_Total - (Energy + Pressure/Density)+0.5*Velocity2) + SoundSpeed2;
6977 
6978  /*--- Dot product of normal and flow direction. This should
6979  be negative due to outward facing boundary normal convention. ---*/
6980 
6981  alpha = 0.0;
6982  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
6983  alpha += UnitNormal[iDim]*Flow_Dir[iDim];
6984 
6985  /*--- Coefficients in the quadratic equation for the velocity ---*/
6986 
6987  aa = 1.0 + 0.5*Gamma_Minus_One*alpha*alpha;
6988  bb = -1.0*Gamma_Minus_One*alpha*Riemann;
6989  cc = 0.5*Gamma_Minus_One*Riemann*Riemann
6990  -2.0*SoundSpeed_Total2/Gamma_Minus_One;
6991 
6992  /*--- Solve quadratic equation for velocity magnitude. Value must
6993  be positive, so the choice of root is clear. ---*/
6994 
6995  dd = bb*bb - 4.0*aa*cc;
6996  dd = sqrt(max(0.0, dd));
6997  Vel_Mag = (-bb + dd)/(2.0*aa);
6998  Vel_Mag = max(0.0, Vel_Mag);
6999  Velocity2 = Vel_Mag*Vel_Mag;
7000 
7001  /*--- Compute speed of sound from total speed of sound eqn. ---*/
7002 
7003  SoundSpeed2 = SoundSpeed_Total2 - 0.5*Gamma_Minus_One*Velocity2;
7004 
7005  /*--- Mach squared (cut between 0-1), use to adapt velocity ---*/
7006 
7007  Mach2 = Velocity2/SoundSpeed2;
7008  Mach2 = min(1.0, Mach2);
7009  Velocity2 = Mach2*SoundSpeed2;
7010  Vel_Mag = sqrt(Velocity2);
7011  SoundSpeed2 = SoundSpeed_Total2 - 0.5*Gamma_Minus_One*Velocity2;
7012 
7013  /*--- Compute new velocity vector at the inlet ---*/
7014 
7015  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
7016  Velocity[iDim] = Vel_Mag*Flow_Dir[iDim];
7017 
7018  /*--- Static temperature from the speed of sound relation ---*/
7019 
7020  Temperature = SoundSpeed2/(Gamma*Gas_Constant);
7021 
7022  /*--- Static pressure using isentropic relation at a point ---*/
7023 
7024  Pressure = P_Total*pow((Temperature/T_Total), Gamma/Gamma_Minus_One);
7025 
7026  /*--- Density at the inlet from the gas law ---*/
7027 
7028  Density = Pressure/(Gas_Constant*Temperature);
7029 
7030  /*--- Using pressure, density, & velocity, compute the energy ---*/
7031 
7032  Energy = Pressure/(Density*Gamma_Minus_One) + 0.5*Velocity2;
7033  if (tkeNeeded) Energy += GetTke_Inf();
7034 
7035  /*--- Primitive variables, using the derived quantities ---*/
7036 
7037  V_inlet[0] = Temperature;
7038  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
7039  V_inlet[iDim+1] = Velocity[iDim];
7040  V_inlet[nDim+1] = Pressure;
7041  V_inlet[nDim+2] = Density;
7042  V_inlet[nDim+3] = Energy + Pressure/Density;
7043 
7044  break;
7045  }
7046  /*--- Mass flow has been specified at the inlet. ---*/
7047 
7048  case INLET_TYPE::MASS_FLOW: {
7049 
7050  /*--- Retrieve the specified mass flow for the inlet. ---*/
7051 
7052  Density = Inlet_Ttotal[val_marker][iVertex];
7053  Vel_Mag = Inlet_Ptotal[val_marker][iVertex];
7054  const su2double* dir = Inlet_FlowDir[val_marker][iVertex];
7055  const su2double mag = GeometryToolbox::Norm(nDim, dir);
7056  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
7057  Flow_Dir[iDim] = dir[iDim] / mag;
7058  }
7059 
7060  /*--- Non-dim. the inputs if necessary. ---*/
7061 
7062  Density /= config->GetDensity_Ref();
7063  Vel_Mag /= config->GetVelocity_Ref();
7064 
7065  /*--- Get primitives from current inlet state. ---*/
7066 
7067  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
7068  Velocity[iDim] = nodes->GetVelocity(iPoint,iDim);
7069  Pressure = nodes->GetPressure(iPoint);
7070  SoundSpeed2 = Gamma*Pressure/V_domain[nDim+2];
7071 
7072  /*--- Compute the acoustic Riemann invariant that is extrapolated
7073  from the domain interior. ---*/
7074 
7075  Riemann = Two_Gamma_M1*sqrt(SoundSpeed2);
7076  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
7077  Riemann += Velocity[iDim]*UnitNormal[iDim];
7078 
7079  /*--- Speed of sound squared for fictitious inlet state ---*/
7080 
7081  SoundSpeed2 = Riemann;
7082  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
7083  SoundSpeed2 -= Vel_Mag*Flow_Dir[iDim]*UnitNormal[iDim];
7084 
7085  SoundSpeed2 = max(0.0,0.5*Gamma_Minus_One*SoundSpeed2);
7086  SoundSpeed2 = SoundSpeed2*SoundSpeed2;
7087 
7088  /*--- Pressure for the fictitious inlet state ---*/
7089 
7090  Pressure = SoundSpeed2*Density/Gamma;
7091 
7092  /*--- Energy for the fictitious inlet state ---*/
7093 
7094  Energy = Pressure/(Density*Gamma_Minus_One) + 0.5*Vel_Mag*Vel_Mag;
7095  if (tkeNeeded) Energy += GetTke_Inf();
7096 
7097  /*--- Primitive variables, using the derived quantities ---*/
7098 
7099  V_inlet[0] = Pressure / ( Gas_Constant * Density);
7100  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
7101  V_inlet[iDim+1] = Vel_Mag*Flow_Dir[iDim];
7102  V_inlet[nDim+1] = Pressure;
7103  V_inlet[nDim+2] = Density;
7104  V_inlet[nDim+3] = Energy + Pressure/Density;
7105 
7106  break;
7107  }
7108  default:
7109  SU2_MPI::Error("Unsupported INLET_TYPE.", CURRENT_FUNCTION);
7110  break;
7111  }
7112 
7113  /*--- Set various quantities in the solver class ---*/
7114 
7115  conv_numerics->SetPrimitive(V_domain, V_inlet);
7116 
7117  if (dynamic_grid)
7118  conv_numerics->SetGridVel(geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint), geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint));
7119 
7120  /*--- Compute the residual using an upwind scheme ---*/
7121 
7122  auto residual = conv_numerics->ComputeResidual(config);
7123 
7124  /*--- Update residual value ---*/
7125 
7126  LinSysRes.AddBlock(iPoint, residual);
7127 
7128  /*--- Jacobian contribution for implicit integration ---*/
7129 
7130  if (implicit)
7131  Jacobian.AddBlock2Diag(iPoint, residual.jacobian_i);
7132 
7133 // /*--- Viscous contribution, commented out because serious convergence problems ---*/
7134 //
7135 // if (viscous) {
7136 //
7137 // /*--- Set laminar and eddy viscosity at the infinity ---*/
7138 //
7139 // V_inlet[nDim+5] = nodes->GetLaminarViscosity(iPoint);
7140 // V_inlet[nDim+6] = nodes->GetEddyViscosity(iPoint);
7141 //
7142 // /*--- Set the normal vector and the coordinates ---*/
7143 //
7144 // visc_numerics->SetNormal(Normal);
7145 // su2double Coord_Reflected[MAXNDIM];
7146 // GeometryToolbox::PointPointReflect(nDim, geometry->nodes->GetCoord(Point_Normal),
7147 // geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint), Coord_Reflected);
7148 // visc_numerics->SetCoord(geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint), Coord_Reflected);
7149 //
7150 // /*--- Primitive variables, and gradient ---*/
7151 //
7152 // visc_numerics->SetPrimitive(V_domain, V_inlet);
7153 // visc_numerics->SetPrimVarGradient(nodes->GetGradient_Primitive(iPoint), nodes->GetGradient_Primitive(iPoint));
7154 //
7155 // /*--- Turbulent kinetic energy ---*/
7156 //
7157 // if (config->GetKind_Turb_Model() == TURB_MODEL::SST)
7158 // visc_numerics->SetTurbKineticEnergy(solver_container[TURB_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetSolution(iPoint,0),
7159 // solver_container[TURB_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetSolution(iPoint,0));
7160 //
7161 // /*--- Compute and update residual ---*/
7162 //
7163 // auto residual = visc_numerics->ComputeResidual(config);
7164 // LinSysRes.SubtractBlock(iPoint, residual);
7165 //
7166 // /*--- Jacobian contribution for implicit integration ---*/
7167 //
7168 // if (implicit)
7169 // Jacobian.SubtractBlock2Diag(iPoint, residual.jacobian_i);
7170 //
7171 // }
7172 
7173  }
7174  }
7175  END_SU2_OMP_FOR
7176 
7177 }
7178 
7179 void CEulerSolver::BC_Outlet(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver_container,
7180  CNumerics *conv_numerics, CNumerics *visc_numerics,
7181  CConfig *config, unsigned short val_marker) {
7182  unsigned short iVar, iDim;
7183  unsigned long iVertex, iPoint;
7184  su2double Pressure, P_Exit, Velocity[3],
7185  Velocity2, Entropy, Density, Energy, Riemann, Vn, SoundSpeed, Mach_Exit, Vn_Exit,
7186  Area, UnitNormal[3];
7187  su2double *V_outlet, *V_domain;
7188 
7189  bool implicit = (config->GetKind_TimeIntScheme() == EULER_IMPLICIT);
7190  su2double Gas_Constant = config->GetGas_ConstantND();
7191  string Marker_Tag = config->GetMarker_All_TagBound(val_marker);
7192  bool gravity = (config->GetGravityForce());
7193  bool tkeNeeded = (config->GetKind_Turb_Model() == TURB_MODEL::SST);
7194 
7195  auto *Normal = new su2double[nDim];
7196 
7197  /*--- Loop over all the vertices on this boundary marker ---*/
7198 
7199  SU2_OMP_FOR_DYN(OMP_MIN_SIZE)
7200  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[val_marker]; iVertex++) {
7201 
7202  /*--- Allocate the value at the outlet ---*/
7203  V_outlet = GetCharacPrimVar(val_marker, iVertex);
7204 
7205  iPoint = geometry->vertex[val_marker][iVertex]->GetNode();
7206 
7207  /*--- Check if the node belongs to the domain (i.e., not a halo node) ---*/
7208  if (geometry->nodes->GetDomain(iPoint)) {
7209 
7210  /*--- Normal vector for this vertex (negate for outward convention) ---*/
7211  geometry->vertex[val_marker][iVertex]->GetNormal(Normal);
7212  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) Normal[iDim] = -Normal[iDim];
7213  conv_numerics->SetNormal(Normal);
7214 
7215  Area = GeometryToolbox::Norm(nDim, Normal);
7216  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
7217  UnitNormal[iDim] = Normal[iDim]/Area;
7218 
7219  /*--- Current solution at this boundary node ---*/
7220  V_domain = nodes->GetPrimitive(iPoint);
7221 
7222  /*--- Build the fictitious inlet state based on characteristics ---*/
7223 
7224  /*--- Retrieve the specified back pressure for this outlet. ---*/
7225  if (gravity) P_Exit = config->GetOutlet_Pressure(Marker_Tag) - geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint, nDim-1)*STANDARD_GRAVITY;
7226  else P_Exit = config->GetOutlet_Pressure(Marker_Tag);
7227 
7228  /*--- Non-dim. the inputs if necessary. ---*/
7229  P_Exit = P_Exit/config->GetPressure_Ref();
7230 
7231  /*--- Check whether the flow is supersonic at the exit. The type
7232  of boundary update depends on this. ---*/
7233  Density = V_domain[nDim+2];
7234  Velocity2 = 0.0; Vn = 0.0;
7235  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
7236  Velocity[iDim] = V_domain[iDim+1];
7237  Velocity2 += Velocity[iDim]*Velocity[iDim];
7238  Vn += Velocity[iDim]*UnitNormal[iDim];
7239  }
7240  Pressure = V_domain[nDim+1];
7241  SoundSpeed = sqrt(Gamma*Pressure/Density);
7242  Mach_Exit = sqrt(Velocity2)/SoundSpeed;
7243 
7244  if (Mach_Exit >= 1.0) {
7245 
7246  /*--- Supersonic exit flow: there are no incoming characteristics,
7247  so no boundary condition is necessary. Set outlet state to current
7248  state so that upwinding handles the direction of propagation. ---*/
7249  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nPrimVar; iVar++) V_outlet[iVar] = V_domain[iVar];
7250 
7251  } else {
7252 
7253  /*--- Subsonic exit flow: there is one incoming characteristic,
7254  therefore one variable can be specified (back pressure) and is used
7255  to update the conservative variables. Compute the entropy and the
7256  acoustic Riemann variable. These invariants, as well as the
7257  tangential velocity components, are extrapolated. Adapted from an
7258  original implementation in the Stanford University multi-block
7259  (SUmb) solver in the routine bcSubsonicOutflow.f90 by Edwin van
7260  der Weide, last modified 09-10-2007. ---*/
7261 
7262  Entropy = Pressure*pow(1.0/Density, Gamma);
7263  Riemann = Vn + 2.0*SoundSpeed/Gamma_Minus_One;
7264 
7265  /*--- Compute the new fictious state at the outlet ---*/
7266  Density = pow(P_Exit/Entropy,1.0/Gamma);
7267  Pressure = P_Exit;
7268  SoundSpeed = sqrt(Gamma*P_Exit/Density);
7269  Vn_Exit = Riemann - 2.0*SoundSpeed/Gamma_Minus_One;
7270  Velocity2 = 0.0;
7271  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
7272  Velocity[iDim] = Velocity[iDim] + (Vn_Exit-Vn)*UnitNormal[iDim];
7273  Velocity2 += Velocity[iDim]*Velocity[iDim];
7274  }
7275  Energy = P_Exit/(Density*Gamma_Minus_One) + 0.5*Velocity2;
7276  if (tkeNeeded) Energy += GetTke_Inf();
7277 
7278  /*--- Conservative variables, using the derived quantities ---*/
7279  V_outlet[0] = Pressure / ( Gas_Constant * Density);
7280  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
7281  V_outlet[iDim+1] = Velocity[iDim];
7282  V_outlet[nDim+1] = Pressure;
7283  V_outlet[nDim+2] = Density;
7284  V_outlet[nDim+3] = Energy + Pressure/Density;
7285 
7286  }
7287 
7288  /*--- Set various quantities in the solver class ---*/
7289  conv_numerics->SetPrimitive(V_domain, V_outlet);
7290 
7291  if (dynamic_grid)
7292  conv_numerics->SetGridVel(geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint), geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint));
7293 
7294  /*--- Compute the residual using an upwind scheme ---*/
7295 
7296  auto residual = conv_numerics->ComputeResidual(config);
7297 
7298  /*--- Add Residuals and Jacobians ---*/
7299 
7300  LinSysRes.AddBlock(iPoint, residual);
7301  if (implicit)
7302  Jacobian.AddBlock2Diag(iPoint, residual.jacobian_i);
7303 
7304 // /*--- Viscous contribution, commented out because serious convergence problems ---*/
7305 //
7306 // if (viscous) {
7307 //
7308 // /*--- Set laminar and eddy viscosity at the infinity ---*/
7309 //
7310 // V_outlet[nDim+5] = nodes->GetLaminarViscosity(iPoint);
7311 // V_outlet[nDim+6] = nodes->GetEddyViscosity(iPoint);
7312 //
7313 // /*--- Set the normal vector and the coordinates ---*/
7314 //
7315 // visc_numerics->SetNormal(Normal);
7316 // su2double Coord_Reflected[MAXNDIM];
7317 // GeometryToolbox::PointPointReflect(nDim, geometry->nodes->GetCoord(Point_Normal),
7318 // geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint), Coord_Reflected);
7319 // visc_numerics->SetCoord(geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint), Coord_Reflected);
7320 //
7321 // /*--- Primitive variables, and gradient ---*/
7322 //
7323 // visc_numerics->SetPrimitive(V_domain, V_outlet);
7324 // visc_numerics->SetPrimVarGradient(nodes->GetGradient_Primitive(iPoint), nodes->GetGradient_Primitive(iPoint));
7325 //
7326 // /*--- Turbulent kinetic energy ---*/
7327 //
7328 // if (config->GetKind_Turb_Model() == TURB_MODEL::SST)
7329 // visc_numerics->SetTurbKineticEnergy(solver_container[TURB_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetSolution(iPoint,0),
7330 // solver_container[TURB_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetSolution(iPoint,0));
7331 //
7332 // /*--- Compute and update residual ---*/
7333 //
7334 // auto residual = visc_numerics->ComputeResidual(config);
7335 // LinSysRes.SubtractBlock(iPoint, residual);
7336 //
7337 // /*--- Jacobian contribution for implicit integration ---*/
7338 //
7339 // if (implicit)
7340 // Jacobian.SubtractBlock2Diag(iPoint, residual.acobian_i);
7341 //
7342 // }
7343 
7344  }
7345  }
7346  END_SU2_OMP_FOR
7347 
7348  /*--- Free locally allocated memory ---*/
7349  delete [] Normal;
7350 
7351 }
7352 
7353 void CEulerSolver::BC_Supersonic_Inlet(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver_container,
7354  CNumerics *conv_numerics, CNumerics *visc_numerics,
7355  CConfig *config, unsigned short val_marker) {
7356  const su2double Gas_Constant = config->GetGas_ConstantND();
7357  const bool implicit = (config->GetKind_TimeIntScheme() == EULER_IMPLICIT);
7358  const auto Marker_Tag = config->GetMarker_All_TagBound(val_marker);
7359  const bool tkeNeeded = (config->GetKind_Turb_Model() == TURB_MODEL::SST);
7360 
7361  /*--- Supersonic inlet flow: there are no outgoing characteristics,
7362  so all flow variables can be imposed at the inlet. ---*/
7363 
7364  SU2_OMP_FOR_DYN(OMP_MIN_SIZE)
7365  for (auto iVertex = 0ul; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[val_marker]; iVertex++) {
7366  const auto iPoint = geometry->vertex[val_marker][iVertex]->GetNode();
7367 
7368  if (!geometry->nodes->GetDomain(iPoint)) continue;
7369 
7370  /*--- Retrieve the inlet profile, note that total conditions are reused as static. ---*/
7371 
7372  const su2double Temperature = Inlet_Ttotal[val_marker][iVertex] / config->GetTemperature_Ref();
7373  const su2double Pressure = Inlet_Ptotal[val_marker][iVertex] / config->GetPressure_Ref();
7374  su2double Velocity[MAXNDIM] = {0.0};
7375  for (unsigned short iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
7376  Velocity[iDim] = Inlet_FlowDir[val_marker][iVertex][iDim] / config->GetVelocity_Ref();
7377  }
7378 
7379  /*--- Density at the inlet from the gas law. ---*/
7380 
7381  const su2double Density = Pressure / (Gas_Constant * Temperature);
7382 
7383  /*--- Compute the energy from the specified state. ---*/
7384 
7385  const su2double Velocity2 = GeometryToolbox::SquaredNorm(int(MAXNDIM), Velocity);
7386  su2double Energy = Pressure / (Density * Gamma_Minus_One) + 0.5 * Velocity2;
7387  if (tkeNeeded) Energy += GetTke_Inf();
7388 
7389  /*--- Primitive variables, using the derived quantities. ---*/
7390 
7391  auto* V_inlet = GetCharacPrimVar(val_marker, iVertex);
7392  V_inlet[prim_idx.Temperature()] = Temperature;
7393  V_inlet[prim_idx.Pressure()] = Pressure;
7394  V_inlet[prim_idx.Density()] = Density;
7395  V_inlet[prim_idx.Enthalpy()] = Energy + Pressure / Density;
7396  for (unsigned short iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
7397  V_inlet[iDim+prim_idx.Velocity()] = Velocity[iDim];
7398 
7399  /*--- Current solution at this boundary node. ---*/
7400 
7401  const auto* V_domain = nodes->GetPrimitive(iPoint);
7402 
7403  /*--- Normal vector for this vertex (negate for outward convention). ---*/
7404 
7405  su2double Normal[MAXNDIM] = {0.0};
7406  geometry->vertex[val_marker][iVertex]->GetNormal(Normal);
7407  for (unsigned short iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) Normal[iDim] = -Normal[iDim];
7408 
7409  /*--- Set various quantities in the solver class. ---*/
7410 
7411  conv_numerics->SetNormal(Normal);
7412  conv_numerics->SetPrimitive(V_domain, V_inlet);
7413 
7414  if (dynamic_grid)
7415  conv_numerics->SetGridVel(geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint),
7416  geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint));
7417 
7418  /*--- Compute the residual using an upwind scheme. ---*/
7419 
7420  auto residual = conv_numerics->ComputeResidual(config);
7421 
7422  LinSysRes.AddBlock(iPoint, residual);
7423 
7424  /*--- Jacobian contribution for implicit integration. ---*/
7425 
7426  if (implicit)
7427  Jacobian.AddBlock2Diag(iPoint, residual.jacobian_i);
7428 
7429  /*--- Viscous contribution, omited to improve convergence. ---*/
7430 
7431  }
7432  END_SU2_OMP_FOR
7433 
7434 }
7435 
7436 void CEulerSolver::BC_Supersonic_Outlet(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver_container,
7437  CNumerics *conv_numerics, CNumerics *visc_numerics,
7438  CConfig *config, unsigned short val_marker) {
7439  unsigned short iDim;
7440  unsigned long iVertex, iPoint;
7441  su2double *V_outlet, *V_domain;
7442 
7443  bool implicit = (config->GetKind_TimeIntScheme() == EULER_IMPLICIT);
7444  string Marker_Tag = config->GetMarker_All_TagBound(val_marker);
7445 
7446  auto *Normal = new su2double[nDim];
7447 
7448  /*--- Supersonic outlet flow: there are no ingoing characteristics,
7449  so all flow variables can should be interpolated from the domain. ---*/
7450 
7451  /*--- Loop over all the vertices on this boundary marker ---*/
7452 
7453  SU2_OMP_FOR_DYN(OMP_MIN_SIZE)
7454  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[val_marker]; iVertex++) {
7455 
7456  iPoint = geometry->vertex[val_marker][iVertex]->GetNode();
7457 
7458  /*--- Check if the node belongs to the domain (i.e, not a halo node) ---*/
7459 
7460  if (geometry->nodes->GetDomain(iPoint)) {
7461 
7462  /*--- Current solution at this boundary node ---*/
7463 
7464  V_domain = nodes->GetPrimitive(iPoint);
7465 
7466  /*--- Allocate the value at the outlet ---*/
7467 
7468  V_outlet = GetCharacPrimVar(val_marker, iVertex);
7469 
7470  /*--- Primitive variables, using the derived quantities ---*/
7471 
7472  V_outlet[0] = V_domain[0];
7473  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
7474  V_outlet[iDim+1] = V_domain[iDim+1];
7475  V_outlet[nDim+1] = V_domain[nDim+1];
7476  V_outlet[nDim+2] = V_domain[nDim+2];
7477  V_outlet[nDim+3] = V_domain[nDim+3];
7478 
7479  /*--- Current solution at this boundary node ---*/
7480 
7481  V_domain = nodes->GetPrimitive(iPoint);
7482 
7483  /*--- Normal vector for this vertex (negate for outward convention) ---*/
7484 
7485  geometry->vertex[val_marker][iVertex]->GetNormal(Normal);
7486  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) Normal[iDim] = -Normal[iDim];
7487 
7488  /*--- Set various quantities in the solver class ---*/
7489 
7490  conv_numerics->SetNormal(Normal);
7491  conv_numerics->SetPrimitive(V_domain, V_outlet);
7492 
7493  if (dynamic_grid)
7494  conv_numerics->SetGridVel(geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint),
7495  geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint));
7496 
7497  /*--- Compute the residual using an upwind scheme ---*/
7498 
7499  auto residual = conv_numerics->ComputeResidual(config);
7500 
7501  LinSysRes.AddBlock(iPoint, residual);
7502 
7503  /*--- Jacobian contribution for implicit integration ---*/
7504 
7505  if (implicit)
7506  Jacobian.AddBlock2Diag(iPoint, residual.jacobian_i);
7507 
7508 // /*--- Viscous contribution, commented out because serious convergence problems ---*/
7509 //
7510 // if (viscous) {
7511 //
7512 // /*--- Set laminar and eddy viscosity at the infinity ---*/
7513 //
7514 // V_outlet[nDim+5] = nodes->GetLaminarViscosity(iPoint);
7515 // V_outlet[nDim+6] = nodes->GetEddyViscosity(iPoint);
7516 //
7517 // /*--- Set the normal vector and the coordinates ---*/
7518 //
7519 // visc_numerics->SetNormal(Normal);
7520 // su2double Coord_Reflected[MAXNDIM];
7521 // GeometryToolbox::PointPointReflect(nDim, geometry->nodes->GetCoord(Point_Normal),
7522 // geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint), Coord_Reflected);
7523 // visc_numerics->SetCoord(geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint), Coord_Reflected);
7524 //
7525 // /*--- Primitive variables, and gradient ---*/
7526 //
7527 // visc_numerics->SetPrimitive(V_domain, V_outlet);
7528 // visc_numerics->SetPrimVarGradient(nodes->GetGradient_Primitive(iPoint), nodes->GetGradient_Primitive(iPoint));
7529 //
7530 // /*--- Turbulent kinetic energy ---*/
7531 //
7532 // if (config->GetKind_Turb_Model() == TURB_MODEL::SST)
7533 // visc_numerics->SetTurbKineticEnergy(solver_container[TURB_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetSolution(iPoint,0),
7534 // solver_container[TURB_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetSolution(iPoint,0));
7535 //
7536 // /*--- Compute and update residual ---*/
7537 //
7538 // auto residual = visc_numerics->ComputeResidual(config);
7539 // LinSysRes.SubtractBlock(iPoint, residual);
7540 //
7541 // /*--- Jacobian contribution for implicit integration ---*/
7542 //
7543 // if (implicit)
7544 // Jacobian.SubtractBlock2Diag(iPoint, residual.jacobian_i);
7545 // }
7546 
7547  }
7548  }
7549  END_SU2_OMP_FOR
7550 
7551  /*--- Free locally allocated memory ---*/
7552 
7553  delete [] Normal;
7554 
7555 }
7556 
7557 void CEulerSolver::BC_Engine_Inflow(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver_container, CNumerics *conv_numerics, CNumerics *visc_numerics, CConfig *config, unsigned short val_marker) {
7558 
7559  unsigned short iDim;
7560  unsigned long iVertex, iPoint;
7561  su2double Pressure, Inflow_Pressure = 0.0, Velocity[3], Velocity2, Entropy, Target_Inflow_MassFlow = 0.0, Target_Inflow_Mach = 0.0, Density, Energy,
7562  Riemann, Area, UnitNormal[3], Vn, SoundSpeed, Vn_Exit, Inflow_Pressure_inc, Inflow_Pressure_old, Inflow_Mach_old, Inflow_MassFlow_old;
7563  su2double *V_inflow, *V_domain;
7564 
7565  su2double DampingFactor = config->GetDamp_Engine_Inflow();
7566  bool implicit = (config->GetKind_TimeIntScheme() == EULER_IMPLICIT);
7567  unsigned short Kind_Engine_Inflow = config->GetKind_Engine_Inflow();
7568  su2double Gas_Constant = config->GetGas_ConstantND();
7569  string Marker_Tag = config->GetMarker_All_TagBound(val_marker);
7570  bool tkeNeeded = (config->GetKind_Turb_Model() == TURB_MODEL::SST);
7571  su2double Baseline_Press = 0.75 * config->GetPressure_FreeStreamND();
7572  bool Engine_HalfModel = config->GetEngine_HalfModel();
7573 
7574  auto *Normal = new su2double[nDim];
7575 
7576 
7577  if (Kind_Engine_Inflow == FAN_FACE_MACH) {
7578 
7579  /*--- Retrieve the specified target fan face mach at the nacelle. ---*/
7580 
7581  Target_Inflow_Mach = config->GetEngineInflow_Target(Marker_Tag);
7582 
7583  /*--- Retrieve the old fan face pressure and mach number in the nacelle (this has been computed in a preprocessing). ---*/
7584 
7585  Inflow_Pressure_old = config->GetInflow_Pressure(Marker_Tag); // Note that has been computed by the code (non-dimensional).
7586  Inflow_Mach_old = config->GetInflow_Mach(Marker_Tag);
7587 
7588  /*--- Compute the pressure increment (note that increasing pressure decreases flow speed) ---*/
7589 
7590  Inflow_Pressure_inc = - (1.0 - (Inflow_Mach_old/Target_Inflow_Mach)) * Baseline_Press;
7591 
7592  /*--- Estimate the new fan face pressure ---*/
7593 
7594  Inflow_Pressure = (1.0 - DampingFactor)*Inflow_Pressure_old + DampingFactor * (Inflow_Pressure_old + Inflow_Pressure_inc);
7595 
7596  }
7597 
7598  if (Kind_Engine_Inflow == FAN_FACE_MDOT) {
7599 
7600  /*--- Retrieve the specified target mass flow (non-dimensional) at the nacelle. ---*/
7601 
7602  Target_Inflow_MassFlow = config->GetEngineInflow_Target(Marker_Tag) / (config->GetDensity_Ref() * config->GetVelocity_Ref());
7603 
7604  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) Target_Inflow_MassFlow /= 32.174;
7605 
7606  if (Engine_HalfModel) Target_Inflow_MassFlow /= 2.0;
7607 
7608  /*--- Retrieve the old fan face pressure and mach number in the nacelle (this has been computed in a preprocessing). ---*/
7609 
7610  Inflow_Pressure_old = config->GetInflow_Pressure(Marker_Tag); // Note that has been computed by the code (non-dimensional).
7611  Inflow_MassFlow_old = config->GetInflow_MassFlow(Marker_Tag); // same here... it is a non dimensional value
7612 
7613  /*--- Compute the pressure increment (note that increasing pressure decreases flow speed) ---*/
7614 
7615  Inflow_Pressure_inc = - (1.0 - (Inflow_MassFlow_old/Target_Inflow_MassFlow)) * Baseline_Press;
7616 
7617  /*--- Estimate the new fan face pressure ---*/
7618 
7619  Inflow_Pressure = (1.0 - DampingFactor)*Inflow_Pressure_old + DampingFactor * (Inflow_Pressure_old + Inflow_Pressure_inc);
7620 
7621  }
7622 
7623  /*--- No iterative scheme if we provide the static pressure ---*/
7624 
7625  if (Kind_Engine_Inflow == FAN_FACE_PRESSURE) {
7626 
7627  /*--- Retrieve the specified pressure (non-dimensional) at the nacelle. ---*/
7628 
7629  Inflow_Pressure = config->GetEngineInflow_Target(Marker_Tag) / config->GetPressure_Ref();
7630 
7631  }
7632 
7633 
7634  /*--- Loop over all the vertices on this boundary marker ---*/
7635 
7636  SU2_OMP_FOR_DYN(OMP_MIN_SIZE)
7637  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[val_marker]; iVertex++) {
7638 
7639  /*--- Allocate the value at the outlet ---*/
7640 
7641  V_inflow = GetCharacPrimVar(val_marker, iVertex);
7642 
7643  iPoint = geometry->vertex[val_marker][iVertex]->GetNode();
7644 
7645  /*--- Check if the node belongs to the domain (i.e, not a halo node) ---*/
7646 
7647  if (geometry->nodes->GetDomain(iPoint)) {
7648 
7649  /*--- Normal vector for this vertex (negate for outward convention) ---*/
7650 
7651  geometry->vertex[val_marker][iVertex]->GetNormal(Normal);
7652  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) Normal[iDim] = -Normal[iDim];
7653 
7654  Area = GeometryToolbox::Norm(nDim, Normal);
7655  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
7656  UnitNormal[iDim] = Normal[iDim]/Area;
7657 
7658  /*--- Current solution at this boundary node ---*/
7659 
7660  V_domain = nodes->GetPrimitive(iPoint);
7661 
7662  /*--- Subsonic nacelle inflow: there is one incoming characteristic,
7663  therefore one variable can be specified (back pressure) and is used
7664  to update the conservative variables.
7665 
7666  Compute the entropy and the acoustic variable. These
7667  riemann invariants, as well as the tangential velocity components,
7668  are extrapolated. ---*/
7669 
7670  Density = V_domain[nDim+2];
7671  Velocity2 = 0.0; Vn = 0.0;
7672  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
7673  Velocity[iDim] = V_domain[iDim+1];
7674  Velocity2 += Velocity[iDim]*Velocity[iDim];
7675  Vn += Velocity[iDim]*UnitNormal[iDim];
7676  }
7677  Pressure = V_domain[nDim+1];
7678  SoundSpeed = sqrt(Gamma*Pressure/Density);
7679  Entropy = Pressure*pow(1.0/Density, Gamma);
7680  Riemann = Vn + 2.0*SoundSpeed/Gamma_Minus_One;
7681 
7682  /*--- Compute the new fictious state at the outlet ---*/
7683 
7684  Density = pow(Inflow_Pressure/Entropy,1.0/Gamma);
7685  Pressure = Inflow_Pressure;
7686  SoundSpeed = sqrt(Gamma*Inflow_Pressure/Density);
7687  Vn_Exit = Riemann - 2.0*SoundSpeed/Gamma_Minus_One;
7688  Velocity2 = 0.0;
7689  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
7690  Velocity[iDim] = Velocity[iDim] + (Vn_Exit-Vn)*UnitNormal[iDim];
7691  Velocity2 += Velocity[iDim]*Velocity[iDim];
7692  }
7693 
7694  Energy = Inflow_Pressure/(Density*Gamma_Minus_One) + 0.5*Velocity2;
7695  if (tkeNeeded) Energy += GetTke_Inf();
7696 
7697  /*--- Conservative variables, using the derived quantities ---*/
7698 
7699  V_inflow[0] = Pressure / ( Gas_Constant * Density);
7700  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
7701  V_inflow[iDim+1] = Velocity[iDim];
7702  V_inflow[nDim+1] = Pressure;
7703  V_inflow[nDim+2] = Density;
7704  V_inflow[nDim+3] = Energy + Pressure/Density;
7705  V_inflow[nDim+4] = SoundSpeed;
7706 
7707  /*--- Set various quantities in the solver class ---*/
7708 
7709  conv_numerics->SetNormal(Normal);
7710  conv_numerics->SetPrimitive(V_domain, V_inflow);
7711 
7712  /*--- Set grid movement ---*/
7713 
7714  if (dynamic_grid)
7715  conv_numerics->SetGridVel(geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint), geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint));
7716 
7717  /*--- Compute the residual using an upwind scheme ---*/
7718 
7719  auto residual = conv_numerics->ComputeResidual(config);
7720 
7721  LinSysRes.AddBlock(iPoint, residual);
7722 
7723  /*--- Jacobian contribution for implicit integration ---*/
7724 
7725  if (implicit)
7726  Jacobian.AddBlock2Diag(iPoint, residual.jacobian_i);
7727 
7728 // /*--- Viscous contribution, commented out because serious convergence problems ---*/
7729 //
7730 // if (viscous) {
7731 //
7732 // /*--- Set laminar and eddy viscosity at the infinity ---*/
7733 //
7734 // V_inflow[nDim+5] = nodes->GetLaminarViscosity(iPoint);
7735 // V_inflow[nDim+6] = nodes->GetEddyViscosity(iPoint);
7736 //
7737 // /*--- Set the normal vector and the coordinates ---*/
7738 //
7739 // visc_numerics->SetNormal(Normal);
7740 // su2double Coord_Reflected[MAXNDIM];
7741 // GeometryToolbox::PointPointReflect(nDim, geometry->nodes->GetCoord(Point_Normal),
7742 // geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint), Coord_Reflected);
7743 // visc_numerics->SetCoord(geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint), Coord_Reflected);
7744 //
7745 // /*--- Primitive variables, and gradient ---*/
7746 //
7747 // visc_numerics->SetPrimitive(V_domain, V_inflow);
7748 // visc_numerics->SetPrimVarGradient(nodes->GetGradient_Primitive(iPoint), nodes->GetGradient_Primitive(iPoint));
7749 //
7750 // /*--- Turbulent kinetic energy ---*/
7751 //
7752 // if (config->GetKind_Turb_Model() == TURB_MODEL::SST)
7753 // visc_numerics->SetTurbKineticEnergy(solver_container[TURB_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetSolution(iPoint,0),
7754 // solver_container[TURB_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetSolution(iPoint,0));
7755 //
7756 // /*--- Compute and update residual ---*/
7757 //
7758 // auto residual = visc_numerics->ComputeResidual(config);
7759 // LinSysRes.SubtractBlock(iPoint, residual);
7760 //
7761 // /*--- Jacobian contribution for implicit integration ---*/
7762 //
7763 // if (implicit)
7764 // Jacobian.SubtractBlock2Diag(iPoint, residual.jacobian_i);
7765 //
7766 // }
7767 
7768  }
7769  }
7770  END_SU2_OMP_FOR
7771 
7772  delete [] Normal;
7773 
7774 }
7775 
7776 void CEulerSolver::BC_Engine_Exhaust(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver_container, CNumerics *conv_numerics, CNumerics *visc_numerics, CConfig *config, unsigned short val_marker) {
7777 
7778  unsigned short iDim;
7779  unsigned long iVertex, iPoint;
7780  su2double Exhaust_Pressure, Exhaust_Temperature, Velocity[3], Velocity2, H_Exhaust, Temperature, Riemann, Area, UnitNormal[3], Pressure, Density, Energy, Mach2, SoundSpeed2, SoundSpeed_Exhaust2, Vel_Mag, alpha, aa, bb, cc, dd, Flow_Dir[3];
7781  su2double *V_exhaust, *V_domain, Target_Exhaust_Pressure, Exhaust_Pressure_old, Exhaust_Pressure_inc;
7782 
7783  su2double Gas_Constant = config->GetGas_ConstantND();
7784  bool implicit = (config->GetKind_TimeIntScheme() == EULER_IMPLICIT);
7785  string Marker_Tag = config->GetMarker_All_TagBound(val_marker);
7786  bool tkeNeeded = (config->GetKind_Turb_Model() == TURB_MODEL::SST);
7787  su2double DampingFactor = config->GetDamp_Engine_Exhaust();
7788  su2double Baseline_Press = 0.75 * config->GetPressure_FreeStreamND();
7789 
7790  auto *Normal = new su2double[nDim];
7791 
7792  /*--- Retrieve the specified exhaust pressure in the engine (non-dimensional). ---*/
7793 
7794  Target_Exhaust_Pressure = config->GetExhaust_Pressure_Target(Marker_Tag) / config->GetPressure_Ref();
7795 
7796  /*--- Retrieve the old exhaust pressure in the engine exhaust (this has been computed in a preprocessing). ---*/
7797 
7798  Exhaust_Pressure_old = config->GetExhaust_Pressure(Marker_Tag);
7799 
7800  /*--- Compute the Pressure increment ---*/
7801 
7802  Exhaust_Pressure_inc = (1.0 - (Exhaust_Pressure_old/Target_Exhaust_Pressure)) * Baseline_Press;
7803 
7804  /*--- Estimate the new exhaust pressure ---*/
7805 
7806  Exhaust_Pressure = (1.0 - DampingFactor) * Exhaust_Pressure_old + DampingFactor * (Exhaust_Pressure_old + Exhaust_Pressure_inc);
7807 
7808  /*--- The temperature is given (no iteration is required) ---*/
7809 
7810  Exhaust_Temperature = config->GetExhaust_Temperature_Target(Marker_Tag);
7811  Exhaust_Temperature /= config->GetTemperature_Ref();
7812 
7813  /*--- The pressure is given (no iteration is required) ---*/
7814 
7815  Exhaust_Pressure = config->GetExhaust_Pressure_Target(Marker_Tag);
7816  Exhaust_Pressure /= config->GetPressure_Ref();
7817 
7818  /*--- Loop over all the vertices on this boundary marker ---*/
7819 
7820  SU2_OMP_FOR_DYN(OMP_MIN_SIZE)
7821  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[val_marker]; iVertex++) {
7822 
7823  /*--- Allocate the value at the exhaust ---*/
7824 
7825  V_exhaust = GetCharacPrimVar(val_marker, iVertex);
7826 
7827  iPoint = geometry->vertex[val_marker][iVertex]->GetNode();
7828 
7829  /*--- Check if the node belongs to the domain (i.e, not a halo node) ---*/
7830 
7831  if (geometry->nodes->GetDomain(iPoint)) {
7832 
7833  /*--- Normal vector for this vertex (negate for outward convention) ---*/
7834 
7835  geometry->vertex[val_marker][iVertex]->GetNormal(Normal);
7836  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) Normal[iDim] = -Normal[iDim];
7837 
7838  Area = GeometryToolbox::Norm(nDim, Normal);
7839  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
7840  UnitNormal[iDim] = Normal[iDim]/Area;
7841 
7842  /*--- Current solution at this boundary node ---*/
7843 
7844  V_domain = nodes->GetPrimitive(iPoint);
7845 
7846  /*--- Subsonic inflow: there is one outgoing characteristic (u-c),
7847  therefore we can specify all but one state variable at the inlet.
7848  The outgoing Riemann invariant provides the final piece of info. ---*/
7849 
7850  /*--- Store primitives and set some variables for clarity. ---*/
7851 
7852  Density = V_domain[nDim+2];
7853  Velocity2 = 0.0;
7854  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
7855  Velocity[iDim] = V_domain[iDim+1];
7856  Velocity2 += Velocity[iDim]*Velocity[iDim];
7857  }
7858  Energy = V_domain[nDim+3] - V_domain[nDim+1]/V_domain[nDim+2];
7859  Pressure = V_domain[nDim+1];
7860  H_Exhaust = (Gamma*Gas_Constant/Gamma_Minus_One)*Exhaust_Temperature;
7861  SoundSpeed2 = Gamma*Pressure/Density;
7862 
7863  /*--- Compute the acoustic Riemann invariant that is extrapolated
7864  from the domain interior. ---*/
7865 
7866  Riemann = 2.0*sqrt(SoundSpeed2)/Gamma_Minus_One;
7867  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
7868  Riemann += Velocity[iDim]*UnitNormal[iDim];
7869 
7870  /*--- Total speed of sound ---*/
7871 
7872  SoundSpeed_Exhaust2 = Gamma_Minus_One*(H_Exhaust - (Energy + Pressure/Density)+0.5*Velocity2) + SoundSpeed2;
7873 
7874  /*--- The flow direction is defined by the surface normal ---*/
7875 
7876  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
7877  Flow_Dir[iDim] = -UnitNormal[iDim];
7878 
7879  /*--- Dot product of normal and flow direction. This should
7880  be negative due to outward facing boundary normal convention. ---*/
7881 
7882  alpha = 0.0;
7883  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
7884  alpha += UnitNormal[iDim]*Flow_Dir[iDim];
7885 
7886  /*--- Coefficients in the quadratic equation for the velocity ---*/
7887 
7888  aa = 1.0 + 0.5*Gamma_Minus_One*alpha*alpha;
7889  bb = -1.0*Gamma_Minus_One*alpha*Riemann;
7890  cc = 0.5*Gamma_Minus_One*Riemann*Riemann - 2.0*SoundSpeed_Exhaust2/Gamma_Minus_One;
7891 
7892  /*--- Solve quadratic equation for velocity magnitude. Value must
7893  be positive, so the choice of root is clear. ---*/
7894 
7895  dd = bb*bb - 4.0*aa*cc;
7896  dd = sqrt(max(0.0, dd));
7897  Vel_Mag = (-bb + dd)/(2.0*aa);
7898 
7899  if (Vel_Mag >= 0.0) {
7900 
7901  Velocity2 = Vel_Mag*Vel_Mag;
7902 
7903  /*--- Compute speed of sound from total speed of sound eqn. ---*/
7904 
7905  SoundSpeed2 = SoundSpeed_Exhaust2 - 0.5*Gamma_Minus_One*Velocity2;
7906  Mach2 = Velocity2/SoundSpeed2;
7907  Velocity2 = Mach2*SoundSpeed2;
7908  Vel_Mag = sqrt(Velocity2);
7909  SoundSpeed2 = SoundSpeed_Exhaust2 - 0.5*Gamma_Minus_One*Velocity2;
7910 
7911  /*--- Compute new velocity vector at the inlet ---*/
7912 
7913  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
7914  Velocity[iDim] = Vel_Mag*Flow_Dir[iDim];
7915 
7916  /*--- Static temperature from the speed of sound relation ---*/
7917 
7918  Temperature = SoundSpeed2/(Gamma*Gas_Constant);
7919 
7920  /*--- Static pressure using isentropic relation at a point ---*/
7921 
7922  Pressure = Exhaust_Pressure*pow((Temperature/Exhaust_Temperature), Gamma/Gamma_Minus_One);
7923 
7924  /*--- Density at the exhaust from the gas law ---*/
7925 
7926  Density = Pressure/(Gas_Constant*Temperature);
7927 
7928  /*--- Using pressure, density, & velocity, compute the energy ---*/
7929 
7930  Energy = Pressure/(Density*Gamma_Minus_One) + 0.5*Velocity2;
7931  if (tkeNeeded) Energy += GetTke_Inf();
7932 
7933  /*--- Primitive variables, using the derived quantities ---*/
7934 
7935  V_exhaust[0] = Temperature;
7936  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
7937  V_exhaust[iDim+1] = Velocity[iDim];
7938  V_exhaust[nDim+1] = Pressure;
7939  V_exhaust[nDim+2] = Density;
7940  V_exhaust[nDim+3] = Energy + Pressure/Density;
7941  V_exhaust[nDim+4] = sqrt(SoundSpeed2);
7942 
7943  }
7944  /*--- The flow goes in the wrong direction ---*/
7945 
7946  else {
7947 
7948  V_exhaust[0] = V_domain[0];
7949  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
7950  V_exhaust[iDim+1] = V_domain[iDim+1];
7951  V_exhaust[nDim+1] = V_domain[nDim+1];
7952  V_exhaust[nDim+2] = V_domain[nDim+2];
7953  V_exhaust[nDim+3] = V_domain[nDim+3];
7954  V_exhaust[nDim+4] = V_domain[nDim+4];
7955 
7956  }
7957 
7958  /*--- Set various quantities in the solver class ---*/
7959 
7960  conv_numerics->SetNormal(Normal);
7961  conv_numerics->SetPrimitive(V_domain, V_exhaust);
7962 
7963  /*--- Set grid movement ---*/
7964 
7965  if (dynamic_grid)
7966  conv_numerics->SetGridVel(geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint), geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint));
7967 
7968  /*--- Compute the residual using an upwind scheme ---*/
7969 
7970  auto residual = conv_numerics->ComputeResidual(config);
7971 
7972  LinSysRes.AddBlock(iPoint, residual);
7973 
7974  /*--- Jacobian contribution for implicit integration ---*/
7975 
7976  if (implicit)
7977  Jacobian.AddBlock2Diag(iPoint, residual.jacobian_i);
7978 
7979 // /*--- Viscous contribution, commented out because serious convergence problems ---*/
7980 //
7981 // if (viscous) {
7982 //
7983 // /*--- Set laminar and eddy viscosity at the infinity ---*/
7984 //
7985 // V_exhaust[nDim+5] = nodes->GetLaminarViscosity(iPoint);
7986 // V_exhaust[nDim+6] = nodes->GetEddyViscosity(iPoint);
7987 //
7988 // /*--- Set the normal vector and the coordinates ---*/
7989 //
7990 // visc_numerics->SetNormal(Normal);
7991 // su2double Coord_Reflected[MAXNDIM];
7992 // GeometryToolbox::PointPointReflect(nDim, geometry->nodes->GetCoord(Point_Normal),
7993 // geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint), Coord_Reflected);
7994 // visc_numerics->SetCoord(geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint), Coord_Reflected);
7995 //
7996 // /*--- Primitive variables, and gradient ---*/
7997 //
7998 // visc_numerics->SetPrimitive(V_domain, V_exhaust);
7999 // visc_numerics->SetPrimVarGradient(nodes->GetGradient_Primitive(iPoint), nodes->GetGradient_Primitive(iPoint));
8000 //
8001 // /*--- Turbulent kinetic energy ---*/
8002 //
8003 // if (config->GetKind_Turb_Model() == TURB_MODEL::SST)
8004 // visc_numerics->SetTurbKineticEnergy(solver_container[TURB_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetSolution(iPoint,0),
8005 // solver_container[TURB_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetSolution(iPoint,0));
8006 //
8007 // /*--- Compute and update residual ---*/
8008 //
8009 // auto residual = visc_numerics->ComputeResidual(config)
8010 // LinSysRes.SubtractBlock(iPoint, residual);
8011 //
8012 // /*--- Jacobian contribution for implicit integration ---*/
8013 //
8014 // if (implicit)
8015 // Jacobian.SubtractBlock2Diag(iPoint, residual.jacobian_i);
8016 //
8017 // }
8018 
8019  }
8020  }
8021  END_SU2_OMP_FOR
8022 
8023  delete [] Normal;
8024 
8025 }

8034  }
