8055 void CEulerSolver::BC_ActDisk(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver_container, CNumerics *conv_numerics, CNumerics *visc_numerics,
8056  CConfig *config, unsigned short val_marker, bool val_inlet_surface) {
8057 
8058  unsigned short iDim;
8059  unsigned long iVertex, iPoint, GlobalIndex_donor, GlobalIndex;
8060  su2double Pressure, Velocity[3], Target_Press_Jump, Target_Temp_Jump,
8061  Velocity2, Entropy, Density, Energy, Riemann, Vn, SoundSpeed, Vn_Inlet, Mach_Outlet,
8062  Area, UnitNormal[3], *V_outlet, *V_domain, *V_inlet, P_Total, T_Total, H_Total, Temperature,
8063  Mach2, SoundSpeed2, SoundSpeed_Total2, Vel_Mag, alpha, aa, bb, cc, dd;
8064  su2double Factor, P_static, T_static, SoS_outlet, Rho_outlet, Rho_inlet;
8065  su2double Vel_normal_inlet[3], Vel_tangent_inlet[3], Vel_inlet[3];
8066  su2double Vel_normal_outlet[3], Vel_tangent_outlet[3], Vel_outlet[3];
8067  su2double Vel_normal_inlet_, Vel_tangent_inlet_, Vel_inlet_;
8068  su2double Vel_normal_outlet_, Vel_outlet_;
8069 
8070  su2double Pressure_out, Density_out, SoundSpeed_out, Velocity2_out,
8071  Mach_out, Pressure_in, Density_in, SoundSpeed_in, Velocity2_in,
8072  Mach_in, PressureAdj, TemperatureAdj;
8073 
8074  bool implicit = (config->GetKind_TimeIntScheme() == EULER_IMPLICIT);
8075  su2double Gas_Constant = config->GetGas_ConstantND();
8076  bool tkeNeeded = (config->GetKind_Turb_Model() == TURB_MODEL::SST);
8077  bool ratio = (config->GetActDisk_Jump() == RATIO);
8078  su2double SecondaryFlow = config->GetSecondaryFlow_ActDisk();
8079 
8080  auto *Normal = new su2double[nDim];
8081  auto *Flow_Dir = new su2double[nDim];
8082 
8083  /*--- Loop over all the vertices on this boundary marker ---*/
8084 
8085  SU2_OMP_FOR_DYN(OMP_MIN_SIZE)
8086  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[val_marker]; iVertex++) {
8087 
8088  iPoint = geometry->vertex[val_marker][iVertex]->GetNode();
8089  GlobalIndex = geometry->nodes->GetGlobalIndex(iPoint);
8090  GlobalIndex_donor = GetDonorGlobalIndex(val_marker, iVertex);
8091 
8092  /*--- Check if the node belongs to the domain (i.e., not a halo node) ---*/
8093 
8094  if ((geometry->nodes->GetDomain(iPoint)) &&
8095  (GlobalIndex != GlobalIndex_donor)) {
8096 
8097  /*--- Normal vector for this vertex (negative for outward convention) ---*/
8098 
8099  geometry->vertex[val_marker][iVertex]->GetNormal(Normal);
8100  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) Normal[iDim] = -Normal[iDim];
8101  conv_numerics->SetNormal(Normal);
8102 
8103  Area = GeometryToolbox::Norm(nDim, Normal);
8104  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
8105  UnitNormal[iDim] = Normal[iDim]/Area;
8106 
8107  /*--- Current solution at this boundary node and jumps values ---*/
8108 
8109  V_domain = nodes->GetPrimitive(iPoint);
8110  Target_Press_Jump = ActDisk_DeltaP[val_marker][iVertex];
8111  Target_Temp_Jump = ActDisk_DeltaT[val_marker][iVertex];
8112 
8113  if (val_inlet_surface) {
8114  V_inlet = nodes->GetPrimitive(iPoint);
8115  V_outlet = DonorPrimVar[val_marker][iVertex];
8116 
8117  Pressure_out = V_outlet[nDim+1];
8118  Density_out = V_outlet[nDim+2];
8119  SoundSpeed_out = sqrt(Gamma*Pressure_out/Density_out);
8120 
8121  Pressure_in = V_inlet[nDim+1];
8122  Density_in = V_inlet[nDim+2];
8123  SoundSpeed_in = sqrt(Gamma*Pressure_in/Density_in);
8124 
8125  Velocity2_out = 0.0; Velocity2_in = 0.0;
8126  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
8127  Velocity2_out += V_outlet[iDim+1]*V_outlet[iDim+1];
8128  Velocity2_in += V_inlet[iDim+1]*V_inlet[iDim+1];
8129  }
8130 
8131  PressureAdj = 1.0; TemperatureAdj = 1.0;
8132  if ((Velocity2_out > 0.0) && (Velocity2_in > 0.0)) {
8133 
8134  Mach_out = sqrt(Velocity2_out)/SoundSpeed_out;
8135  Mach_in = sqrt(Velocity2_in)/SoundSpeed_in;
8136 
8137  PressureAdj = pow( 1.0 + Mach_out * Mach_out * 0.5 * (Gamma - 1.0), Gamma / (Gamma - 1.0)) /
8138  pow( 1.0 + Mach_in * Mach_in * 0.5 * (Gamma - 1.0), Gamma / (Gamma - 1.0));
8139  TemperatureAdj = (1.0 + Mach_out * Mach_out * 0.5 * (Gamma - 1.0)) /
8140  (1.0 + Mach_in * Mach_in * 0.5 * (Gamma - 1.0));
8141 
8142  }
8143 
8144  if (ratio) {
8145  P_static = V_outlet[nDim+1] / (Target_Press_Jump/PressureAdj);
8146  T_static = V_outlet[0] / (Target_Temp_Jump/TemperatureAdj);
8147  }
8148  else { P_static = V_outlet[nDim+1] - Target_Press_Jump; T_static = V_outlet[0] - Target_Temp_Jump; }
8149  }
8150  else {
8151  V_outlet = nodes->GetPrimitive(iPoint);
8152  V_inlet = DonorPrimVar[val_marker][iVertex];
8153 
8154  Pressure_out = V_outlet[nDim+1];
8155  Density_out = V_outlet[nDim+2];
8156  SoundSpeed_out = sqrt(Gamma*Pressure_out/Density_out);
8157 
8158  Pressure_in = V_inlet[nDim+1];
8159  Density_in = V_inlet[nDim+2];
8160  SoundSpeed_in = sqrt(Gamma*Pressure_in/Density_in);
8161 
8162  Velocity2_out = 0.0; Velocity2_in = 0.0;
8163  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
8164  Velocity2_out += V_outlet[iDim+1]*V_outlet[iDim+1];
8165  Velocity2_in += V_inlet[iDim+1]*V_inlet[iDim+1];
8166  }
8167 
8168  PressureAdj = 1.0; TemperatureAdj = 1.0;
8169  if ((Velocity2_out > 0.0) && (Velocity2_in > 0.0)) {
8170 
8171  Mach_out = sqrt(Velocity2_out)/SoundSpeed_out;
8172  Mach_in = sqrt(Velocity2_in)/SoundSpeed_in;
8173 
8174  PressureAdj = pow( 1.0 + Mach_out * Mach_out * 0.5 * (Gamma - 1.0), Gamma / (Gamma - 1.0)) /
8175  pow( 1.0 + Mach_in * Mach_in * 0.5 * (Gamma - 1.0), Gamma / (Gamma - 1.0));
8176  TemperatureAdj = (1.0 + Mach_out * Mach_out * 0.5 * (Gamma - 1.0)) /
8177  (1.0 + Mach_in * Mach_in * 0.5 * (Gamma - 1.0));
8178  }
8179 
8180  if (ratio) {
8181  P_static = V_inlet[nDim+1] * (Target_Press_Jump/PressureAdj);
8182  T_static = V_inlet[0] * (Target_Temp_Jump/TemperatureAdj);
8183  }
8184  else { P_static = V_inlet[nDim+1] + Target_Press_Jump; T_static = V_inlet[0] + Target_Temp_Jump; }
8185  }
8186 
8187  /*--- Subsonic inlet ---*/
8188 
8189  if (val_inlet_surface) {
8190 
8191  /*--- Build the fictitious intlet state based on characteristics.
8192  Retrieve the specified back pressure for this inlet ---*/
8193 
8194  Density = V_domain[nDim+2];
8195  Velocity2 = 0.0; Vn = 0.0;
8196  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
8197  Velocity[iDim] = V_domain[iDim+1];
8198  Velocity2 += Velocity[iDim]*Velocity[iDim];
8199  Vn += Velocity[iDim]*UnitNormal[iDim];
8200  }
8201  Pressure = V_domain[nDim+1];
8202  SoundSpeed = sqrt(Gamma*Pressure/Density);
8203 
8204  Entropy = Pressure*pow(1.0/Density, Gamma);
8205  Riemann = Vn + 2.0*SoundSpeed/Gamma_Minus_One;
8206 
8207  /*--- Compute the new fictious state at the outlet ---*/
8208 
8209  Pressure = P_static;
8210  Density = pow(Pressure/Entropy,1.0/Gamma);
8211  SoundSpeed = sqrt(Gamma*Pressure/Density);
8212  Vn_Inlet = Riemann - 2.0*SoundSpeed/Gamma_Minus_One;
8213 
8214  Velocity2 = 0.0;
8215  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
8216  Velocity[iDim] = Velocity[iDim] + (Vn_Inlet-Vn)*UnitNormal[iDim];
8217  Velocity2 += Velocity[iDim]*Velocity[iDim];
8218  }
8219  Energy = Pressure/(Density*Gamma_Minus_One) + 0.5*Velocity2;
8220  if (tkeNeeded) Energy += GetTke_Inf();
8221 
8222  /*--- Conservative variables, using the derived quantities ---*/
8223 
8224  V_inlet[0] = Pressure / ( Gas_Constant * Density);
8225  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
8226  V_inlet[iDim+1] = Velocity[iDim];
8227  V_inlet[nDim+1] = Pressure;
8228  V_inlet[nDim+2] = Density;
8229  V_inlet[nDim+3] = Energy + Pressure/Density;
8230  V_inlet[nDim+4] = SoundSpeed;
8231  conv_numerics->SetPrimitive(V_domain, V_inlet);
8232 
8233  }
8234 
8235  /*--- Subsonic outlet ---*/
8236 
8237  else {
8238 
8239  GetFluidModel()->SetTDState_PT(P_static, T_static);
8240  SoS_outlet = GetFluidModel()->GetSoundSpeed();
8241  Rho_outlet = GetFluidModel()->GetDensity();
8242 
8243  /*--- We use the velocity and the density from the flow inlet
8244  to evaluate flow direction and mass flow ---*/
8245 
8246  Rho_inlet = V_inlet[nDim+2];
8247  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
8248  Vel_inlet[iDim] = V_inlet[iDim+1];
8249 
8250  Vel_normal_inlet_ = 0.0; Vel_inlet_ = 0.0;
8251  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
8252  Vel_normal_inlet[iDim] = -Vel_inlet[iDim]*UnitNormal[iDim];
8253  Vel_normal_inlet_ += Vel_normal_inlet[iDim]*Vel_normal_inlet[iDim];
8254  Vel_inlet_+= Vel_inlet[iDim]*Vel_inlet[iDim];
8255  }
8256  Vel_inlet_ = sqrt(Vel_inlet_);
8257  Vel_normal_inlet_ = sqrt(Vel_normal_inlet_);
8258 
8259  Vel_tangent_inlet_ = 0.0;
8260  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
8261  Vel_tangent_inlet[iDim] = Vel_inlet[iDim] - Vel_normal_inlet[iDim];
8262  Vel_tangent_inlet_ += Vel_tangent_inlet[iDim]*Vel_tangent_inlet[iDim];
8263  }
8264  Vel_tangent_inlet_ = sqrt(Vel_tangent_inlet_);
8265 
8266  /*--- Mass flow conservation (normal direction) and
8267  no jump in the tangential velocity ---*/
8268 
8269  Vel_normal_outlet_ = (1.0-SecondaryFlow/100.0)*(Rho_inlet*Vel_normal_inlet_)/Rho_outlet;
8270 
8271  Vel_outlet_ = 0.0;
8272  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
8273  Vel_normal_outlet[iDim] = -Vel_normal_outlet_*UnitNormal[iDim];
8274  Vel_tangent_outlet[iDim] = Vel_tangent_inlet[iDim];
8275  Vel_outlet[iDim] = Vel_normal_outlet[iDim] + Vel_tangent_outlet[iDim];
8276  Vel_outlet_ += Vel_outlet[iDim]*Vel_outlet[iDim];
8277  }
8278  Vel_outlet_ = sqrt(Vel_outlet_);
8279 
8280  Mach_Outlet = min(Vel_outlet_/SoS_outlet, 1.0);
8281 
8282  /*--- Reevaluate the Total Pressure and Total Temperature using the
8283  Fan Face Mach number and the static values from the jum condition ---*/
8284 
8285  Factor = 1.0 + 0.5*Mach_Outlet*Mach_Outlet*Gamma_Minus_One;
8286  P_Total = P_static * pow(Factor, Gamma/Gamma_Minus_One);
8287  T_Total = T_static * Factor;
8288 
8289  /*--- Flow direction using the velocity direction at the outlet ---*/
8290 
8291  if (Vel_outlet_ != 0.0) {
8292  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) Flow_Dir[iDim] = Vel_outlet[iDim]/Vel_outlet_;
8293  }
8294  else {
8295  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) Flow_Dir[iDim] = 0.0;
8296  }
8297 
8298  /*--- Store primitives and set some variables for clarity. ---*/
8299 
8300  Density = V_domain[nDim+2];
8301  Velocity2 = 0.0;
8302  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
8303  Velocity[iDim] = V_domain[iDim+1];
8304  Velocity2 += Velocity[iDim]*Velocity[iDim];
8305  }
8306  Energy = V_domain[nDim+3] - V_domain[nDim+1]/V_domain[nDim+2];
8307  Pressure = V_domain[nDim+1];
8308  H_Total = (Gamma*Gas_Constant/Gamma_Minus_One)*T_Total;
8309  SoundSpeed2 = Gamma*Pressure/Density;
8310 
8311  /*--- Compute the acoustic Riemann invariant that is extrapolated
8312  from the domain interior. ---*/
8313 
8314  Riemann = 2.0*sqrt(SoundSpeed2)/Gamma_Minus_One;
8315  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
8316  Riemann += Velocity[iDim]*UnitNormal[iDim];
8317 
8318  /*--- Total speed of sound ---*/
8319 
8320  SoundSpeed_Total2 = Gamma_Minus_One*(H_Total - (Energy + Pressure/Density)+0.5*Velocity2) + SoundSpeed2;
8321 
8322  /*--- Dot product of normal and flow direction. This should
8323  be negative due to outward facing boundary normal convention. ---*/
8324 
8325  alpha = 0.0;
8326  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
8327  alpha += UnitNormal[iDim]*Flow_Dir[iDim];
8328 
8329  /*--- Coefficients in the quadratic equation for the velocity ---*/
8330 
8331  aa = 1.0 + 0.5*Gamma_Minus_One*alpha*alpha;
8332  bb = -1.0*Gamma_Minus_One*alpha*Riemann;
8333  cc = 0.5*Gamma_Minus_One*Riemann*Riemann - 2.0*SoundSpeed_Total2/Gamma_Minus_One;
8334 
8335  /*--- Solve quadratic equation for velocity magnitude. Value must
8336  be positive, so the choice of root is clear. ---*/
8337 
8338  dd = bb*bb - 4.0*aa*cc;
8339  dd = sqrt(max(0.0, dd));
8340  Vel_Mag = (-bb + dd)/(2.0*aa);
8341  Vel_Mag = max(0.0, Vel_Mag);
8342  Velocity2 = Vel_Mag*Vel_Mag;
8343 
8344  /*--- Compute speed of sound from total speed of sound eqn. ---*/
8345 
8346  SoundSpeed2 = SoundSpeed_Total2 - 0.5*Gamma_Minus_One*Velocity2;
8347 
8348  /*--- Mach squared (cut between 0-1), use to adapt velocity ---*/
8349 
8350  Mach2 = min(1.0, Velocity2/SoundSpeed2);
8351  Velocity2 = Mach2*SoundSpeed2;
8352  Vel_Mag = sqrt(Velocity2);
8353  SoundSpeed2 = SoundSpeed_Total2 - 0.5*Gamma_Minus_One*Velocity2;
8354 
8355  /*--- Compute new velocity vector at the exit ---*/
8356 
8357  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
8358  Velocity[iDim] = Vel_Mag*Flow_Dir[iDim];
8359 
8360  /*--- Static temperature from the speed of sound relation ---*/
8361 
8362  Temperature = SoundSpeed2/(Gamma*Gas_Constant);
8363 
8364  /*--- Static pressure using isentropic relation at a point ---*/
8365 
8366  Pressure = P_Total*pow((Temperature/T_Total), Gamma/Gamma_Minus_One);
8367 
8368  /*--- Density at the inlet from the gas law ---*/
8369 
8370  Density = Pressure/(Gas_Constant*Temperature);
8371 
8372  /*--- Using pressure, density, & velocity, compute the energy ---*/
8373 
8374  Energy = Pressure/(Density*Gamma_Minus_One) + 0.5*Velocity2;
8375  if (tkeNeeded) Energy += GetTke_Inf();
8376 
8377  /*--- Primitive variables, using the derived quantities ---*/
8378 
8379  V_outlet[0] = Temperature;
8380  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
8381  V_outlet[iDim+1] = Velocity[iDim];
8382  V_outlet[nDim+1] = Pressure;
8383  V_outlet[nDim+2] = Density;
8384  V_outlet[nDim+3] = Energy + Pressure/Density;
8385  V_outlet[nDim+4] = sqrt(SoundSpeed2);
8386  conv_numerics->SetPrimitive(V_domain, V_outlet);
8387 
8388  }
8389 
8390  /*--- Grid Movement ---*/
8391 
8392  if (dynamic_grid)
8393  conv_numerics->SetGridVel(geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint), geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint));
8394 
8395  /*--- Compute the residual using an upwind scheme ---*/
8396 
8397  auto residual = conv_numerics->ComputeResidual(config);
8398 
8399  /*--- Update residual value ---*/
8400 
8401  LinSysRes.AddBlock(iPoint, residual);
8402 
8403  /*--- Jacobian contribution for implicit integration ---*/
8404 
8405  if (implicit) Jacobian.AddBlock2Diag(iPoint, residual.jacobian_i);
8406 
8407 // /*--- Viscous contribution, commented out because serious convergence problems ---*/
8408 //
8409 // if (viscous) {
8410 //
8411 // /*--- Set laminar and eddy viscosity at the infinity ---*/
8412 //
8413 // if (val_inlet_surface) {
8414 // V_inlet[nDim+5] = nodes->GetLaminarViscosity(iPoint);
8415 // V_inlet[nDim+6] = nodes->GetEddyViscosity(iPoint);
8416 // }
8417 // else {
8418 // V_outlet[nDim+5] = nodes->GetLaminarViscosity(iPoint);
8419 // V_outlet[nDim+6] = nodes->GetEddyViscosity(iPoint);
8420 // }
8421 //
8422 // /*--- Set the normal vector and the coordinates ---*/
8423 //
8424 // visc_numerics->SetNormal(Normal);
8425 // su2double Coord_Reflected[MAXNDIM];
8426 // GeometryToolbox::PointPointReflect(nDim, geometry->nodes->GetCoord(Point_Normal),
8427 // geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint), Coord_Reflected);
8428 // visc_numerics->SetCoord(geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint), Coord_Reflected);
8429 //
8430 // /*--- Primitive variables, and gradient ---*/
8431 //
8432 // if (val_inlet_surface) visc_numerics->SetPrimitive(V_domain, V_inlet);
8433 // else visc_numerics->SetPrimitive(V_domain, V_outlet);
8434 //
8435 // visc_numerics->SetPrimVarGradient(nodes->GetGradient_Primitive(iPoint), nodes->GetGradient_Primitive(iPoint));
8436 //
8437 // /*--- Turbulent kinetic energy ---*/
8438 //
8439 // if (config->GetKind_Turb_Model() == TURB_MODEL::SST)
8440 // visc_numerics->SetTurbKineticEnergy(solver_container[TURB_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetSolution(iPoint,0),
8441 // solver_container[TURB_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetSolution(iPoint,0));
8442 //
8443 // /*--- Compute and update residual ---*/
8444 //
8445 // auto residual = visc_numerics->ComputeResidual(config);
8446 // LinSysRes.SubtractBlock(iPoint, residual);
8447 //
8448 // /*--- Jacobian contribution for implicit integration ---*/
8449 //
8450 // if (implicit) Jacobian.SubtractBlock2Diag(iPoint, residual.jacobian_i);
8451 //
8452 // }
8453 
8454  }
8455 
8456  }
8457  END_SU2_OMP_FOR
8458 
8459  /*--- Free locally allocated memory ---*/
8460 
8461  delete [] Normal;
8462  delete [] Flow_Dir;
8463 
8464 }
8465 
8466 void CEulerSolver::BC_ActDisk_VariableLoad(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver_container, CNumerics *conv_numerics, CNumerics *visc_numerics,
8467  CConfig *config, unsigned short val_marker, bool val_inlet_surface) {
8468 
8469  /*!
8470  * \function BC_ActDisk_VariableLoad
8471  * \brief Actuator disk model with variable load along disk radius.
8472  * \author: E. Saetta, L. Russo, R. Tognaccini (GitHub references EttoreSaetta, lorenzorusso07, rtogna).
8473  * Theoretical and Applied Aerodynamics Research Group (TAARG), University of Naples Federico II.
8474  * First release date : July 1st 2020
8475  * modified on:
8476  *
8477  * Force coefficients distribution given in an input file. Actuator disk data initialized in function SetActDisk_BCThrust.
8478  * Entropy, acoustic Riemann invariant R+ and tangential velocity extrapolated from upstream flow;
8479  * acoustic Riemann invariant R- is extrapolated from downstream.
8480  * Hovering condition simulation not available yet: freestream velocity must be different than zero.
8481  */
8482 
8483  unsigned short iDim;
8484  unsigned long iVertex, iPoint, GlobalIndex_donor, GlobalIndex;
8485  su2double Pressure, Velocity[MAXNDIM],
8486  Velocity2, Entropy, Density, Energy, Riemann, Vn, SoundSpeed, Vn_Inlet,
8487  Area, UnitNormal[MAXNDIM] = {0.0}, *V_outlet, *V_domain, *V_inlet;
8488 
8489  su2double Pressure_out, Density_out,
8490  Pressure_in, Density_in;
8491 
8492  su2double Prop_Axis[MAXNDIM];
8493  su2double Fa, Fx, Fy, Fz;
8494  su2double u_in, v_in, w_in, u_out, v_out, w_out, uJ, vJ, wJ;
8495  su2double Temperature_out, H_in, H_out;
8496  su2double FQ, Q_out, Density_Disk;
8497  su2double SoSextr, Vnextr[MAXNDIM], Vnextr_, RiemannExtr, QdMnorm[MAXNDIM], QdMnorm2, appo2, SoS_out;
8498  su2double Normal[MAXNDIM];
8499 
8500  const bool implicit = (config->GetKind_TimeIntScheme() == EULER_IMPLICIT);
8501  const auto Gas_Constant = config->GetGas_ConstantND();
8502  const bool tkeNeeded = (config->GetKind_Turb_Model() == TURB_MODEL::SST);
8503 
8504  unsigned short Kind_ActDisk = config->GetKind_ActDisk();
8505 
8506  /*--- Get the actuator disk center and axis coordinates for the current marker. ---*/
8507  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++){
8508  Prop_Axis[iDim] = ActDisk_Axis(val_marker, iDim);
8509  }
8510 
8511  /*--- Loop over all the vertices on this boundary marker. ---*/
8512  SU2_OMP_FOR_DYN(OMP_MIN_SIZE)
8513  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[val_marker]; iVertex++) {
8514 
8515  iPoint = geometry->vertex[val_marker][iVertex]->GetNode();
8516  GlobalIndex = geometry->nodes->GetGlobalIndex(iPoint);
8517  GlobalIndex_donor = GetDonorGlobalIndex(val_marker, iVertex);
8518 
8519  /*--- Check if the node belongs to the domain (i.e., not a halo node) ---*/
8520 
8521  if ((geometry->nodes->GetDomain(iPoint)) &&
8522  (GlobalIndex != GlobalIndex_donor)) {
8523 
8524  /*--- Normal vector for this vertex (negative for outward convention) ---*/
8525 
8526  geometry->vertex[val_marker][iVertex]->GetNormal(Normal);
8527  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) Normal[iDim] = -Normal[iDim];
8528  conv_numerics->SetNormal(Normal);
8529 
8530  Area = GeometryToolbox::Norm(nDim, Normal);
8531  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
8532  UnitNormal[iDim] = Normal[iDim]/Area;
8533 
8534  /*--- Current solution at this boundary node. ---*/
8535 
8536  V_domain = nodes->GetPrimitive(iPoint);
8537 
8538  /*--- Get the values of Fa (axial force per unit area), Fx, Fy and Fz (x, y and z components of the tangential and
8539  radial forces per unit area resultant). ---*/
8540  if (Kind_ActDisk == BLADE_ELEMENT) {
8541  Fa = ActDisk_Fa_BEM[val_marker][iVertex];
8542  Fx = ActDisk_Fx_BEM[val_marker][iVertex];
8543  Fy = ActDisk_Fy_BEM[val_marker][iVertex];
8544  Fz = ActDisk_Fz_BEM[val_marker][iVertex];
8545  } else { /*--- default (Kind_ActDisk == VARIABLE_LOAD) ---*/
8546  Fa = ActDisk_Fa[val_marker][iVertex];
8547  Fx = ActDisk_Fx[val_marker][iVertex];
8548  Fy = ActDisk_Fy[val_marker][iVertex];
8549  Fz = ActDisk_Fz[val_marker][iVertex];
8550  }
8551 
8552  /*--- Get the primitive variables and the extrapolated variables. ---*/
8553  if (val_inlet_surface){
8554  V_inlet = nodes->GetPrimitive(iPoint);
8555  V_outlet = DonorPrimVar[val_marker][iVertex];}
8556  else{
8557  V_outlet = nodes->GetPrimitive(iPoint);
8558  V_inlet = DonorPrimVar[val_marker][iVertex];}
8559 
8560  /*--- u, v and w are the three momentum components. ---*/
8561  Pressure_out = V_outlet[nDim+1];
8562  Density_out = V_outlet[nDim+2];
8563  u_out = V_outlet[1]*V_outlet[nDim+2];
8564  v_out = V_outlet[2]*V_outlet[nDim+2];
8565  w_out = V_outlet[3]*V_outlet[nDim+2];
8566 
8567  Pressure_in = V_inlet[nDim+1];
8568  Density_in = V_inlet[nDim+2];
8569  u_in = V_inlet[1]*Density_in;
8570  v_in = V_inlet[2]*Density_in;
8571  w_in = V_inlet[3]*Density_in;
8572  H_in = V_inlet[nDim+3]*Density_in;
8573 
8574  /*--- Density on the disk is computed as an everage value between the inlet and outlet values. ---*/
8575  Density_Disk = 0.5*(Density_in + Density_out);
8576 
8577  /*--- Computation of the normal momentum flowing through the disk. ---*/
8578  Q_out = 0.5*((u_in + u_out)*Prop_Axis[0] + (v_in + v_out)*Prop_Axis[1] + (w_in + w_out)*Prop_Axis[2]);
8579 
8580  FQ = Q_out/Density_Disk;
8581 
8582  /*--- Computation of the momentum jumps due to the tnagential and radial forces per unit area. ---*/
8583  if (FQ < EPS){
8584  uJ = 0.0;
8585  vJ = 0.0;
8586  wJ = 0.0;}
8587  else{
8588  uJ = Fx/FQ;
8589  vJ = Fy/FQ;
8590  wJ = Fz/FQ;}
8591 
8592  if (val_inlet_surface) {
8593  /*--- Build the fictitious intlet state based on characteristics.
8594  Retrieve the specified back pressure for this inlet ---*/
8595 
8596  Density = V_domain[nDim+2];
8597  Velocity2 = 0.0; Vn = 0.0;
8598  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
8599  Velocity[iDim] = V_domain[iDim+1];
8600  Velocity2 += Velocity[iDim]*Velocity[iDim];
8601  Vn += Velocity[iDim]*UnitNormal[iDim];
8602  }
8603  Pressure = V_domain[nDim+1];
8604  SoundSpeed = sqrt(Gamma*Pressure/Density);
8605 
8606  Entropy = Pressure*pow(1.0/Density, Gamma);
8607  Riemann = Vn + 2.0*SoundSpeed/Gamma_Minus_One;
8608 
8609  /*--- Compute the new fictious state at the outlet ---*/
8610 
8611  Pressure = Pressure_out - Fa;
8612  Density = pow(Pressure/Entropy,1.0/Gamma);
8613  SoundSpeed = sqrt(Gamma*Pressure/Density);
8614  Vn_Inlet = Riemann - 2.0*SoundSpeed/Gamma_Minus_One;
8615 
8616  Velocity2 = 0.0;
8617  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
8618  Velocity[iDim] = Velocity[iDim] + (Vn_Inlet-Vn)*UnitNormal[iDim];
8619  Velocity2 += Velocity[iDim]*Velocity[iDim];
8620  }
8621  Energy = Pressure/(Density*Gamma_Minus_One) + 0.5*Velocity2;
8622  if (tkeNeeded) Energy += GetTke_Inf();
8623 
8624  /*--- Conservative variables, using the derived quantities ---*/
8625 
8626  V_inlet[0] = Pressure / ( Gas_Constant * Density);
8627  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) V_inlet[iDim+1] = Velocity[iDim];
8628  V_inlet[nDim+1] = Pressure;
8629  V_inlet[nDim+2] = Density;
8630  V_inlet[nDim+3] = Energy + Pressure/Density;
8631  V_inlet[nDim+4] = SoundSpeed;
8632  conv_numerics->SetPrimitive(V_domain, V_inlet);
8633  }
8634  else {
8635  /*--- Acoustic Riemann invariant extrapolation form the interior domain. ---*/
8636  SoSextr = V_domain[nDim+4];
8637 
8638  Vnextr_ = 0.0;
8639  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++){
8640  Vnextr[iDim] = V_domain[iDim+1]*Prop_Axis[iDim];
8641  Vnextr_ += Vnextr[iDim]*Vnextr[iDim];
8642  }
8643  Vnextr_ = sqrt(max(0.0,Vnextr_));
8644  RiemannExtr = Vnextr_ - ((2*SoSextr)/(Gamma_Minus_One));
8645 
8646  /*--- Assigning the momentum in tangential direction jump and the pressure jump. ---*/
8647  Velocity[0] = u_in + uJ;
8648  Velocity[1] = v_in + vJ;
8649  Velocity[2] = w_in + wJ;
8650  Pressure_out = Pressure_in + Fa;
8651 
8652  /*--- Computation of the momentum normal to the disk plane. ---*/
8653  QdMnorm[0] = u_in*Prop_Axis[0];
8654  QdMnorm[1] = v_in*Prop_Axis[1];
8655  QdMnorm[2] = w_in*Prop_Axis[2];
8656 
8657  QdMnorm2 = 0.0;
8658  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) QdMnorm2 += QdMnorm[iDim]*QdMnorm[iDim];
8659 
8660  /*--- Resolving the second grade equation for the density. ---*/
8661  appo2 = -((2*sqrt(QdMnorm2)*RiemannExtr)+((4*Gamma*Pressure_out)/(pow(Gamma_Minus_One,2))));
8662  Density_out = (-appo2+sqrt(max(0.0,pow(appo2,2)-4*QdMnorm2*pow(RiemannExtr,2))))/(2*pow(RiemannExtr,2));
8663 
8664  Velocity2 = 0;
8665  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) Velocity2 += (Velocity[iDim]*Velocity[iDim]);
8666 
8667  /*--- Computation of the enthalpy, total energy, temperature and speed of sound. ---*/
8668  H_out = H_in/Density_in + Fa/Density_out;
8669  Energy = H_out - Pressure_out/Density_out;
8670  if (tkeNeeded) Energy += GetTke_Inf();
8671  Temperature_out = (Energy-0.5*Velocity2/(pow(Density_out,2)))*(Gamma_Minus_One/Gas_Constant);
8672 
8673  SoS_out = sqrt(Gamma*Gas_Constant*Temperature_out);
8674 
8675  /*--- Set the primitive variables. ---*/
8676  V_outlet[0] = Temperature_out;
8677  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
8678  V_outlet[iDim+1] = Velocity[iDim]/Density_out;
8679  V_outlet[nDim+1] = Pressure_out;
8680  V_outlet[nDim+2] = Density_out;
8681  V_outlet[nDim+3] = H_out;
8682  V_outlet[nDim+4] = SoS_out;
8683  conv_numerics->SetPrimitive(V_domain, V_outlet);
8684  }
8685 
8686  /*--- Grid Movement (NOT TESTED!)---*/
8687 
8688  if (dynamic_grid)
8689  conv_numerics->SetGridVel(geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint), geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint));
8690 
8691  /*--- Compute the residual using an upwind scheme ---*/
8692 
8693  auto residual = conv_numerics->ComputeResidual(config);
8694 
8695  /*--- Update residual value ---*/
8696 
8697  LinSysRes.AddBlock(iPoint, residual);
8698 
8699  /*--- Jacobian contribution for implicit integration ---*/
8700 
8701  if (implicit) Jacobian.AddBlock2Diag(iPoint, residual.jacobian_i);
8702  }
8703  }
8704  END_SU2_OMP_FOR
8705 }
8706 
8707 void CEulerSolver::PrintVerificationError(const CConfig *config) const {
8708 
8709  if ((rank != MASTER_NODE) || (MGLevel != MESH_0)) return;
8710 
8711  if (config && !config->GetDiscrete_Adjoint()) {
8712 
8713  cout.precision(5);
8714  cout.setf(ios::scientific, ios::floatfield);
8715 
8716  cout << endl << "------------------------ Global Error Analysis --------------------------" << endl;
8717 
8718  cout << setw(20) << "RMS Error [Rho]: " << setw(12) << VerificationSolution->GetError_RMS(0) << " | ";
8719  cout << setw(20) << "Max Error [Rho]: " << setw(12) << VerificationSolution->GetError_Max(0);
8720  cout << endl;
8721 
8722  cout << setw(20) << "RMS Error [RhoU]: " << setw(12) << VerificationSolution->GetError_RMS(1) << " | ";
8723  cout << setw(20) << "Max Error [RhoU]: " << setw(12) << VerificationSolution->GetError_Max(1);
8724  cout << endl;
8725 
8726  cout << setw(20) << "RMS Error [RhoV]: " << setw(12) << VerificationSolution->GetError_RMS(2) << " | ";
8727  cout << setw(20) << "Max Error [RhoV]: " << setw(12) << VerificationSolution->GetError_Max(2);
8728  cout << endl;
8729 
8730  if (nDim == 3) {
8731  cout << setw(20) << "RMS Error [RhoW]: " << setw(12) << VerificationSolution->GetError_RMS(3) << " | ";
8732  cout << setw(20) << "Max Error [RhoW]: " << setw(12) << VerificationSolution->GetError_Max(3);
8733  cout << endl;
8734  }
8735 
8736  cout << setw(20) << "RMS Error [RhoE]: " << setw(12) << VerificationSolution->GetError_RMS(nDim+1) << " | ";
8737  cout << setw(20) << "Max Error [RhoE]: " << setw(12) << VerificationSolution->GetError_Max(nDim+1);
8738  cout << endl;

8740  cout << "-------------------------------------------------------------------------" << endl << endl;
8741  cout.unsetf(ios_base::floatfield);
8742  }

8745 void CEulerSolver::SetFreeStream_Solution(const CConfig *config) {
8746  SU2_OMP_FOR_STAT(omp_chunk_size)
8747  for (auto iPoint = 0u; iPoint < nPoint; iPoint++) {
8748  nodes->SetSolution(iPoint,0, Density_Inf);
8749  for (auto iDim = 0u; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
8750  nodes->SetSolution(iPoint,iDim+1, Density_Inf*Velocity_Inf[iDim]);
8751  }
8752  nodes->SetSolution(iPoint,nVar-1, Density_Inf*Energy_Inf);
8753  }
8754  END_SU2_OMP_FOR
8755 }
8756 
8757 void CEulerSolver::SetFreeStream_TurboSolution(CConfig *config) {
8758 
8759  const su2double Alpha = config->GetAoA()*PI_NUMBER/180.0;
8760  const auto Mach = config->GetMach();
8761 
8762  su2double turboVelocity[MAXNDIM] = {0}, cartVelocity[MAXNDIM] = {0};
8763 
8764  auto turboNormal = config->GetFreeStreamTurboNormal();
8765 
8766  GetFluidModel()->SetTDState_Prho(Pressure_Inf, Density_Inf);
8767  const auto SoundSpeed = GetFluidModel()->GetSoundSpeed();
8768 
8769  /*--- Compute the Free Stream velocity, using the Mach number ---*/
8770  turboVelocity[0] = cos(Alpha)*Mach*SoundSpeed;
8771  turboVelocity[1] = sin(Alpha)*Mach*SoundSpeed;
8772 
8773  const auto iZone = config->GetiZone();
8774  ComputeBackVelocity(turboVelocity, turboNormal, cartVelocity, INFLOW, config->GetKind_TurboMachinery(iZone));
8775 
8776  for (auto iPoint = 0u; iPoint < nPoint; iPoint++) {
8777  nodes->SetSolution(iPoint,0, Density_Inf);
8778  for (auto iDim = 0u; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
8779  nodes->SetSolution(iPoint,iDim+1, Density_Inf*cartVelocity[iDim]);
8780  }
8781  nodes->SetSolution(iPoint,nVar-1, Density_Inf*Energy_Inf);
8782 
8783  nodes->SetPrimVar(iPoint, GetFluidModel());
8784  nodes->SetSecondaryVar(iPoint, GetFluidModel());
8785  }
8786 }
8787 
8788 void CEulerSolver::PreprocessAverage(CSolver **solver, CGeometry *geometry, CConfig *config, unsigned short marker_flag) {
8789 
8790  const auto nSpanWiseSections = config->GetnSpanWiseSections();
8791  const auto iZone = config->GetiZone();
8792 
8793  for (auto iSpan= 0u; iSpan < nSpanWiseSections; iSpan++){
8794  su2double TotalAreaVelocity[MAXNDIM]={0.0},
8795  TotalAreaPressure{0},
8796  TotalAreaDensity{0};
8797  for (auto iMarker = 0u; iMarker < config->GetnMarker_All(); iMarker++){
8798  for (auto iMarkerTP=1; iMarkerTP < config->GetnMarker_Turbomachinery()+1; iMarkerTP++){
8799  if (config->GetMarker_All_Turbomachinery(iMarker) == iMarkerTP){
8800  if (config->GetMarker_All_TurbomachineryFlag(iMarker) == marker_flag){
8801 
8802  /*--- Retrieve Old Solution ---*/
8803 
8804  /*--- Loop over the vertices to sum all the quantities pithc-wise ---*/
8805  for (auto iVertex = 0u; iVertex < geometry->GetnVertexSpan(iMarker,iSpan); iVertex++) {
8806  auto iPoint = geometry->turbovertex[iMarker][iSpan][iVertex]->GetNode();
8807  if (geometry->nodes->GetDomain(iPoint)){
8808  /*--- Compute the integral fluxes for the boundaries ---*/
8809 
8810  auto Pressure = nodes->GetPressure(iPoint);
8811  auto Density = nodes->GetDensity(iPoint);
8812 
8813  su2double UnitNormal[MAXNDIM]={0},
8814  TurboNormal[MAXNDIM]={0},
8815  TurboVelocity[MAXNDIM],
8816  Area;
8817  /*--- Normal vector for this vertex (negate for outward convention) ---*/
8818  geometry->turbovertex[iMarker][iSpan][iVertex]->GetNormal(UnitNormal);
8819  geometry->turbovertex[iMarker][iSpan][iVertex]->GetTurboNormal(TurboNormal);
8820  Area = geometry->turbovertex[iMarker][iSpan][iVertex]->GetArea();
8821 
8822  su2double Velocity[MAXNDIM]={0};
8823  for (auto iDim=0u; iDim<nDim;iDim++) Velocity[iDim] = nodes->GetVelocity(iPoint, iDim);
8824 
8825  ComputeTurboVelocity(Velocity, TurboNormal , TurboVelocity, marker_flag, config->GetKind_TurboMachinery(iZone));
8826 
8827  /*--- Compute different integral quantities for the boundary of interest ---*/
8828 
8829  TotalAreaPressure += Area*Pressure;
8830  TotalAreaDensity += Area*Density;
8831  for (auto iDim = 0u; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
8832  TotalAreaVelocity[iDim] += Area*Velocity[iDim];
8833  }
8834  }
8835  }
8836  }
8837  } // iMarkerTP
8838  } // iMarker
8839 
8840 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
8841 
8842  /*--- Add information using all the nodes ---*/
8843 
8844  su2double MyTotalAreaDensity = TotalAreaDensity;
8845  su2double MyTotalAreaPressure = TotalAreaPressure;
8846 
8847  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(&MyTotalAreaDensity, &TotalAreaDensity, 1, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
8848  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(&MyTotalAreaPressure, &TotalAreaPressure, 1, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
8849 
8850  auto* MyTotalAreaVelocity = new su2double[nDim];
8851 
8852  for (auto iDim = 0u; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
8853  MyTotalAreaVelocity[iDim] = TotalAreaVelocity[iDim];
8854  }
8855 
8856  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(MyTotalAreaVelocity, TotalAreaVelocity, nDim, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
8857 
8858  delete [] MyTotalAreaVelocity;
8859 
8860 #endif
8861 
8862  /*--- initialize spanwise average quantities ---*/
8863 
8864 
8865  for (auto iMarker = 0u; iMarker < config->GetnMarker_All(); iMarker++){
8866  for (auto iMarkerTP=1; iMarkerTP < config->GetnMarker_Turbomachinery()+1; iMarkerTP++){
8867  if (config->GetMarker_All_Turbomachinery(iMarker) == iMarkerTP){
8868  if (config->GetMarker_All_TurbomachineryFlag(iMarker) == marker_flag){
8869 
8870  auto TotalArea = geometry->GetSpanArea(iMarker,iSpan);
8871  auto AverageTurboNormal = geometry->GetAverageTurboNormal(iMarker,iSpan);
8872 
8873  /*--- Compute the averaged value for the boundary of interest for the span of interest ---*/
8874 
8875  AverageDensity[iMarker][iSpan] = TotalAreaDensity / TotalArea;
8876  AveragePressure[iMarker][iSpan] = TotalAreaPressure / TotalArea;
8877  for (auto iDim = 0u; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
8878  AverageVelocity[iMarker][iSpan][iDim] = TotalAreaVelocity[iDim] / TotalArea;
8879 
8880  /* --- compute static averaged quantities ---*/
8881  ComputeTurboVelocity(AverageVelocity[iMarker][iSpan], AverageTurboNormal , AverageTurboVelocity[iMarker][iSpan], marker_flag, config->GetKind_TurboMachinery(iZone));
8882 
8883  OldAverageDensity[iMarker][iSpan] = AverageDensity[iMarker][iSpan];
8884  OldAveragePressure[iMarker][iSpan] = AveragePressure[iMarker][iSpan];
8885  for(auto iDim = 0u; iDim < nDim;iDim++)
8886  OldAverageTurboVelocity[iMarker][iSpan][iDim] = AverageTurboVelocity[iMarker][iSpan][iDim];
8887 
8888  }
8889  }
8890  } // iMarkerTP
8891  } // iMarker
8892  } // iSpan
8893 
8894  /*--- initialize 1D average quantities ---*/
8895 
8896  for (auto iMarker = 0u; iMarker < config->GetnMarker_All(); iMarker++){
8897  for (auto iMarkerTP=1; iMarkerTP < config->GetnMarker_Turbomachinery()+1; iMarkerTP++){
8898  if (config->GetMarker_All_Turbomachinery(iMarker) == iMarkerTP){
8899  if (config->GetMarker_All_TurbomachineryFlag(iMarker) == marker_flag){
8900 
8901  auto AverageTurboNormal = geometry->GetAverageTurboNormal(iMarker,nSpanWiseSections);
8902 
8903  /*--- Compute the averaged value for the boundary of interest for the span of interest ---*/
8904 
8905  AverageDensity[iMarker][nSpanWiseSections] = AverageDensity[iMarker][nSpanWiseSections/2];
8906  AveragePressure[iMarker][nSpanWiseSections] = AveragePressure[iMarker][nSpanWiseSections/2];
8907  for (auto iDim = 0u; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
8908  AverageVelocity[iMarker][nSpanWiseSections][iDim] = AverageVelocity[iMarker][nSpanWiseSections/2][iDim];
8909 
8910  /* --- compute static averaged quantities ---*/
8911  ComputeTurboVelocity(AverageVelocity[iMarker][nSpanWiseSections], AverageTurboNormal , AverageTurboVelocity[iMarker][nSpanWiseSections], marker_flag, config->GetKind_TurboMachinery(iZone));
8912 
8913  OldAverageDensity[iMarker][nSpanWiseSections] = AverageDensity[iMarker][nSpanWiseSections];
8914  OldAveragePressure[iMarker][nSpanWiseSections] = AveragePressure[iMarker][nSpanWiseSections];
8915  for(auto iDim = 0u; iDim < nDim;iDim++)
8916  OldAverageTurboVelocity[iMarker][nSpanWiseSections][iDim] = AverageTurboVelocity[iMarker][nSpanWiseSections][iDim];
8917 
8918  }
8919  }
8920  } // iMarkerTP
8921  } // iMarker
8922 }
8923 
8924 
8925 void CEulerSolver::TurboAverageProcess(CSolver **solver, CGeometry *geometry, CConfig *config, unsigned short marker_flag) {
8926 
8927  const auto average_process = config->GetKind_AverageProcess();
8928  const auto performance_average_process = config->GetKind_PerformanceAverageProcess();
8929  const auto iZone = config->GetiZone();
8930  const bool turbulent = (config->GetKind_Turb_Model() != TURB_MODEL::NONE);
8931  const bool spalart_allmaras = (config->GetKind_Turb_Model() == TURB_MODEL::SA);
8932  const bool menter_sst = (config->GetKind_Turb_Model() == TURB_MODEL::SST);
8933  const auto nSpanWiseSections = config->GetnSpanWiseSections();
8934 
8935  for (auto iSpan= 0; iSpan < nSpanWiseSections + 1; iSpan++){
8936  su2double TotalDensity{0}, TotalPressure{0}, TotalNu{0}, TotalOmega{0}, TotalKine{0}, TotalVelocity[MAXNDIM],
8937  TotalAreaDensity{0}, TotalAreaPressure{0}, TotalAreaNu{0}, TotalAreaOmega{0}, TotalAreaKine{0}, TotalAreaVelocity[MAXNDIM],
8938  TotalMassDensity{0}, TotalMassPressure{0}, TotalMassNu{0}, TotalMassOmega{0}, TotalMassKine{0}, TotalMassVelocity[MAXNDIM];
8939 
8940  su2double TotalFluxes[MAXNVAR];
8941  /*--- Forces initialization for contenitors ---*/
8942  for (auto iVar=0u;iVar<nVar;iVar++)
8943  TotalFluxes[iVar]= 0.0;
8944  for (auto iDim=0u; iDim<nDim; iDim++) {
8945  TotalVelocity[iDim] = 0.0;
8946  TotalAreaVelocity[iDim] = 0.0;
8947  TotalMassVelocity[iDim] = 0.0;
8948  }
8949 
8950  auto UpdateTotalQuantities = [&](const size_t iMarker, const size_t iSpan, const size_t iVertex){
8951  /*--- Increment integral quantities for averaging ---*/
8952 
8953  const auto iPoint = geometry->turbovertex[iMarker][iSpan][iVertex]->GetNode();
8954 
8955  /*--- Retrieve local quantities ---*/
8956  const auto Pressure = nodes->GetPressure(iPoint);
8957  const auto Density = nodes->GetDensity(iPoint);
8958  const auto Enthalpy = nodes->GetEnthalpy(iPoint);
8959 
8960  su2double Velocity[MAXNDIM] = {0}, UnitNormal[MAXNDIM] = {0}, TurboNormal[MAXNDIM] = {0}, TurboVelocity[MAXNDIM] = {0};
8961  geometry->turbovertex[iMarker][iSpan][iVertex]->GetNormal(UnitNormal);
8962  geometry->turbovertex[iMarker][iSpan][iVertex]->GetTurboNormal(TurboNormal);
8963  const auto Area = geometry->turbovertex[iMarker][iSpan][iVertex]->GetArea();
8964 
8965  for (auto iDim=0u; iDim < nDim; iDim++) Velocity[iDim] = nodes->GetVelocity(iPoint, iDim);
8966 
8967  ComputeTurboVelocity(Velocity, TurboNormal , TurboVelocity, marker_flag, config->GetKind_TurboMachinery(iZone));
8968 
8969  /*--- Compute different integral quantities for the boundary of interest ---*/
8970  TotalDensity += Density;
8971  TotalPressure += Pressure;
8972 
8973  TotalAreaPressure += Area*Pressure;
8974  TotalAreaDensity += Area*Density;
8975 
8976  TotalMassPressure += Area*(Density*TurboVelocity[0] )*Pressure;
8977  TotalMassDensity += Area*(Density*TurboVelocity[0] )*Density;
8978 
8979  for (auto iDim = 0u; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
8980  TotalVelocity[iDim] += Velocity[iDim];
8981  TotalAreaVelocity[iDim] += Area*Velocity[iDim];
8982  TotalMassVelocity[iDim] += Area*(Density*TurboVelocity[0] )*Velocity[iDim];
8983  }
8984 
8985  TotalFluxes[0] += Area*(Density*TurboVelocity[0]);
8986  TotalFluxes[1] += Area*(Density*TurboVelocity[0]*TurboVelocity[0] + Pressure);
8987  for (auto iDim = 2; iDim < nDim+1; iDim++)
8988  TotalFluxes[iDim] += Area*(Density*TurboVelocity[0]*TurboVelocity[iDim -1]);
8989  TotalFluxes[nDim+1] += Area*(Density*TurboVelocity[0]*Enthalpy);
8990 
8991  /*--- Compute turbulent integral quantities for the boundary of interest ---*/
8992 
8993  if(turbulent){
8994  su2double Kine{0}, Omega{0}, Nu{0};
8995  if(menter_sst){
8996  Kine = solver[TURB_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetSolution(iPoint,0);
8997  Omega = solver[TURB_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetSolution(iPoint,1);
8998  }
8999  if(spalart_allmaras){
9000  Nu = solver[TURB_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetSolution(iPoint,0);
9001  }
9002 
9003  TotalKine += Kine;
9004  TotalOmega += Omega;
9005  TotalNu += Nu;
9006 
9007  TotalAreaKine += Area*Kine;
9008  TotalAreaOmega += Area*Omega;
9009  TotalAreaNu += Area*Nu;
9010 
9011  TotalMassKine += Area*(Density*TurboVelocity[0] )*Kine;
9012  TotalMassOmega += Area*(Density*TurboVelocity[0] )*Omega;
9013  TotalMassNu += Area*(Density*TurboVelocity[0] )*Nu;
9014  }
9015  };
9016 
9017  for (auto iMarker = 0u; iMarker < config->GetnMarker_All(); iMarker++){
9018  for (auto iMarkerTP=1; iMarkerTP < config->GetnMarker_Turbomachinery()+1; iMarkerTP++){
9019  if (config->GetMarker_All_Turbomachinery(iMarker) == iMarkerTP){
9020  if (config->GetMarker_All_TurbomachineryFlag(iMarker) == marker_flag){
9021 
9022  /*--- Loop over the vertices to sum all the quantities pitch-wise ---*/
9023  if(iSpan < nSpanWiseSections){
9024  for (auto iVertex = 0ul; iVertex < geometry->GetnVertexSpan(iMarker,iSpan); iVertex++) {
9025  UpdateTotalQuantities(iMarker, iSpan, iVertex);
9026  }
9027  } else {
9028  for (auto jSpan= 0u; jSpan < nSpanWiseSections; jSpan++){
9029  for (auto iVertex = 0ul; iVertex < geometry->GetnVertexSpan(iMarker,jSpan); iVertex++) {
9030  UpdateTotalQuantities(iMarker, jSpan, iVertex);
9031  }
9032  }
9033  }
9034 
9035  } // marker_flag match
9036  } // iMarkerTP match
9037  } // iMarkerTP
9038  } // iMarker
9039 
9040 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
9041 
9042  /*--- Add information using all the nodes ---*/
9043 
9044  auto Allreduce = [](su2double x) {
9045  su2double tmp = x; x = 0.0;
9046  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(&tmp, &x, 1, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
9047  return x;
9048  };
9049 
9050  TotalDensity = Allreduce(TotalDensity);
9051  TotalPressure = Allreduce(TotalPressure);
9052  TotalAreaDensity = Allreduce(TotalAreaDensity);
9053  TotalAreaPressure = Allreduce(TotalAreaPressure);
9054  TotalMassDensity = Allreduce(TotalMassDensity);
9055  TotalMassPressure = Allreduce(TotalMassPressure);
9056 
9057  TotalNu = Allreduce(TotalNu);
9058  TotalKine = Allreduce(TotalKine);
9059  TotalOmega = Allreduce(TotalOmega);
9060  TotalAreaNu = Allreduce(TotalAreaNu);
9061  TotalAreaKine = Allreduce(TotalAreaKine);
9062  TotalAreaOmega = Allreduce(TotalAreaOmega);
9063 
9064  TotalMassNu = Allreduce(TotalMassNu);
9065  TotalMassKine = Allreduce(TotalMassKine);
9066  TotalMassOmega = Allreduce(TotalMassOmega);
9067 
9068  auto* buffer = new su2double[max(nVar,nDim)];
9069 
9070  auto Allreduce_inplace = [buffer](int size, su2double* x) {
9071  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(x, buffer, size, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
9072  for(int i=0; i<size; ++i) x[i] = buffer[i];
9073  };
9074 
9075  Allreduce_inplace(nVar, TotalFluxes);
9076  Allreduce_inplace(nDim, TotalVelocity);
9077  Allreduce_inplace(nDim, TotalAreaVelocity);
9078  Allreduce_inplace(nDim, TotalMassVelocity);
9079 
9080  delete [] buffer;
9081 
9082 #endif
9083 
9084  /*--- Compute pitch-wise averaged quantities ---*/
9085  for (auto iMarker = 0u; iMarker < config->GetnMarker_All(); iMarker++){
9086  for (auto iMarkerTP=1; iMarkerTP < config->GetnMarker_Turbomachinery()+1; iMarkerTP++){
9087  if (config->GetMarker_All_Turbomachinery(iMarker) == iMarkerTP){
9088  if (config->GetMarker_All_TurbomachineryFlag(iMarker) == marker_flag){
9089 
9090  const auto TotalArea = geometry->GetSpanArea(iMarker,iSpan);
9091  const auto AverageTurboNormal = geometry->GetAverageTurboNormal(iMarker,iSpan);
9092  const auto nVert = geometry->GetnTotVertexSpan(iMarker,iSpan);
9093 
9094  /*--- compute normal Mach number as a check for massflow average and mixedout average ---*/
9095  GetFluidModel()->SetTDState_Prho(TotalAreaPressure/TotalArea, TotalAreaDensity / TotalArea);
9096  const su2double soundSpeed = GetFluidModel()->GetSoundSpeed(),
9097  MachTest = TotalFluxes[0]/(TotalAreaDensity*soundSpeed);
9098 
9099  /*--- Compute the averaged value for the boundary of interest for the span of interest ---*/
9100 
9101  const bool belowMachLimit = (abs(MachTest)< config->GetAverageMachLimit());
9102  su2double avgDensity{0}, avgPressure{0}, avgKine{0}, avgOmega{0}, avgNu{0}, avgVelocity[MAXNDIM] = {0};
9103  for (auto iVar = 0u; iVar<nVar; iVar++){
9104  AverageFlux[iMarker][iSpan][iVar] = TotalFluxes[iVar]/TotalArea;
9105  SpanTotalFlux[iMarker][iSpan][iVar] = TotalFluxes[iVar];
9106  }
9107 
9108  switch (average_process)
9109  {
9110  case ALGEBRAIC:
9111  /*--- compute algebraic average ---*/
9112  avgDensity = TotalDensity / nVert;
9113  avgPressure = TotalPressure / nVert;
9114  for (auto iDim = 0u; iDim < nDim; iDim++) avgVelocity[iDim] = TotalVelocity[iDim] / nVert;
9115  if (turbulent) {
9116  avgKine = TotalKine/nVert;
9117  avgOmega = TotalOmega/nVert;
9118  avgNu = TotalNu/nVert;
9119  }
9120  break;
9121  case AREA:
9122  /*--- compute area average ---*/
9123  avgDensity = TotalAreaDensity / TotalArea;
9124  avgPressure = TotalAreaPressure / TotalArea;
9125  for (auto iDim = 0u; iDim < nDim; iDim++) avgVelocity[iDim] = TotalAreaVelocity[iDim] / TotalArea;
9126  if (turbulent) {
9127  avgKine = TotalAreaKine / TotalArea;
9128  avgOmega = TotalAreaOmega / TotalArea;
9129  avgNu = TotalAreaNu / TotalArea;
9130  }
9131  break;
9132  case MASSFLUX:
9133  /*--- compute mass-flux average ---*/
9134  if (belowMachLimit) {
9135  avgDensity = TotalAreaDensity / TotalArea;
9136  avgPressure = TotalAreaPressure / TotalArea;
9137  for (auto iDim = 0u; iDim < nDim; iDim++) avgVelocity[iDim] = TotalAreaVelocity[iDim] / TotalArea;
9138  if (turbulent) {
9139  avgKine = TotalAreaKine / TotalArea;
9140  avgOmega = TotalAreaOmega / TotalArea;
9141  avgNu = TotalAreaNu / TotalArea;
9142  }
9143  } else {
9144  avgDensity = TotalMassDensity / TotalFluxes[0];
9145  avgPressure = TotalMassPressure / TotalFluxes[0];
9146  for (auto iDim = 0u; iDim < nDim; iDim++) avgVelocity[iDim] = TotalMassVelocity[iDim] / TotalFluxes[0];
9147  if (turbulent) {
9148  avgKine = TotalMassKine / TotalFluxes[0];
9149  avgOmega = TotalMassOmega / TotalFluxes[0];
9150  avgNu = TotalMassNu / TotalFluxes[0];
9151  }
9152  }
9153  break;
9154  case MIXEDOUT:
9155  /*--- compute mixed-out average ---*/
9156  avgDensity = TotalAreaDensity / TotalArea;
9157  avgPressure = TotalAreaPressure / TotalArea;
9158  if (belowMachLimit) {
9159  for (auto iDim = 0u; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
9160  avgVelocity[iDim] = TotalAreaVelocity[iDim] / TotalArea;
9161  if (turbulent) {
9162  avgKine = TotalAreaKine / TotalArea;
9163  avgOmega = TotalAreaOmega / TotalArea;
9164  avgNu = TotalAreaNu / TotalArea;
9165  }
9166  }else {
9167  auto val_init_pressure = OldAveragePressure[iMarker][iSpan];
9168  MixedOut_Average (config, val_init_pressure, AverageFlux[iMarker][iSpan], AverageTurboNormal, avgPressure, avgDensity);
9169  avgVelocity[0] = ( AverageFlux[iMarker][iSpan][1] - avgPressure) / AverageFlux[iMarker][iSpan][0];
9170  for (auto iDim = 2; iDim < nDim +1;iDim++)
9171  avgVelocity[iDim-1] = AverageFlux[iMarker][iSpan][iDim] / AverageFlux[iMarker][iSpan][0];
9172 
9173  if (isnan(avgDensity) || isnan(avgPressure) || avgPressure < 0.0 || avgDensity < 0.0 ){
9174  val_init_pressure = TotalAreaPressure / TotalArea;
9175  MixedOut_Average (config, val_init_pressure, AverageFlux[iMarker][iSpan], AverageTurboNormal, avgPressure, avgDensity);
9176  avgVelocity[0] = ( AverageFlux[iMarker][iSpan][1] - avgPressure) / AverageFlux[iMarker][iSpan][0];
9177  for (auto iDim = 2; iDim < nDim +1;iDim++)
9178  avgVelocity[iDim-1] = AverageFlux[iMarker][iSpan][iDim] / AverageFlux[iMarker][iSpan][0];
9179  }
9180  if (turbulent) {
9181  avgKine = TotalMassKine / TotalFluxes[0];
9182  avgOmega = TotalMassOmega / TotalFluxes[0];
9183  avgNu = TotalMassNu / TotalFluxes[0];
9184  }
9185  }
9186 
9187  if (iSpan == nSpanWiseSections){
9188  AverageMassFlowRate[iMarker] = TotalFluxes[0];
9189  }
9190 
9191  break;
9192  default:
9193  SU2_MPI::Error(" Invalid AVERAGE PROCESS input!", CURRENT_FUNCTION);
9194  break;
9195  }
9196  AverageDensity[iMarker][iSpan] = avgDensity;
9197  AveragePressure[iMarker][iSpan] = avgPressure;
9198  if ((average_process == MIXEDOUT) && !belowMachLimit) {
9199  for (auto iDim = 0u; iDim < nDim; iDim++) AverageTurboVelocity[iMarker][iSpan][iDim] = avgVelocity[iDim];
9200  } else {
9201  ComputeTurboVelocity(avgVelocity, AverageTurboNormal , AverageTurboVelocity[iMarker][iSpan], marker_flag, config->GetKind_TurboMachinery(iZone));
9202  }
9203  if (turbulent) {
9204  AverageKine[iMarker][iSpan] = avgKine;
9205  AverageOmega[iMarker][iSpan] = avgOmega;
9206  AverageNu[iMarker][iSpan] = avgNu;
9207  }
9208 
9209  /* --- check if averaged quantities are correct otherwise reset the old quantities ---*/
9210  const bool nanSolution = (isnan(AverageDensity[iMarker][iSpan]) || isnan(AveragePressure[iMarker][iSpan]));
9211  const bool negSolution = (AverageDensity[iMarker][iSpan] < 0.0 || AveragePressure[iMarker][iSpan] < 0.0);
9212  if (nanSolution || negSolution){
9213  if (nanSolution)
9214  cout<<"nan in mixing process routine for iSpan: " << iSpan<< " in marker " << config->GetMarker_All_TagBound(iMarker)<< endl;
9215  else
9216  cout << " negative density or pressure in mixing process routine for iSpan: " << iSpan<< " in marker " << config->GetMarker_All_TagBound(iMarker)<< endl;
9217  AverageDensity[iMarker][iSpan] = OldAverageDensity[iMarker][iSpan];
9218  AveragePressure[iMarker][iSpan] = OldAveragePressure[iMarker][iSpan];
9219  for(auto iDim = 0u; iDim < nDim;iDim++)
9220  AverageTurboVelocity[iMarker][iSpan][iDim] = OldAverageTurboVelocity[iMarker][iSpan][iDim];
9221  } else {
9222  /* --- update old average solution ---*/
9223  OldAverageDensity[iMarker][iSpan] = AverageDensity[iMarker][iSpan];
9224  OldAveragePressure[iMarker][iSpan] = AveragePressure[iMarker][iSpan];
9225  for(auto iDim = 0u; iDim < nDim;iDim++)
9226  OldAverageTurboVelocity[iMarker][iSpan][iDim] = AverageTurboVelocity[iMarker][iSpan][iDim];
9227  }
9228 
9229  /*--- to avoid back flow ---*/
9230  if (AverageTurboVelocity[iMarker][iSpan][0] < 0.0){
9231  AverageTurboVelocity[iMarker][iSpan][0] = soundSpeed*config->GetAverageMachLimit();
9232  }
9233 
9234  /*--- compute cartesian average Velocity ---*/
9235  ComputeBackVelocity(AverageTurboVelocity[iMarker][iSpan], AverageTurboNormal , AverageVelocity[iMarker][iSpan], marker_flag, config->GetKind_TurboMachinery(iZone));
9236 
9237  /*--- Store averaged performance value for the selected average method ---*/
9238  if (marker_flag == INFLOW) {
9239  DensityIn[iMarkerTP - 1][iSpan] = AverageDensity[iMarker][iSpan];
9240  PressureIn[iMarkerTP - 1][iSpan] = AveragePressure[iMarker][iSpan];
9241  KineIn[iMarkerTP - 1][iSpan] = AverageKine[iMarker][iSpan];
9242  OmegaIn[iMarkerTP - 1][iSpan] = AverageOmega[iMarker][iSpan];
9243  NuIn[iMarkerTP - 1][iSpan] = AverageNu[iMarker][iSpan];
9244  } else {
9245  DensityOut[iMarkerTP - 1][iSpan] = AverageDensity[iMarker][iSpan];
9246  PressureOut[iMarkerTP - 1][iSpan] = AveragePressure[iMarker][iSpan];
9247  KineOut[iMarkerTP - 1][iSpan] = AverageKine[iMarker][iSpan];
9248  OmegaOut[iMarkerTP - 1][iSpan] = AverageOmega[iMarker][iSpan];
9249  NuOut[iMarkerTP - 1][iSpan] = AverageNu[iMarker][iSpan];
9250  }
9251 
9252  auto TurboVel = (marker_flag == INFLOW) ? TurboVelocityIn[iMarkerTP - 1][iSpan] : TurboVelocityOut[iMarkerTP - 1][iSpan];
9253 
9254  if (performance_average_process == MIXEDOUT) {
9255  for (auto iDim = 0u; iDim < nDim; iDim++) TurboVel[iDim] = avgVelocity[iDim];
9256  } else {
9257  ComputeTurboVelocity(avgVelocity, AverageTurboNormal , TurboVel, marker_flag, config->GetKind_TurboMachinery(iZone));
9258  }
9259  }
9260  }
9261  } // iMarkerTP
9262  } // iMarker
9263  } // iSpan
9264 
9265  /*--- Compute Outlet Static Pressure if Radial equilibrium is imposed ---*/
9266 
9267  for (auto iMarker = 0u; iMarker < config->GetnMarker_All(); iMarker++){
9268  for (auto iMarkerTP=1; iMarkerTP < config->GetnMarker_Turbomachinery()+1; iMarkerTP++){
9269  if (config->GetMarker_All_Turbomachinery(iMarker) == iMarkerTP){
9270  if (config->GetMarker_All_TurbomachineryFlag(iMarker) == marker_flag){
9271  auto Marker_Tag = config->GetMarker_All_TagBound(iMarker);
9272  if(config->GetMarker_All_Giles(iMarker) || config->GetBoolRiemann()){ // May have to implement something similar for Riemann?
9273  if(config->GetBoolRiemann()){
9274  if(config->GetKind_Data_Riemann(Marker_Tag) == RADIAL_EQUILIBRIUM){
9275  RadialEquilibriumPressure[iMarker][nSpanWiseSections/2] = config->GetRiemann_Var1(Marker_Tag)/config->GetPressure_Ref();
9276  }
9277  } else {
9278  if(config->GetKind_Data_Giles(Marker_Tag) == RADIAL_EQUILIBRIUM){
9279  RadialEquilibriumPressure[iMarker][nSpanWiseSections/2] = config->GetGiles_Var1(Marker_Tag)/config->GetPressure_Ref();
9280  }
9281  }
9282  for (auto iSpan= nSpanWiseSections/2; iSpan < nSpanWiseSections-1; iSpan++){
9283  const auto Radius2 = geometry->GetTurboRadius(iMarker,iSpan+1);
9284  const auto Radius1 = geometry->GetTurboRadius(iMarker,iSpan);
9285  const su2double Vt2 = AverageTurboVelocity[iMarker][iSpan +1][1]*AverageTurboVelocity[iMarker][iSpan +1][1];
9286  RadialEquilibriumPressure[iMarker][iSpan +1] = RadialEquilibriumPressure[iMarker][iSpan] + AverageDensity[iMarker][iSpan +1]*Vt2/Radius2*(Radius2 - Radius1);
9287  }
9288  for (auto iSpan= nSpanWiseSections/2; iSpan > 0; iSpan--){
9289  const su2double Radius2 = geometry->GetTurboRadius(iMarker,iSpan);
9290  su2double Radius1 = geometry->GetTurboRadius(iMarker,iSpan-1);
9291  const su2double Vt2 = AverageTurboVelocity[iMarker][iSpan -1][1]*AverageTurboVelocity[iMarker][iSpan - 1][1];
9292  Radius1 = (Radius1 > EPS)? Radius1 : Radius2;
9293  RadialEquilibriumPressure[iMarker][iSpan -1] = RadialEquilibriumPressure[iMarker][iSpan] - AverageDensity[iMarker][iSpan -1]*Vt2/Radius1*(Radius2 - Radius1);
9294  }
9295  } // Giles or Riemann
9296  } // marker_flag
9297  } // iMarkerTP
9298  } // iMarker is iMarkerTP
9299  } // iMarker
9300 }
9301 
9302 void CEulerSolver::MixedOut_Average(CConfig *config, su2double val_init_pressure, const su2double *val_Averaged_Flux,
9303  const su2double *val_normal, su2double& pressure_mix, su2double& density_mix) {
9304 
9305  const auto relax_factor = config->GetMixedout_Coeff(0);
9306  const auto toll = config->GetMixedout_Coeff(1);
9307  unsigned short maxiter = SU2_TYPE::Int(config->GetMixedout_Coeff(2));
9308 
9309  pressure_mix = val_init_pressure;
9310 
9311  /*--- Newton-Raphson's method with central difference formula ---*/
9312  unsigned short iter{0};
9313  while ( iter <= maxiter ) {
9314 
9315  const su2double density_mix = val_Averaged_Flux[0]*val_Averaged_Flux[0]/(val_Averaged_Flux[1] - pressure_mix);
9316  GetFluidModel()->SetTDState_Prho(pressure_mix, density_mix);
9317  const su2double enthalpy_mix = GetFluidModel()->GetStaticEnergy() + (pressure_mix)/(density_mix);
9318 
9319  GetFluidModel()->ComputeDerivativeNRBC_Prho(pressure_mix, density_mix);
9320  const su2double dhdP = GetFluidModel()->GetdhdP_rho();
9321  const su2double dhdrho = GetFluidModel()->Getdhdrho_P();
9322 
9323  su2double vel[MAXNDIM] = {0};
9324  vel[0] = (val_Averaged_Flux[1] - pressure_mix) / val_Averaged_Flux[0];
9325  for (auto iDim = 1u; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
9326  vel[iDim] = val_Averaged_Flux[iDim+1] / val_Averaged_Flux[0];
9327 
9328 
9329  const su2double velsq = GeometryToolbox::DotProduct(nDim, vel, vel);
9330 
9331  const su2double f = val_Averaged_Flux[nDim+1] - val_Averaged_Flux[0]*(enthalpy_mix + velsq/2);
9332  const su2double df = -val_Averaged_Flux[0]*(dhdP - 1/density_mix) - dhdrho*density_mix*density_mix/val_Averaged_Flux[0];
9333  const su2double dx = -f/df;
9334  const su2double resdl = dx/val_init_pressure;
9335  pressure_mix += relax_factor*dx;
9336 
9337  iter += 1;
9338  if ( abs(resdl) <= toll ) {
9339  break;
9340  }
9341 
9342  }
9343  density_mix = val_Averaged_Flux[0]*val_Averaged_Flux[0]/(val_Averaged_Flux[1] - pressure_mix);
9344 
9345 }
